NK071(du)001:1: // ma ni ka d+ai pa sh+r+ai gu h+ya ga r+b+ha
NK071(du)001:2: bi k+ai r+na na ma bi ha ra ti sma
NK071(du)001:5: // // dpal gsang ba snying po'i rgyud kyi mchan 'grel nor bu'i sgron me zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:8: srid gzhi'i dpal gyur kun la khyab cing rtag par sman mdzad kun tu bzang //
NK071(du)001:9: mi phyed ye shes brtan bsdus rtogs pa'i rnam par yongs shar rdo rje sems //
NK071(du)001:10: bden gnyis dbyer med gang 'dul der snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sprul pa'i gar //
NK071(du)001:11: sku gsum rigs 'dus bla ma'i zhabs rdul snying dbus dwangs mar rtag tu mchod //
NK071(du)001:12: gang gi gsang ba 'gog bden rtag pa'i dbyangs //
NK071(du)001:13: lam bden ming tshig yi ge'i sprin phung can //
NK071(du)001:14: chos tshul rgya mtsho'i snying po zla med pa'i //
NK071(du)001:15: rgyud don 'bru gnyer sgo nas cung zad dbye //
NK071(du)001:16: de la 'phags yul nub phyogs kyi pan+ti ta lnga
NK071(du)001:17: brgya'i gtsug rgyan bi ma la mi tra'i zhal snga
NK071(du)001:18: nas / rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye /
NK071(du)001:20: zhes pa'i rjes su 'brang te 'chad pa la /
NK071(du)001:21: dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:22: 'bring la spyi don rnam par dbye ba /
NK071(du)001:23: tha ma 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas bshad par
NK071(du)001:24: gsung pa'i dang po gnyis spyi don rnams las gsal
NK071(du)001:25: / rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas spros te bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:26: rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:27: mtshan de dang ldan pa'i rgyud don dngos so //
NK071(du)001:30: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid rgyal ba kun gyi thugs
NK071(du)001:31: kyi ngo bo zab cing brtag par bka' bas gsang
NK071(du)001:32: ba'i de nyid chos thams cad kyi 'phro ba'i gzhi
NK071(du)001:33: dang / mthar thug gi don dang /
NK071(du)001:34: chos thams cad kyi dbus su gnas pa na snying po rgyu 'bras ro gcig tu gyur pas /
NK071(du)001:35: de kho na nyid drang nges gnyis kyi zlas phye
NK071(du)001:36: bas nges pa'i don 'ba' zhig yin pas na nges
NK071(du)001:38: klad kyi don ston pa la phyag 'tshal ba /
NK071(du)001:39: gzhung gi don rgyud don dngos bshad pa /
NK071(du)001:40: mjug gi don rgyud don rdzogs pa'i bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:43: bcom pas spangs pa phun tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:44: dbang phyug sogs che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)001:45: ldan pas rtogs pa phun tshogs /
NK071(du)001:47: rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK071(du)001:48: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal dang ldan pa /
NK071(du)001:49: chos kun gyi rang bzhin yongs su dag pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:50: kun tu bzang po de la rgyud kyi sdud pa pos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK071(du)001:51: gnyis pa rgyud don dngos bshad pa la /
NK071(du)001:52: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis su gnas pa las /
NK071(du)001:54: sa bcad kyi sgo nas mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:55: rgyud rang gi 'bru gnyer ba'i sgo nas rgyas pa bshad pa /
NK071(du)001:56: spyi don gyi skabs dang sbyar nas don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)001:61: rgyud gleng gzhi'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa /
NK071(du)001:78: dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK071(du)001:79: gnyis pa ston pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK071(du)001:82: dbu gsum dang ldan pa zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK071(du)001:83: bzhi pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:91: lnga pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:93: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor ro //
NK071(du)001:95: rigs kyi yab lnga dang yum lnga'o //
NK071(du)001:97: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa nas tshor ba zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:100: khyab par bzhugs so zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:101: gnyis pa rigs khyad par can gyi 'khor la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:109: gnyis pa ni byang chub chen po sogs /
NK071(du)001:110: gnyis pa 'joms byed khro bo'i 'khor ni /
NK071(du)001:112: gnyis pa bsdu ba la gsum /
NK071(du)001:113: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:115: bka' gsang mtshon byed kyi tshig go /
NK071(du)001:117: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa zhes sogs /
NK071(du)001:119: e e ma e ma'o sogs /
NK071(du)001:124: gnyis pa sa bcad de dang 'grel ba'i rgyud rang
NK071(du)001:125: gi 'bru gnyer ba'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa
NK071(du)001:126: ni / 'di zhes es mtshon pa'i gnas skad ces
NK071(du)001:127: wam yig gi mtshon pa'i ston pa bshad ces pa
NK071(du)001:128: ma yig gis mtshon pa'i 'khor pa'i zhes pa ya
NK071(du)001:129: yig gis mtshon pa'i bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:130: dus na zhes pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK071(du)001:131: gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral ba mthar thug pas gzhi ji ltar ba de bzhin du gshegs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:132: de yang rang byung gi ye shes la spang bya ma grub pas /
NK071(du)001:133: yang dag par 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su rdzogs par rang snang pa'i bdag nyid ni /
NK071(du)001:134: sangs rgyas bdud bzhi bcom zhing /
NK071(du)001:135: sku lnga sogs yon tan dang ldan la /
NK071(du)001:137: chos kun la rdzogs par longs spyod cing /
NK071(du)001:138: gzhan las 'phags pas na chen po steng 'og phyogs mtshams brgyad do //
NK071(du)001:139: phyogs bcu dang 'das ma 'ong da lta ma nges te /
NK071(du)001:140: dus bzhi'i dbyings na bzhugs shing 'gro don mdzad pa'i
NK071(du)001:141: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi che ba'i yon
NK071(du)001:142: tan gyi rten byed pas sku dang gdul bya'i bsam
NK071(du)001:143: pa mthun pa'i chos ston pa'i /
NK071(du)001:144: gsung dang shes bya ma lus par mkhyen pa'i thugs dang /
NK071(du)001:145: de rnams dbyer mi phyed pa 'dus ma byas pa /
NK071(du)001:147: sngar 'das pa'i 'khor 'das ma lus pa dang /
NK071(du)001:148: da ltar ba'i mi lus pa ma 'ongs pa'i 'khor 'das lus pa med pa thams cad dang /
NK071(du)001:149: rgyud kyi bdag po kun rdzob tu sgyu ma'i snang
NK071(du)001:150: brnyan yin pas so so ma yin don dam par
NK071(du)001:151: ma skyes pas / tha mi dad bden pa gnyis
NK071(du)001:152: ka'i tha snyad las 'das pas dbyer med rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:153: ma skyes pas / te / 'og min rnams las
NK071(du)001:154: 'dir 'og min chen po zhes bya ba longs spyod
NK071(du)001:155: rdzogs sku'i sangs rgyas kyi bzhugs gnas gtsang ma'i gnas
NK071(du)001:156: las spags pa chos dbyings rnam par dag pa yin
NK071(du)001:157: pas mtha' dang dbus la sogs pa gang yang ris
NK071(du)001:158: su chad pa med pas nam mkha' ltar bsam gyis
NK071(du)001:159: mi khyab pa de lta bu'i gnas na 'og gzhi'i
NK071(du)001:160: tshad dmigs su med pa'i rang bzhin ye shes lnga
NK071(du)001:162: rnam pa 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas ma 'dres par gsal ba'i steng la /
NK071(du)001:163: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog rang snang bas
NK071(du)001:164: 'dul bya'i re ba skong ba'i rtags su rin po
NK071(du)001:165: che 'od 'bar ba las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang
NK071(du)001:166: chen po / chos kyi dbyings la rgya tshad med
NK071(du)001:167: pa'i rtags su gzhal yas khang gi tshad phyogs bcur
NK071(du)001:168: thams cad du rgya yongs su ma chad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:169: rang byung gi ye shes la 'bras bu che ba'i
NK071(du)001:170: yon tan dpag tu med par rgyas pa'i phyir de'i
NK071(du)001:171: rtags kyi phyag rgya dbyibs gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK071(du)001:172: ye shes re re la yang lhag pa'i ye shes /
NK071(du)001:173: bzhi bzhi dang ldan pas re ba skong ba'i rtags
NK071(du)001:174: su gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba'i rin po che'i
NK071(du)001:175: glo 'bur rigs bzhi'i kha dog can gyis mdzes pa
NK071(du)001:176: de'i rtse mor bum pa zlum po'i rnam par 'khyil
NK071(du)001:177: ba ni thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid phyogs
NK071(du)001:178: bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kun gyi dkyil 'khor ma
NK071(du)001:179: lus pa thams cad rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:180: rang bzhin so so ma yin zhing ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)001:181: gcig pa'i ye shes spros pa kun dang bral ba'i
NK071(du)001:182: klong tu 'khyil ba mtshon pa'i rtags so //
NK071(du)001:183: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal ma 'gags
NK071(du)001:184: pa las ye shes lnga la sogs pa'i bye brag
NK071(du)001:185: bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' ba'i rtags su ye
NK071(du)001:186: shes rang snang ba'i rgyan rin po che las grub
NK071(du)001:187: pa'i dbyibs dang kha dog la sogs pa rnam pa
NK071(du)001:188: tha dad pa'i bye brag tshad med pa dang ldan
NK071(du)001:189: pas gzhal yas khang gzhan las khyad par du gyur
NK071(du)001:190: pa'i bkod pa phun sum tshogs pas rgyan pa /
NK071(du)001:191: theg pa dang sa lam gzhan las 'di nyid 'phags
NK071(du)001:192: pa'i rtags su sgo dang khyams sogs nas lte ba'i
NK071(du)001:193: bar rdo rje 'greng bu res rim par spags pa
NK071(du)001:194: / chos kyi dbyings mu mtha' med pa'i rtags su mtho dam'i tshad 'di zhes dpag tu med pa /
NK071(du)001:195: ye shes kyi rtsal snang las grub pa'i rgyan gyi
NK071(du)001:196: khyad par yang rin po che sna tshogs kyi thugs
NK071(du)001:197: rje dang phrin las rgyun mi chad pa'i rtags su
NK071(du)001:198: phreng ba dang / bden gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa'i rtags su chun 'phyang dang /
NK071(du)001:199: thabs sna tshogs ma 'dres yongs rdzogs rtags su shar bu'i rgyan dang /
NK071(du)001:200: 'dod yon thams cad ma spangs rnam dag rol pa'i
NK071(du)001:201: rgyan du shar ba'i rtags su yid du 'ong ba'i
NK071(du)001:206: reg bya sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:207: de dag thogs pa'i rdo rje'i lha mo rnams kyis
NK071(du)001:208: phyogs bcur sprin phung ltar 'khrigs par ni 'bad rtsol
NK071(du)001:209: med par rang byung la de dag thams cad kyang
NK071(du)001:210: phan tshun gcig gis gcig mi sgrib par phyi nang
NK071(du)001:211: zang thal du gsal ba'i rgyan gyi bye brag bsam
NK071(du)001:212: gyis mi khyab pa'i bkod pas mdzes par brgyan cing
NK071(du)001:213: klubs pa dngos po dang mtshan 'dzin gyi sgrib pa
NK071(du)001:214: las rnam par thar pa'i sgo thun mong pa gsum
NK071(du)001:215: dang / thun mong ma yin pa rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal ba ste /
NK071(du)001:216: bzhi'i sgo nas byang chub chen por lhun gyis 'jug
NK071(du)001:217: pa'i rtags su sgo bzhi sgo khyud kyi zlas drangs
NK071(du)001:218: pa'i 'gram log dang ya phub can gyis phyogs bzhir
NK071(du)001:220: rnam par thar pa thegs pa brgyad bgrod nas 'jug
NK071(du)001:221: pa'i rtags su sgo phud kyi phyi nang gnyis ka
NK071(du)001:222: them skas bzhi bzhi ste bab zhon gyi rta bab
NK071(du)001:223: brgyad dang ldan pa gzhal yas khang de'i phyi dang
NK071(du)001:224: nang med pa thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:225: kyi rtsal snang 'ba' zhig tu gyur pa'i phyir kun
NK071(du)001:226: tu yang nang du gyur pa na rgyal ba'i thugs
NK071(du)001:227: la mi 'jigs pa bzhi lhun gyis grub pa'i mtshon
NK071(du)001:228: byed du dbus su seng ge'i khri dang /
NK071(du)001:229: sku stobs bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su shar du stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK071(du)001:230: gdul bya rnams myur du sgrol zhing yon tan rdzu
NK071(du)001:231: 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags su
NK071(du)001:233: las nyon ma spangs par dbang du byed cing gsung
NK071(du)001:234: dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su nub tu rma
NK071(du)001:235: bya'i khri dang / phrin las 'gro ba sgrol ba la chags pa dang /
NK071(du)001:236: thog pa med pa'i rtags su byang du nam mkha' lding ste shang shang gi khri dang /
NK071(du)001:237: thugs rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas 'od gsal
NK071(du)001:238: ba dang thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i rtags su
NK071(du)001:240: nyes pa'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa'i rtags su pad+ma dang /
NK071(du)001:241: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i rtags
NK071(du)001:242: su rin po che'i gdan la ston pa ni ye
NK071(du)001:243: shes kyi sku can yin pa'i phyir de'i sku la
NK071(du)001:244: mdun dang rgyab kho nar ris su chad pa med
NK071(du)001:245: pas phyogs thams cad du sgrib par med par zhal
NK071(du)001:246: gyi dkyil 'khor thal le bar gsal ba ste kun
NK071(du)001:247: tu zhal gyi rang bzhin du bzhugs shing skyes bu
NK071(du)001:248: chen po'i mtshan dang dpe byad bzang po gsal zhing
NK071(du)001:249: so sor 'byed pa dang ldan pas sku la rnam
NK071(du)001:250: par spras pa / de lta bu'i sku las mi
NK071(du)001:251: g.yo ba bzhin du zhing khams bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)001:252: pa thams cad du gang la gang 'dul gyi sku'i
NK071(du)001:253: par spras pa / bkod pa dang / sgra skad
NK071(du)001:254: mtha' yas par theg pa ma lus par ston pa'i
NK071(du)001:255: gsung dang spangs rtogs yon tan ye shes kyi khyab
NK071(du)001:256: pa'i thugs dang gdul bya'i snang ba dang mthun pa'i
NK071(du)001:257: rnam 'phrul sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK071(du)001:258: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa
NK071(du)001:259: nyid kyi ye shes kyis mtha' gnyis la mi gnas
NK071(du)001:260: pa'i brdar zhabs gnyis yab mnyam pa'i skyil krung dang
NK071(du)001:261: / yum brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung du mtshungs par bzhugs nas snyoms par 'jug pa dang /
NK071(du)001:262: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug
NK071(du)001:263: gi don mtshon byed phyag drug dang ye shes de
NK071(du)001:264: dag gi gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong
NK071(du)001:265: ba'i rtags su rin po che las grub pa'i rigs
NK071(du)001:266: lnga ye shes lnga dang chos dbyings kyi phyag rgya
NK071(du)001:267: rdo rje la sogs pa'i 'od 'bar ba can 'dzin
NK071(du)001:268: pa / sku stong pa nyid dang /
NK071(du)001:269: gsung mtshan ma med pa dang thugs smon pa med
NK071(du)001:270: pa gsum ni blo'i yul las 'das pas bsam gyis
NK071(du)001:271: mi khyab pa'i bdag nyid yin la de'i rtags su
NK071(du)001:273: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa yul rnam par
NK071(du)001:274: rig pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs brgyad po'i rnam
NK071(du)001:275: par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK071(du)001:276: de yang rigs lnga ka'i mtshan la rgyal po zhes
NK071(du)001:277: smos pa ni dper rgyal po rnams rang gi rgyal
NK071(du)001:278: srid la dbang bsgyur ba bzhin du /
NK071(du)001:279: thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs tshogs dbang bsgyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:280: de bzhin gshegs pa gzugs su rung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi rgyu'i gzugs bzhi /
NK071(du)001:281: 'bras bu'i gzugs bcu gcig ste bco lnga'i gzugs kyi rgyal po dang /
NK071(du)001:282: de bzhin gshegs pa nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid
NK071(du)001:283: can gyi bde sdug btang snyoms pa'i tshor ba'i rgyal
NK071(du)001:284: po dang / de bzhin gshegs pa mtshan mar 'dzin
NK071(du)001:285: pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi 'du shes kyi rgyal po
NK071(du)001:286: po dang / dang / de bzhin gshegs pa mngon
NK071(du)001:287: par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems pa
NK071(du)001:288: po dang / dang / ste / kun 'gro lnga sogs 'du byed kyi rgyal po dang /
NK071(du)001:289: de dag kun gyi rigs kyi mtshan mar gyur pa'i kha dog kyang rdo rje rigs mthing kha dang /
NK071(du)001:290: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dkar po dang /
NK071(du)001:291: rin chen rigs ser po dang /
NK071(du)001:292: pad+ma'i rigs le brgan te dmar po dang /
NK071(du)001:293: las kyi rigs ljang gu ste thams cad kyang so so'i mdog tu gsal zhing bkrag mdog 'tsher ba'o //
NK071(du)001:294: rigs lnga'i yum du gyur ba na btsun mo'i yon
NK071(du)001:295: tan gyi khyad par gzhan las 'phags pa na dam
NK071(du)001:296: pa snang ba nam mkha'i khams gnas su dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:297: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma dang /
NK071(du)001:298: srab ba sa'i dbyings gnas su dag pa spyan ma dang /
NK071(du)001:299: mnyen pa chu'i dbyings gnas su dag pa m+aa ma ki dang /
NK071(du)001:300: dro ba me'i dbyings gnas su dag pa gos dkar mo dang /
NK071(du)001:301: bskyod pa'i dbyings rlung gi khams gnas su dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:302: sgrol ma ste de dag la sogs pa rigs kyi
NK071(du)001:304: don rang bzhin gnyis su med par rtags yab yum
NK071(du)001:305: mnyam par sbyor ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs te ji ltar
NK071(du)001:306: na khyab byed chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab bya shes
NK071(du)001:307: bya thams cad la khyab pa kun tu ston pa'i
NK071(du)001:308: mdzad spyod kyi rol mo mtha' yas par snang bas
NK071(du)001:309: khyab pa ni / 'di lta ste dper na til
NK071(du)001:310: gyi gang bu kha phye ba bzhin du go mtshams
NK071(du)001:311: med par gang nas kun tu khyab par bzhugs so
NK071(du)001:312: khyab pa ni / // de bzhin gshegs pa lnga
NK071(du)001:313: bshad pa'i rjes de nas spangs rtogs mthar phyin pas
NK071(du)001:314: byang chub kyang yin la sar gnas kyi sems dpa'
NK071(du)001:315: las 'phags pas chen po dang rdo rje ni rtogs
NK071(du)001:316: tshogs su snang yang rang bzhin lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)001:317: nges par dbyer mi phyed pa'i don te spyi'i mtshan
NK071(du)001:318: khyab pa ni / // no // mthong ba ste
NK071(du)001:319: mig gi rnam shes gnas su dag pa sa'i snying
NK071(du)001:320: khyab pa ni / // no // po dang /
NK071(du)001:321: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos pa ste rna
NK071(du)001:322: ba'i rnam shes dag pa phyag na rdo rje dang
NK071(du)001:323: khyab pa ni / // no // po dang /
NK071(du)001:324: / byang chub chen po rdo rje snom pa sna'i
NK071(du)001:325: rnam shes te nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK071(du)001:326: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba lce yi rnam shes te spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK071(du)001:327: de dag gi yul shes pa rnams kyi spyad byar
NK071(du)001:328: gyur pas btsun mo yin la mthong bar bya ba
NK071(du)001:329: gzugs te rdo rje sgeg mo dang /
NK071(du)001:330: mnyan par bya ba sgra ste glu ma dang /
NK071(du)001:331: snam par bya ba dri ste phreng ba ma dang /
NK071(du)001:332: myong bar bya ba ro ste gar ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:333: 'dir yang byang chub chen po rdo rje spyi'i mtshan
NK071(du)001:334: yin la mthong byed ni mig dbang ste byams pa
NK071(du)001:335: da nga / byang chub chen po rdo rje thos
NK071(du)001:336: byed ni rna ba'i dbang po ste sgrib sel dang
NK071(du)001:337: da nga / / byang chub chen po rdo rje
NK071(du)001:338: snom byed ni sna'i dbang po kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)001:339: da nga / / dang / byang chub chen po
NK071(du)001:340: rdo rje myong byed lce'i dbang po 'jam dpal dang
NK071(du)001:341: da nga / / dang / / de dag gi
NK071(du)001:342: yum yang dus bzhi'i go phye nas dbang po rnams
NK071(du)001:343: da nga / / dang / / bskyed pas na
NK071(du)001:344: / btsun mo dus 'das pa bdug spos ma dang
NK071(du)001:345: da nga / / dang / / bskyed pas na / / da lta ba me tog ma dang /
NK071(du)001:346: 'byung ba ste ma 'ongs pa mar me ma dang /
NK071(du)001:347: ma byon pa ste ma nges pa'i dus dri chab ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:348: gdug pa can 'jom pa'i brtul zhugs chen pos thams
NK071(du)001:349: cad 'joms shing phas kyi rgol bas mi tshug pas
NK071(du)001:350: rdo rje dang / bye brag tu lus kyi yul
NK071(du)001:351: dbang shes gsum 'dus pa'i reg pa ste bdud rtsi
NK071(du)001:352: rdo rje dang / 'khyil ba dang / 'joms pa
NK071(du)001:353: chen po rdo rje reg byed lus kyi dbang po
NK071(du)001:354: rdo rje dang / 'khyil ba dang / rta mgrin
NK071(du)001:355: dang / 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg bya
NK071(du)001:356: yul te stobs po che dang /
NK071(du)001:357: 'joms pa chen po rdo rje reg shes lus kyi rnam par shes pa ste gshin rje gshed dang /
NK071(du)001:358: tshad med pa bzhi yang spyad bya'i yul yin pas
NK071(du)001:359: na btsun mo chos thams cad rtag par ma yin
NK071(du)001:360: pa ste byams pa'i bdag nyid lcags kyu ma dang
NK071(du)001:361: / de bzhin du chad par 'dzin pa ma yin
NK071(du)001:362: pa ste snying rje'i rang bzhin zhags pa ma dang
NK071(du)001:363: / / bdag tu 'dzin pa ma yin pa dga' ba'i rang bzhin lcags sgrog ma dang /
NK071(du)001:364: mtshan mar 'dzin pa ma yin pa ste btang snyoms kyi rang bzhin dril bu ma la sogs pa /
NK071(du)001:365: de lta bu'i thugs ye shes rang snang gi 'khor
NK071(du)001:366: dang gzhan yang rgyud las sbyangs kyi tshogs dang bcas
NK071(du)001:367: pa brjod kyis mi lang ba rnam pa dang rang
NK071(du)001:368: bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:369: gleng gzhi rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin
NK071(du)001:370: gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang dgongs
NK071(du)001:371: pa gnyis su med pa'i ngo bo rtogs dka' ba
NK071(du)001:372: gsang ba'i ye shes rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK071(du)001:373: dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi gdon gzhan gyis spyod
NK071(du)001:374: yul las 'das pa'i gsang ba chen po 'di nyid
NK071(du)001:375: ston pa rigs drug pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs
NK071(du)001:376: dang yon tan phrin las lnga'i ngo bo 'char pa'i
NK071(du)001:377: skyes bu rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:378: ngang de las mngon par snang bas na phyung ngo
NK071(du)001:380: e e ma e ma ho /
NK071(du)001:381: zhes pa shin tu ngo mtshar bar ston pa'i tshig go /
NK071(du)001:382: de yang sems nyid rang byung ye shes /
NK071(du)001:383: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos pa'o //
NK071(du)001:384: dbyings de nyid la mnga' mdzad cing dbang sgyur ba'i
NK071(du)001:385: ye shes nyid ston pa'i ngo bor snang la rtogs
NK071(du)001:386: pa'i rig pa nyid ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)001:387: gsal zhing chos can chos nyid tha mi dad par
NK071(du)001:388: gnas pa thugs rje'i ngang ste ston pa'o //
NK071(du)001:389: pho brang gi gzhi la sogs par rnam 'phrul sna
NK071(du)001:390: tshogs par rang snang ba nyid rnam thar bzhi'i ting
NK071(du)001:391: 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug pa'i brdar sgo bzhir snang
NK071(du)001:392: ba'o // theg pa brgyad nas bsgrod pa'i rgyu 'bras
NK071(du)001:393: mtshon byed rta bab kyi gzugs brnyan du rang snang
NK071(du)001:394: ba'o sgyu ma ltar snang ba sems can lnga'i gdan
NK071(du)001:395: dang rnam par dag pa pad+ma dang 'od gsal ba
NK071(du)001:397: ston pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon tan
NK071(du)001:398: dang phrin las lnga las 'char ba'i skyes bu rigs
NK071(du)001:399: lnga yab yum du snang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:400: chos thams cad la sku dang ye shes kyi khyab
NK071(du)001:401: pas nyes skyon gyi sel med pa yi sku kha
NK071(du)001:402: dog dang 'od zer ni 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs
NK071(du)001:403: ma 'dres par gsal ba'i yon tan mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)001:404: gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i rtags
NK071(du)001:405: su yid bzhin rin po che'i gdan du snang ba'o
NK071(du)001:406: // de yang ston pa nyid kyi sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)001:407: mi zad par rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i khyad par las
NK071(du)001:408: // rang snang ba'o // rdo rje theg pa'i rgyun
NK071(du)001:409: mchog gi bstan pa yin la de 'byung ba'i gnas
NK071(du)001:410: ni gnas dus ston 'khor tshogs pa'i dus nyid do
NK071(du)001:411: // rang snang ba'o // // zhes rdo rje gsang
NK071(du)001:412: ba'i zhes pa ni rdo rje theg pa yin la
NK071(du)001:413: de mtshon par byed pa'i tshig tu bsdus pa'o //
NK071(du)001:414: zhes so gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa /
NK071(du)001:415: rtsa ba'i rgyud 'di la le'u rtsa gnyis su yod
NK071(du)001:416: pa las 'dis rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu phun sum tshogs
NK071(du)001:417: pa lnga bstan pas na gleng gzhi dang gzhung ris
NK071(du)001:418: su bcad pa'i phyir le'u zhes bya ste yas nas
NK071(du)001:419: bgrangs pa'i thog ma yin pas na /
NK071(du)001:422: // gsum pa spyi don gyi skabs dang sbyar nas don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)001:423: de lta bu'i le'u dang po 'dis spyi don gyi skabs gang dang gang bstan snyam na /
NK071(du)001:424: dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:425: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK071(du)001:427: dbang po 'bring la spyi don rnam par dbye ba la lnga las /
NK071(du)001:428: dang po rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu gleng gzhi la gsum gyi /
NK071(du)001:429: dang po longs sku'i gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga'i don bstan pa yin te /
NK071(du)001:430: zhib par sa bcad kyi skabs su bshad pa ltar ro //
NK071(du)001:434: thun mong ma yin par gleng bslang ba dang /
NK071(du)001:435: thun mong du gleng bslang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:437: yab yum gnyis kyis gleng bslang ba'i sgo nas gsang dbang bskur ba dang /
NK071(du)001:438: dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:440: gsang dbang bskur ba'i ched du yab yum snyom par 'jug tshul /
NK071(du)001:441: nyams su bstar ba'i don las rdzas kyi dbang bskur zhing rtogs pa brjod pa /
NK071(du)001:442: dbang thob pa'i yon tan nges tshig dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:444: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:445: de nas btsun mo sogs 'og nas blangs te gzhung tshan gnyis po des bstan /
NK071(du)001:447: dang po yab kyi nyams su bstar ba'i don thabs kyi cha zur nas brjod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:449: gnyis pa yum gyis gleng ba ni /
NK071(du)001:451: gsum pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan nges tshigs bcas pa ni /
NK071(du)001:452: zhes brjod pas thams cad sogs /
NK071(du)001:453: gnyis pa dbang gnyis kyi las la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:455: sems bskyed cing ji ltar bskur ba'i rim pa dngos dang /
NK071(du)001:458: de nas gnyis su med pa zhes sogs /
NK071(du)001:462: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed do //
NK071(du)001:465: gnyis pa la grol lam dang /
NK071(du)001:471: gsum pa mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed ni /
NK071(du)001:475: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng bslang ba la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:479: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK071(du)001:482: zhes brjod pas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK071(du)001:484: zhes par gnyis pa le'u'i mtshan ni /
NK071(du)001:486: gnyis pa sa bcad de dang 'grel ba'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:487: de yang gleng gzhi tshogs pa /
NK071(du)001:489: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi byed pa po
NK071(du)001:490: 'khor 'das rdo rje ltar dbyer mi phyed par thugs
NK071(du)001:491: su chud pa'i yid rang byung gi ye shes /
NK071(du)001:492: spyod yul yongs su dag pas kun tu bzang po //
NK071(du)001:493: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma lus pa'i rang
NK071(du)001:494: bzhin bdag nyid kyi tshul du ro gcig cing dbyer
NK071(du)001:496: btsun mo ste yul gtan la dbab par bya ba
NK071(du)001:497: mo 'khor 'das kyi chos rang bzhin dag pa'i dbyings
NK071(du)001:498: kyi phyag rgya yum kun tu bzang mo la snyoms
NK071(du)001:500: snyoms par zhugs pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin
NK071(du)001:501: gshegs pa ma lus pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa
NK071(du)001:503: gcig gi rang bzhin du dbyer med par mkhyen pas
NK071(du)001:504: nyid las gzhan pa'i gdul bya ma gzigs nas ston
NK071(du)001:505: pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid lhan gcig pa'i 'khor
NK071(du)001:506: rang bzhin gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched
NK071(du)001:507: du brjod pa'i tshul thabs shes kyi gleng bslang gnyis
NK071(du)001:509: rtog tshogs thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du rtogs la e ma'o //
NK071(du)001:511: ji ltar na srid zhi'i chos kun rang rig ye
NK071(du)001:512: shes kyi rang bzhin du dbyer mi phyed pas rdo
NK071(du)001:513: rje dang phung po ni spung pa'i don yin la
NK071(du)001:514: de'i yan lag gi dbye ba ni /
NK071(du)001:515: rnam shes kyi phung po mi bskyod par grub par sogs phung po lnga /
NK071(du)001:516: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags shing de bzhin
NK071(du)001:517: du dbang yul las rnam shes drug skye zhing skad
NK071(du)001:518: cig phyi mar rgyun mched par byed pa dang /
NK071(du)001:519: rnam shes yul dbang gi khams bco brgyad po rnams
NK071(du)001:520: kyi rtog pa'i bye brag mang po kun kyang byang
NK071(du)001:521: chub sems dpa'i yab yum sogs kyi 'khor gyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:522: 'khor nyid du gnas te de dag ni nang sems
NK071(du)001:524: 'byung ba lnga ni rigs kyi yum lnga ste /
NK071(du)001:525: sa dang chu ni sangs rgyas spyan ma dang m+aa ma ki'o /
NK071(du)001:526: me dang rlung ni gos dkar mo dang dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK071(du)001:527: nam mkha' ni yum dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'o //
NK071(du)001:528: de ltar na srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas kyi sku dang zhing khams su rnam par dag pas /
NK071(du)001:529: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad dang 'das pa'i chos ma lus pa ste /
NK071(du)001:530: snang zhing srid pa'i chos so cog thams cad sku
NK071(du)001:531: dang ye shes su sangs rgyas pa nyid las gzhan
NK071(du)001:532: ma yin te sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan du gyur
NK071(du)001:533: pa'i chos 'di zhes rang mtshan du grub pa zhig
NK071(du)001:534: sangs rgyas nyid kyis btsal kyang don la med pas
NK071(du)001:535: mi brnyes so ste rnyed pa ma yin no //
NK071(du)001:537: de ltar rtog tshogs thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:538: zhes ston pa yab kyis brjod pas yum dang 'khor
NK071(du)001:539: gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur
NK071(du)001:540: to // de'i rjes de nas btsun mo bya ba
NK071(du)001:541: mo chos kyi dbyings kun tu bzang mo yang bcom
NK071(du)001:542: ldan 'das yid kun tu bzang po dang thabs shes
NK071(du)001:543: gnyis su med par snyoms par 'jug par gyur nas
NK071(du)001:544: to // / ched du brjod pa'i tshul gleng bslang 'di brjod par mdzad do //
NK071(du)001:545: rang gi rtogs pa'i don gzhan la ston par bzhed nas kye ma'o //
NK071(du)001:547: 'di 'dra'i ngo mtshar ba bstan du yod ces /
NK071(du)001:549: de ji lta bu zhe na /
NK071(du)001:551: phyogs bcu'i stong khams kyi 'jig rten tu snang ba
NK071(du)001:552: thams cad log rtog gis btags pa las ye nas
NK071(du)001:554: de'i rgyu mtshan gyis srid pa gsum ni rnam par
NK071(du)001:555: dag pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi zhing khams dang
NK071(du)001:556: / nyon mongs sogs snyigs ma lnga nyid ma spangs par bde ldan gyi gnas su rtogs te /
NK071(du)001:557: 'gro ba'i phung po lnga nyid rang bzhin gyis mngon
NK071(du)001:558: par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa na chos thams cad
NK071(du)001:559: gnas lugs la mchog gi 'bras bu bsgrub bya'i gzhi
NK071(du)001:560: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste /
NK071(du)001:561: gnyug ma rang bzhin rnam dag gi sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK071(du)001:562: de las gzhan du rgyal ba'i chos shig yod dam snyams nas mi btsal bar bya ste /
NK071(du)001:563: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan du gyur pa ma dag
NK071(du)001:564: pa 'di zhes bya ba'i chos shig gud nas btsal
NK071(du)001:565: kyang gzigs pa rnam par dag pa rgyal bas kyang
NK071(du)001:566: mi brnyes so // ste don med nges yin pa'i phyir mi rnyed do //
NK071(du)001:567: zhes rtogs pa brjod pas rkyen byas te /
NK071(du)001:568: lhag pa kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa
NK071(du)001:569: mthong ste rtogs tshogs thams cad ye gdod ma nas
NK071(du)001:570: sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa ston pa yab
NK071(du)001:571: yum nyid dang dgongs pa tha mi dad pa'i 'khor
NK071(du)001:572: rnams kyis mkhyen to zhes 'dir gzhan rnam par bcad
NK071(du)001:573: pa'i tshig gi gsang dbang gi nges tshig kyang grub
NK071(du)001:574: ste / 'khor thun mongs pa rnams kyis dbang thob
NK071(du)001:575: pas don dam skye med kyi ye shes rgyud la
NK071(du)001:576: skyes kyang ston pa dang dgongs pa dbyer med kyi
NK071(du)001:577: ye shes chen po da rung ba ma myong ba'i
NK071(du)001:578: phyir spyod yul ma yin pas na gsang ba'i dbang
NK071(du)001:579: ste / zhes bya'o // gsang dbang bskur ba de
NK071(du)001:580: nas don dgongs pa dang rtags yab yum gyi nyi
NK071(du)001:581: zla byang chub kyi sems gnyis su med pa'i bdag
NK071(du)001:582: nyid bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin gyis 'khor rnams
NK071(du)001:583: la chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don
NK071(du)001:584: sems nyid ye shes lngar dngos su bskyed pa 'di
NK071(du)001:585: ste / zhes bya'o // gsungs so // e ma
NK071(du)001:586: ho ngo mtshar sogs 'di rnams gzhi lam 'bras gsum
NK071(du)001:587: dang sbyar tshul yod kyang 'dir re zhig gzhi la
NK071(du)001:588: sbyar ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)001:589: e ma ho zhes pa ngo mtshar ba'i tshig ste /
NK071(du)001:591: rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi rang bzhin ye shes lngar
NK071(du)001:592: dag pa'i gnas lugs ngo mtshar zhing gzhan las rmad
NK071(du)001:593: du byung ba'i chos nyid 'di ni rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK071(du)001:594: rgyas kun gyi thugs kyi gsang ba zab mo ste
NK071(du)001:595: phal gyi spyod yul ma yin pa'o //
NK071(du)001:597: don dam par sems nyid gdod nas skye ba med
NK071(du)001:598: pa las kun rdzob 'khrul ngor rtog bcas kyi sems
NK071(du)001:599: thams cad rgyu rkyen las skyes pa ltar snang ba
NK071(du)001:600: la de ltar skyes par snang tsam nyid na don
NK071(du)001:601: la de lta bur skye ba grub pa med pa
NK071(du)001:602: 'di ni kun gzhi nyid chos nyid ye shes su
NK071(du)001:604: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK071(du)001:605: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK071(du)001:606: zhes pa'i rkang pa gnyis ni gong du bshad pa ltar la /
NK071(du)001:607: don dam par sems nyid gdod nas 'gag pa med
NK071(du)001:608: pa las kun rdzob tu chos thams cad 'gag pa
NK071(du)001:609: ltar snang la de ltar snang ba thams cad 'gag
NK071(du)001:610: pa nyid na don la 'gag pa med pa'i zung
NK071(du)001:611: 'jug rtogs med rang gsal ba 'di ni kun gzhi'i
NK071(du)001:612: rnam shes me long lta bu'i ye shes su'o //
NK071(du)001:613: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK071(du)001:614: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK071(du)001:615: don dam par chos thams cad gnas pa med pa
NK071(du)001:616: las kun rdzob tu thams cad gnas pa ltar snang
NK071(du)001:617: la / rten gang la gnas pa ltar snang tsam
NK071(du)001:618: nyid na don la gnas pa med pa'i zung 'jug
NK071(du)001:619: dngos po'i gshis tha dad dang phyogs ris bral ba
NK071(du)001:620: 'di ni nyon mongs pa can gyi yid mnyam nyid
NK071(du)001:622: e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK071(du)001:623: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK071(du)001:624: don dam par chos thams cad dmigs pa med pa
NK071(du)001:625: las kun rdzob tu thams cad dmigs pa ltar snang
NK071(du)001:627: dmigs pa nyid na don la dmigs pa med pa'i
NK071(du)001:628: zung 'jug yul yul can gnyis med gsal la ma
NK071(du)001:629: 'dres pa ni yid so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:630: su'o // e ma ho ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos /
NK071(du)001:631: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK071(du)001:632: don dam par chos thams cad 'gro 'ong med pa
NK071(du)001:633: las kun rdzob tu 'gro ba dang 'ong ba ltar
NK071(du)001:634: snang la / yul gang du 'gro ba dang 'ong
NK071(du)001:635: ba ltar snang tsam nyid na don la 'gro 'ong
NK071(du)001:636: med pa'i zung 'jug sems nyid ma btsal lhun gyis
NK071(du)001:637: grub pa ni sgo lnga bya ba grub pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:639: sems bskyed cing dbang bskur ba'i rim pa de skad
NK071(du)001:640: ces brjod pas lhan gcig pa'i 'khor gyi de bzhin
NK071(du)001:641: gshegs pa yab thams cad dang yum btsun mo'i tshogs
NK071(du)001:642: thams cad kyang don dam 'od gsal dang dbyer med
NK071(du)001:643: kyi dgongs pa nyams su myong ste ston 'khor dgongs
NK071(du)001:644: pa khyad med du gyur pa la mnyes pas khyab
NK071(du)001:645: par gyur to // thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng
NK071(du)001:646: bslang ba de nas 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:647: thams cad dang rang rang gi btsun mo'i tshogs thams
NK071(du)001:648: cad dang bcas pas go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched
NK071(du)001:649: du ston pa'i thugs rje bskul ba'i brjod pa 'di
NK071(du)001:650: par gyur to // brjod do // ji ltar zhus na /
NK071(du)001:651: ma rtogs pa'i 'gro ba la skyo ba'i tshul gyis e ma ho zhes ngams te /
NK071(du)001:652: gnyis su med pa'i don thog ma nyid nas ma rtogs pas ye nas gsang ba'i chos so //
NK071(du)001:654: de nyid sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos thams cad
NK071(du)001:655: kyang 'bras bu mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor
NK071(du)001:656: gnas pa la phyin ci log gi shes pas bslad
NK071(du)001:657: nas rang gi rang bzhin ma rtogs pa ni rang
NK071(du)001:659: gnas lugs de yang yul sems sogs gnyis chos thams
NK071(du)001:660: cad la ngo bo nyid kyis grol te yul du
NK071(du)001:661: byar med kyang ma rtogs pas de ltar lta ba
NK071(du)001:663: de yang sems nyid las gzhan zhig gud du yod
NK071(du)001:664: pa min kyang sgrib gnyis bag chags bcas pas sgrib
NK071(du)001:665: ste rang la gnas pa gzhan las 'tshol ba ni
NK071(du)001:667: 'khor gyis gsang ba bzhi'i don de skad ces brjod des zhus pas ston pa thugs rje skyes te /
NK071(du)001:669: dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba thams cad dang /
NK071(du)001:670: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba thams
NK071(du)001:671: cad rtogs rung ma rtogs rung gnyis su med de
NK071(du)001:672: / byed pa po med par ye nas rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:673: lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas bden pa dbyer med pa'i
NK071(du)001:674: ngo bo nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas
NK071(du)001:675: dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir thugs rjes don dbyer med
NK071(du)001:676: / na'ang / 'gro ba rang rang gi rnam par
NK071(du)001:677: rtog pa bskyed pa'i rtsa ba ma rig pa las
NK071(du)001:678: 'bras bu 'gro ba lam rgyud lnga'i sdug bsngal ris
NK071(du)001:679: / na'ang / mi mthun pa / bsam gyis mi khyab par smin pa la /
NK071(du)001:680: thabs dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje chen po dang /
NK071(du)001:681: shes rab sangs rgyas kyi thugs ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes chen po ste /
NK071(du)001:682: de nyid kyi ngang nas ji snyed mkhyen pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:683: shes mi 'gags pas gdul bya'i ngo la thugs rje
NK071(du)001:684: skye nas don mdzad par dgongs te ched du brjod
NK071(du)001:686: de yang ma rtogs pa la brtse ba'i rang bzhin gyis e ma ho zhes ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK071(du)001:687: sems nyid ye nas dag pa ni /
NK071(du)001:688: bde gshegs snying po'i de ltar yin pa las rgyun
NK071(du)001:689: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas rang ngo ma
NK071(du)001:690: shes shing / rkyen sems can rang rang gi phyin
NK071(du)001:691: ci log gi rnam par rtog pa kun brtags kyis
NK071(du)001:692: nyon mongs pa skyes nas las sna tshogs la spyad
NK071(du)001:693: pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba'i chos med snang blo bur
NK071(du)001:694: shes shing / du sprul te / de las 'gro ba /
NK071(du)001:695: sna tshogs pa'i lus dang rang rang gi 'dod pa'i yul gzugs sogs longs spyod dang /
NK071(du)001:696: mtho dman sna tshogs pa'i gnas dang tsha grang gi sdug bsngal la sogs pa snang ba la /
NK071(du)001:697: lus can rnams kyi nga'o zhes bdag dang /
NK071(du)001:698: nga'i 'di zhes bdag gir byed pas so sor bzung ba dang 'dzin pas bcing te nyam thag go /
NK071(du)001:699: de yang 'ching byed kyi mkhan po sus kyang ma bcings shing /
NK071(du)001:700: dngos po gang gis kyang bcings pa med de gang bcings bar bya ba /
NK071(du)001:701: rang yang yod pa ma yin kyang /
NK071(du)001:702: kun rdzob tu bcings pa ltar snang ba ni /
NK071(du)001:703: rang gi rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis bcings pa las 'ching byed gzhan med de /
NK071(du)001:704: dper na rab rib can gyis nan gyis brtags kyang mkha' las skra shad med bzhin du mthong nas /
NK071(du)001:705: de la mdud pa 'dor ba'i 'khrul snang byung ba na /
NK071(du)001:706: de yang bcings pa yod na de ltos kyi grol ba'ang srid pa las /
NK071(du)001:707: ltos gzhi bcings pa med pas de la ltos pa'i chos rnam par grol ba'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:708: 'gro ba mtha' dag ye nas bcings grol med pa'i
NK071(du)001:709: gnas lugs sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)001:710: lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:711: du sangs rgyas pas 'khor 'das mnyam nyid du la
NK071(du)001:713: de nyid mtshon byed kyi rgyud 'di gdul bya'i khyad
NK071(du)001:714: par gyi dngos dang ba rgyud nas bstan par bya
NK071(du)001:715: ba'i phyir bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i sprul pa drug
NK071(du)001:716: spro ba sogs 'gag med thugs rje'i rol pa sna
NK071(du)001:718: ces ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du gyur
NK071(du)001:719: pa la go phye ba'i 'khor gyi ched du gleng
NK071(du)001:720: ngo // gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid
NK071(du)001:721: nges pa las 'dis don dam par spros pa nye
NK071(du)001:722: bar zhi ba dang kun rdzob tu de nyid ma
NK071(du)001:723: rtogs pa'i dbang gi 'khor ba la don mdzad tshul
NK071(du)001:725: don la gnyis ka byang chub kyi sems 'ching grol
NK071(du)001:726: med pa'i ngo bor dbyer mi phyed pas na 'khor
NK071(du)001:727: 'das ye nas dbyer med du gnas pa la gnas
NK071(du)001:728: par shes pa'i bdag nyid du sems bskyed par bstan
NK071(du)001:732: gleng gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga 'dzom pa'i dus der /
NK071(du)001:733: gnyis pa rgyud don 'byung ba'i rkyen gleng bslang ba thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK071(du)001:734: thun mong pa rdzogs par bstan pa'i tshul sa bcad kyi skabs su'ang bshad pa ltar ro //
NK071(du)001:741: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK071(du)001:742: yongs su shes par bya ba lta ba'o //
NK071(du)001:743: dang po la'ang rgyu dang ngo bo gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:745: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK071(du)001:748: gnyis pa ngo bo la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:757: rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK071(du)001:760: bltams pa dang nas ston pa'i thub pas bar /
NK071(du)001:762: dus bzhi nas drug dang zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:764: kun tu sku nas snang bar 'gyur ro bar /
NK071(du)001:768: thams cad kyang nas theg pas zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:770: gnyen po la dgongs te dbye ba dang /
NK071(du)001:771: de'ang dbang po'i bye brag gi bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)001:773: ma rig pa nas gsung bar 'gyur ro bar gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)001:774: de dag nas mthar thug go /
NK071(du)001:775: gnyis pa yongs su shes par bya ba lta ba la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:776: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:777: gtan la dbab pa dngos so //
NK071(du)001:781: brtag gzhii 'khor ba'i chos rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK071(du)001:782: 'das pa'i chos brjod med du gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK071(du)001:784: gzhal bya gtan tshigs grub mtha' rdo rje'i theg par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:786: ji snyed sogs rkang pa lnga gnyis pa la thun mong dang /
NK071(du)001:787: thun mong ma yin pa gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:788: dang po thun mong pa bden pa'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)001:789: yang dag sgyu ma'i sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:792: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)001:794: bdag dang sogs nas nyid spyod phyir bar gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)001:797: gnyis pa 'das pa'i chos brjod med du gtan la dbab pa la lnga ste /
NK071(du)001:798: theg bzhi'i 'bras bu bla med theg par bstan pa
NK071(du)001:799: chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa'i cho 'phrul du
NK071(du)001:800: bstan pa / sangs rgyas dang chos la 'pho 'gyur
NK071(du)001:801: med kyang de ltar bstan pa rgyud kyi che ba
NK071(du)001:802: bstan pa de thams cad rtags pa tsam ste rang
NK071(du)001:803: bzhin brjod med du bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:805: theg pa gzhi sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:807: yang dag rtogs sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:809: sangs rgyas sogs tshig bcad gcig bzhi pa ni /
NK071(du)001:812: chos rnams nas brjod do bar gnyis pa bsdu ba la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:813: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa bsdu ba dngos /
NK071(du)001:817: de nas sogs gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)001:818: a ho srid rtsa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:822: zhes brjod pas thub pa sogs /
NK071(du)001:825: bcad de dang ldan pa'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:826: gang gi ched du spro bar zhal gyis bzhes pa /
NK071(du)001:827: de nas ji ltar spro na /
NK071(du)001:828: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK071(du)001:829: dmigs med kun khyab rang byung gi thugs rje chen
NK071(du)001:830: por rang shar ba'i byin gyis brlabs pa dus su
NK071(du)001:831: 'byung ba zhes bya ba thugs rig pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:832: las rnam par 'phrul bas na rig pa'i skyes bu
NK071(du)001:833: dang / las nyon gyi dpung bcom pas na thub pa ste /
NK071(du)001:834: gdul bya'i dbang gis rnam pa drug go gang las na ston pa /
NK071(du)001:835: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs drug pa'i sku dang gsung
NK071(du)001:836: dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las 'thon
NK071(du)001:837: te / de ltar thub pa drug 'thon nas kyang /
NK071(du)001:838: don bya ba'i zhing gdul bya'i las kyi bye brag
NK071(du)001:839: tha dad pa'i dbang gi mgo 'phred la bstan nas
NK071(du)001:841: gyen mthur du bstan nas 'gro ba yan man gyi
NK071(du)001:842: 'jig rten snod kyi bye brag zlum po sogs bzhi
NK071(du)001:843: dang gzhi phyal ba dang steng g.yog med pa ste
NK071(du)001:844: rnam pa mi 'dra ba drug gi rang bzhin gyis
NK071(du)001:845: phyogs bcur khyab cing tshad bzung du med pas mtha'
NK071(du)001:846: yas mu med pa'i zhing khams nam mkha'i dbyings ltar
NK071(du)001:847: snang ba las stong gsum gyi stong chen po de
NK071(du)001:848: re rer gang gis don mdzad pa po thub pa
NK071(du)001:849: chen po bcom ldan 'das re reer snang nas sku
NK071(du)001:850: bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba sogs /
NK071(du)001:851: 'dul ba rnam bzhis don mdzad pa'i yul lam rgyud lnga'i /
NK071(du)001:852: theg pa lnga'i rigs can gyi 'gro ba lnga'i don mdzad de /
NK071(du)001:854: bdag cag gi ston pa lum+bi ni'i tshal du sku
NK071(du)001:855: bltams te nyer dgu'i bar khab tu bzhugs pa dang
NK071(du)001:856: / de nas khyim spangs te mchod rten rnam dag gi drung du rab tu byung ba dang /
NK071(du)001:857: chu bo ner+aany+dza na'i 'gram du lo drug gi bar
NK071(du)001:858: dka' thub mdzad nas legs skyes mas drangs pa'i 'o
NK071(du)001:859: thug bzhes te sku gser gyi mdog tu gyur pa
NK071(du)001:860: dang / byang chub shing drung du bsam gtan bzhi
NK071(du)001:861: yi rab mtha' la brten nas sgrib gnyis bag chags
NK071(du)001:862: dang bcas pa ma lus pa spangs shing /
NK071(du)001:863: shes bya thams cad thugs su chud de mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK071(du)001:864: de'i snga logs su 'od zer bkye ba la sogs pa'i sgo nas bdud btul ba dang /
NK071(du)001:867: yangs pa can sogs la chos kyi 'khor lo rnam pa gsum bskor ba dang /
NK071(du)001:868: mnyan yod du mu stegs pa 'dul ba sogs cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:869: gyad yul rtsa can gyi gnas su sku myang ngan
NK071(du)001:870: las 'da' ba'i tshul dang sku gdung ring bsrel la
NK071(du)001:871: sogs pa rnam 'phrul mtha' yas par ston pa'i thub
NK071(du)001:872: pa gang gi sku'i mdzad pa de dag ni bsod
NK071(du)001:873: nams gzhan las 'phags par bstan pas na sku bsod
NK071(du)001:875: sngon dang phyi ma'i gnas mkhyen pa'i mngon shes kyi
NK071(du)001:876: 'das pa la sogs pa'i dus bzhi kun tu sgrib
NK071(du)001:877: pa med par sa ler mkhyen pa dang /
NK071(du)001:878: pha rol gyi sems mkhyen pa'i mngon shes kyis gzhan
NK071(du)001:879: thams cad kyi sems kyi rgyud kyi 'gyu ba sna
NK071(du)001:880: tshogs pa kun tu ma sgrib par mkhyen pa dang
NK071(du)001:881: / sgrib pa med pa rdzu 'phrul gyi lha'i spyan
NK071(du)001:882: gyis nye ring med pa'i gzugs dang 'chi 'pho skye
NK071(du)001:883: ba sogs thams cad kun tu gzigs pa dang sgrib
NK071(du)001:884: pa med pa rdzu 'phrul gyi lha'i snyan gyis sgra
NK071(du)001:885: che chung nye ring med par kun tu gsan pa
NK071(du)001:886: / dang / thogs pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK071(du)001:887: cho gas ste bya ba grub pa'i mngon shes gang
NK071(du)001:888: 'dul gyis sprul sgyur sna tshogs ston pas kun tu
NK071(du)001:889: sems can gyi don spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:890: sgrib pa dag pa'i ye shes zag pa med pa'i
NK071(du)001:891: mngon shes kyis ji ltar spyad kyang mi dgos pa
NK071(du)001:892: kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK071(du)001:893: shes pa dang / de lta bu'i mngon par shes
NK071(du)001:894: pa chen po drug dang ldan pas don mdzad pa'i
NK071(du)001:895: phyir thugs mngon sum pas 'dul ba'o //
NK071(du)001:896: gdul bya'i zhing kun tu rang rang gi snang ba
NK071(du)001:897: dang mthun pa'i sku'i bkod pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK071(du)001:898: pa dang / rgyud kun tu mos pa dang mthun
NK071(du)001:899: par 'jug pa'i thugs mkhyen pa'i ye shes bsam gyis
NK071(du)001:901: sku re re la'ang 'gro ba'i mos pa tha dad
NK071(du)001:902: pa'i spyod yul kun tu de dang mthun pa'i zhal
NK071(du)001:903: gyi dkyil 'khor zhi khro dang phra men la sogs
NK071(du)001:904: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK071(du)001:905: gdul bya'i skal pa ji ltar yod pa kun tu
NK071(du)001:906: so so'i skad dang mthun par chos ston pa'i gsung
NK071(du)001:907: bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK071(du)001:908: de ltar rnam 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pa cing
NK071(du)001:909: mtha' yas par 'phro bas grangs med pa dag phyogs
NK071(du)001:910: bcu'i zhing kun tu snang nas 'dul bar gyur to
NK071(du)001:911: // spyir ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa ma zad kyi bar theg pa'i mthar thug pa med cing /
NK071(du)001:912: brtsi tshul yang mtha' yas pa zhig 'byung mod //
NK071(du)001:913: 'on kyang bye brag rgyud gzhung 'di nyid du grags pa ltar na /
NK071(du)001:914: sprul sku'i gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa de dag /
NK071(du)001:915: thams cad kyang bsdu na 'di lta ste /
NK071(du)001:916: rigs can lnga'i gdul bya 'dul ba'i dbang gis theg pa'i bye brag lngar phye nas bstan to //
NK071(du)001:918: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)001:919: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK071(du)001:920: rang byang chub ste rang rgyal gyi theg pa dang /
NK071(du)001:921: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)001:922: rgyu'i theg pa las khyad par du 'phags shing /
NK071(du)001:923: de dag thams cad 'dir rdzogs pas na /
NK071(du)001:924: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang bcas pas /
NK071(du)001:925: 'gro ba rnams lhan gcig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i
NK071(du)001:926: dbang gis phyin ci log gi rnam par rtog pas
NK071(du)001:927: bskyed pa'i nyon mongs pa dug gsum dang cha mnyam
NK071(du)001:928: nyi khri chig stong re ste sdom pas /
NK071(du)001:929: stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi spyod pa'i gnyen por chos kyi sgo yang sde snod gsum dang /
NK071(du)001:930: cha mnyam rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod de bzhis
NK071(du)001:931: bsdus pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi lngar gsungs
NK071(du)001:933: ma 'ongs pa na'ang gsung bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:934: chos kyi sgo de dag thams cad kyang dbang po'i bye brag lngar 'du ste /
NK071(du)001:935: de yang gang zag gi bdag med rtogs shing chos
NK071(du)001:936: bdag gzung ba rdul phran dang 'dzin pa'i skad cig
NK071(du)001:937: ma don dam tu 'dod pa nyan thos kyi theg
NK071(du)001:938: pa nyon mongs pa spong ba'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)001:939: shes pa skad cig ma don dam du 'dod pas phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba /
NK071(du)001:940: 'khor bar 'dod pas rang rgyal gyi theg pa la nyon mongs pa 'geb pa'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)001:941: bdag med pa gnyis rtogs pas bzung ba'i yul kyang
NK071(du)001:942: 'dzin pa'i shes pa rkyen gyis 'khrul pa'i las kyis
NK071(du)001:943: yul du sgro 'dogs par zad kyi /
NK071(du)001:944: don la bden med sgyu ma lta bur shes kyang /
NK071(du)001:945: thabs kyis zin ma zin las phan gnod gyi bya ba yang byed par shes nas /
NK071(du)001:946: kun rdzob rdzas yod du bltas te blangs dor phyed
NK071(du)001:947: pas byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa nyon mongs pa
NK071(du)001:948: chos nyid du sbyong ba'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)001:949: yang las dge sdig dang mi g.yo ba'i las kyi
NK071(du)001:950: 'bras bu thams cad chud mi za bar so sor
NK071(du)001:951: smin par yid ches pas blang dor la ma nor
NK071(du)001:952: bar spyod kyang 'khor ba las nges par 'byung mi
NK071(du)001:953: nus pa lha mi'i theg pa dang /
NK071(du)001:954: lha mi'i theg pa 'di bshad pa'i dus su nyan
NK071(du)001:955: thos theg pa'i gong du blang nas bshad dgos so
NK071(du)001:956: // yang kun rdzob rdzas su med kyang btags yod
NK071(du)001:957: mi 'gog pas 'di ltar las dang las kyi 'bras
NK071(du)001:958: bu rnams med ces mi skur la 'on kyang nyon
NK071(du)001:959: mongs pa lha dang ye shes su sgyur ba'i thabs
NK071(du)001:960: la rten na de dag gis mi gos so zhes
NK071(du)001:961: ston pa kri yog sde gsum gyi theg pa dang
NK071(du)001:962: // / las dang 'bras bu bdag nyid chen po'i
NK071(du)001:963: rol par rtogs pas nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes
NK071(du)001:964: lnga'i rang mdangs su shes te /
NK071(du)001:965: spangs gnyen gnyis med pas na /
NK071(du)001:967: ji ltar spyad kyang yon tan du 'char ba sngags
NK071(du)001:968: nang pa gnyis la nyon mongs pa dbang du byas
NK071(du)001:969: pa'i thabs dang / chos dbyings rnam dag rang byung
NK071(du)001:970: gi ye shes rang shar bas spong sbyong sogs thams
NK071(du)001:971: cad dngos zhen gyi lta ba las byung bar rtogs
NK071(du)001:972: pa'i thabs dang / nas / dgag sgrub spang gnyen gyi tha snyad las grol nas /
NK071(du)001:973: las dang 'bras bus gos su med par ston pa ste /
NK071(du)001:974: theg pa thams cad kyi grub mtha'i mthar thug pa gsang ba snying po'i rgyud gzhung 'di dag go /
NK071(du)001:975: bstan pa spyi'i gleng gzhi bshad pa de nas ston
NK071(du)001:976: pa de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po
NK071(du)001:977: nyid kyis go phye ba 'khor gyi ched du dgongs
NK071(du)001:978: pa brda'i gsung gis brjod pa dang 'dra bar brda
NK071(du)001:979: spyod pa 'di brjod pas go bar mdzad do //
NK071(du)001:980: zhes sdud pa pos lo rgyus brjod de 'brel sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:981: phyi nang snod bcud kyi dngos po ji snyed pa'i
NK071(du)001:982: 'jig rten 'di dag rmi lam ltar 'khrul pa'i chos
NK071(du)001:983: te / rtsa ba lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang /
NK071(du)001:984: bdag gnyis su rtog pa'i kun brtags gzung 'dzin gnyis snang gis shes pa /
NK071(du)001:985: phyi nang gi rten 'brel gnyis su bar med par shing rta'i 'khor lo ltar 'khor te /
NK071(du)001:986: las mi mthun pa'i dbang gis bde sdug sna tshogs myong bar 'gyur zhing de'i rang bzhin chos nyid /
NK071(du)001:988: 'khor bar snang tsam nyid nas yang dag par ma grub pa don dam dang /
NK071(du)001:989: sgyu ma lta bur ma 'gag par snang ba kun rdzob ste /
NK071(du)001:990: de ltar mtshan nyid theg pa bas chos thams cad
NK071(du)001:991: bden pa gnyis su 'byed pa'i 'dod pa dang tshul
NK071(du)001:992: mthun par 'dir yang gnyis su smra ste /
NK071(du)001:993: 'di ltar bdag tu 'dzin pa'i shes pa dang /
NK071(du)001:994: bdag gi bar rtog pa phung po lnga /
NK071(du)001:995: 'byung ba lnga la gzhan du sgro btags te yul
NK071(du)001:996: du 'dzin pa 'di dag snang tsam nyid nas de
NK071(du)001:998: rnam par dag pa'i dbyings de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du tshul gcig go /
NK071(du)001:999: ji ltar na bdag dang bdag gi ba dang gzhan zhes tha dad du snang ba 'di rnams ni /
NK071(du)001:1000: log par rtog pa'i 'khrul snang tsam nyid las /
NK071(du)001:1001: gzhan du ma mthong bas phra zhing phra ba ste rdul phran dang /
NK071(du)001:1003: zab pa ste shes pa skad cig ma yang log na yod pa ma yin kyang /
NK071(du)001:1004: 'di ltar snang ba ni log rtog gi rgyun snga
NK071(du)001:1005: ma nyid la phyi ma nyid spyod pa ni rmi
NK071(du)001:1006: lam gyi snang ba ltar 'khrul pa las byung ba
NK071(du)001:1007: yin la don du chos nyid las gzhan du g.yo
NK071(du)001:1008: ba ci yang med la rnam par dpyad na log
NK071(du)001:1009: rtog tsam yang yod pa ma yin te /
NK071(du)001:1010: de'i rgyu ma rig pa'i bdag dang 'bras bu phung po lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:1011: zhen pa'i rgyun rnam shes su snang ba nyid kyang
NK071(du)001:1012: brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba ye nas
NK071(du)001:1014: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su log rtog skad cig ma'i rgyun tsam yang ma grub bo //
NK071(du)001:1015: de ltar log rtog gi rgyun rnam par dag pa'i dbyings nyid kyi tshul /
NK071(du)001:1016: de nyid la dbang sgyur ba skye 'gag gnyis med
NK071(du)001:1017: bden par dbyer med du ye nas sangs rgyas par
NK071(du)001:1018: rtogs pa'i mthus / rang rig mngon sum gyis nyid
NK071(du)001:1019: la nyid spyod pa ltar yul med rang gsal du
NK071(du)001:1020: rtogs pa'i mthus / rtogs pa'i phyir / bdag phung
NK071(du)001:1021: po lnga dang gzhan 'byung ba lnga dang rtog pa'i
NK071(du)001:1022: rgyun rnam shes phyi nang gi chos 'di dag rang
NK071(du)001:1023: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de nyid gtan la
NK071(du)001:1024: rtogs pa'i mthus / rtogs pa'i phyir / phebs pa
NK071(du)001:1025: ni / bla med rdo rje theg pa 'di grub
NK071(du)001:1026: rtogs pa'i mthus / rtogs pa'i phyir / phebs pa
NK071(du)001:1027: ni / mtha' ste / mtshan nyid phyi rgyud kyi
NK071(du)001:1028: theg pa las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir mchog
NK071(du)001:1029: rtogs pa'i mthus / rtogs pa'i phyir / phebs pa
NK071(du)001:1030: ni / mtha' ste / go / lha mi nyan
NK071(du)001:1031: rang byang sems kyi theg pa bzhi yis rang rang
NK071(du)001:1032: gi mi mthun phyogs las nges par 'byung la /
NK071(du)001:1033: mthar bla na med pa'i theg pa gcig pu 'di ni de dag gi bsgrub bya dang /
NK071(du)001:1034: 'di las bgrod cing sbyang du med pas 'bras bur nges shing gnas pa'i sa yang yin no //
NK071(du)001:1035: yang dag pa'i gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis rab tu brtags shing dpyad na /
NK071(du)001:1036: chos thams cad rang bzhin cir yang grub pa med
NK071(du)001:1037: pa'i ngang las rten 'brel tsam du rol pa cir
NK071(du)001:1038: yang 'char bas thabs rnams kyang gdul bya'i blo dang
NK071(du)001:1039: mthun par 'grub bo yang dag par na sku gsum
NK071(du)001:1040: dbyer med pas sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku'ang myang ngan
NK071(du)001:1041: las yongs su mi 'da' zhing des gsungs pa'i chos
NK071(du)001:1042: kyang nam yang nub par mi 'gyur te /
NK071(du)001:1043: 'on kyang 'pho 'gyur yod pa ltar snang ba ni /
NK071(du)001:1044: gnas lugs ma rig pa'i sems can rnams smin par
NK071(du)001:1045: mdzad pa dang 'dul bar mdzad ba'i phyir sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:1046: 'jig rten du dang po byung ba nas mthar mya
NK071(du)001:1047: ngan las 'da' ba'i bar gyi mdzad pa'i tshul ston
NK071(du)001:1048: pa thams cad sprul pa tsam las rang rgyud pa
NK071(du)001:1049: ma yin no // bslab pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:1050: gtso bor ston pas bzhag pa 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon pa ste sde snod gsum dang /
NK071(du)001:1051: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs 'da' bar dka' ba'i dam tshig gis bcings pa bya rgyud dang /
NK071(du)001:1052: kri yog gnyis la brten nas sgrub pa spyod rgyud dang /
NK071(du)001:1053: phyi yi spyod pa grogs tsam las gtso bor rnal
NK071(du)001:1054: 'byor la brten pas don grub par byed pa yo
NK071(du)001:1055: ga dang / cho ga gsum bskyed sogs bskyed rim
NK071(du)001:1056: dang rdzogs rim gsal stong gtso bor ston pa sku'i
NK071(du)001:1059: rdzogs rim bde stong gtso bor ston pa gsung gi rgyud bla med ma dang /
NK071(du)001:1060: bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug cing 'od gsal ye shes
NK071(du)001:1061: chen po'i rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa thugs kyi
NK071(du)001:1062: rgyud gnyis su med pa ste phyogs bcu'i zhing khams
NK071(du)001:1063: rnams su rab tu grags pa'i mdo rgyud thams cad
NK071(du)001:1064: gsang ba'i snying po 'di las 'phros te /
NK071(du)001:1065: rgyud 'di ni 'khor ba ji srid bar du //
NK071(du)001:1066: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi /
NK071(du)001:1067: 'byung gnas de phyi mo lta bur 'gyur zhing /
NK071(du)001:1068: de thams cad gtan la'ang 'dis nges par 'bebs pas
NK071(du)001:1069: na mdo rgyud kun gyis spyi 'grel lta bu'ang yin
NK071(du)001:1070: no // de ltar bstan pa'i chos rnams ming du btags pa tsam /
NK071(du)001:1071: las don la grub pa med kyang ston pas tha
NK071(du)001:1072: snyad la brten nas yang dag pa'i don la rim
NK071(du)001:1073: gyis dkri ba'i ched du re zhig gdul bya'i blo
NK071(du)001:1075: ming dang tshig tu sgro btags nas chos bstan pa tsam las /
NK071(du)001:1076: de ltar ston pa'i dus nyid nas ming tshig la
NK071(du)001:1077: don gyi dngos po cung zad kyang grub pa med
NK071(du)001:1078: do // de ltar chos thams cad brjod du med pa'o zhes brjod par mdzad do //
NK071(du)001:1079: rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:1080: yab yum dgongs pa gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:1081: gyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyii don spyod yul
NK071(du)001:1082: las 'das pa'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston pa'i sku
NK071(du)001:1083: la sogs lnga'i ngo bo rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed
NK071(du)001:1084: pa'i rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)001:1085: a hohzhesa 'khor 'das gnyis med du gtan la pheb pa la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:1086: 'di ltar srid pa'i rtsa ba 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs
NK071(du)001:1087: thams cad dang bdag tu rtog pa'i ma rig pa
NK071(du)001:1088: ste / de las 'phros pa las nyon 'du byed
NK071(du)001:1089: kyi bag chags smin pa'i dbang gis mngon par grub
NK071(du)001:1090: pa rgyud drug sems can so so'i snang ba la
NK071(du)001:1091: skye ba dang srog 'gag pas 'chi ba dang lus
NK071(du)001:1092: ste / bzang ngan dang / longs spyod che chung dang /
NK071(du)001:1094: 'pho ltung sogs sdug bsngal gyi 'khrul 'khor bar med
NK071(du)001:1095: du 'khor ba la sogs pa ste de dag kyang
NK071(du)001:1096: log rtog nyid de ltar snang tsam las don gzhan
NK071(du)001:1097: du grub pa ci yang med de /
NK071(du)001:1098: rnam par dag pa'i stong nyid bdag med pa'i don
NK071(du)001:1099: ye nas mkhyen pa so so rang gis rig pa'i
NK071(du)001:1100: ye shes thugs su chud pa ni dmigs bya gzung
NK071(du)001:1101: ba'i yul dang dmigs byed 'dzin sems kyi rtog pa
NK071(du)001:1102: gnyis ngang gis med par dran snang ye shes su
NK071(du)001:1103: dbang bsgyur bas yon tan lhun gyis grub pa la
NK071(du)001:1104: ngo mtshar ba'i mdzad pa gleng gzhi spro ba'i rgyu
NK071(du)001:1105: dang sku bsod nams chen po dang /
NK071(du)001:1106: gsung rig pa dang yon tan nyid rdzu 'phrul dang
NK071(du)001:1107: mngon shes su shar bas thugs mngon sum pa dang
NK071(du)001:1108: / rdzu 'phrul bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste 'dul
NK071(du)001:1109: ba'i zhing khams mtha' yas par snang ba ye shes
NK071(du)001:1110: rang snang las gzhan logs na rang mtshan du grub
NK071(du)001:1111: pa med de ye shes de nyid gdul bya'i snang
NK071(du)001:1112: ba la de ltar snang ba yin no //
NK071(du)001:1113: de ltar chos thams cad snang ba gnyis las ma 'das so //
NK071(du)001:1114: zhes rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1115: de skad ces brjod pas ston pa'i thugs rje las
NK071(du)001:1116: thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs med pa spros
NK071(du)001:1117: nas 'dul ba'i dbang gis chos kyi sgo du ma
NK071(du)001:1118: bstan pa dang / gdod nas grub pa'i de bzhin
NK071(du)001:1119: gshegs pa thams cad kyis dgongs pa dang brdal la
NK071(du)001:1121: gsungs pa yang chos thams cad sems dang ye shes
NK071(du)001:1122: rang snang bar bstan pa de dag tu 'dus par
NK071(du)001:1123: ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa rigs drug pa nyid
NK071(du)001:1124: kyis mkhyen to // gsang ba'i snying po de kho
NK071(du)001:1125: na nyid nges pa las 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK071(du)001:1126: cad sems dang ye shes nyid rang bzhin gyi rnam
NK071(du)001:1127: par dag pa'i chos nyid du gtan la phab nas
NK071(du)001:1128: bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1131: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nas /
NK071(du)001:1132: gos su med par ston pa'i mthar thug go /
NK071(du)001:1133: zhes pa'i bar gyis sprul sku 'gro ba 'dul ba'i gleng gzhi bstan te /
NK071(du)001:1134: de ltar na de yan chad kyis rgyud 'byung ba'i
NK071(du)001:1135: rgyu rkyen rdzogs par slob dpon sgegs pa'i rdo rje
NK071(du)001:1136: dang / sangs rgyas gsang bas bzhed cing /
NK071(du)001:1137: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa man chad kyis de
NK071(du)001:1138: kho na nyid lta ba'i rim pa gtso bor bstan
NK071(du)001:1139: par gsungs la / slob dpon bi ma las /
NK071(du)001:1140: le'u gnyis pas yum gyi sleng bslang ba'i rgyud 'byung ba'i rgyu rkyen rdzogs nas /
NK071(du)001:1141: de nas gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen po zhes /
NK071(du)001:1142: le'u gnyis pa'i smad chas byang chub kyi sems gnyis bskyed pa bstan par bzhed /
NK071(du)001:1144: byang chub mchog ldan rnal 'byor des /
NK071(du)001:1145: chos kun nges don gtan la phab ces byang chub kyi sems gnyis bskyed pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK071(du)001:1146: gnas skabs su lam gyi rim pa sna tshogs su bstan kyang /
NK071(du)001:1147: mthar thug nges pa'i don kho na la 'bab cing /
NK071(du)001:1148: gzhol bas gtan la phab pa'i tshul bstan to //
NK071(du)001:1151: gnyis pa kun bzang yab yum gyi gleng bslangs dang /
NK071(du)001:1152: de ma rtog pa'i 'gro la byang chub kyi sems gnyis bskyed pa /
NK071(du)001:1153: gsum par de'i byin rlabs thub pa drug spros te 'dul ba bzhis 'gro don mdzad tshul bstan nas /
NK071(du)001:1154: le'u bzhi pa man chad kyis rgyud kyi dngos bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:1156: lugs de gsum ka gang ltar bshad kyang 'gal ba med cing 'chad bde mod kyi /
NK071(du)001:1157: 'on kyang 'dir bka' sde zur pa'i bshad srol gyi man ngag dbang btsan du byas te /
NK071(du)001:1158: re zhig bshad pa dang po'i rjes su 'brang ste smra'o //
NK071(du)001:1159: zhi khro spyi bye brag gi le'u chos ston pa'i le'u tshom dang sbyar ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)001:1160: le'u gsum pa'i stod cha yan chad kyis zhi ba sngon byung gi le'u bstan te /
NK071(du)001:1161: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor mtshon par byed pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:1162: rgyud kyi dngos po ji ltar ston pa dang sbyar ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)001:1163: de kho na nyid lta ba las /
NK071(du)001:1164: le'u gsum pa 'dis theg pa sna tshogs pa'i lta ba ston pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:1165: le'u bzhi pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:1166: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1171: phyung ngo bar le'u'i gzhung la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1175: yi ge ji ltar byung ba'i tshul /
NK071(du)001:1177: lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba /
NK071(du)001:1180: a ka kha sogs nas e oo bar /
NK071(du)001:1183: gsum pa lam pa'i dbang du sems sbyang ba la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:1185: yi ge gzhan la sbyang ba /
NK071(du)001:1186: de ye shes kyi rgyur bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1188: a rab tu brtan gyur sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1190: de las sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1193: bzhi pa yi ge don bshad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:1200: yi ge spyi'i don bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1201: bye brag bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i don bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1204: rang bzhin byed las nges tshig go /
NK071(du)001:1206: yi ge sku gsum gyi bdag nyid du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1207: de dag gi rdo rje gsum mtshon byed bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1209: dang po dmigs med chos skur bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1210: a ni stong dang sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1211: gnyis pa dbang sgyur longs skur bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1212: a nyid sna tshogs sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1213: gsum pa rol pa sna tshogs par snang ba sprul skur bstan pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)001:1214: dang po sprul sku'i gsung du bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1215: e ma ho ngo mtshar sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1216: gnyis pa sprul sku'i thugs su bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1217: dngos med sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1218: gsum pa sprul sku'i skur bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1219: dbyibs dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1220: gnyis pa de dag gis rdo rje gsum mtshon byed du bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1221: phyogs bcu dus bzhir sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1222: gnyis pa yi ge'i rang bzhin ni /
NK071(du)001:1223: sems kyi sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1225: dmigs med sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1228: gnyis pa bye brag gi don bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1230: khyab bya zhe gnyis kyi don bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1232: mgo ni sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:1234: a ni skye mched sogs nas /
NK071(du)001:1235: zhig pa yin zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:1236: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)001:1238: gnyis pa bsdus te bstan pa la bzhi /
NK071(du)001:1239: gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa /
NK071(du)001:1241: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:1245: a ho thabs dang nas a hohbar /
NK071(du)001:1247: rdo rje nas tshig tu 'o bar /
NK071(du)001:1252: de nas gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1253: chos thams cad gtan la phab pa de dang mtshon
NK071(du)001:1254: byed yi ge la brten nas 'bebs dgos pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:1255: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:1256: thams cad dgongs pa tha dad med de gcig tu
NK071(du)001:1257: gyur nas srid zhi mnyam pa chen po'i tshul du
NK071(du)001:1258: dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje dbyings su 'khor 'das
NK071(du)001:1259: kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye nas dag pa
NK071(du)001:1260: sangs rgyas par gyur pa'i ting nge 'dzin las dgongs
NK071(du)001:1261: pa mi g.yo bar bzhugs pas chos thams cad ngo
NK071(du)001:1262: bo med pa ming tsam du gnas pa'i don mtshon
NK071(du)001:1263: par byed pa yi ge 'phreng ba'i 'khor lo zhes
NK071(du)001:1264: bya ba 'di ston pa nyid kyi sku dang gsung
NK071(du)001:1265: dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung
NK071(du)001:1266: ngo // ah rang gi snang stong gnyis su med
NK071(du)001:1267: pa'i rang bzhin a yig dkar po gsal brtan gyi
NK071(du)001:1268: tshad brgyad dang ldan pa bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:1269: ji ltar na mi g.yo mi 'gyur mngon par mi 'gyur /
NK071(du)001:1270: cir yang 'gyur du rung ba ste /
NK071(du)001:1271: rab tu brtan par gyur pa'i tshad bzhi dang ldan
NK071(du)001:1272: pa'i a dkar po sal le sing nge lhag ge
NK071(du)001:1273: lhang nge ba ste gsal ba'i tshad bzhi dang ldan
NK071(du)001:1274: pa la blo gnas pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1275: spyod yul gyi snang zhen sbyong phyir de las shin
NK071(du)001:1276: tu phra ba'i a grangs med pa rnams spro bar
NK071(du)001:1277: bya'o // des phyogs bcu thams cad as gang bar snang yul du gsal bar gyur nas /
NK071(du)001:1278: 'phro gzhi'i a de la bsdus kyang gzhi dang mkha' khyab kyi a'i rang bzhin la /
NK071(du)001:1279: 'phel ba 'am 'grib pa med de ma 'dres par gsal zhing brtan pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:1280: a yig de las ming gi gzhi dang nga ro
NK071(du)001:1281: rnams gsal bar byed pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK071(du)001:1282: gnyis kyi tshogs kha dog gsal zhing 'od 'bar ba
NK071(du)001:1283: phyogs kun khyab par spro zhing bsdu ba'ang sngar a
NK071(du)001:1284: la ji ltar sbyangs pa de bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:1285: de ltar yi ge la sems sbyongs ba'i thabs 'di
NK071(du)001:1286: la 'bad pas ni rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub
NK071(du)001:1287: kyi rgyu ting nge 'dzin brtan pa nyid 'byung ste
NK071(du)001:1288: des 'bras bu ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyu byed pa
NK071(du)001:1289: yin no // yi ge'i 'khor lo'i 'phro gazhi'am rtsa
NK071(du)001:1290: ba a yig ni khong nas rang byung ba dang
NK071(du)001:1294: ljags las tsa tsha dza dz+nya nya /
NK071(du)001:1296: ta tha da d+ha na dang /
NK071(du)001:1300: gzhan sku'i cha nyi shu las /
NK071(du)001:1302: sha sha sa ha k+shah i +ai u +au /
NK071(du)001:1303: e ee o oo ste bcu bdun /
NK071(du)001:1304: mgo rig shad ste khyab byed kyi yi ge gsum dang nyi shu 'thon te /
NK071(du)001:1305: de dag 'byung khung dang sbyar tshul 'grel pa sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:1306: yi ge 'di dag phyung ba tsam gyi mthus 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa /
NK071(du)001:1308: mtha' dbus sogs phan tshun mtho dam'i rnam pa drug
NK071(du)001:1309: tu g.yos cher rab tu g.yos ches cher kun tu
NK071(du)001:1310: g.yos pas dngos po'i 'khrul pa zhig nas 'khor 'das
NK071(du)001:1311: kyi chos thams cad ming du btags pa las don
NK071(du)001:1312: gyi ngo bo ma grub pa'i mtshan nyid tsam du
NK071(du)001:1313: gyur to // de ltar gyur pa la mnyes pas hoh zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)001:1314: yi ge la sems sbyong ba sogs bstan pa'i rjes
NK071(du)001:1315: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag
NK071(du)001:1316: nyid ston pa yi ge'i don bshad kyi ched du
NK071(du)001:1318: yi ge a ni stong pa dang mi stong pa
NK071(du)001:1319: gnyis kyi mtha' dang bral bar ma zad zung 'jug
NK071(du)001:1320: dbu ma tsam du'ang dmigs su yod pa ma yin
NK071(du)001:1321: pas / de ltar gtan la pheb pas chos thams
NK071(du)001:1322: cad ming du btags pa tsam las don bsam brjod
NK071(du)001:1323: kyi yul las 'das pa ni sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK071(du)001:1325: de'i rang gdangs yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo nyid
NK071(du)001:1326: kyang chos sku'i ngang la gnas pa las gzhan du
NK071(du)001:1327: ma g.yos / yi ge'i 'byung khung a nyid kyis
NK071(du)001:1328: go phye bas sna tshogs par snang ba'i tshul ni
NK071(du)001:1329: ngag gi 'du byed kyi dbang las ka la sogs
NK071(du)001:1330: pa bzhi bcu gnyis su snang ba'ang sgra yi nga
NK071(du)001:1331: ro dbyangs dang ming gzhi gsal byed kyi yi ge
NK071(du)001:1332: ji snyed pa thams cad 'dir de snyed du bsdus
NK071(du)001:1333: ma g.yos / pa ste / de'ang sangs rgyas bzhi
NK071(du)001:1334: bcu rtsa gnyis su mngon par rdzogs par mnga' mdzad
NK071(du)001:1335: pa'i rgyal po de kho na nyid longs sku'i ngo
NK071(du)001:1336: ma g.yos / pa ste / bor nges pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1337: e ma ho zhes yi ge'i 'khor lo shin tu
NK071(du)001:1338: ngo mtshar zhing ches ya mtshan gyi gnas te ci'i
NK071(du)001:1339: ma g.yos / pa ste / bor nges pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1340: phyir na / cho 'phrul chen po mnga' ba'i yi
NK071(du)001:1341: ge zhe gnyis kyi steng du khyab byed gsum bsnan
NK071(du)001:1342: pas bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i tshogs 'di dag 'dus pa
NK071(du)001:1343: las ming dang tshig rnams byung zhing /
NK071(du)001:1344: de 'dus pa las ngag gi rnam pa ma lus pa 'dzin pa'i gnas su gyur te /
NK071(du)001:1345: gang 'dul sprul sku'i gsung rgya che ba theg pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1346: thabs brjod bya'i don chen po 'dul bya'i snang ngor smra zhing gzhan la ston pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:1347: yi ger snang dus nyid nas bden pa'i dngos po med de /
NK071(du)001:1348: ci phyir na yi ge'i rang bzhin sems nyid yin pas /
NK071(du)001:1349: sems kyi rang bzhin bdag med cing spros pa'i mtha'
NK071(du)001:1350: dang bral bas cir yang mi dmigs pa thugs kyi
NK071(du)001:1352: brdar btags pa yi ge'i dbyibs dang kha dog la
NK071(du)001:1353: brten nas ngo bo ming tshig sna tshogs kyi rnam
NK071(du)001:1354: 'phrul las lha bskyed pa'i sa bon dang /
NK071(du)001:1355: glegs bam gyi snang brnyan sogs thugs rje'i rol pa
NK071(du)001:1356: cir yang snang bas sprul sku'i mdzad pa sgrub cing
NK071(du)001:1357: ston pa'i phrin las can no //
NK071(du)001:1358: phyogs bcu dus bzhir 'gro don la gshegs shing bzhugs
NK071(du)001:1359: pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyang ye shes sems dpa'i
NK071(du)001:1360: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor zhe gnyis su 'dus pa
NK071(du)001:1361: khyab byar byas pa'i de re re la khyab byed
NK071(du)001:1362: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1363: zhe gnyis khyab byed gsum dang bcas te bzhi bcu
NK071(du)001:1365: de yang yi ge'i mgo shar rig gsum dang /
NK071(du)001:1366: ka nas k+sha'i gsal byed so bzhi /
NK071(du)001:1367: i sogs dbyangs brgyad dril bas /
NK071(du)001:1368: khyab bya'i yi ge zhe gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1369: mdor na a'i cho 'phrul yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa
NK071(du)001:1370: lnga la 'dus shing rdzogs pas chos sku'i rol ba
NK071(du)001:1371: gzugs sku'i dkyil 'khor mtshon byed ni yi ge'o //
NK071(du)001:1372: de yang sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba nyid yi ger snang ba ste /
NK071(du)001:1373: de las gzhan du yi ge zhes dngos por grub pa /
NK071(du)001:1375: cir yang dmigs med kyi yi ge de nyid kyang
NK071(du)001:1376: rol ba sna tshogs pa'i yi ge sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)001:1377: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo chen por ma 'gags pa
NK071(du)001:1378: ste / des ye nas sku gsung thugs su lhun
NK071(du)001:1379: gyis grub pa ni ngo mtshar gyi gnas ya mtshan
NK071(du)001:1380: ste / / zhing cho 'phrul chen por snang ba'i
NK071(du)001:1381: dngos grub nyid rang rig pa'i mngon sum du rab
NK071(du)001:1383: yul chos dbyings la yul can mtshan med shes rab
NK071(du)001:1384: kyi dbyings kyis bya rtsol med par bris pa ste
NK071(du)001:1385: / ye nas lhun grub kyis grub pa'i yi ge'i sprin 'gyur ba med pa dang ldan pas /
NK071(du)001:1386: yi ge zhes pa'i ming ni de'i phyir tha snyad tsam du brjod pa ste /
NK071(du)001:1387: mtshon byed yi ge mgo ni ber ka ris te /
NK071(du)001:1389: ma nor ba gnyis med ye shes kyi rang bzhin thugs rdo rje mtshon /
NK071(du)001:1390: byed las ni yi ge'i mgo 'dren cing 'jug pa'i sgor gyur pas lam dang 'dra ba yin te /
NK071(du)001:1391: yi ge tig ni tsheg ste don shes rab brjod med kyi rang bzhin gsungs rdo rje /
NK071(du)001:1392: byed las yi ge rnams 'dus pa dbyangs kyis bcings
NK071(du)001:1393: pas dngos po so so'i ming du grub pa ma
NK071(du)001:1395: yi ge shad ni don thabs snying rje chen pos 'dul ba'i rang bzhin sku rdo rje /
NK071(du)001:1396: byed las rkang pa sdeb nas tshigs su gcod par byed pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1397: yi ge a ni chos thams cad skyed med de
NK071(du)001:1398: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings bya ba mo kun tu bzang
NK071(du)001:1399: mo dang / tha yig ni sgyu ma lta bu
NK071(du)001:1400: rnam shes chos dbyings ye shes su dag pa phyag
NK071(du)001:1401: rgyar 'phrul pa rdo rje mi bskyod pa nyid dang
NK071(du)001:1402: mo dang / / de bzhin du phung lnga dag pa ye shes lnga rigs lngar sbyar te /
NK071(du)001:1403: ta ni me long ye shes kyi phyag rgyar snang bas sgyu 'phrul lha rnam snang nyid dang /
NK071(du)001:1404: da ni sgyu 'phrul mnyam nyid ye shes kyis re
NK071(du)001:1405: ba yid bzhin du skong ba'i phyag rgya rin 'byung
NK071(du)001:1406: nyid dang / d+ha ni sgyu 'phrul chos kun so
NK071(du)001:1407: sor gzigs pa rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya snang
NK071(du)001:1408: nyid dang / mtha' nyid dang / na ni 'dul
NK071(du)001:1409: bya'i don kun tu mthar phyin par mdzad pa'i sgyu
NK071(du)001:1410: 'phrul ye shes kyi phyag rgya don grub nyid do
NK071(du)001:1411: nyid dang / mtha' nyid dang / // tha ni
NK071(du)001:1412: dra ba ste yum rnams dbyings kyi phyag rgya yin
NK071(du)001:1413: pas chos can thams cad dang 'brel zhing /
NK071(du)001:1414: rnam pa'ang yab dang phan tshun thabs shes zung 'brel du bzhugs pa /
NK071(du)001:1415: chos nyid kyi mkha' la chos can thams cad mngon
NK071(du)001:1416: par rdzogs pa'i phyag rgya dbyings phyug ma nyid do
NK071(du)001:1417: // ta ni d+r+wa ba sra brtan pa'i khams yon
NK071(du)001:1418: tan gyi rten du gyur pa spyan ma nyid dang
NK071(du)001:1419: // / da ni dra ba lhag mthong gi me
NK071(du)001:1420: lham mer gsal ba gos dkar nyid dang d+ha ni
NK071(du)001:1421: d+r+wa ba mnyen cing 'khril ba chus yon tan sdud
NK071(du)001:1422: pa m+aa ma k+ai nyid dang /
NK071(du)001:1423: na ni d+r+wa ba kun tu g.yo zhing 'gyur bas gdul bya sgrol ba dam tshig sgrol ma'o //
NK071(du)001:1424: yul so sor rig pa sgo lnga'i rnam shes la 'dir thugs kyi sgras bstan te /
NK071(du)001:1425: ka ni spyan gyi rnam shes dag pas thugs kyi mchog sa snying /
NK071(du)001:1426: kha ni snyan gyi rnam shes dag pa thugs kyi mchog phyag rdor /
NK071(du)001:1427: ga ni shangs kyi rnam shes dag pa thugs kyi mchog nam snying /
NK071(du)001:1428: g+ha ni ljags kyi rnam shes dag pa thugs kyi mchog spyan ras gzigs /
NK071(du)001:1429: nga ni 'du shes kyi mthar thug gsang ba'i rnam
NK071(du)001:1430: shes kyis bde ba myong dus mig shes la sogs
NK071(du)001:1431: pa'i rtog pa gzhan 'gag pas thugs kyang 'jig par
NK071(du)001:1432: byed pa'o // ste gshin rje gshed do //
NK071(du)001:1433: phyi'i yul lnga la sku'i sgras bstan te /
NK071(du)001:1434: tsa ni spyan gyi yul gzugs rnam par dag pas sku yi mchog sgeg mo /
NK071(du)001:1435: tsha ni snyan gyi yul sgra dag pa sku yi mchog glu ma /
NK071(du)001:1436: dza ni shangs kyi yul dri dag pa sku yi
NK071(du)001:1437: mchog phreng ma dz+ha ni ljags kyi yul ro dag
NK071(du)001:1438: pa sku yi mchog gar ma /
NK071(du)001:1439: nya ni yul reg bya'i mthar thugs gsang ba'i pad+ma
NK071(du)001:1440: dang 'phrad pa'i dus yul gzhan gyi rtog pa 'gag
NK071(du)001:1441: pas sku yang 'jig par byed pa stobs chen po
NK071(du)001:1442: // yul dang shes pa gnyis phyi nang du brda
NK071(du)001:1443: sbyor ba dbang po lnga la gsung gi sgras bstan
NK071(du)001:1444: // te / pa ni spyan gyi dbang po dag pas gsung gi mchog byams pa /
NK071(du)001:1445: pha ni snyan gyi dbang po dag pas /
NK071(du)001:1446: gsung gi mchog sgrib sel ba ni shangs kyi dbang po dag pas gsung gi mchog kun bzang /
NK071(du)001:1447: b+ha ni ljags kyi dbang po dag pas gsung gi
NK071(du)001:1448: mchog 'jam dpal ma ni reg byed lus dbang gi
NK071(du)001:1449: mthar thug gsang ba'i dbang pos yul bzhir 'dzin pa'ang
NK071(du)001:1450: mi gnas pas gsung yang 'jig par byed pa rta
NK071(du)001:1451: mgrin no // ya ni da lta ba skye ba'i
NK071(du)001:1452: go 'byed byed 'das pa'i dus rnam par dag pa
NK071(du)001:1453: mgrin no // spos ma / wa ni gnas bzhin
NK071(du)001:1454: pa da lta ba'i dus dag pa me tog ma
NK071(du)001:1455: mgrin no // spos ma / yin no // ra
NK071(du)001:1456: ni da lta ba 'di 'jig pa ma 'ongs pa'i
NK071(du)001:1459: la ni dus gsum gang du'ang tha snyad gdags rung
NK071(du)001:1460: gis stong pa ma nges pa'i dus dag pa dri
NK071(du)001:1461: chab ma'o // sha ni chos la rtag par 'dzin
NK071(du)001:1462: pa dag pa ste lcags kyu ma sha ni chad
NK071(du)001:1463: par 'dzin pa'ang yod ma yin pa ste zhags pa
NK071(du)001:1464: chab ma'o // ma / sa ni bdag gnyis su
NK071(du)001:1465: 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang bral bas bdag med pa ste
NK071(du)001:1466: lcags sgrog ma ha ni mtshan ma med pa'i chos
NK071(du)001:1467: nyid du 'dzin pa'ang dag pa dril bu ma'o //
NK071(du)001:1468: k+sha ni rnam shes ye shes su dag pa thugs
NK071(du)001:1469: kyi bdag nyid rang byung ye shes kyi thugs rigs
NK071(du)001:1470: drug pa kun tu bzang po dang /
NK071(du)001:1471: i ni rdul phra rab ji snyed pa de snyed
NK071(du)001:1472: kyi lha rnams kyi gnas su 'dul byed brgya byin
NK071(du)001:1473: dang / +ai ni rdul snyed lha ma yin gyi thub pa thag bzang ris /
NK071(du)001:1474: u ni rdul snyed mi rnams kyi gnas su shaka thub /
NK071(du)001:1475: +au ni rdul snyed byol song rnams kyi thub pa seng ge rab brtan /
NK071(du)001:1476: e ni rdul snyed yi dwags kyi gnas su kha 'bar /
NK071(du)001:1477: ee ni rdul snyed dmyal ba'i thub pa chos kyi rgyal po rnams su bstan nas 'dul ba'o //
