NK071(du)001:1478: o ni lus dbang shes gsum 'dus pa reg pa'i
NK071(du)001:1479: mthar thug gsang ba'i khams gsum gyi rtog pa thams
NK071(du)001:1480: cad bde ba'i ngang du 'jig par byed cing oo
NK071(du)001:1481: ni bde ba'ang stong par grol bas rtog pa thams
NK071(du)001:1482: cad mi gnas par zhig pa yin te rgyu 'bras
NK071(du)001:1483: ro gcig pas yi ge gnyis po de bdud rtsi
NK071(du)001:1485: de ltar gsung yi ge 'khor lo'i tshogs chen 'di
NK071(du)001:1486: rnams kyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)001:1487: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i phreng ba rnams
NK071(du)001:1490: de ltar gsung yi ge'i 'khor lo gtan la phab pa la dgyes pas /
NK071(du)001:1491: a hohzhesa ngo mtshar bar bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1492: rgyas par bstan pa de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:1493: yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su med
NK071(du)001:1494: pa'i rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi
NK071(du)001:1495: don rtogs dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston pa'i
NK071(du)001:1496: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rigs lnga dbyer
NK071(du)001:1497: mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)001:1498: a skye med shes rab hohdagyesa pa thabs te zung 'jug yi ge'i 'khor lo la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:1499: de yang thabs dang shes rab snang stong dbyer med
NK071(du)001:1500: du sbyor ba'i dgyes sprin byang chub sems kyi rang
NK071(du)001:1501: bzhin a las yi ge tshogs la sems sbyong ba'i
NK071(du)001:1503: gsung mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo yi ge'i sprin
NK071(du)001:1504: dang rdo rje gsum gyi phyag rgya rmad du byung
NK071(du)001:1505: ba'i 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su
NK071(du)001:1506: smin pas don gnyis grub pa ste /
NK071(du)001:1507: de ltar yi ge'i sgo nas zab rgyas kyi don ston pa la ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK071(du)001:1508: chos thams cad ming gi tshogs pa tsam las ngo bo ma grub na'ang /
NK071(du)001:1509: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni rgyal ba zhe gnyis kyi rang bzhin du grub pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1510: yi ge yang gsar du 'dus ma byas pa sems
NK071(du)001:1511: kyi chos nyid dmigs pa dang bral ba de lta
NK071(du)001:1512: na'ang / lam pa'i ngor yi ge de dag 'dus byas ltar dbyibs sogs ma 'gag par snang ba /
NK071(du)001:1513: sangs rgyas kyi rdo rje gsum dbyer med pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:1514: 'khor thams cad gsung yi ge'i 'khor los mngon du
NK071(du)001:1515: 'byin pa las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig ste /
NK071(du)001:1516: de ltar rdo rje gsum gyi dam las 'da' bar
NK071(du)001:1517: mi mdzad pas 'bras bu sku dang ye shes sogs
NK071(du)001:1518: dngos grub mi 'grub pa'i dbang med de /
NK071(du)001:1519: 'grub byed kyi rgyu lta ba dang rkyen sgom pa'i
NK071(du)001:1520: ting nge 'dzin 'a tshogs pa'i mthu chen po las
NK071(du)001:1521: 'bras bu mngon du thob pa chos nyid yin pa'i
NK071(du)001:1522: phyir ro // gong du bshad pa'i thabs dang shes
NK071(du)001:1523: rab sogs nas yi ge'i 'khor lo'i bsdu tshig go
NK071(du)001:1524: phyir ro // / de ltar bsdus pa a hoh zhes ngo mtshar bas mnyes pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1525: yi ge 'khor lo bkod pa'i don rnams rdo rje
NK071(du)001:1526: 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o
NK071(du)001:1527: // chos thams cad ming tsam du gnas pa'i yi
NK071(du)001:1528: ge'i phreng ba'ii 'khor lo'i don thams cad de tsam
NK071(du)001:1529: // du 'dus so // zhes ched du brjod pas
NK071(du)001:1530: gzhi 'bras kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK071(du)001:1531: cad yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor lo dang gnyis su
NK071(du)001:1533: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:1534: las 'dis chos thams cad ming tsam las don la
NK071(du)001:1535: ma grub pa mtshon byed yi ge phreng ba'i 'khor
NK071(du)001:1536: lo ston pa'i thugs rje dang /
NK071(du)001:1537: gdul bya'i sems nyid las rang snang bar bkod cing bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1540: zhi khro gnyis las zhi ba'i le'u /
NK071(du)001:1541: de la sngon byung ston pa'i rnams 'phrul dang /
NK071(du)001:1542: rjes 'jug gdul bya'i nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:1543: de rgyud kyi dngos po bcu dang sbyar ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)001:1544: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa /
NK071(du)001:1545: sgrub pa la bskyed rdzogs gnyis las bskyed rim /
NK071(du)001:1546: bskyed rim la'ang lam lnga las phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK071(du)001:1548: phra ba yig 'bru la bslab tshul zhi ba rgyu'i sa bon rdzogs par bstan pa yin te /
NK071(du)001:1549: 'og ma rnams la'ang tshul 'di ltar sbyar shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:1551: nges pa'i don nyid rtogs pa'i tshe //
NK071(du)001:1552: ming tsam snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK071(du)001:1553: yi ge 'khor lor mngon sangs rgyas //
NK071(du)001:1555: le'u gsum pas chos thams cad nges don du gtan
NK071(du)001:1556: la phab nas le'u bzhi pas ming tsam snang ba'i
NK071(du)001:1557: chos thams cad yi ge'i 'khor lor mngon par rdzogs
NK071(du)001:1558: par sangs rgyas par bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:1559: le'u lnga pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:1560: gsung ba'i lo rgyus su brjod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1564: de nas yi ge sogs nas /
NK071(du)001:1565: brjod do bar gnyis pa gzhung dngos la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:1566: gang gi bsgrub pa rten gyi gang zag /
NK071(du)001:1567: rtogs goms kyi thabs kyis ji ltar 'grub tshul /
NK071(du)001:1568: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:1570: ston pa mchod brtson sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1572: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba /
NK071(du)001:1573: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin /
NK071(du)001:1574: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK071(du)001:1576: rtogs pa'i thabs la gdams pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1577: rtogs bya lta ba'i ngo bo bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1579: gang gi dmigs med sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1581: gzhi rtsa med pa sogs rkang pa bdun /
NK071(du)001:1582: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin la drug ste /
NK071(du)001:1583: ci'i phyir bsgom pa'i dgos ched /
NK071(du)001:1584: ji ltar bsgom pa'i thabs de nyid thams cad du rang snang ba /
NK071(du)001:1585: de las dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor bsgom pa /
NK071(du)001:1586: de nyid lhar dag pas blangs dor dang bral bar dpes bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:1587: de la 'dres par bslab pas 'bras bu la mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK071(du)001:1589: dngos rnams sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1591: gang gi glang chen sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1593: rtsa ba med pa'i sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1595: thabs las sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:1596: lnga pa ni de nyid ye shes sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1598: sngags dang sogs rkang pa gnyis so //
NK071(du)001:1599: gsum pa mngon gyur 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1603: yon tan 'byung ba'i dngos grub drug /
NK071(du)001:1607: bdud rtsi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1609: nam mkha' sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:1610: gsum pa ni dgugs dang sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:1611: gnyis pa mchog gi dngos grub la bstan bshad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1613: sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor sogs gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1614: dus gsum sogs rkang pa drug gsum pa gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:1615: zhes brjod pas sogs nas gyur to bar /
NK071(du)001:1618: de dang 'grel ba'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:1619: gsung yi ge'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas bshad
NK071(du)001:1620: ma thag gi yi ge'i 'khor lo'i sprin bkod pa'i
NK071(du)001:1621: mthu las thabs shes zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul lha'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:1622: 'khor dang / las dang dngos grub sgrub pa'i rim rnam par 'phro ba 'di ched du brjod do //
NK071(du)001:1623: gzhi dang rtsa ba gang du'ang grub pa med pa'i sems kyi chos nyid ni /
NK071(du)001:1624: ma 'gag pas 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin par nges nas /
NK071(du)001:1625: de ltar skye 'gag med pa'i sems nyid du rang
NK071(du)001:1626: snang ba las 'dir yi ge a'i rang bzhin du
NK071(du)001:1627: sgom ste / yi ge de las a phra mo
NK071(du)001:1628: dang ka la sogs pa'i 'phro 'du la sems sbyong
NK071(du)001:1629: ba ji ltar yid bzhin nor bu'i char 'bebs pa
NK071(du)001:1630: la rin chen gyi khams las grub pa'i sprin dgos
NK071(du)001:1631: sgom ste / pa bzhin du / dkyil 'khor spro
NK071(du)001:1632: ba'i rgyu phra ba yig 'bru la bslab pa zhes
NK071(du)001:1633: sgom ste / pa bzhin du / bya'o // rtogs
NK071(du)001:1634: tshogs sgyu 'phrul lha'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK071(du)001:1635: rnams thabs shes zung 'brel d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor rang
NK071(du)001:1636: rig mngon sum gyi yul du rdzogs par gsal bas
NK071(du)001:1637: bsgrub bya phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba yon tan
NK071(du)001:1638: rdzogs pas gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol ba'i
NK071(du)001:1639: phyir rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1640: thams cad yongs su 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:1642: zas dug can a yig bkod de 'ju 'dul gyis
NK071(du)001:1643: sman mchog bdud rtsir 'gyur ba zos pas 'dod bya
NK071(du)001:1645: gzhan ji ltar dmigs pa ltar 'byung ba dang /
NK071(du)001:1646: nad pa'i lus la yi ge bkod pa'i 'phro 'dus
NK071(du)001:1647: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad thams cad sel cing bde
NK071(du)001:1648: ba dang / tram las rin po che'i gter du
NK071(du)001:1649: bsam pas longs spyod ci 'dod 'byung zhing 'byung ba'i
NK071(du)001:1650: yi gsum gyi 'phro 'dus ngan song sbyong ba dang
NK071(du)001:1651: gang dang cir snang ba'i chos kyi rnam pa yang
NK071(du)001:1652: de dang mi mthun pa'i snang ba gzhan bye ma
NK071(du)001:1653: las gser du 'gyur pa sogs 'grub pa yin no
NK071(du)001:1654: ba dang / // 'grel sgrub ltar na nam mkha'
NK071(du)001:1655: la h'u zhes rdo rje'i skas bsam na sra ba'i
NK071(du)001:1656: ba dang / // skas 'byung zhing / lag mthil
NK071(du)001:1657: du ram bkod pas 'bar ba ye shes kyis mer
NK071(du)001:1658: gyur nas tha mal gyi me yang tshig par 'gyur
NK071(du)001:1659: ba dang / // skas 'byung zhing / ba dang
NK071(du)001:1660: / kham bkod pas ye shes kyi chur 'gyur pas
NK071(du)001:1661: tha mal gyi chur 'bab pa'ang dag par byed pa
NK071(du)001:1663: yam bkod pas 'jig rten khams ni /
NK071(du)001:1664: gzhan du 'thor bar byed pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1665: yi ge es khams thams cad stong par byed cing steng 'og tu 'phen pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1668: gzungs ma sogs bsgrub bya 'gugs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1669: yul gzhan du btang ste bskrad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1670: dgra rkun sogs bcing pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1671: byad bcing sogs dgrol ba dang /
NK071(du)001:1672: nad pa gso ba dang dgra sogs bsad pa dang gzhan de pham pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1673: rang sde rgyal bar bya ba sogs las dang thun
NK071(du)001:1674: mong gi dngos grub de rnams thams cad phyag rgya
NK071(du)001:1675: gcig spros kyi ting nge 'dzin 'di la brten pa
NK071(du)001:1676: thob pa yis byed nus par 'gyur zhing de nyid
NK071(du)001:1677: rang rig pa'i ye shes las rang snang ba'i phyir
NK071(du)001:1678: na yi ge dang ming tshig gis bsdus pa'i sa
NK071(du)001:1679: bon las gzugs kyi cha shas rdzogs pa'i skur sgom
NK071(du)001:1680: pa sogs yid la ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin ting
NK071(du)001:1681: nge 'dzin la 'dod dgu byar yod pa'i yon tan
NK071(du)001:1682: gyis dpe ni mun nag la sgron mes snang ba
NK071(du)001:1683: byung ba ji lta ba de bzhin du rtogs tshogs
NK071(du)001:1685: lcags gser du 'gyur ba gser 'gyur gyi rtsis theb pa ltar /
NK071(du)001:1686: 'byung lnga yum lnga'i rang bzhin dang /
NK071(du)001:1687: bcud len gyi rtsis dug sman gyi rang bzhin du
NK071(du)001:1688: 'gyur ba'i tshul dug lnga ye shes lngar grol ba'o
NK071(du)001:1689: // mthar lam ston pa po bla ma rdo rje
NK071(du)001:1690: slob dpon mchod pa la brtson zhing phan nus zab
NK071(du)001:1691: mo'i dbang gsum thob pas rgyud smin pa /
NK071(du)001:1692: lta ba bden gnyis dbyer med rtogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1693: don sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba rtsa ba
NK071(du)001:1694: dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams dang sngags gsum
NK071(du)001:1696: rim pa ltar ma nyams pa dang legs par shes
NK071(du)001:1697: shing sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad dang ldan pas
NK071(du)001:1699: chos de dag dang mi ldan pas sgrub kyang don
NK071(du)001:1700: med par ma zad sgrub po rang nyid brlag par
NK071(du)001:1701: 'gyur ro // snang spyod thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi ngo bor gsal ba ni /
NK071(du)001:1702: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK071(du)001:1703: de dag gis thugs su chud pa'i don de /
NK071(du)001:1704: rnal 'byor pa'i lta ba'ang yin la /
NK071(du)001:1705: thun mong gi grub pa las khyad par du gyur
NK071(du)001:1706: pa dngos grub mchog gi sgrub bya'i snying po'i mngon
NK071(du)001:1707: du gyur pa'i yon tan ni ngo bo nyid kyis
NK071(du)001:1708: rtag pa'i phyir / thob nas zad pa'i dus med
NK071(du)001:1709: pas yid bzhin nor bu'i mdzod ltar 'phel 'grib gyi
NK071(du)001:1710: 'gyur ba med par byung ba yin te /
NK071(du)001:1711: don dam par dngos por grub pa med pa'i ngang
NK071(du)001:1712: las gdul bya'i ngor dngos po ltar snang ba'i sprin
NK071(du)001:1713: las dngos grub sna tshogs pa'i rnam par 'byung zhing
NK071(du)001:1714: / don mdzad pa'i phrin las cir yang 'gyur ba'o //
NK071(du)001:1715: 'di ltar dngos por snang ba'i chos rnams snang dus
NK071(du)001:1716: nyid na dngos por grub pa rdul tsam yang med
NK071(du)001:1717: par / rtogs pa'i don la rang dbang sgyur ba'i thabs ni ting nge 'dzin yin no //
NK071(du)001:1718: gang zag gang gis sems nyid gang du'ang dmigs su
NK071(du)001:1719: med pa'i don mi shes pa de yis chos kyi
NK071(du)001:1720: dbyings kyi gnas lugs zab mo mi shes la /
NK071(du)001:1721: rgyu mtshan de'i phyir phyi nang gi grub mtha' dngos por lta ba rnams dang /
NK071(du)001:1723: 'dzin pa de rnams sems nyid mtha' bral gyi ngang
NK071(du)001:1724: der 'jig pa'i tshul rtogs pas chos rnams kyi rang
NK071(du)001:1725: bzhin dmigs med bsam brjod dang bral ba'i don de
NK071(du)001:1726: nyid shes par gyis shig ces gdams so //
NK071(du)001:1727: brten pa'i gzhi dang bskyed pa'i rtsa ba med pa'i sems nyid gnyug ma'i rang bzhin ni /
NK071(du)001:1728: 'di zhes cir yang gdags su med de /
NK071(du)001:1729: pho mo ma yin la de bzhin du ma ning
NK071(du)001:1730: yang min la de las gzhan du mtshan med yang
NK071(du)001:1731: ma yin / 'gro ba'i rigs dang mi rgyud sogs kyang min no //
NK071(du)001:1732: dkar dmar sogs kha dog ma yin la /
NK071(du)001:1733: zlum po sogs dbyibs kyang ma yin /
NK071(du)001:1734: brten bya gnas dang rten byed kyi rdzas sogs dngos
NK071(du)001:1735: dngos med kyi chos su grub pa ma yin te
NK071(du)001:1736: / mdor na gang yang min pa ni chos nyid
NK071(du)001:1737: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings rnam rang byung gi ye
NK071(du)001:1738: / shes te / de nyid gzhi mngon du byas
NK071(du)001:1739: pa las mi 'da' ba thabs kyi phyag rgya lam
NK071(du)001:1741: ba kun gyi gazhi'am rgyu ste ci'i phyir na sems
NK071(du)001:1742: kyi chos nyid las gzhan du gyur pa'i chos 'ga'
NK071(du)001:1744: rtsa ba'i thabs rang rig yi ger snang ba las /
NK071(du)001:1745: rten gyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba gzhi'i thabs byung
NK071(du)001:1746: zhing der brten pa lha sgom pa ni thabs bsam
NK071(du)001:1748: de ni rags pa lha sku la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1749: de ltar thabs gsum dang ldan pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams
NK071(du)001:1750: rang rig ye shes kyi cho 'phrul du snang bas
NK071(du)001:1751: bzang ngan tha dad par grub pa min kyang /
NK071(du)001:1752: rnam pa gtso bo las tha dad pa'i 'khor sogs
NK071(du)001:1753: nang brten pa lha dang nang gi phyi rol rten
NK071(du)001:1755: snang ba rnam par 'byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)001:1756: dkyil 'khor zhi ba la tshom bu steng sogs phyag
NK071(du)001:1757: rgya spros pa mkha' khyab bsam yas kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1758: du sgom pa de rnams rang rig ye shes kyi
NK071(du)001:1759: rol par shar bas 'khor ba dang tshogs lam gyi
NK071(du)001:1761: spyod yul yongs dag kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog de
NK071(du)001:1762: nas ma btab pa ci yang med pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)001:1763: // sgom pa po gang gi ma dul ba'i glang
NK071(du)001:1764: chen chang gis myos pa dang 'dra ba'i sems 'khrul
NK071(du)001:1765: rtogs kyi myos pa'i las su mi rung ba 'di
NK071(du)001:1766: // nyid / ji ltar glang rdzi mkhas pas lcags
NK071(du)001:1767: kyu la sogs pa'i thabs kyis btul na thul ba
NK071(du)001:1768: // nyid / ltar / gdams ngag gam shes rab
NK071(du)001:1769: kyi stobs kyis mnyam par bzhag pas btul ba na
NK071(du)001:1770: dngos dang mtshan 'dzin gyi 'khrul rtogs thams cad zhi
NK071(du)001:1771: nas gzhi ji lta ba bzhin klongs su pheb pa
NK071(du)001:1772: // nyid / ltar / ni thul ba'o // phyag
NK071(du)001:1773: rgya gcig spros kyi skabs su sngags kyi yan lag
NK071(du)001:1774: lnga dang ldan pa'i lha sku phyag rgya chen po'i
NK071(du)001:1775: ting nge 'dzin la 'dris par bslab pa rkyen gyi
NK071(du)001:1776: mi 'phrog pa'i gsal snang la rab tu brtan zhing
NK071(du)001:1777: goms pa na dngos grub ya mtshan chen po rnams
NK071(du)001:1779: de ltar sgyu 'aphrulala dra ba bsgrub pa'i rim pa'ang
NK071(du)001:1780: shes 'jug mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid gsum po der
NK071(du)001:1781: 'dus so // zhes ched du brjod pas 'khor gyi
NK071(du)001:1782: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ting nge 'dzin las dngos
NK071(du)001:1783: grub sna tshogs yul med rang gsal du shar ba'i
NK071(du)001:1784: gzigs mos mnyes par gyur to //
NK071(du)001:1785: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:1786: las 'dis zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dngos grub
NK071(du)001:1787: thams cad sgrub pa'i thabs ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u
NK071(du)001:1789: zhes pa'i spyi'i don skabs zhi ba rjes 'jug gdul bya'i nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:1790: dngos po bcu las de kho na nyid lta ba las dngos grub sgrub pa'i lta ba /
NK071(du)001:1791: spyod pa'i skabs dngos grub sgrub pa'i spyod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1792: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa las /
NK071(du)001:1793: sgrub par bya ba dngos grub kyi rnam grangs bcas bstan /
NK071(du)001:1794: bi ma las mngon rdzogs yi ge de nyid las /
NK071(du)001:1795: ting nge 'dzin rol mo mtha' yas spro /
NK071(du)001:1797: le'u bzhi par chos thams cad /
NK071(du)001:1798: yi ge'i 'khor lo mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par bstan pa'i yi ge de nyid las /
NK071(du)001:1799: ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo mtha' yas pa spro bar bstan to //
NK071(du)001:1800: le'u drug pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:1805: de nas de bzhin nas 'di brjod do bar /
NK071(du)001:1806: gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1811: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin sku'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:1812: rang bzhin nam 'bras bu mthar phyin sku'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK071(du)001:1814: ye shes phyogs sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1818: dkyil 'khor gyi che ba bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1821: gnyis pa la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:1824: rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:1825: gdan gang la ji ltar bzhugs tshul /
NK071(du)001:1828: sku mdog zhi tshul 'od dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1830: seng ge sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1832: 'khor lo rgyal po sogs rkang pas dman pas tshigs bcad gsum gsum pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1833: rdo rje sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:1835: mthing ga sogs rkang pa drug /
NK071(du)001:1836: gsum pa dkyil 'khor gyi che ba bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1837: mtha' dbus sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1838: gsum pa rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin sku'i dkyil 'khor bzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:1842: de gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:1844: sku'i phyag rgya sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:1845: gnyis pa sku'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1846: sku ji ltar snang ba'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)001:1849: de tshe mi mthun sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:1850: gnyis pa sku'i mdzad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1851: de tshe 'gro drug sogs rkang pa bcu /
NK071(du)001:1852: gsum pa 'bras bu thob tshul la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:1854: gsang sngags kyi thob tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:1856: sgrib pa sbyangs pas grol tshul ni /
NK071(du)001:1857: me long bstan pa'i sogs rkang pa bdun /
NK071(du)001:1859: de ltar thob pa'i 'bras bu'i ngo bo sku gsum ni /
NK071(du)001:1860: chos sku sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:1861: gnyis pa sngags kyi thob tshul la'ang gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:1862: mthar thug gi sa'i khyad par ni /
NK071(du)001:1863: mtshan dang dpe byad sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:1864: gnyis pa 'bras bu sku lngar bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1865: skye shis sogs rkang pa bdun /
NK071(du)001:1866: bzhi pa gsungs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:1869: gnyis pa bsdus te bstan pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:1870: lo rgyus brjod pa bsdu ba dngos /
NK071(du)001:1871: gsang sngags mtshon pa'i tshig go /
NK071(du)001:1876: gsum pa ni zhes rdo rje sogs /
NK071(du)001:1878: de lta'i gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:1879: snga mar thabs gsum mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:1880: de nas gzhi dang bsam gyi mi khyab kyi thabs gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:1882: 'bras bu rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor gnyis rgyas par
NK071(du)001:1883: bston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi
NK071(du)001:1884: rang bzhin gcig dang du ma med pas ma 'dres
NK071(du)001:1885: yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid chen po sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:1886: thams cad kyi spyi gzugs ston pas 'dul bar bya
NK071(du)001:1887: ba'i yul 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad
NK071(du)001:1889: 'dul byed ston pa nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK071(du)001:1890: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par dbyung bar
NK071(du)001:1891: bzhed nas 'khor gyi ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK071(du)001:1892: do // rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin la phyogs ris med kyang /
NK071(du)001:1893: ye shes lnga'i mtshon byed phyogs bzhi dang dbus lnga'i tha snyad btags te /
NK071(du)001:1894: de ltar ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor de nyid dmigs med bsam brjod las 'das shing /
NK071(du)001:1895: mtha' yas pa'i chos kyi khyab byed du ma tsal
NK071(du)001:1896: lhun grub ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying por ye
NK071(du)001:1897: nas rdzogs pa'i chos nyid rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1898: chen po ste / de rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK071(du)001:1899: chos kun 'byung ba'i gzhi rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1900: chen po de nyid ting nge 'dzin gyi yul du
NK071(du)001:1901: byas te goms shing 'dres par bslab pa'i phyir sgom
NK071(du)001:1902: pa'i bya bas spyod cig pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1903: de nas rin po che'i gzhal yas khang sgom pa ste /
NK071(du)001:1904: de'ang ye shes lngas ma rig pa gcod pa'i rtags
NK071(du)001:1905: su nang gi gzhi 'khor lo rtsib bzhi dbus kyi
NK071(du)001:1907: de nyid spros bral chos nyid du zlum pas rdo rje rwa ba'i mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)001:1908: de'i phyir bden pa bzhi mtshon pa'i sgo bzhi gru chad bzhi brgyan pa /
NK071(du)001:1909: bden gnyis dbyer med mtshon pa'i bar khyams 'khor yug dang /
NK071(du)001:1910: yon tan kun tu rgyas pa'i rtags su dbyibs gru
NK071(du)001:1911: bzhi rnam thar bzhi mtshon pa'i sgo bzhi sgo khyud
NK071(du)001:1912: can rgyu 'bras kyi rta bab sogs rgyan dang ldan
NK071(du)001:1913: pa / ye shes kyi rtsal snang ma 'gags pa'i
NK071(du)001:1914: rol mo rtsigs pa lnga sbrag gi steng na mu
NK071(du)001:1915: tig gi d+r+wa ba sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:1916: gzhan yang rgyal mtshan sogs gzhal yas khang gi rgyan sna tshogs pas kun tu khrigs shing /
NK071(du)001:1917: gzhan yang gzugs rdo rje ma sogs mchod rdzas thogs
NK071(du)001:1918: pa'i lha mo sprin phung bzhin du gtibs pa bcas
NK071(du)001:1919: bkod pa khyad par 'phags pa ni rten gzhal yas
NK071(du)001:1920: khang dang / de nyid mdzes byed bdag po'i rgyan
NK071(du)001:1921: lha'i dkyil 'khor rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi
NK071(du)001:1923: dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsib bzhir mi
NK071(du)001:1924: 'jigs pa bzhi sogs mtshon byed seng ge glang chen
NK071(du)001:1925: rta dang khyung nam mkha' lding gi ste /
NK071(du)001:1926: shang shang rnams re re yang brgyad brgyad kyis btegs
NK071(du)001:1927: pa'i khri chen po la thabs shes rnam dag nyi
NK071(du)001:1929: de dag kyang 'dod dgu 'byung ba rin po che'i khri rkang mdzod mig bdun pas btegs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1930: so so'i gdan de dag la bzhugs tshul ji ltar
NK071(du)001:1931: zhe na rigs lnga yab lnga ni don gnyis kyi
NK071(du)001:1932: mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa sogs kyis yab yum
NK071(du)001:1933: bcu po ni rgyal po'i tshul ltar de dang de'i
NK071(du)001:1934: skyil krung du bzhugs shing sems dpa' rnams ni yab
NK071(du)001:1935: g.yas dang yum rnams g.yon cung zad brkyang pa'i phyed
NK071(du)001:1936: skyil te blon po'i tshul dang /
NK071(du)001:1937: bya byed gnyis rdo rje dang pad+ma'i skyil krung mthar
NK071(du)001:1938: byed rnams gyad kyi dor stabs thub drug bzhengs stabs
NK071(du)001:1939: kyi bzhugs pa'o // dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba
NK071(du)001:1940: dang rtsib bzhi la rgyal po rigs lnga rgyal mo
NK071(du)001:1941: ste yum lnga dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1942: gtso bo'i g.yas nas brtsams te rtsib mchan la rim pa ltar mthong bas snying dang /
NK071(du)001:1943: thos pa phyag rdor dang snom pa nam snying dang /
NK071(du)001:1944: myong ba spyan ras gzigs dang bzhi btsun mo 'ang
NK071(du)001:1945: rim par sgeg mo gar ma phreng ma glu ma'i
NK071(du)001:1947: de bzhin du gru chad bzhi la ni /
NK071(du)001:1948: shar lho nas rim par mthong byed byams pa dang /
NK071(du)001:1949: thos byed sgrib sel dang snom byed kun bzang dang /
NK071(du)001:1953: me tog ma mar me ma /
NK071(du)001:1954: dri chab ma'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas so //
NK071(du)001:1955: bar khyams la ni shar lho brgya byin sogs thub
NK071(du)001:1956: pa drug dang gzhan yang bar khyams de'i shar nub
NK071(du)001:1957: gtso bo'i mdun dang rgyab tu byed pa kun tu
NK071(du)001:1958: bzang po dang / bya ba bzang mo dag ni gnas par bstan to /
NK071(du)001:1959: sgo khyud bzhi la gdug pa can 'joms par byed
NK071(du)001:1960: pa'i shar sgor gshin rje gshed sogs bzhi ni lcags
NK071(du)001:1961: kyu ma sogs rang rang gi btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK071(du)001:1963: ye shes lnga mtshon pa rigs lnga'i rang rtags phyag mtshan ni /
NK071(du)001:1964: mi bskyod pa'i rdo rje rnam snang gi 'khor lo
NK071(du)001:1965: rin 'byung gi rin po che snang mtha'i pad+ma don
NK071(du)001:1966: grub kyi ral gri ye shes kyi yul dbyings kyi
NK071(du)001:1967: phyag rgya dril bu ste thams cad kyang 'od 'bar
NK071(du)001:1968: ba can no // sems dpa' rnams ni /
NK071(du)001:1969: 'jam dpal ut+pala byams pa klu shing la sogs rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan 'dzin pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1970: sems ma rnams ni mdzes pa'i 'jo sgeg gi tshul
NK071(du)001:1971: dang bcas te mnyes par byed pa'i mchod rdzas me
NK071(du)001:1973: sku mdog la dang po rigs kyi kha dog /
NK071(du)001:1974: mi bskyod pa mthing ga sogs kyis mtshon dkar po
NK071(du)001:1975: ser po le brgan te dmar po ljang gu dang
NK071(du)001:1976: de la sogs pa'i khong nas rigs gnyis 'dres sna
NK071(du)001:1977: tshogs pa'i sku mdog ni byams pa dkar ser sogs
NK071(du)001:1978: so // zhi ba'i tshul lha de dag kyang sku
NK071(du)001:1979: sha mnyen pa yan lag lcug pa'am dku skabs phyed
NK071(du)001:1980: cing 'tshams pa sku 'khril bag chags sku slod por
NK071(du)001:1981: ma gyur pa sku drang zhing ldem pa sku gzhon
NK071(du)001:1982: sha chags pa'i ngang tshul can /
NK071(du)001:1983: gtsang zhing gsal ba bkrag cing mtsher ba brjid cing
NK071(du)001:1984: yid du 'ong bas lhun sdug pa zil gyis mi
NK071(du)001:1985: non pas / gzi byin ldan pa ste /
NK071(du)001:1986: snga ma lnga ngo bo'i yon tan dang phyi ma bzhi rnam pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:1988: 'od zer kha dog sna tshogs phyogs bcur 'phro ba'i
NK071(du)001:1989: tshogs chen po dang khro bo rnams me ltar 'bar
NK071(du)001:1990: zhing rno ba'i 'od zer gyi phreng bas kun tu
NK071(du)001:1991: 'khrigs pa'i klong na bzhugs pa ste /
NK071(du)001:1992: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg pa'o //
NK071(du)001:1993: mtha' dbus med par chos thams cad la khyab pa'i
NK071(du)001:1994: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bsam brjod las 'das pas
NK071(du)001:1995: mtha' yas pa'i gnas lugs de nyid rtogs don sgom
NK071(du)001:1996: pa'i thabs lhag pa ting 'dzin la goms pa'i mthus
NK071(du)001:1997: 'bras bu rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:1999: yon tan gyi rten sku ste /
NK071(du)001:2000: 'bras bu sku lnga las mi 'da' zhing khyad par
NK071(du)001:2001: du 'gyur pa yi phyag rgya ches che ba'i mchog
NK071(du)001:2002: ni rigs drug pa nyid yin pa de las ldog
NK071(du)001:2003: cha sku lngar snang ba ni /
NK071(du)001:2004: gzhi chos dbyings de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos pa ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK071(du)001:2005: de ltar ma g.yos kyang sgrib gnyis bag chags dang
NK071(du)001:2006: bcas pa las yang dag par thar pa'i gzugs sku
NK071(du)001:2007: dag pa'i 'dul bya la snang ba'i longs sku dang
NK071(du)001:2008: / gdul bya'i 'gro ba ma lus pa dngos rgyud ci rig par 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:2009: de dag gi bsam pa dang mthun par byas pa'i
NK071(du)001:2010: sku'i bkod pa ni gcig tu ma nges par sna
NK071(du)001:2011: tshogs su ston pa'i sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK071(du)001:2012: de ltar ston pa nyid kyang dpe sgyu ma'i mig yor gyi tshul dang 'dra bar /
NK071(du)001:2013: gzugs sku gnyis su snang ba'i tshul de nyid kyang
NK071(du)001:2014: dbyings chos kyi sku las g.yos pa med pas sku
NK071(du)001:2015: gsum dbyer med rdo rje sku'o //
NK071(du)001:2016: de ltar chos sku las ma g.yos bzhin du gdul
NK071(du)001:2017: bya'i las dang mthun par sku sna tshogs su snang
NK071(du)001:2018: bas sku gsum snang cha ma 'dres pa'i mngon byang
NK071(du)001:2019: gi sku'o // sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i de'i
NK071(du)001:2020: tshe 'dul bya'i skal pa mi mthun pa sna tshogs
NK071(du)001:2021: gi sku'o // la / 'dul byed kyi sku so
NK071(du)001:2022: so'i rig pa dang 'dra bar snang ba ni de
NK071(du)001:2023: bzhin nyid kyi ngang las ma bcos kyang gdul bya'i
NK071(du)001:2024: skal pa dang sngon gyi las 'phro'i dbang gis sku
NK071(du)001:2026: dper na gzugs gcig me long du ma'i nang du so sor 'char ba'i /
NK071(du)001:2027: chu snod du mar zla gzugs gcig nyid so sor 'char ba bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:2028: sku de ltar snang nas don mdzad pa de'i tshe
NK071(du)001:2029: lha dang mi sogs 'gro drug gi sems can thams
NK071(du)001:2030: cad la 'dul byed sdig spong gi gzugs brgya byin
NK071(du)001:2031: dang 'khor lo'i bsgyur rgyal sogs su snang bar bstan
NK071(du)001:2034: dge tshul gyis mtshon pa'i nyan thos kyi rigs can
NK071(du)001:2035: rnams la nyan thos dgra bcom pa'i gzugs dang rang
NK071(du)001:2036: rgyal gyi rigs can rnams la bse ru lta bur
NK071(du)001:2037: rigs mthun pa'i tshul du bstan nas don mdzad do
NK071(du)001:2038: // de las gzhan yang rgyu dang 'bras bu'i theg
NK071(du)001:2039: pa mchog gi rigs can rnams la sh+aakya thub pa
NK071(du)001:2040: sogs 'dul byed kyi ston pa'ang gdul bya'i dbang po'i
NK071(du)001:2041: rim pa bzhin du bstan nas 'dul ba ni sprul
NK071(du)001:2042: // sku'i mdzad pa'o // longs sku'i mdzad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2043: gnas nges pa 'og min bla na med pa'i gnas
NK071(du)001:2044: gzugs khams las 'phags pa'i mchog tu ston pa nges
NK071(du)001:2045: pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni rnam par snang
NK071(du)001:2046: mdzad chen po'i tshul gyis 'khor nges pa sa bcu'i
NK071(du)001:2047: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la dus nges pa
NK071(du)001:2048: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor chos ston te /
NK071(du)001:2049: de'i sprul sku bzhin du chos rnams gsung mchog tshig tu mi smra ste /
NK071(du)001:2050: sku'i brda' yi chos nges pa theg pa chen po
NK071(du)001:2051: nyid 'khor rnams kyi blo la mjal bar ston no
NK071(du)001:2052: // ji ltar me long bstan pa'i nang du byad
NK071(du)001:2053: kyi dri ma snang ba'i tshul bzhin du byad dngos
NK071(du)001:2054: kyi mdog bzang po ngan par bsgyur ba'i dri ma
NK071(du)001:2055: thams cad ngos zin nas gdod sel bar byed pa
NK071(du)001:2056: de bzhin du 'khor rnams kyis bston pa de bzhin
NK071(du)001:2057: gshegs pa'i skur bltas pa na bla na med pa'i
NK071(du)001:2058: byang chub la sgrib par byed pa'i dri ma gting
NK071(du)001:2059: dpag med pa rnams me long la snang ba bzhin
NK071(du)001:2060: du ston pa sku la snang bas rang rgyud kyi
NK071(du)001:2061: sbyang bya'i dri ma ngos zin pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2062: de nas brtsams te mthong zin goms par byed pa
NK071(du)001:2063: sgom lam sa dgur lhan skyes kyi sgrib pa je
NK071(du)001:2065: sa bcu'i mi mthun phyogs rnams sbyong bas rim gyis
NK071(du)001:2066: 'byang ba ste dag pas sa bcu mthar phyin nas
NK071(du)001:2067: 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur bas rdo rje lta
NK071(du)001:2068: bu'i ting 'dzin thob ste shes sgrib phra ba bag
NK071(du)001:2069: nyal gyi dri ma bcom nas bla na med pa'i
NK071(du)001:2070: byang chub kun tu 'od kyi sa yang dag par
NK071(du)001:2071: thob bo // dag pa gnyis ldan chos kyi sku
NK071(du)001:2072: ni blos dpag tu med cing ngag gis brjod du
NK071(du)001:2073: med de nam mkha' lta bu'o //
NK071(du)001:2074: de'i ngang las longs spyod rdzogs sku ni rtag tu
NK071(du)001:2075: zad pa med pa yid bzhin nor bu rin chen
NK071(du)001:2076: gyi gter dang 'dra bar bzhugs pa dang sprul pa'i
NK071(du)001:2077: sku ni gang la gang 'dul gyi sku'i bkod pa
NK071(du)001:2078: bye ba phrag brgya sogs bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK071(du)001:2080: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dang dpe byed thams
NK071(du)001:2081: cad rdzogs shing spyod yul kun tu ye shes rang
NK071(du)001:2082: snang bde ba chen po'i man+dala zhes dkyil 'khor ro
NK071(du)001:2083: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang la
NK071(du)001:2084: ma zhen par shar ba'i phyir tshogs chen gnyis kyang
NK071(du)001:2085: ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs pas gdul bya gzhan snang
NK071(du)001:2086: du rnam par rol pa'i sprul pa ston par nus
NK071(du)001:2087: pa'i ye shes 'khor lo tshogs chen sprul sku'i sa'o
NK071(du)001:2088: // thabs 'gags med dkyil 'khor 'khor lo rab 'byams su 'char yang /
NK071(du)001:2089: dmigs pa dang bral bas gos pa med pa'i ye shes ni pad+ma can longs sku'i sa dang /
NK071(du)001:2090: sgrib bral gyi dgongs pa shes rab spros bral gyi
NK071(du)001:2091: ye shes ni thun mong ma yin pa'i sa yi
NK071(du)001:2092: mchog kun tu 'od de chos sku'i sa'o //
NK071(du)001:2093: de la sogs te sa'i grangs dang yon tan bsam
NK071(du)001:2094: yas pa'i mchog rdzogs pa mthar thug gi sa gsum
NK071(du)001:2095: po de rgyu'i theg pa'i kun tu 'od las khyad
NK071(du)001:2098: skye shi sogs spros dang bral ba'i ye shes 'gyur ba med pa'i yongs grub rtag brtan /
NK071(du)001:2099: g.yung drung gi sku ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK071(du)001:2100: 'gro ba nyon mongs pa can kun gyi bsod nams
NK071(du)001:2101: kyi zhing du gnas pa sprul pa'i sku'i snang brnyan
NK071(du)001:2102: gdul bya'i blo dang mthun par zad mi shes par
NK071(du)001:2103: 'byung pa'i gter du gyur pa ni longs spyod rdzogs
NK071(du)001:2104: pa'i sku'o // sku gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK071(du)001:2105: rje rang gi rig pa'i ngang du 'dul 'bral med
NK071(du)001:2106: par 'dzin pa'i sku ni rdo rje sku'o //
NK071(du)001:2107: chos thams cad rig pa'i ye shes su dbyer med
NK071(du)001:2108: pas mnyam pa nyid du gnas pa'i phyir sku gsum
NK071(du)001:2109: ma 'dres pa ni mngon byang ngo //
NK071(du)001:2110: chos can thams cad ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:2111: shes kyis gdul bya'i mos ngor brtan g.yo sna tshogs
NK071(du)001:2112: pa'i rnam par ston pa'i sku ni sprul pa'i sku
NK071(du)001:2113: ste mthar thug thun mong ma yin pa de'i tshe
NK071(du)001:2114: sku lnga po de dag kun kyang rdzogs par thob
NK071(du)001:2115: pas snga phyi med de sku dang sa lam ye
NK071(du)001:2116: shes phrin las zhes btags na'ang ngo bo tha mi
NK071(du)001:2117: dad par gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:2118: rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi don de skad ces
NK071(du)001:2119: brjod pas gdul bya'i yul 'jig rten drug gi phyogs
NK071(du)001:2120: bcu'i zhing mtha' yas mu med pa thams cad du
NK071(du)001:2121: 'dul byed sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par rol pa
NK071(du)001:2122: brjod kyi mi lang ba phyogs bcu'i zhing gi rdul
NK071(du)001:2123: snyed rang rig pa'i yul du gsal zhing snang bar
NK071(du)001:2124: gyur to // rgyas par bstan pa de nas de
NK071(du)001:2125: bzhin gshegs pa yab rnams yum btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK071(du)001:2126: gnyis su med pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi
NK071(du)001:2127: rang bzhin rtogs dka' ba'i gsang ba 'di nyid ston
NK071(du)001:2128: pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rigs lnga
NK071(du)001:2129: dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)001:2130: rang bzhin skye 'gag med pa lam dang 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba la /
NK071(du)001:2131: a ho zhes ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:2132: de'ang dmigs bya dbyings dang dmigs byed rang rig gnyis
NK071(du)001:2133: med dbyer med kyi ye shes tsam du'ang mi dmigs
NK071(du)001:2134: pas blos dpag med bsam gyis mi khyab par rtogs
NK071(du)001:2136: der ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa tshigs bcad gcig bsdu'o //
NK071(du)001:2137: gzhi rang byung gi ye shes la rang rig ting
NK071(du)001:2138: nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod kyis mi
NK071(du)001:2139: lang bar snang ba ste lo rgyus dang /
NK071(du)001:2140: dkyil 'khor ro ston pa'i tshigs bcad brgyad bsdu'o //
NK071(du)001:2141: dag pa chos mnyam nyid du rtogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2142: mi mnyam par tha dad du 'dzin pas ma dag
NK071(du)001:2143: pa'i gdul bya ste de dag kun la rgyal ba'i
NK071(du)001:2144: phrin las khyab bya khyab byed med pas gnyis med
NK071(du)001:2145: du khyab pa snang stong tha mi dad pa'i dbyings
NK071(du)001:2146: rnam par dag pa ste sku'i mtshan nyid dang phrin
NK071(du)001:2147: las rgyu'i 'bras bu thob tshul sngags kyi mthar thug
NK071(du)001:2148: sa yi khyad par bstan pa rnams bsdus so //
NK071(du)001:2149: ye nas sku lnga po kun kyang bde ba chen
NK071(du)001:2150: po'i sku las rang gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams par
NK071(du)001:2151: spros pa tsam nyid nas spros pa'i mtshan ma med
NK071(du)001:2152: pa ste / 'bras bu sku lnga bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2153: de gsungs pa'i yon tan gnyis bsdu'o //
NK071(du)001:2154: de ltar bsdus pa'i don la hoh zhes mnyes pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2155: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi don de skad ces rdo rje
NK071(du)001:2156: 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu bsdus pa'o
NK071(du)001:2157: // gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges
NK071(du)001:2158: pa las 'dis ting 'dzin lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gnyis
NK071(du)001:2159: // dang / 'bras bu rang bzhin sku'i dkyil 'khor spros nas bstan pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2162: zhi ba rjes 'jug gdul bya'i nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:2164: bkod pa dkyil 'khor las sku'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:2165: sgrub pa'i skabs bskyed bya rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams bstan /
NK071(du)001:2167: spros nyid dkyil 'khor bsam yas gsal /
NK071(du)001:2170: ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mo mtha' yas par spros pa nyid las /
NK071(du)001:2171: le'u dang po dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub sogs bstan par gsungs so //
NK071(du)001:2172: le'u bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2177: de nas de bzhin sogs gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2178: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gsung gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:2179: rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)001:2181: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags /
NK071(du)001:2182: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dgugs bstim gyi sngags /
NK071(du)001:2185: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i /
NK071(du)001:2187: dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:2199: dang po nang sems yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2201: gnyis pa phyi sems yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2209: gsum pa dbang bskur gyi byin rlobs pa'i sngags la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2210: lo rgyus sngags dngos de'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:2212: de nas bcom ldan 'das nas 'byung ngo zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:2215: byin gyis rlob pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:2217: ma h+aa shu nya ta sogs /
NK071(du)001:2218: gnyis pa ni sarba ta th+aa ga ta sogs /
NK071(du)001:2220: zhes brjod pas nas gyur to bar gnyis pa ye
NK071(du)001:2221: shes kyi dkyil 'khor dgugs stim gyi sngags la bzhi
NK071(du)001:2222: las dang po snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2224: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2226: gsum pa rigs pa'i me tog dor ba'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2229: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul te stim pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2230: ye shes rgyal po sogs nas hohbar gsum pa yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:2231: zhes brjod pas nas grags so bar /
NK071(du)001:2232: gnyis par rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor la gsum /
NK071(du)001:2233: gsung lnga'i mtshan nyid byed las rnam grangs so mtshan nyid la lnga las /
NK071(du)001:2234: dang po skye med don gyi gsung ni /
NK071(du)001:2235: e ma ho ngo mtshar sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2236: gnyis pa brjod pa tshig gi gsung ni /
NK071(du)001:2237: gsung gcig sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2238: gsum pa rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung ni /
NK071(du)001:2239: rgyud mchog sogs rkang pa lnga bzhi pa dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ni /
NK071(du)001:2240: theg pa mtho dman sogs rkang pa drug /
NK071(du)001:2241: lnga pa tshangs dbyangs kyi gsung ni /
NK071(du)001:2242: brjod med de nyid sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:2243: gnyis pa gsung gi byed las ni /
NK071(du)001:2244: theg pa mtho dman sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2245: gsum pa gsung gi rnam grangs ni /
NK071(du)001:2246: ji ltar gsung rab sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang gsum /
NK071(du)001:2249: sa bcad de dang 'brel ba'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:2251: de nas lhag ting dang 'bras bu rang bzhin gsung
NK071(du)001:2252: gi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:2253: btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad kyi sku
NK071(du)001:2254: dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje
NK071(du)001:2255: las gsung gsang sngags kyi gsang ba 'di dag phyung
NK071(du)001:2256: ngo // dang po rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2257: b+h+r+au ni rigs lnga 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang gi
NK071(du)001:2258: sa bon bi shwa sna tshogs bi shud+d+he rnam par
NK071(du)001:2259: dag pa'o // rigs lnga yab lnga'i sngags kyi mgo
NK071(du)001:2260: 'dren h'u sogs lnga po rnams ni thugs rdo rje
NK071(du)001:2261: mi bskyod pa sogs rigs kyi sa bon no //
NK071(du)001:2262: badz+ra rdo rje d+h+rika 'dzin pa ste /
NK071(du)001:2263: rnam shes dag pa rdo rje 'dzin pa mi bskyod pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2265: dzi na dzika rgyal bas rgyal te rnam snang s+w+aa
NK071(du)001:2266: ra t+na d+h+rika rin chen 'dzin pa te rin 'byung
NK071(du)001:2268: chags chen mtshon te snang mtha' h+aam pra dz+nya d+h+rika shes rab 'dzin pa ste don grub /
NK071(du)001:2270: m+aum ni mok+sha thar pa ste rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK071(du)001:2271: par dag pa'i dbyings d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai dbyings kyi
NK071(du)001:2272: dbang phyug ma l+aam lo tsa na te spyan ma
NK071(du)001:2273: dwe sha zhe sdang ra ti zhes pa ni dga'
NK071(du)001:2275: m+aam ma m+aa ki ste bdag mo mo ha gti
NK071(du)001:2276: mug ra ti p+y+aam pan+da ra ste dkar mo r+aa
NK071(du)001:2277: ga 'dod chags ra ti t+aam t+aa re ste sgrol
NK071(du)001:2278: ma badz+ra rdo rje phrag dog de rnams dag pa
NK071(du)001:2279: rigs kyi yab rnams mnyes par byed pa na ra
NK071(du)001:2282: k+shim k+shi hi zhes pa hi r+aa dza ya /
NK071(du)001:2283: ngo mtshar rgyal po ste sa snying tram rin chen
NK071(du)001:2284: rigs kyis sa bon +aa +aa ka sha nam mkha'
NK071(du)001:2285: gar+b+ha ya snying po te nam snying h+r+ai ha h'u
NK071(du)001:2287: pad+ma pa da ma pad+ma'i phyag ste spyan ras gzigs
NK071(du)001:2288: dz+rim rgyal ba'i sa bon ku ru p+aa na h+r+ai
NK071(du)001:2289: dang sprel bas rgyal mdzad phyag rdor h'u sogs bzhi
NK071(du)001:2290: ni yum bzhi'i sa bon la s+ye sgeg mo sa
NK071(du)001:2291: ma ya s+t+wam dus la bab ces /
NK071(du)001:2292: yum gyis bskul ba t+r+aam m+aa l+ye phreng ma /
NK071(du)001:2293: sa ma ya hoh dus yin no zhes lan byin
NK071(du)001:2294: la h+r+ai g+ai ti glu ma r+aa go&a ham bdag
NK071(du)001:2295: chags so zhes bskul ba a n+ri ti gar pa
NK071(du)001:2296: r+aa ga y+aa mi chags par bagyi'o /
NK071(du)001:2301: bskyod par gyur pa'i ming gi mthar snyoms 'jug gi brda' bzhi sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:2302: phyi sems yab yum ni mee ni me tri te
NK071(du)001:2303: byams pa'i sa bon d+ha ra ni gzung la ste
NK071(du)001:2304: / byams pas rjes su 'dzin pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2306: th+l+him sgrib sel gyi sa bon nis+sa ram b+ha ya
NK071(du)001:2307: s+w+aa h+aa sgrib pa bsal ba'i ched du h'u byang
NK071(du)001:2309: sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2310: sa ni sa man+ta te kun nas rgyal po'i ched du zhes kun bzang /
NK071(du)001:2311: mum ni muk+t+ra ste rnam grol mtshon pa'i sa bon /
NK071(du)001:2312: sh+r+ai dpal am gsung gi r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2313: chags pa'i ched du ste 'jam dpal le dzahsogasa bzhi
NK071(du)001:2314: ni bzung 'khyud sdom mnyes te phyag rgya bzhi'i sa
NK071(du)001:2315: bon d+hu pe bdug spos ma pra be sha rab
NK071(du)001:2316: tu zhugs pa / h'u push+pe me tog a be sha /
NK071(du)001:2318: bam d+ai pa sgron me su khu n+ai de ba
NK071(du)001:2319: ma ho gan+b+he dri ma tsit+ta thugs te sems tshim
NK071(du)001:2320: pa'o // khro bo bzhi'i mgo 'dren h'u /
NK071(du)001:2321: bzhi rigs kyi sa bon ya man+ta krita /
NK071(du)001:2322: gshin rje mthar byed phatah bkas pa'i don te las la sbyar ba'i bskul tshig go /
NK071(du)001:2324: shes rab dang h'u pad+man+ta krita phata /
NK071(du)001:2325: pad+ma sor bzhag dang h'u big+h+n+aa bgegs n+ta kri ta de mthar byed phata gong bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:2327: ni rab basngagasa te spyi'i sa bon /
NK071(du)001:2328: ma h+aa chen po badz+ra rdo rje d+ha ra 'chang ba ma h+aa chen po kro d+hi sh+w+aa r+ai /
NK071(du)001:2330: dz+wa l+ai n+ai 'bar ba ma h'u /
NK071(du)001:2331: khyab byed zhugs pa'i rigs kyi snying po phata bskul tshig sbyar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:2332: de bzhin du ma h+aa rat+na rin chen /
NK071(du)001:2333: d+h+aa ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwo ri dz+wa la n+ai h'u phata /
NK071(du)001:2334: ma h+aa pad+ma pad+ma d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK071(du)001:2335: ma h+aa karma las d+ha ro ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK071(du)001:2338: ye shes kyi sa bon badz+ra tsit+ta rdo rje thugs
NK071(du)001:2339: thabs kyi snying po ste byed pa po kun bzang
NK071(du)001:2340: / a a a chos dbyings kyi sa bon /
NK071(du)001:2341: badz+ri b+ha dra sa man+ta rdo rje kun tu bzang
NK071(du)001:2342: mo a ni shes rab kyi snying po ste bya
NK071(du)001:2344: thub drug rnams ni rab basngagasa mu ne thub pa
NK071(du)001:2345: krem ni byed pa ste 'dod yon gyi byed pas
NK071(du)001:2347: s+w+aa h+aa ni 'gro ba'i rigs de dang de'i bag
NK071(du)001:2348: chags zhi ba'i ched du gzhi 'dzug pa'i don no
NK071(du)001:2350: mu ni h'u t+r+aum ni go cha bgod pa ste lha min gyi sa bon /
NK071(du)001:2352: mu ne srum sa ra 'khyil ba ste blo dkyil che ba mi'i sa bon s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2353: mu ne bram ni pra ho te 'dud pa'i don gyis dud 'gro'i sa bon s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2354: mu ne k+sham k+sha ra ste /
NK071(du)001:2355: gdung ba yi dwags kyi sa bon s+w+aa h+aa /
NK071(du)001:2356: mu ni ye ni dmad pa'i gnas te dmyal ba'i sa bon rnams so //
NK071(du)001:2359: tshur spyon tshur spyon b+ha ga wan bcom ldan 'das
NK071(du)001:2360: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni k+aa thugs rje chen po
NK071(du)001:2361: dang ldan pa dri sh+ya hoh gzigs shig sa ma
NK071(du)001:2362: ya s+t+wam dus la bab zhes so //
NK071(du)001:2366: 'gugs 'ching sdom dgyes te spyan drangs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2367: am h'u s+w+aa h+aa ba ba ba ba ba /
NK071(du)001:2373: zhes bdag dam tshig pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK071(du)001:2374: phrin las rnams rdo rje ltar dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK071(du)001:2375: dam tshig de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi 'bras
NK071(du)001:2376: bu chos lnga dang gnyis su med du rtogs pa'i
NK071(du)001:2377: byed pa'o // zhes rig pa'i me tog dor ba bzhes so //
NK071(du)001:2378: ni dngos grub gsol ba'i glu'i mgo 'dren no //
NK071(du)001:2379: rang rig pa'i ye shes la mnga' mdzad pa'i rgyal po zhes bos te /
NK071(du)001:2380: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las gzhan las chos rmad po che /
NK071(du)001:2381: de nyid dus da lta nyid du 'dir ni dbyer med mnyam par sbyor bas ye shes lha'i /
NK071(du)001:2382: rdo rje gsum gyi phyag rgya chen por bdag gi
NK071(du)001:2383: sgo gsum sbyor bar mdzad cig ces bskul ba dang
NK071(du)001:2385: zhes pa'i thugs bskul ba'i sa bon du byas te
NK071(du)001:2386: rab sngags rdo rje mnyam par mdzod cig badz+ra sa
NK071(du)001:2387: ma ya s+t+wam zhes pas nam mkha' lha'i 'khor lo
NK071(du)001:2388: grub par ma gyur gyi bar du bstan par bzhugs
NK071(du)001:2389: pa'i rdo rje'i dam tshig khyod ces so //
NK071(du)001:2390: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh mchog ster rdo rje'i dam tshig mnyes par mdzod ces dang /
NK071(du)001:2391: dzahmh'u bam ho zhes phyag rgya bzhis brtan cing gsal bar byas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2392: de skad ces brjod pas lhag ting gsung gsang sngags
NK071(du)001:2393: kyi dkyil 'khor 'di dag gis yul 'jig rten drug
NK071(du)001:2394: gi phyogs bcu thams cad kyi gdul bya'i ngag la
NK071(du)001:2395: ye nas khyab par grags so //
NK071(du)001:2396: de las rkyen gyi sngags sgrar rab tu grags so //
NK071(du)001:2397: des 'gags med gsung rdo rjer krol bas kun tu grags so //
NK071(du)001:2398: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po /
NK071(du)001:2399: phyogs bcus bde gshegs thams cad dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje rigs kyi yab lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:2400: yul bya ba mo rdo rje yum lnga'i rnam par
NK071(du)001:2401: rang gi thugs ka'i dngas ma'i srog h'u yig gis
NK071(du)001:2402: 'od kyis spyan drangs pa rnams gnyis su med par
NK071(du)001:2403: sbyor ba'i rjes chags kyis mes zhu ba ye shes
NK071(du)001:2404: lnga'i chu rgyun dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i dbus gnas lnga
NK071(du)001:2406: dbang bskur ba de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi de
NK071(du)001:2407: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK071(du)001:2408: po rigs bdag sprul sku'i cha byad can lnga yis
NK071(du)001:2409: dbu brgyan cing phung lnga bdag nyid chen po'i rang
NK071(du)001:2410: bzhin du dag pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo rigs
NK071(du)001:2411: lnga sogs rigs rnams la de dag gi dbang bskur
NK071(du)001:2413: de ltar dbang dang byin bsdu ba zhes bya ba'i
NK071(du)001:2414: gsang sngags 'di dag ston pa'i sku dang gsung dang
NK071(du)001:2415: thugs mi phyed pa'i rdo rje thabs shes zung 'brel
NK071(du)001:2416: sgyu 'phrul dra ba las phyung ngo //
NK071(du)001:2417: dbang dang byin rlabs kyi sngags gnyis las dang po dbang bskur ba'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:2418: rab basngagasa ma h+aa chen po sh+au nya t+aa stong
NK071(du)001:2419: pa nyid dz+ny+aa na badz+ra ye shes rdo rje swa
NK071(du)001:2420: b+h+aa wa rang bzhin nam ngo bo nyid +aat+ma ko&a
NK071(du)001:2421: a mtsham sbyar ba ham bdag nyid pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2422: de bzhin du ma h+aa a dar+sha me long lta bu /
NK071(du)001:2423: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK071(du)001:2424: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na so sor rtogs pa /
NK071(du)001:2425: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba +aat+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2426: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa mnyam pa nyid /
NK071(du)001:2427: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2428: ma h+aa kri t+ya nu sh+th+aa na bya ba grub pa /
NK071(du)001:2429: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2431: rab basngagasa sarba thams cad ta th+aa ga ta de
NK071(du)001:2432: bzhin gshegs pa ma h+aa chen po k+aa ya sku
NK071(du)001:2433: badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2434: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa wa ka gsung /
NK071(du)001:2435: badz+ra swa b+ha ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2436: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta thugs /
NK071(du)001:2437: badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2438: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na rjes su chags pa /
NK071(du)001:2439: badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2440: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza mchod pa /
NK071(du)001:2441: badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa ba at+ma ko&aham /
NK071(du)001:2443: ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun spyi bo nas thim par
NK071(du)001:2444: gyur pas dbu'i gnas lnga na dbang lha rigs lnga
NK071(du)001:2445: gsal bar gyur / gnas gsum du rdo rje gsum gyi lha rnams 'bar bar gyur to //
NK071(du)001:2446: e ma hoh zhes brjod med las don go bas
NK071(du)001:2447: ngo mtshar zhing ches rmad kyi chos te ji ltar
NK071(du)001:2448: na / rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi khyab byed
NK071(du)001:2449: chos sku'i gsung ni grags pa'i sgra dang btags pa'i
NK071(du)001:2450: na / ming dang / brjod pa'i tshig sogs kun
NK071(du)001:2451: las 'das pa'i brjod med kyi gsung des go phye
NK071(du)001:2452: pas sna tshogs pa'i sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung ba'i
NK071(du)001:2453: na / ming dang / gzhir gyur pa'o // de
NK071(du)001:2454: bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gi gsang ba gcig la yang
NK071(du)001:2455: gsung gi dkyil 'khor yan lag drug cu la sogs
NK071(du)001:2457: gdul bya'i gnas bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i zhing khams
NK071(du)001:2458: kun tu khyab cing rang rang gi skad du brda
NK071(du)001:2459: sprod pa'i sgra dang ming tshig so sor grag cing
NK071(du)001:2460: grags pa de thams cad kyang zab pa dang rgya
NK071(du)001:2461: che ba'i gsung gi phyag rgya las mi 'da' ba'i
NK071(du)001:2463: rgyud thams cad kyi mchog sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud
NK071(du)001:2464: las 'bras bu bde ba chen po dang ldan pa
NK071(du)001:2465: rang rig pa'i ye shes gsung gi don 'byung ba'ang
NK071(du)001:2466: ji ltar zhe na 'khor 'das sgra thams cad gzung
NK071(du)001:2467: 'dzin gyi ma gos pa pad+ma lta bu'i ngang du
NK071(du)001:2469: rnam par grol ba 'das pa dang thar par 'gro byed lam dang /
NK071(du)001:2470: bcings pa 'khor ba'i sgra skad kyi rnam pa ji
NK071(du)001:2471: skad brjod pa thams cad kyang mtshan mas ma gos
NK071(du)001:2473: theg pa mtho dman thams cad dang //
NK071(du)001:2474: phyin ci log mu stegs pa dang //
NK071(du)001:2475: gzhan yang 'gro ba ma lus thams cad kyi sgra
NK071(du)001:2476: skad kun kyang don la grag stong gnyis med kyi
NK071(du)001:2477: ngo bor ye nas byang chub pa rdo rje'i gsung
NK071(du)001:2478: du bsdus shing bsdus tsam nyid na'ang de las ma
NK071(du)001:2479: g.yos bzhin du phyogs bcur rnam par grags pa'i sgra
NK071(du)001:2480: nyid ji ltar pad+ma la chus mi gos pa ltar
NK071(du)001:2481: ma chags 'dzin med kyi ngang du gsungs pas mtha'
NK071(du)001:2483: ma 'gags par gsungs pa'i dus nyid na ma dmigs pas brjod du med pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2484: brjod med don gyi gsung de nyid brjod pa sna
NK071(du)001:2485: tshogs pa'i sgra'i 'byungs su snang bas gdul bya kun
NK071(du)001:2486: la tshig mthun par grags shing don so sor 'jal
NK071(du)001:2488: dper na tshul de bzhin thub pa'i dbang pos sbrid
NK071(du)001:2489: pa bsangs pa la nad pa sman pa khyim bdag
NK071(du)001:2490: mo gsum gyis don so sor go ba bzhin de
NK071(du)001:2491: bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung gcig gi sgra yis so so'i
NK071(du)001:2492: bsod nams dang mthun pa'i chos thams cad go ba
NK071(du)001:2493: de ni gsung gcig gis kun la khyab pas gsung
NK071(du)001:2494: mchog rgyal po ste tshangs dbyangs kyi gsungs yin no
NK071(du)001:2495: // gdul bya'i snang bar theg pa mtho dman bsam
NK071(du)001:2496: yas gsungs pa ltar snang yang bcom ldan 'das kyi
NK071(du)001:2497: de bzhin nyid la 'bab pa kho na las gzhan
NK071(du)001:2498: // ma gsungs te / gdul bya 'dul ba'i thabs
NK071(du)001:2499: su chos kyi rnam grangs so sor thos pa tsam
NK071(du)001:2500: // ma gsungs te / du zad de / ji
NK071(du)001:2501: ltar gsung rab kyi don kun brjod kyang don chos
NK071(du)001:2502: nyid de bzhin nyid kyis gzhal nas brjod du med
NK071(du)001:2503: // ma gsungs te / du zad de / phyir
NK071(du)001:2504: / cung zad kyang gsungs pa med de chos sku
NK071(du)001:2505: skye med don gyi gsungs so //
NK071(du)001:2506: de nyid mtshon byed yi ger grub pa med pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2507: rig pa ye shes kyi gsung de nyid sgrar brjod
NK071(du)001:2508: du med pas ljags kyi rtse mor tshig tu ma
NK071(du)001:2509: phyung yang longs sku'i dgongs pa brda'i gsung ngo //
NK071(du)001:2510: thugs rje lhun gyis grub pa'i gsung gi byin rlabs
NK071(du)001:2511: stobs kyis don mdzad pa ni mngon byang rig pa
NK071(du)001:2513: 'gro ba'i mos pa dang mthun pa'i sgra don sna
NK071(du)001:2514: tshogs tshig gcig gis so sor gsal zhing thos pas
NK071(du)001:2515: brda sprod pa sprul sku brjod pa tshig gi gsung
NK071(du)001:2516: ngo // de ltar gsal ba nyid na'ang mi dmigs
NK071(du)001:2517: pas gsung gi rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pas rdo
NK071(du)001:2518: rje'i mchog ste dbyer med rdo rje'i gsung ngo //
NK071(du)001:2519: tshul de bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi sgo
NK071(du)001:2520: nas 'gro don mdzad pa rnams ni brjod med de
NK071(du)001:2521: bzhin nyid kyi ngang las gzhan du ma g.yos kyang
NK071(du)001:2522: rgyal ba'i thun mong dang 'dul bya'i mos pa las
NK071(du)001:2524: dper na brag cha'i sgra nyid kyang brjod 'dod rtog pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2525: rtsol ba gang yang med bzhin du rkyen gyis sgra yi rnam par 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:2526: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK071(du)001:2527: 'dis rang bzhin gsung gi dkyil 'khor ji snyed pa
NK071(du)001:2528: gsung ltar bsdus pa dang lhag pa ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:2529: gsung gi dkyil 'khor gsang sngags kyi don bstan pa'i
NK071(du)001:2533: bzhi pa rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang //
NK071(du)001:2534: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las sgrub pa'i skabs bskyed pa rkyen gyi sngags dang /
NK071(du)001:2535: 'ching zlos sngags dang phyag rgya las zhi ba'i sngags rnams bstan to /
NK071(du)001:2537: gang byed sngags kyi yi ge brjod /
NK071(du)001:2540: dkyil 'khor bsam yas su gsal ba las /
NK071(du)001:2541: rang gi lhag pa'i lha gang la byed pa'i zhi
NK071(du)001:2542: pa rab 'byams kyi sngags kyi yi ge gsal bar
NK071(du)001:2543: brjod pa'o // le'u brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2548: de nas bzhin nas brjod do bar //
NK071(du)001:2549: gnyis pa gzhung la lnga ste /
NK071(du)001:2550: rang bzhin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK071(du)001:2551: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK071(du)001:2553: phyag rgya spros bcas kyi ting nge 'dzin bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2554: phyag rgya'i rnams kyi sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)001:2556: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2559: de las byung ba rigs lnga spyi'i dam rgya /
NK071(du)001:2560: de las 'phros pa lha so so'i phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)001:2562: mi skyod sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2564: dang mum gnyis sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2565: gsum pa so so'i phyag rgya la lnga las //
NK071(du)001:2566: dang po rigs lnga'i phyag rgya las gtso bo yab yum ni /
NK071(du)001:2567: 'bru bzhi sbas nas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis dang /
NK071(du)001:2568: rnam snang yab yum sogs rigs gzhan bzhi po'i phyag rgya yang 'bru bzhi sbas nas sogs bcad brgyad /
NK071(du)001:2569: gnyis pa sems dpa' yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)001:2570: ut+pala klu shing sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK071(du)001:2571: gsum pa sgo ba yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)001:2572: sgo bzhi sogs rkang pa bdun /
NK071(du)001:2573: bzhi pa thub drug gi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)001:2574: thub pa drug sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2575: lnga pa kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)001:2576: kun bzang sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:2577: gsum pa lta ba'i phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)001:2578: phyag rgya chen po'i tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2579: bzhi pa phyag rgya spros bcas la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:2580: snang ba rnam 'byed la ji ltar bslab pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2585: bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2587: yan lag sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2589: de ltar ldan pa sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2591: de la sogs te sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2592: gnyis pa de'i don byed tshul ni /
NK071(du)001:2593: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2594: lnga pa phyag rgya'i rnam grangs bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)001:2595: mdor na phyag rgya sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2598: sa bcad de ldan gyi gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2602: lhag ting ste thugs phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsum ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:2603: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid
NK071(du)001:2604: kyis lus dang rtog pa'i yan lag thams cad sku
NK071(du)001:2605: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du ye nas lhun
NK071(du)001:2606: gyis grub pa nyid rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas mthar
NK071(du)001:2607: phyin par byin gyis rlobs pa zhes bya ba'i phyag
NK071(du)001:2608: rgya'i rim pa 'di ched du brjod do //
NK071(du)001:2609: chos thams cad zung 'jug sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:2610: 'khor du ye nas rang bzhin gyis mngon par rdzogs
NK071(du)001:2611: pa sangs rgyas pa'i phyir rtog tshogs thams cad la
NK071(du)001:2612: chos nyid byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po
NK071(du)001:2613: mchog gi phyag rgyas btab pa ste //
NK071(du)001:2615: gsang ba de kho na nyid du nges pa yi /
NK071(du)001:2616: don chos nyid snying po'i phyag rgyas btab pa ni
NK071(du)001:2617: rgyal po'i bka' rtags pa ltar 'da' dka' ba ste
NK071(du)001:2620: mi bskyod pa'i rigs lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo
NK071(du)001:2621: lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lnga'i steng du thabs
NK071(du)001:2622: rigs lnga'i yi ge h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa dang /
NK071(du)001:2623: rin chen rigs lag pa g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la /
NK071(du)001:2624: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor lnga'i steng du shes rab yum
NK071(du)001:2625: lnga'i yi ge m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams ma
NK071(du)001:2627: sor mo lnga phrag gnyis po zung du sprad pa'i
NK071(du)001:2628: las kyi thal mo mnyam par sbyar bas lha so
NK071(du)001:2629: so'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyur 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:2630: de yang g.yas kyi mdzub mo'i dang g.yon gyi gung mo'i m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK071(du)001:2631: lhags ma rigs bzhi'i yi ge 'bru brgyad kyang g.yas
NK071(du)001:2632: kyi gung mo'i h+aum dang g.yon gyi mdzub mo'i l+aam
NK071(du)001:2633: de bzhin du mthe bong dang mathe'u chung g.yas g.yon
NK071(du)001:2634: gyi h+aa dang p+aam am dang tam rnams phan tshun
NK071(du)001:2635: so sor bsnol nas rtse sprad pa las srin lag
NK071(du)001:2636: gi s+w+aa m+aam gnyis mathe'u chung nang du bkug pa'i
NK071(du)001:2637: rgyab tu sbyar nas sbreng ba ni /
NK071(du)001:2639: dbyer med mnyam par sbyor ba'i dngos grub /
NK071(du)001:2640: bde ba chen po'i ye shes sbyin par byed pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK071(du)001:2641: lag g.yas h+aum ma gtogs pa'i yig 'bru bzhi sbas
NK071(du)001:2642: nas gung mo gyen du sbreng ba'i rgyas thugs kar
NK071(du)001:2643: gtad do bkan pa ni bca' ba dam rgya /
NK071(du)001:2644: h+aum mthing ga gung mo sgreng ba'i rtse mor bsgom pa chos rgya /
NK071(du)001:2645: h+aum zhu ba las rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar bar gyur pa ni dam rgya /
NK071(du)001:2646: lag g.yon pa'i zla ba lnga nang du brtul bas
NK071(du)001:2647: yum gyi yig 'bru lnga sbas pa'i khu tshur gyis
NK071(du)001:2648: dril bu bzung ba gsil zhing /
NK071(du)001:2649: yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos
NK071(du)001:2650: kyi sems dpa' ma pad+ma'i rigs kyi steng du bzhag
NK071(du)001:2651: pas dku la rten pa ni las rgya dang /
NK071(du)001:2652: lag g.yon gyi 'bru bzhi nang du sbas nas gung
NK071(du)001:2653: mo thugs kar bkan thabs su sgreng ba dam rgya
NK071(du)001:2654: m+aum mthing ga gung mo sbreng pa'i rtse mor bsgom
NK071(du)001:2656: m+aum zhu ba las dril bu gsil ba'i sgra can
NK071(du)001:2657: 'od 'bar bar gyur pa bsam pa ni dam rgya
NK071(du)001:2658: / lag g.yas nyi ma la gnas pa'i 'bru lnga
NK071(du)001:2659: ma bcings pas yab kyi barla g.yas pa las su
NK071(du)001:2660: 'khril zhing dbu yab la cung zad btud de zhal
NK071(du)001:2661: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyis zhal la blta ba'i
NK071(du)001:2662: tshul du bca' ba ni las rgya'o //
NK071(du)001:2663: yang bdag nyid rnam snang sogs rigs bzhi gang yin de gsal ba la /
NK071(du)001:2664: lag g.yas pa'i 'bru bzhi sbas nas rang rigs kyi
NK071(du)001:2665: sor mo sbreng ba thugs kar bkan thabs su bcas
NK071(du)001:2666: shing dang po rnam snang la gyi sor mo sgreng
NK071(du)001:2667: ba'i rtse mor bsam pa la /
NK071(du)001:2668: rang gi thugs phyag mtshan 'khor lo 'od 'bar ba bsam zhing /
NK071(du)001:2669: g.yon zla brtul gyis yum gyi 'bru lnga sbas pa'i
NK071(du)001:2670: khu tshur gyis dril bu gsil zhing yum la 'khril
NK071(du)001:2671: ba'i tshul gyis barla g.yon pa chos la brten pa'o
NK071(du)001:2672: // yang g.yon du rnam snang la rigs kyi yum dbyings phyug gsal ba las /
NK071(du)001:2673: g.yon pa'i 'bru bzhi sbas nas rang rigs kyi sor
NK071(du)001:2674: mo sbreng ba thugs kar bkan zhing l+aam rigs kyi
NK071(du)001:2675: kha dog can sor mo sgreng ba'i rtse mor dril
NK071(du)001:2676: bu gsil ba'i sgra gcan 'od 'bar bar gyur cing
NK071(du)001:2677: / g.yas nyi ma 'bru lnga dang bcas pa ma
NK071(du)001:2678: bcings pas las su ste yab kyi barla g.yas pa'i
NK071(du)001:2679: steng du bzhag pas 'khril zhing yab la dbu btud
NK071(du)001:2680: de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi zhal la blta ba ste
NK071(du)001:2681: / / yab yum so so'i sngags mthar sngags brjod
NK071(du)001:2682: cing thabs shes phan tshun rgyas 'debs kyis dkrol bar
NK071(du)001:2683: / / bya ste / de dag gis 'og ma rnams la rigs 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:2684: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK071(du)001:2685: s+w+aa sgreng rtse mor rin chen 'bar //
NK071(du)001:2686: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing //
NK071(du)001:2687: 'khril ba'i tshul gyi chos la brten //
NK071(du)001:2688: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan /
NK071(du)001:2689: m+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK071(du)001:2691: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi blta //
NK071(du)001:2692: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK071(du)001:2694: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing //
NK071(du)001:2695: 'khril ba'i tshul gyi chos la brten //
NK071(du)001:2696: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK071(du)001:2697: p+y+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK071(du)001:2699: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK071(du)001:2700: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK071(du)001:2701: h+aum sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK071(du)001:2702: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing //
NK071(du)001:2703: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK071(du)001:2704: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK071(du)001:2705: t+aam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK071(du)001:2707: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK071(du)001:2708: ba ste rigs lnga gtso bo'i phyag rgya sogs nas /
NK071(du)001:2709: de nas lag g.yas pa'i mthe bong ma gtog gzhan
NK071(du)001:2710: bzhi la nyi dkyil re re'ii steng du mdzub mo
NK071(du)001:2711: nas brtsams te thugs kyi sems dpa'i bzhi'i sa bon
NK071(du)001:2712: k+shim tram h+r+aim dz+rim bzhi dang /
NK071(du)001:2713: gsung gi sems dpa'i tshe mee th+l+him h+aum mum bzhi bkod /
NK071(du)001:2714: g.yon gyi sor rtse bzhi la zla dkyil re rer nang sems kyi yum bzhi sa bon /
NK071(du)001:2716: phyi yi sems ma dzahh+aum bam hobzhi bkod nas /
NK071(du)001:2717: sems dpa'i sems ma gang yin gyi skur gsal ba las /
NK071(du)001:2718: 'bru gsum sbas nas rang rigs kyi sor mo sgreng
NK071(du)001:2719: ba'i rtser sa bon so so yongs su gyur pa
NK071(du)001:2720: las / 'jam dpal gyi ut+pala byams pa'i klu shing
NK071(du)001:2721: la sogs pa thugs phyag mtshan 'od 'bar pa dang
NK071(du)001:2722: las / / de bzhin du sa snying gi rin
NK071(du)001:2723: chen myu gu nam snying gi ral gri 'od 'bar
NK071(du)001:2724: spyan ras gzigs kyi pad+ma dkar po /
NK071(du)001:2725: phyag rdor gyi rdo rje 'od 'bar ba /
NK071(du)001:2726: sgrib sel gyi chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK071(du)001:2727: kun bzang gi rin chen snye ma ste yab brgyad /
NK071(du)001:2728: de dag gi yum sgeg mo gzugs mdzes gsal ba'i me long /
NK071(du)001:2729: m+aa les rin chen phreng ba dang /
NK071(du)001:2731: n+airtisa gar mkhan mchog gi mtshan ma rnga yab nyid
NK071(du)001:2732: dang de bzhin du push+pe me tog phreng ba dang
NK071(du)001:2733: / bdug spos kyi mchod snod 'char pa'i d+hu pe ma /
NK071(du)001:2734: a lo ke'i mar me g+han+d+he ma'i dri'i byug pa rnams 'od 'bar bar bsam pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2735: la sogs zhes pa'i khong nas /
NK071(du)001:2736: sems ma brgyad kyi lag g.yas nyi ma 'bru lnga
NK071(du)001:2737: ma bcings pas yab kyi barla g.yas las la bstan
NK071(du)001:2738: pas 'khril zhing / sems dpa' brgyad kyi g.yon zla
NK071(du)001:2739: brtul 'bru sbas kyi phyag mtshan dril bu bzung ba
NK071(du)001:2740: gsil zhing barla g.yon pa chos la brten pa dang
NK071(du)001:2741: pas 'khril zhing / / yab kyi dbu rnams kyang
NK071(du)001:2742: yum la cung zad 'byo bar sgom zhing yum rnams
NK071(du)001:2743: yab la cung zad 'dud pa'i tshul dang bcas pa'o
NK071(du)001:2744: pas 'khril zhing / / // mdor na gong gi
NK071(du)001:2745: phyag rgya chen po sogs phyag rgya bdun ldan rigs
NK071(du)001:2746: lnga'i skabs bzhin du thabs shes gnyis med chos nyid
NK071(du)001:2748: sgo bzhir gnas pa'i khro bo yab yum gyi phyag
NK071(du)001:2749: rgya ni sngar bzhin rigs 'dres pa las bye brag
NK071(du)001:2750: / gshin rje gshed kyi n+ri mgo gdengs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2751: stobs chen rdo rje gnod thabs dang rta mgrin thod dbyug sbrul chen pos dkris gnon pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2752: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rdo rje rgya gram las kyis
NK071(du)001:2753: mtshan ma gnon thabs yum rnams g.yas kyi rim par
NK071(du)001:2754: lcags kyu dang zhags pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2755: s+pho ta ste lcags sgrog dang hoh ste dgyes byed
NK071(du)001:2756: dril bu 'dzin pa'i sgo bzhir gnas pa'i yab yum
NK071(du)001:2757: de dag kyang / phan tshun dbu 'dud pa dang
NK071(du)001:2758: 'jo ba'i tshul gyis yab yum 'khril ba'ang gong du
NK071(du)001:2759: bshad ma thag pa bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:2760: thub pa drug gi phyag rgya ni gdul bya ma nges par 'dul ba'i phyir sna tshogs te /
NK071(du)001:2761: mdor bsdus na phyag rgya drug tu bstan pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:2762: yum ni dmigs med chos kyi dbyings kyi yum dang 'du 'bral med par mnyes par byed do //
NK071(du)001:2763: byed pa kun bzang phyag g.yas steng du bkod pa'i
NK071(du)001:2764: mnyam bzhag las ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro ba
NK071(du)001:2765: yum de las 'gyur te phyag g.yon steng du bkod
NK071(du)001:2767: bzhugs thabs yab rdzogs pa rdor dkyil dang /
NK071(du)001:2768: yum pad+mo'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2769: de las gzhan yang yum gyi phyag rgya ni ma nges par sna tshogs te /
NK071(du)001:2770: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa yab ltar mnyam bzhag nyid dam /
NK071(du)001:2771: yang na rdo rje thal mo thugs kar sbyar ba nyid do //
NK071(du)001:2772: rtogs tshogs thams cad phyag rgya chen po'i rol par snang ba'i tshogs mchog ni /
NK071(du)001:2773: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa'i don rtogs pa'i blo dang ldan cing rgyud la 'byor na /
NK071(du)001:2774: lus ma bskyod cing yan lag ma bsgul yang ci
NK071(du)001:2775: byas cir snang thams cad kun lha sku phyag chen
NK071(du)001:2776: po'i ngang du gnas pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:2777: yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la ldan par bsgom pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2778: bdag nyid mi bskyod par gsal ba'i dbu la rnam
NK071(du)001:2779: snang bsgom pa sogs kyis mtshon sbyar tshul 'grel pa
NK071(du)001:2781: de ltar thabs lha bzhi bcu po de nyid 'dra
NK071(du)001:2782: ba'i yan lag gi lha ye shes sems dpa' spros
NK071(du)001:2783: te bsgom pa shes rab lha bzhi bcu de re
NK071(du)001:2784: re la'ang rigs bdag gtsos dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga
NK071(du)001:2786: gzhan yang yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu tham pa
NK071(du)001:2787: lha re re la'ang gnas gsum byin rlabs kyi lha
NK071(du)001:2789: de ltar ldan pa'i lha gtso mchog mi bskyod pa yab yum gyis mtshon te /
NK071(du)001:2791: rgyal mchog kun bzang yab yum dang de bzhin du sems dpa' brgyad sgo skyong bzhi ste bcu gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2792: thub pa drug gi yan lag gi lha dang bcas
NK071(du)001:2793: pa thams cad kyang 'od 'phro zhing gzi 'bar bsgom
NK071(du)001:2794: pa ste / dkyil 'khor rgyas par rtsi tshul gzhan du shes so //
NK071(du)001:2795: gong du bshad pa de la sogs te /
NK071(du)001:2796: dkyil 'khor rab 'byams bsam gyis mi khyab pa la bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2797: don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK071(du)001:2798: zhing khams bsam yas rnams su 'dul byed kyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:2799: 'khor gdul bya 'gro ba'i don rnams mos pa bzhin
NK071(du)001:2800: so sor ston cing der ma zad theg pa mtho
NK071(du)001:2801: ba sngags dang byang sems dman pa nyan rang ste
NK071(du)001:2802: yang dag grub mthar zhugs pa thams cad dang phyin
NK071(du)001:2803: ci log mu stegs rnams dang /
NK071(du)001:2804: gang la'ang ma zhugs pa'i skye bo bsam yas dang /
NK071(du)001:2805: de dag kyang lha sogs zhi ba'i rigs dang /
NK071(du)001:2806: bdud srin sogs khro ba'i rigs kyi gdul bya'i tshogs chen po thams cad la /
NK071(du)001:2807: so sor mos pa dang mthun par byas pa'i 'dul
NK071(du)001:2808: byed kyi sku'i bkod pa kun tu snang bar mdzad
NK071(du)001:2810: ma g.yos bzhin rtogs pa dang bral bas don mdzad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2811: dper na zlos gar mkhan nyid dang 'dra ba /
NK071(du)001:2812: gar mkhan de yang lus gcig pu de las ma
NK071(du)001:2813: g.yos bzhin du bkod pa sna tshogs ston pa bzhin
NK071(du)001:2814: no // mdor na phyag rgya ji ltar bshad pa thams cad ni /
NK071(du)001:2816: grangs gcig tu nges zhes brjod du med de /
NK071(du)001:2817: ji ltar na lus kyi yan lag gi dbang du
NK071(du)001:2818: gnyis dang gsum gcig tu sdom ste yan lag lnga
NK071(du)001:2819: po re re'ang rigs lnga yab yum bcu bcur rnam
NK071(du)001:2820: par 'phro bas phyag rgya lnga bcu'am rtog pa'i dbang
NK071(du)001:2821: gis de ltar 'byung bas lus kyi yan lag bskyod
NK071(du)001:2822: pa dang / rtog pa'i yan lag spro ba'ang de
NK071(du)001:2823: bzhin nyid las mi 'da' bar bslab par bya ba
NK071(du)001:2824: pa dang / ste / mdor na yan lag bsgul
NK071(du)001:2825: zhing lus skyod pa thams cad kun lha sku phyag
NK071(du)001:2826: rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas zhing de ltar gnas
NK071(du)001:2827: dus nyid na'ang der 'dzin med pa'i phyir mi gnas
NK071(du)001:2828: pa'ang ma yin la gnas pa'ang min te mtha' dang
NK071(du)001:2830: zhes de skad du spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i rgyal mchog ston pa nyid kyis bshad /
NK071(du)001:2832: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:2833: las 'dis lus dang rtogs pa'i yan lag thams cad
NK071(du)001:2834: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs nas rang
NK071(du)001:2835: bzhin lta ba ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi phyag rgya
NK071(du)001:2836: spros nas bstan pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2839: zhi ba rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:2840: dngos po bcu las phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab pa /
NK071(du)001:2841: gnas su stob pa mchod pa la zhi ba phyag rgya'i mchod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2842: 'ching zlos gnyis las 'ching ba'i phyag rgya rnams bstan to /
NK071(du)001:2843: bi ma las de nyid thugs rtags phyag rgyar gsal /
NK071(du)001:2845: le'u bdun par sngags kyi yi ge brjod pa de
NK071(du)001:2846: nyid le'u 'dir thugs rtags phyag rgyar gsal bar bstan
NK071(du)001:2847: to // le'u dgu pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2851: de nas sogs brjod do bar /
NK071(du)001:2857: sngon du slob dpon gyi bsnyen pa bya ba dang /
NK071(du)001:2858: dkyil 'khor gyi las rim dngos so //
NK071(du)001:2860: shin tu sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2861: gnyis pa la gnyis zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2862: des khro bo dang mchog gi dkyil 'khor mtshon par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2864: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa la'ang spyir bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2865: go ma ye btang ba bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2867: yang na sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2870: gnyis pa tshad la gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:2871: dang po lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad ni /
NK071(du)001:2872: dkyil 'khor khru gang sogs rkang pa gsum dang /
NK071(du)001:2873: yang na khru ni sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2874: gnyis pa mchog dkyil lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi tshad ni /
NK071(du)001:2875: yang na rgyang grags sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2877: phur bu sogs tshigs bcad gcig gi rkang pa tha
NK071(du)001:2878: ma'i gong du rigs pas thig ni gdab pa bya
NK071(du)001:2879: / zhes bcug pas rkang pa lnga bzhi pa mtshon ni /
NK071(du)001:2880: ma mthong sogs tshigs bcad gcig gi lnga yi zhes pa'i 'og /
NK071(du)001:2881: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom /
NK071(du)001:2882: zhes bcug pa'i rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:2883: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2884: sku gsung thugs sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2885: bdun par rab gnas la drug yo byad dgram pa /
NK071(du)001:2886: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba /
NK071(du)001:2887: rol mo lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bskyed pa /
NK071(du)001:2888: de ltar sbyangs shing skyed pa'i yon tan /
NK071(du)001:2889: ye shes pa drangs shing gzhug pa /
NK071(du)001:2892: bcos bu'i sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2893: gnyis pa ni lus ngag sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2895: ting 'dzin rol mo sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:2897: sa la sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2899: phyogs dus sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2901: dang po phyi nang gi mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2902: glu tshigs sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2903: gnyis pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2905: rkang pas dman pa'i tshigs bcad drug /
NK071(du)001:2907: gsal ldan ma'am sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK071(du)001:2909: dbyibs dang kha dog sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2910: dgu pa dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2914: kun byas sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2916: de nas slob ma sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2917: bskal pa mnyam pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2918: bcu pa dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:2919: bde ba chen po'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2920: gnyis pa des khro bo dang mchog gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa la gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:2922: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:2923: gnyis pa mchog gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK071(du)001:2924: shin tu phra la sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2925: gnyis pa dbang la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2927: snod dang mtshams par bskur tshul /
NK071(du)001:2928: gsang dbang gi dkyil 'khor bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2930: de nas rigs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2931: gnyis pa ni dad brtson sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2934: de la mtshan ma dgod pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2938: shin tu phra ba'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2939: de nas rdo rje'i tshad ni /
NK071(du)001:2940: yang na thal mo sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2941: gnyis pa mtshan ma dgod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2942: sen zlum sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2943: gsum pa sgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2948: cho ga lnga ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2950: mthong lam 'bras bu pa'i dus dang /
NK071(du)001:2951: mthar thug sku lnga 'grub pa'i dus so //
NK071(du)001:2953: zhag ni sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:2955: de tshe sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2956: gsum pa sgrub pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:2960: 'grub tshul rang snang du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:2961: de dpe'i sgo nas bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:2963: ye shes thig las rkang pas dman pas tshigs bcad gsum /
NK071(du)001:2965: dpag bsam sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2966: gnyis pa 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:2967: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes shing don byed nus par bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:2968: gcig tu bral gyi don rang byung gi ye shes su bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:2969: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gdul bya gzigs tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:2971: shes rab dbyings sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:2973: gcig dang du ma sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:2975: log par sogs tshigs bcad gcig dang /
NK071(du)001:2979: de lta'i gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:2980: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:2981: de nas lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:2982: de bzhin gshegs pa zag med bde ba'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:2983: la dgyes pa chen por longs spyod pa'i bdag nyid
NK071(du)001:2984: kun tu bzang pos sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo
NK071(du)001:2985: rje'i gsang ba'i dam tshig bkod cing de nyid ston
NK071(du)001:2986: pa'i dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK071(du)001:2987: nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)001:2988: dkyil 'khor khru gang sogs la ltos na /
NK071(du)001:2989: shin tu phra zhing mtshon byed rtags kyis mtshon bya
NK071(du)001:2990: mkha' dbyings bde ba'i ye shes kyi rgyur mtshon pa'i
