NK071(du)001:2991: dam tshig mchog gi dkyil 'khor ste /
NK071(du)001:2992: slob dpon lha sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba'i phyag mnyam bzhag gi mthil du /
NK071(du)001:2993: thugs bde ba'i ye shes bskyed byed kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:2994: dam pa yum gyi mkha' de nyid mtshon byed pad+ma
NK071(du)001:2995: dmar po 'dab ma bzhi pa tshad dga' bzhi mtshon
NK071(du)001:2996: pa'i sor ni bzhi yi tshad du bya ba yin
NK071(du)001:2997: no // phung po sku lngar dag byed 'bru lnga
NK071(du)001:2998: dbang lnga phrin las lngar dag byed spos lnga yul
NK071(du)001:2999: lnga yon tan lngar dag byed rin chen lnga rnam
NK071(du)001:3000: shes ye shes lngar dag byed snying po lnga dang
NK071(du)001:3001: 'dod yon lnga gsung lngar dag byed sman lnga dang
NK071(du)001:3002: no // / khams lnga rigs lngar dag byed bdud
NK071(du)001:3003: rtsi lnga nyid de rdzas sum cu po rab tu
NK071(du)001:3004: mnyam par sbyar ba'i lde gus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi
NK071(du)001:3005: la go ma ye btang bar bya zhes pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3006: thig g.yog rig ma sogs lhar gsal bar byas pas
NK071(du)001:3007: dam tshig gi thig btab pa'i steng du ye shes
NK071(du)001:3008: kyi thig ni mkha' la gdab par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3009: de nas dbus kyi lte ba zlum po'i mthar 'khor
NK071(du)001:3010: lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang ldan pa yi nang
NK071(du)001:3011: du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'i
NK071(du)001:3012: gnas lngar rtsibs bzhi pa'i 'khor lo chung ba mu
NK071(du)001:3013: khyud dang bcas pa re res mtshan pa dang phyi
NK071(du)001:3014: rol du gru chad bzhi dang dbyibs gru bzhi pa'i
NK071(du)001:3015: rnam pa can gru chad kyi phyir bar khyams dang
NK071(du)001:3016: sgo bzhir sgo khyud can rta bab sogs dang ldan
NK071(du)001:3017: par bya'o // gsang dkyil gnyis kyi pad+ma'i lte ba dang 'dab bzhir /
NK071(du)001:3018: sen zlum tsam gyi nyi dkyil dang /
NK071(du)001:3019: rdo rje'i rwa lnga la de tsam gyi zla ba
NK071(du)001:3020: la sran ma tsa na ka'i 'bru tsam gyi pad+ma'i
NK071(du)001:3021: gdan re re'i steng du yung 'bru tsam gyi yi
NK071(du)001:3022: ge yab yum gyi 'bru lnga lnga bkod pa las
NK071(du)001:3023: / lha'i phyag rgya til 'bru tsam du bri ba ste gsal gdab bo //
NK071(du)001:3024: gzhan yang dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan bcos bu'i ras la dbyibs ni bla bre sogs sna tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:3025: rin po che'i rgyan phreng dang /
NK071(du)001:3026: btung ba dang bza' ba bro mchog ldan pas kyang yongs su bskor zhing brgyan par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3027: mchod par ngag gi glu tshig lus kyi bro gar
NK071(du)001:3028: rol mo sogs mchod pa'i sprin phung tshogs kyis rab
NK071(du)001:3029: tu mchod cing rgyas 'debs ma sogs gsang yum bzhi
NK071(du)001:3030: dang / sgo ma bzhi dang phyi nang gi sems
NK071(du)001:3031: ma brgyad de lha mo bcu drug gis ji ltar
NK071(du)001:3032: 'dod pa'i skabs kyis las gang byed pa de bzhin
NK071(du)001:3033: dang / du mchod do // sbyin sreg la thab khung dbyibs ni zhi bar zlum po sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:3034: kha dog dkar po sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:3035: dbus su mtshan ma ni zhi bar 'khor lo yig
NK071(du)001:3036: dang ldan par bya ba sogs gzhan la'ang des rigs
NK071(du)001:3037: 'gre zhing mchod sbyin gsol ba'i zhal du gyur pa'i
NK071(du)001:3038: me lha bskyed cing ye shes pa gsal la bstim
NK071(du)001:3039: bza' btung ro bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyi cho gas
NK071(du)001:3040: las bzhi so so'i skabs dang sbyar ba'i mchod pa
NK071(du)001:3042: yang sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi las rim
NK071(du)001:3043: zhi ba'i skabs de bzhin te 'dzin gnad shin tu
NK071(du)001:3044: phra zhing zab pa la blo sbyangs pa yi rnal
NK071(du)001:3045: 'byor pas bsam yas lhun grub sogs lhag ting gi
NK071(du)001:3046: dkyil 'khor dag la'ang bshad ma thag pa de bzhin
NK071(du)001:3047: du bya'o // de rnams kyi tshad ni /
NK071(du)001:3048: rgyang grags sogs nas ji srid mkha' khyab kyi bar
NK071(du)001:3049: rang gi rig pas ji tsam dpag nus pas bsgom
NK071(du)001:3050: pa'o // yang yid sprul gyi ji ltar mchod pa las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK071(du)001:3051: rang sems kyi bkod pa yid bzhin gyi char 'bebs pa'i rin po che'i sprin tshogs kyis mchod de /
NK071(du)001:3052: de yang byang chub las phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi
NK071(du)001:3053: khams thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing rnam par dag
NK071(du)001:3054: par rlob ste / de'i yon tan yang mnyen 'jam
NK071(du)001:3055: reg na bde ba ldan pa'i rang bzhin rgyu sna
NK071(du)001:3056: tshogs rin po che'i sa gzhi khod snyoms la mig
NK071(du)001:3057: mang ris su mdzes par bris shing rin po che'i
NK071(du)001:3058: phra tshom gyis spras pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3059: ri bo rnams 'dod dgu kun 'byung ba'i rin chen gyi phung por gnas pa 'od 'bar ba dang /
NK071(du)001:3060: rgya mtsho sogs kha dog dang /
NK071(du)001:3061: dbyibs legs pa'i rdzing bu ro bro ba'i mchog bsil
NK071(du)001:3062: zhing yangs pa sogs yan lag brgyad ldan gyi tshul
NK071(du)001:3063: dang / rgyun rin chen las grub pa'i khang pa rgyan bkod sna tshogs kyis mdzes pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3064: rin po che'i rgyan dang dar gyi lda ldi sbrel ba'i lha'i dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal dang /
NK071(du)001:3066: chos kyi tshigs su bcad pa'i sgrar rang byung ba
NK071(du)001:3067: dang gos bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs la
NK071(du)001:3068: sogs pa sna tshogs dang do shal dpung rgyan se
NK071(du)001:3069: mo do // sogs rin po che'i rgyan gyi khyad par dang /
NK071(du)001:3070: ro brgya ldan pa'i bza' ba dang /
NK071(du)001:3071: bdud rtsi'i btung ba ro bro ba'i tshogs rnams dang /
NK071(du)001:3072: 'gro ba kun kyang rang lus la ji ltar mdzes
NK071(du)001:3073: par brgyan cing 'dod yon sna tshogs thogs pa'i lha
NK071(du)001:3074: dang lha mo zhing gi rdul snyed kyis lus kyi
NK071(du)001:3075: bro gar dang ngag gi glu dbyangs la sogs pa
NK071(du)001:3076: bsam yas kyis phyogs bcu nam mkha' khams thams cad
NK071(du)001:3077: yongs su bkang nas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun la
NK071(du)001:3078: re re zhing nas rgyas par dbul te ji ltar
NK071(du)001:3079: na / skal ldan rnal 'byor ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:3080: mi gsal ba'am gsal ba'i khyad par gyis dus rim
NK071(du)001:3081: gyis yang na gcig car du spros te 'khor gsum
NK071(du)001:3082: mi dmigs chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam pa nyid du
NK071(du)001:3083: na / sbyor zhing / snang srid mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3084: las rgya shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gsal ldan
NK071(du)001:3085: ma yin na rang nyid kyis bya ba'am mi ldan
NK071(du)001:3086: na yab kyi lhar bskyed cing mkha' gsang byin gyis
NK071(du)001:3087: rlabs la dper na 'phags pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis stong
NK071(du)001:3088: gsum gyi khams yungs 'brur gzhug cing chud pa'i tshul
NK071(du)001:3089: bzhin du yum gyi pad+ma sna rtse yungs 'bru tsam
NK071(du)001:3090: la rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad tshang
NK071(du)001:3091: zhing ma 'dres par bkod pa la chos kyi dbyings
NK071(du)001:3092: nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim
NK071(du)001:3093: pa thabs shes rol pa'i bde bas mchod do //
NK071(du)001:3094: des lha rnams mnyes nas dngos grub ster ba las
NK071(du)001:3095: mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig mchog gi bdud rtsi ste
NK071(du)001:3096: de ltar bde ba'i bdag nyid chen po yum gyi
NK071(du)001:3098: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mnyes shing
NK071(du)001:3099: de'i byin rlabs kyi srid gsum gyi 'gro ba thams
NK071(du)001:3100: cad la / dga' ba chen po'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:3101: gyi ros khyab par gyur zhing der ma zad rnal
NK071(du)001:3102: 'byor rang nyid sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:3103: la brtan pa thob pa yis /
NK071(du)001:3104: 'bras bu phyogs bcu dus bzhir don gnyis mthar phyin par gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)001:3105: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mnyes pa'i rang bzhin dang /
NK071(du)001:3106: khams gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams la thugs rjes gzigs
NK071(du)001:3107: pa'i ye shes mngon du gsal bar 'gyur ba yin
NK071(du)001:3108: no // rang gi lus ngag sems gsum dang /
NK071(du)001:3109: phyi nang gi chos thams cad /
NK071(du)001:3110: sems kyi snang ba las gzhan gang na'ang mi gnas
NK071(du)001:3111: shing cir yang mi dmigs ngang las med bzhin du
NK071(du)001:3113: mig yor lta bu'i tshul du mnyam par sbyor ba
NK071(du)001:3114: yis yul chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu la yul
NK071(du)001:3115: can rig pa ni ro gcig tu 'dres pas yul
NK071(du)001:3116: med rang gsal nam mkha' ltar mtha' bral du bsgom
NK071(du)001:3117: mo // de ltar las rim kun byas nas dbang
NK071(du)001:3118: gi phyug cing dbang don shes pa'i rdo rje slob
NK071(du)001:3119: dpon rang nyid dbang mchog rgyas bsdus ci rig pas
NK071(du)001:3120: mo // zhugs pa'am / yang na rig pa'i me
NK071(du)001:3121: tog dor bas dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing slob dpon
NK071(du)001:3122: zhugs pa de nas khrus bya ba sogs kyi slob
NK071(du)001:3123: ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs par bya ste zhugs pa
NK071(du)001:3124: de nas rigs kyi bur byas pa skal pa mchog
NK071(du)001:3126: me tog phog pa'i lha dang sbyar nas yon dbul te /
NK071(du)001:3127: de bzhin rigs la rgyal srid de rang gi 'byor
NK071(du)001:3128: pa thams cad dang rdo rje'i rigs la ni rang
NK071(du)001:3129: gis lus dang / pad+ma'i la bu dang chung ma
NK071(du)001:3130: rin chen rigs la gser dngul sogs nor gyi dbyig
NK071(du)001:3131: las kyi rigs la rang gi dngos po'i nang nas
NK071(du)001:3132: rab tu gces pa de dang /
NK071(du)001:3133: rigs drug la rang gi yid du 'ong zhing bla
NK071(du)001:3134: ma'i thugs la gang 'thad kyi dngos po ste rigs
NK071(du)001:3136: yang na ma phyed par rgyal srid sogs rang la gang gces de nyid dbul lo //
NK071(du)001:3137: de ltar dbang phyug la 'dod pa'i longs spyod lngas
NK071(du)001:3138: mchod na rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyang mchod
NK071(du)001:3139: par 'gyur ba yin pas nye ba da lta zhugs
NK071(du)001:3140: pa'i dkyil 'khor de nyid mchod pa lta smos kyang
NK071(du)001:3141: ci dgos te / sangs rgyas thams cad rdo rje
NK071(du)001:3142: slob dpon gyi sku la zhugs nas 'dul bya'i mchod
NK071(du)001:3144: des nyams chags sogs nyes pa thams cad byang zhing dag par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:3145: thog mar slob dpon gyis slob ma'i rgyud brtags pa
NK071(du)001:3146: dad pa dang brtson 'grus dang brtul zhugs sogs dbang
NK071(du)001:3147: bskur rung gi snod ldan du rab tu rtogs na
NK071(du)001:3148: blo tshod dang sbyar te de'ang slob bu dad pa
NK071(du)001:3149: can la phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu sbyin zhing rang
NK071(du)001:3150: gzhan gyi don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nang
NK071(du)001:3151: nus pa'i dbang lnga spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs
NK071(du)001:3152: can la gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum snod kyi
NK071(du)001:3153: rim pa bzhin 'tshams par sbyin par bya zhing slob
NK071(du)001:3154: dpon gyis lhag pa'i snying rjes slob bu'i rgyud chud
NK071(du)001:3155: ma zos par rjes su bzung ba bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3156: yang gong du gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de
NK071(du)001:3157: las gzhan yang rdo rje'i tshad ji ltar na thal
NK071(du)001:3158: mo ni brda' ste slob dpon yab yum gnyis kyi
NK071(du)001:3159: dbang po rab tu bsnol nas yab lha sku phyag
NK071(du)001:3160: rgya chen por gsal ba'i 'phangs su yum blangs nas
NK071(du)001:3161: ni bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rten gyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:3162: 'khor gsang ba'i rdo rje mtshon byed rdo rje sngon
NK071(du)001:3163: po rtse lnga pa mdzub gang ba'i tshad yang /
NK071(du)001:3164: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bzo bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3165: de las gzhan yang lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:3166: 'khor bzhengs der 'jug pa'i dbang du byas na 'dzin
NK071(du)001:3167: rtog rig pa'i dbyings su mnyam pa'i sa gzhi sa
NK071(du)001:3168: yi cho gas rab tu mnyam par bya ste /
NK071(du)001:3169: dkyil 'khor ni gnas khang dang 'byor pa'i khyad par
NK071(du)001:3170: la chung 'bring che gsum du 'gyur pas dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:3171: du log rer khru gang gi tshad du bya ba'am
NK071(du)001:3172: yang na lus gang tshad du bya ste /
NK071(du)001:3173: chung tshad gnyis po yang na lus gsum gyi tshad de khru bcu gnyis dang /
NK071(du)001:3174: yang thig skabs 'gying skor gyi phur bu gnyis dang
NK071(du)001:3175: srad bu la pad+ma'i rgyus pa dang ras bal skud
NK071(du)001:3176: pa gnyis tshon gyi kha dog so sor phye ba
NK071(du)001:3177: ste / thig skud kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga 'am lnga sgril dang /
NK071(du)001:3178: dam tshig gi thig skud kha dog dagu'am gsum sgril lo //
NK071(du)001:3179: gos rgyan bzang pos mdzes par brgyan pa'i mtshan ldan
NK071(du)001:3180: yid du 'ong ba'i grogs phyag rgya lo bcu drug
NK071(du)001:3182: ye thig gdab pa'i srad bu dang /
NK071(du)001:3183: dam tshig gi thig skud byin gyis rlobs pa'i cho ga phun sum tshogs par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3184: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi las la mkhas shing lag
NK071(du)001:3185: len dang ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon chen pos
NK071(du)001:3186: rig pa bsgrim te thig gi las bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3187: dkyil 'khor gyi tshad yang na khru ni bcu drug gi tshad dang /
NK071(du)001:3188: gong gi khru bcu gnyis po dang gnyis 'bring tshad dang /
NK071(du)001:3189: khru nyi shu'am yang na nyi shu rtsa lngar bya ba gnyis ni che tshad do //
NK071(du)001:3190: de nyid rab tu gnas pa sa bon phyag mtshan
NK071(du)001:3191: las rigs kyi dkyil 'khor thabs shes zung 'brel lnga'am
NK071(du)001:3192: rgyas par na so so'i rigs chung dang bcas lha
NK071(du)001:3193: lnga bcu rnams sgom pa zhu ba las rin po
NK071(du)001:3194: che'i rdul du gyur par bsam de nas rjes 'brel
NK071(du)001:3195: du sku phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan dang /
NK071(du)001:3196: gsung sa bon dang thugs phyag mtshan sogs mtshan ma
NK071(du)001:3197: gang rung dang ldan pa'i gzugs kyang dgod par bya'o
NK071(du)001:3198: // bris dkyil las gzhan yang na rgyang grags bsgom pa chung tshad dang 'bring dpag tshad dam /
NK071(du)001:3200: bsam yas par khyab pa'i sangs rgyas stong sogs bsam yas lhun gyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs bsgom mo //
NK071(du)001:3201: mtshon ye shes lnga'i don ma mthong ba'i rmong pa
NK071(du)001:3202: rnams la don bstan pa'i phyir tshon gyi kha dog
NK071(du)001:3203: lnga lngar phye bas nyi shu rtsa lnga'am /
NK071(du)001:3204: yang na kha dog lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3205: dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum gang gis 'dul ba'i
NK071(du)001:3206: cho ga ste de'i lugs bzhin du bag dang ldan
NK071(du)001:3208: de nas bskyed rim stong nyid kyi ngang las ting
NK071(du)001:3209: 'dzin gyi rtsal ma 'gags pa'i rol mo mtha' yas
NK071(du)001:3210: mchog / dang ldan pas sa bon las 'byung lnga'i rim rtsegs sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:3211: sems sprin las tha ta sogs gsung yi ge'i 'khor lo'am /
NK071(du)001:3212: yang na yig 'bru rnams so so'i gdan la bkod de 'od zer spro bsdu bya'am /
NK071(du)001:3213: h'u m+aum sogs snying po bskyed pa'am /
NK071(du)001:3214: yang na phyag rgya phra ba phyag mtshan nam /
NK071(du)001:3215: rag pa lha'i sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i lha dang
NK071(du)001:3216: ldan par bskyed cing byin gyis rlabs na dngos grub
NK071(du)001:3217: rnams gnyis ya mtshan rmad po che /
NK071(du)001:3218: 'grub par gyur ba ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dam
NK071(du)001:3219: tshig go 'di ltar sa dang shing la sogs pa
NK071(du)001:3220: rgyud dman pa las phyag rgya'i rnam par byas pas
NK071(du)001:3221: kyang rnam grol 'bras bu'i rim pa skal pa dang
NK071(du)001:3222: mthun pa thob par 'gyur na gzung 'dzin dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:3223: stong nyid ye shes kyis sbyangs shing lhar bskyed pas
NK071(du)001:3224: 'bras bu thob pa smos ci dgos te sems kyi
NK071(du)001:3225: de kho na nyid ye nas lha yin pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:3226: ro // phyogs dus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK071(du)001:3227: pa'i bdag nyid chen po cir yang mi dmigs pa
NK071(du)001:3228: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spros bral las gzugs sku ye
NK071(du)001:3229: shes kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK071(du)001:3230: gang du na rig pa rang snang dbyer med dam
NK071(du)001:3231: tshig gi dkyil 'khor la spyan drangs pa de nyid
NK071(du)001:3232: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid kyis dam ye mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)001:3233: bas / phyogs dus kun nas don gnyis mthar phyin pa yi /
NK071(du)001:3234: rgyal ba thams cad sngon bsnyen pa'i smon lam gyi
NK071(du)001:3235: dbang gis 'gro don mdzad pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:3236: 'khor du thugs rjes bzhengs nas byon pa dam tshig
NK071(du)001:3237: gi dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs pas nye bar 'brel
NK071(du)001:3238: bar gyur pa'i phyir dam tshig gi mchog ces bya'o
NK071(du)001:3239: // yang 'bras bu ni dper na lha'i gnas sogs
NK071(du)001:3240: su dpag bsam gyi shing dang yid bzhin gyi nor
NK071(du)001:3241: bu rin po ches mchod par byed pa rnams kyi
NK071(du)001:3242: re ba skong nus pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3243: der ma zad gzhan yang 'dod 'byung ba'i gnas su gyur pa kun snang yang don /
NK071(du)001:3244: de dag rdzas grub tu yod nas de la spyod pa ma yin te /
NK071(du)001:3245: rang rang gi sems kyi snang ba bsod nams kyi
NK071(du)001:3246: mthu brtas shing brtan par gyur pa nyid de lta
NK071(du)001:3248: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ngo mtshar ba'i
NK071(du)001:3249: cho 'phrul chen po ya mtshan rmad byung ston gyi
NK071(du)001:3250: chos de yang lam pas phar 'grod nas der slebs
NK071(du)001:3251: pa'am / gzhan zhig na yod pa tshur 'ongs pa ma yin te /
NK071(du)001:3252: thabs bde ba chen po la goms pa brten pa'i
NK071(du)001:3253: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid shes rab stong pa
NK071(du)001:3254: nyid kyi dbyings su grol ba'i zung 'jug /
NK071(du)001:3255: de lta bu yi ngang du ma brtsal bar rang byung du snang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3256: shes rab chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po nyid /
NK071(du)001:3257: thabs lam gyi phyag rgya chen po goms par gyur
NK071(du)001:3258: pa'i phyir gzhi'i ye shes de nyid la ni 'bras
NK071(du)001:3259: bu rang snang ba'i ye shes rol pa tsam du
NK071(du)001:3260: zad do // de yang ye shes la ye shes rol pa nyid kyang dngos po la grub ste /
NK071(du)001:3261: sgyu ma ltar gsog gsob ya ma barla'o //
NK071(du)001:3262: der ma zad sku yang de dang 'dra ste /
NK071(du)001:3263: rgyal ba sprul pa'i sku 'jig rte mngon du 'byung zhing 'gro ba sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3264: longs sku rang snang ba'i byin rlabs kyis brda'i chos
NK071(du)001:3265: ston pa'ang ye shes la brjod pa de bzhin te
NK071(du)001:3266: / don bya ba'i yul la don byed nus pa'i
NK071(du)001:3267: thugs rjes gzi byin mnga' ba'i phrin las kyis sku
NK071(du)001:3268: dang ye shes kyi rol par bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:3269: sgyu ma lta bu phrin las kyi don mdzad na'ang /
NK071(du)001:3270: ngo bo 'gyur med sku lnga dbyer mi phyed pa
NK071(du)001:3271: rdo rje'i rang bzhin can mi shig pa'i mthu mnga'
NK071(du)001:3272: bas btsan po ste che ba'i mchog dam pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3273: yang bskyed rim skabs stong chen snying rje sgyu ma
NK071(du)001:3274: phyag rgya gcig pa phra rag gnyis phyag rgya spros
NK071(du)001:3275: bcas kyi cho ga lnga ni sngon du rdzogs pa
NK071(du)001:3276: ste brtan pa thob par byas shing /
NK071(du)001:3277: dam tshig sogs lam gyi dang bro gar sogs sgrub
NK071(du)001:3278: rdzas kyi yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan pa
NK071(du)001:3279: dang yid skyob pa'i phyir sngags te yan lag gi
NK071(du)001:3280: lha dgu'i dbu rgyan rigs bdag gcig tu brtsis pas
NK071(du)001:3281: yan lag gi lha lnga'am de dag rdzogs par gsal
NK071(du)001:3283: dam tshig ma nyams par sgrub pa la 'jug cing
NK071(du)001:3284: zhugs nas nyams len la rab tu brtson na 'grub
NK071(du)001:3285: par 'gyur ro // de'ang dbang brtson yang rab kyis
NK071(du)001:3286: zhag ni sum bcu phrag drug ste zla ba drug
NK071(du)001:3287: gam rab kyi zla ba bcu gnyis 'bring gis bcu
NK071(du)001:3288: bzhi tha mas kyang zla ba bcu drug rnams kyis
NK071(du)001:3289: dbang po brtul na rnam smin nam /
NK071(du)001:3290: rno na tshe la dbang bsgyur ba'i rigs kyi dam
NK071(du)001:3291: pa ste tshe dbang rig 'dzin 'grub par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)001:3292: // mthong lam la gnyis las nus thob tshe dbang rig 'dzin thob pa de tshe lo //
NK071(du)001:3293: brgya brgya na phyir bsnur ba lan bcu drug ste
NK071(du)001:3294: stong drug brgya tshun chad kyis rim gyis pa phyag
NK071(du)001:3295: chen dang thod rgal ba tshe dbang sogs nas mthar
NK071(du)001:3296: thug gi 'bras bu sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa
NK071(du)001:3297: rdzogs pa ni sangs rgyas te /
NK071(du)001:3298: de nyid thob par byed do //
NK071(du)001:3299: rim gyis dang thod rgal gyi rig 'dzin gyi dgongs
NK071(du)001:3300: pa rang rig pa'i ye shes spros bral thig le
NK071(du)001:3301: de nyid kyi ngang la mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus
NK071(du)001:3302: su sangs rgyas kyi ye shes spros pa dang bral
NK071(du)001:3303: ba'i thig le de nyid rang snang ba'i phyir dgongs
NK071(du)001:3304: pa'i ngo bo bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yas
NK071(du)001:3305: pa'i yon tan ma btsal lhun gyi grub pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:3306: mchog ste / de tshe phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon
NK071(du)001:3307: par rdzogs pa byang chub pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK071(du)001:3308: zhing khams rnam par dag par yon tan bsam gyis
NK071(du)001:3309: mi khyab cing mtha' yas pa dang zhing der rgya
NK071(du)001:3310: gar du'ang ma chad pas 'di tsam zhes bsam pa'i
NK071(du)001:3311: yul dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang gzhi tshad med
NK071(du)001:3312: ye shes kyi 'khor lo la brten pa'i rgyan dang
NK071(du)001:3313: mchog ste / / 'dod yon gyi rol mo'i sprin tshogs rnam par 'khrigs shing /
NK071(du)001:3314: de ltar rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yon tan ma lus
NK071(du)001:3315: zad med rgyan gyi 'khor lo bsam yas kun kyang
NK071(du)001:3316: / skad cig dang por mngon gsum gyis mthong nas
NK071(du)001:3317: gnyis par nye bar brnyes pa ste de thob pa
NK071(du)001:3318: dang gsung yang rgya chen po'i gsung gi snang ba
NK071(du)001:3319: las gdul bya'i don lhun grub tu byung ba'ang gzhi
NK071(du)001:3320: lam 'bras bu ye shes gsum tshul mthun pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:3321: shes de nyid gzhan du ma grub pas rig pa'i
NK071(du)001:3322: ye shes la rang snang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3323: sangs rgyas gzugs sku'i rol pa tha dad du ston
NK071(du)001:3324: kyang chos nyid las ma g.yos pas gcig dang du
NK071(du)001:3325: ma'i mthar bral ba yis mtha' gnyis kheg pas yod
NK071(du)001:3327: de ltos kyi dbus kyang grub pa med de brjod
NK071(du)001:3328: med de bzhin nyid kyi phyir sangs rgyas kyis kyang
NK071(du)001:3329: gzigs bya gzigs byed las 'das pas mi gzigs te
NK071(du)001:3330: / de lta na'ang rang byung ye shes kyi dgongs
NK071(du)001:3331: pa ni gnas yul dang yul can gnyis med par
NK071(du)001:3332: rang gsal ma 'gags par snang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3333: 'gro ba'i log pa rtog pas rnam par brtags pa'i
NK071(du)001:3334: sgrib pa ye nas rnam par dag cing chos dang
NK071(du)001:3335: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis 'brel ba dang /
NK071(du)001:3336: sangs rgyas rnams ni ye shes kyang chos dbyings las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3337: yul yul can tha mi dad par 'brel ba dang /
NK071(du)001:3338: sangs rgyas rnams sngon byang chub spyod pa'i tshe thugs
NK071(du)001:3339: rje chen pos sems can sgrol bar dam bcas pas
NK071(du)001:3341: de ltar 'brel pa gsum gyis 'brel bas na thugs
NK071(du)001:3342: rjes gzigs pa zhes bya la mkhyen gnyis kyis 'gro
NK071(du)001:3343: ba rigs drug gi 'jig rten dus snga phyi dang
NK071(du)001:3344: gnas mtho dman sogs ma lus pa 'khor 'das kyi
NK071(du)001:3345: chos thams cad dbyer med mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK071(du)001:3346: snang la rang bzhin med par gzigs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3347: yang dbang gi skabs dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:3348: thabs shes zung 'brel bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:3349: la rgyas par 'dri ba'am mi nus pas ni gtso
NK071(du)001:3350: bo stangs dpyal te yab yum gnyis sam yang na
NK071(du)001:3351: rigs lnga yab yum tsam byas te dad ldan gyi
NK071(du)001:3352: slob ma der rab tu zhugs na /
NK071(du)001:3353: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa la zhugs pa dang 'dra bar
NK071(du)001:3354: 'dod pa'i don dbang dngos grub yid 'ong thob pas
NK071(du)001:3355: na sngar 'og min du thar lam pa zhugs pa
NK071(du)001:3356: dang skal pa mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3357: de ltar dkyil 'khor la zhugs phyin chad yi dam
NK071(du)001:3358: gyi lha dang skal pa mnyam par gyur pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:3359: ye shes de nyid don du gnyer nas bsgrubs na
NK071(du)001:3360: dus nye bar mngon du 'byung ba'i mchog thun gyi
NK071(du)001:3361: dngos grub ya mtshan chen po nyid 'byung zhing thob
NK071(du)001:3362: par nges pas lha bsgom pa la nan du bya
NK071(du)001:3363: ste / gzhan du lha'i bsgom bzlas la dad pa
NK071(du)001:3364: med na rdo rje gsung gi dam tshig nyams par
NK071(du)001:3365: gyur pas na 'di phyir mi 'dod pa'i gnas su
NK071(du)001:3366: lhung ba'i phyir phung bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3367: de skad ces ston pas ched du brjod par mdzad do //
NK071(du)001:3368: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:3369: las 'dis rdo rje gsum thob byed las kyi rim
NK071(du)001:3370: pa gsum du bkod pa'i don mchog tu gsang ba
NK071(du)001:3371: 'da' daka'i dam tshig gi le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3374: zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:3375: rim par bgrod pa dbang las dbang gi dkyil 'khor der 'jug pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3376: snod dang sbyar te bskul tshul sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:3377: rol pa'i phrin las las me sgo nas phrin las bya tshul zur tsam dang /
NK071(du)001:3378: mchod pa'i skabs lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa rnams bstan /
NK071(du)001:3379: bi ma las ma mthong rmongs la bstan pa'i phyir //
NK071(du)001:3380: dkri drangs rdul tshon bstan pa gces //
NK071(du)001:3382: le'u brgyad par thugs rtags phyag rgyar gsal ba de nyid ma mthong ba'i rmongs pa bstan pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3383: le'u 'dir gdul bya rnams lam 'dir dkri zhing drangs
NK071(du)001:3384: ba'i rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bstan par gsungs so
NK071(du)001:3390: de nas sogs brjod de bar gnyis pa gzhung la gsum /
NK071(du)001:3391: dbang bskur ba'i rim pa ma bskur ba'i skyon /
NK071(du)001:3396: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ba'i rim pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3398: dbu rgyan sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3399: gnyis pa nus dbang lnga po rigs bsdus na gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:3400: bdag don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan sgom /
NK071(du)001:3401: gzhan don nus pa la phrin las dang 'chad pa dbang /
NK071(du)001:3402: gnyis ka'i don nus pa la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dang gsum /
NK071(du)001:3404: nyan dbang dang sgom dbang ngo //
NK071(du)001:3406: bsam rgyud dang sgrag tshig go /
NK071(du)001:3408: nyan byed sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3409: gnyis pa ni tram gsang ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3410: gnyis pa bsgom dbang la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3414: gsal ba'i 'khor lo'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3416: dus gsum sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3417: gnyis pa la phrin las dang /
NK071(du)001:3419: phrin las la bsam rgyud dang /
NK071(du)001:3422: lag pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3424: khyed ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3425: de nas 'chad dbang la gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:3427: smra byed sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3429: chos kyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3430: gsum pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gi bsam rgyud ni /
NK071(du)001:3431: bskyod chen sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:3433: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3434: gsum pa zab dbang bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3435: shes rab sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3436: gnyis pa dbang ma bskur ba'i skyon ni /
NK071(du)001:3437: slob dpon sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3438: gsum pa bskur ba'i yon tan ni /
NK071(du)001:3442: de lta'i gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3443: dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur tshul mdor bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:3444: de nas ji ltar bskur ba'i rim pa ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3445: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po chos kyi rgyal
NK071(du)001:3446: po'i go 'phang sbyin pa zhes bya'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:3448: dbang bskur ba'i ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)001:3449: dbang rnams las dang po zab dbang bskur ba ni /
NK071(du)001:3450: yum shes rab ma mtshan ldan lo nyi shu bcu
NK071(du)001:3451: drug bcu gnyis ma rnams rim par dbang gsum gyi
NK071(du)001:3452: rten dang thabs yab ni gsang dbang la slob dpon
NK071(du)001:3453: dang / gong ma gnyis la slob ma ste /
NK071(du)001:3454: yab yum lhar gsal bas thabs shes gnyis kyi mkha'
NK071(du)001:3455: gsang byin gyis rlobs shing sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas
NK071(du)001:3456: phyag rgya bzhis snyoms par zhugs pa las yab kyi
NK071(du)001:3457: byang sems bde ba'i rang bzhin h'u yig gi 'bru
NK071(du)001:3458: tshogs su gsal ba'i chu rgyun yab kyi rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:3459: lam nas yab yum gyi pad+mora 'khyil ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3460: gsang dbang gi dus mkha' gsang gi /
NK071(du)001:3461: rtse nas dngos su len cing rdor sems su gsal
NK071(du)001:3462: ba snying gar babs te bstim zhing des sbyang bya
NK071(du)001:3463: kun sbyangs te sems nyid don dam spros med kyi
NK071(du)001:3465: de nas nyan dbang slob bu'i nyan byed rna bar
NK071(du)001:3466: byang chub las 'khor lo rtsib bzhi sgo dang bcas
NK071(du)001:3467: pa'i gzhal yas su sgra gsal ba'i thig le shin
NK071(du)001:3468: tu dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid du gnas pa de
NK071(du)001:3469: tram yig zung lnga gsung chos kyi phyag rgya'i tshogs
NK071(du)001:3470: mchog las rin chen 'byung kyi dkyil 'khor gsal bar
NK071(du)001:3471: bskyed la bskur slob sogs dang slob dpon gyi sbyor
NK071(du)001:3472: mtshams nas spros pa'i 'od kyis bskul bas lha rjes
NK071(du)001:3473: chags kyis zhu ba slob bur thim pas slob bu
NK071(du)001:3474: zhu ba rin 'byung gi skur bskyed la glegs bam
NK071(du)001:3475: gtad de t+r+aam yig 'go 'dren gsang ba ma h+aa
NK071(du)001:3476: gsang chen a nu gsang mchog a ti yo ga'i
NK071(du)001:3477: rgyud gang dang der ma zad gsang ba rgyud kri
NK071(du)001:3478: yog sogs kun la'ang nyan par dbang bas mnyan par
NK071(du)001:3479: bya zhes gnang ba sbyin zhing nyan nas gsang ba'i
NK071(du)001:3480: don nyid bsam pas brtag cing spyod pa las gzhan
NK071(du)001:3481: 'chad dbang ma thob kyi bar de srid du su
NK071(du)001:3482: la'ang smra bar bya ba min pas ma ston ces
NK071(du)001:3483: dam sgrag pa'o // de nas dran pa gsal bar
NK071(du)001:3484: byed pa'i rten snying rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su
NK071(du)001:3485: dran pa gsal ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid me
NK071(du)001:3486: tog phog pa'i lha gang yin gyi yi ge zung
NK071(du)001:3487: lnga'i phreng ba'i tshogs mchog las /
NK071(du)001:3488: rigs gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim pa
NK071(du)001:3489: sogs sngar ltar las slob bu'i lag tu phreng ba
NK071(du)001:3490: gtad de / bu khyod dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po /
NK071(du)001:3491: yin pas sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje las mi 'da' bar gzung ste /
NK071(du)001:3492: rgyal ba thams cad ni sgrub pas mnyes par mchod
NK071(du)001:3493: la 'bras bu rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)001:3495: lag pa'i rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su bya byed
NK071(du)001:3496: gsal ba'i rten gyi thig le dwangs pa'i ngo bo
NK071(du)001:3497: nyid / h+aam gi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las /
NK071(du)001:3498: 'phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim /
NK071(du)001:3499: pa sogs las slob bu don grub gsal ba'i lag tu rgya gram gtad de /
NK071(du)001:3500: bu khyod ni da phyin chad rdo rje las mkhan
NK071(du)001:3501: yin gyis zhi rgyas sogs las rnams ma lus kun
NK071(du)001:3502: gyis shig dang de'i grogs pho nya mang po'i rol
NK071(du)001:3503: pa nang du 'du zhing phyir 'phro ba kun gyis
NK071(du)001:3504: khyod kyi gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi dgos pa
NK071(du)001:3505: sgrub par byed pa yin zhes so /
NK071(du)001:3506: smra byed lce'i 'do rtsa'i 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su
NK071(du)001:3507: sgra gsal ba'i thig le dwangs pa'i ngo bo nyid
NK071(du)001:3508: h+r+aihzunga lnga yig phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las /
NK071(du)001:3509: gsung chos kyi rigs snang mtha'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo gsal spro thim sogs gong bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:3510: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos kyi bdud rtsi bla med kyis /
NK071(du)001:3511: gdul phyir dad ldan gyi skyes bu ngom par byos
NK071(du)001:3512: shig ji ltar na dbang po rab 'bring tha ma'i
NK071(du)001:3513: blo can la / so so'i blo yi rim pa
NK071(du)001:3514: dang mthun par chos kyi gsang ba sgrags par bya
NK071(du)001:3515: ba las gzhan du min te don du mi 'gyur
NK071(du)001:3516: ba'i phyir ro zhes bsgrags so //
NK071(du)001:3517: bskyod chen yan lag lngar 'khor lo'i gzhal yas khang
NK071(du)001:3518: cha lnga'i gnas su bskyod byed gsal ba'i reg shes
NK071(du)001:3521: mgo bor lag g.yon par s+w+aa /
NK071(du)001:3522: rkang g.yon par +aam g.yas par h+aa rnams zung lnga
NK071(du)001:3523: lnga las rigs lnga so so'i rigs chung dang bcas
NK071(du)001:3524: pa'i dkyil 'khor lnga dang lus kyi steng 'og phyogs
NK071(du)001:3525: mtshams bcur khro bcu yab yum gyi phreng ba sgom
NK071(du)001:3526: pa sogs sngar ltar las slob bu kun bzang gsal
NK071(du)001:3527: ba'i lag tu rdor dril gtad de /
NK071(du)001:3528: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba thams cad kyi /
NK071(du)001:3529: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag nyid che ba'i mchog ste /
NK071(du)001:3530: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po khyod
NK071(du)001:3531: yin pas dkyil 'khor kun gyi bdag po gyis la
NK071(du)001:3532: skal pa dang mtshams par sbyin pa'i bya ba la
NK071(du)001:3534: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i slob dpon sgo gsum gyis
NK071(du)001:3535: mnyes par ma byas shing phan nus zab mo'i dbang
NK071(du)001:3536: rnams rgyud la thob par ma byas par gsang sngags
NK071(du)001:3537: kyi rgyud dang man ngag nyan 'chad sgrub pa la
NK071(du)001:3538: sogs pa'i bya ba rtsom pa rnams tshe 'dir sgrub
NK071(du)001:3539: pa rnams 'bras bu dngos grub med cing phyi ma
NK071(du)001:3540: ngan 'gror ltung ba las brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3541: dbang ni slob bu lhar gsal ba la rigs lnga
NK071(du)001:3542: sogs kyis rlabs pa'i dbang rdzas dbu rgyan spyi bor
NK071(du)001:3543: bskon la dar dmar mthing gi cod pan mgo bo'i
NK071(du)001:3544: g.yas g.yon du 'phur zhing phreng ba mgor bcings pa
NK071(du)001:3545: dang / go cha lus la bskon zhing rgyal mtshan lag tu gtad de /
NK071(du)001:3546: phyag rgya spyi bo'am snying gar bzhag pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3547: gdugs spyi bor bzhag pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3548: bum pa'i chus spyi bor bskur zhing bza' btung khar sbyin pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3549: snying po lnga gnas lnga yis rdzas la bstim pa ste /
NK071(du)001:3550: de ltar dbang bskur na phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3551: dbang thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad bu khyod rgyal
NK071(du)001:3552: ba'i sras su gyur pa yin zhing phyi mar ngan
NK071(du)001:3553: song du lhung ba'i las zad par byas ngan 'gro'i
NK071(du)001:3554: sdug bsngal thams cad med pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3555: 'dir yang tshe ring zhing bde ba phun sum tshogs
NK071(du)001:3556: pa dang ldan la skye ba phyi mar phan dbang
NK071(du)001:3557: gi mtho ris lha mi'i rgyal po dang nus dbang
NK071(du)001:3558: gis thar pa'i lam ston pa'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK071(du)001:3559: zab dbang gis rgyal kun rigs kyi bdag po chen por 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3561: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:3562: las 'dis snod dang 'tshams par dbang gsum sbyin pa'i
NK071(du)001:3565: // zhes pa'i le'u 'dis zhi khro thun mong dbang gi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:3566: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las /
NK071(du)001:3567: rim par bgrod pa dbang gi skabs /
NK071(du)001:3568: dbang gi bskur thabs dngos bstan no //
NK071(du)001:3569: bi ma las dkyil 'khor bdag la bstan pa'i las //
NK071(du)001:3570: dbang mchog sbyin pa mchog yin no //
NK071(du)001:3572: le'u dgu par rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nyid la bstan pa'i las /
NK071(du)001:3573: le'u 'dir dbang mchog sbyin par bstan pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:3575: bcu gnyis pa 'brel bsdebs nas tshogs sgrub bstan pa gsum la ste /
NK071(du)001:3580: le'u gnyis ka de nas sogs brjod do bar gnyis pa gzhung gnyis sdeb pa la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:3582: de gsungs pa'i tshul lo dang po gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3583: mtshan gnyis gsum mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3588: rgyu shes pa'i dang rkyen 'jug pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:3589: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'ii mtshan nyid do //
NK071(du)001:3592: grub 'bras gzhan tshol byed kyi zhen pa dgag pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3594: rtogs pa bzhi'i dang dag pa gsum gyi dang /
NK071(du)001:3595: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs so //
NK071(du)001:3597: rgyu gcig sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3599: snod bcud rgyud sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:3601: mnyam gnyis sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:3603: dus bzhi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3604: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid la rim gyis pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3608: ji ltar sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3611: gnas yo thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3614: yan lag sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3616: gnas dang sogs rkang pa bdun /
NK071(du)001:3618: sgrub pa'i sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3619: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:3621: khro bo'i sgo nas sgrub pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3623: bsnyen sgrub bzhi mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3626: bsnyen pa dang ni sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3627: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:3629: nye sgrub thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3636: mkha' dkyil sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3638: tshom bu lnga pa gsum pa gcig pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3639: dang po ni lnga dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3641: de bzhin sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3643: rigs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3645: rnal 'byor pho mos lha so sor bsgom pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3646: tshom bu'i lha sgrub thabs so //
NK071(du)001:3648: rnal 'byor thabs dang sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:3652: lnga pa bsgrub pa'i thabs so //
NK071(du)001:3654: rdo rje rig sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3656: yang na sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3659: gsum pa bsgrub pa chen po la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:3660: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)001:3661: de'i bsgrub bya dngos grub bo //
NK071(du)001:3663: yo byad bzhi la spyad pa'i thabs dang /
NK071(du)001:3664: +aa li k+aa li la spyad pa'i thabs so //
NK071(du)001:3666: gos rgyan sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3670: de gnyis spyad kyang nyes pas mi gos par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3674: yum gyi mkha' las dngos grub chen po blang ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3676: lha mo sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3678: yum gyi sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3680: sgrub pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3681: gnyis pa k+aa li sgrol ba'i thabs ni /
NK071(du)001:3682: zhing gyur sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3683: gsum pa nyes pas mi dgos par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3684: ye nas sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3685: gnyis pa bsgrub bya dngos grub la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:3689: rnal 'byor sngags 'chang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3691: yan lag sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3692: gnyis pa khro bo'i sgo nas bsgrub pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3693: khro bo khro mo'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3694: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid gcig char ba ni /
NK071(du)001:3695: cho ga lhag gam sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3696: gsum pa 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i mtshan nyid la'ang rim gyis dang gcig 'char gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:3697: dang po rim gyis la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:3698: yo byad lnga la spyad pa'i 'bras bu tshe dbang rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs /
NK071(du)001:3699: mthar thug gi 'bras bu bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3702: glu tshig sgra'i rgyan dang bgo ba'i /
NK071(du)001:3704: +aa li k+aa li'i yo byad rnams la spyad pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK071(du)001:3706: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:3708: glu tshig sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3709: gsum pa ni rgyan dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3711: bza' dang sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3714: gnyis pa tshe dbang gi cha lugs ni /
NK071(du)001:3715: mi dang sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:3717: pha rol sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:3718: gnyis pa gcig 'char ba'i 'bras bu ni /
NK071(du)001:3719: dkyil 'khor kun tu sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:3720: gnyis pa gsungs tshul la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:3721: bka' gsang sngags mtshon pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3722: gzhung gsungs pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:3728: gsum pa mtshan gnyis sdeb pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3729: gsang ba'i sogs nas bcu gcig pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3732: de gnyis ka'i gzhung dngos bshad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:3733: sngar tshogs sgrub mdor bstan pa de nas le'u gong
NK071(du)001:3734: 'og sdeb nas bshad kyang 'dir dkyus bzhin bkod pas
NK071(du)001:3735: 'chad nyan sogs kyi dus 'grel sgrig par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3736: tshogs sgrub rgyas par ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3737: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos bsgrub bya zung 'jug /
NK071(du)001:3738: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po'i go 'phang mchog gi
NK071(du)001:3739: dngos grub la dbang sgyur ba zhes bya ba'i ting
NK071(du)001:3740: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod
NK071(du)001:3742: de yang 'khor 'das gnyis snang gi chos ni rgyu gcig pa'i rtags kyi gzhal bya yin la /
NK071(du)001:3743: gzhal tshul snga ma'i gtan tshigs phyi ma'i gzhal byar byas te /
NK071(du)001:3745: yig 'bru'i tshul gyi dang byin gyis rlabs pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:3746: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs bzhi btsal bas /
NK071(du)001:3747: rim pa ji lta bar rang bzhin skye med rol
NK071(du)001:3748: pa 'gags med ngo bo dbyer med de'ang yul yul
NK071(du)001:3749: can med par mngon sum du rtogs pa ni mtshan
NK071(du)001:3750: nyid blo bral te grub mtha' 'o //
NK071(du)001:3751: de ltar rab tu rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi yi
NK071(du)001:3752: gtan tshigs kyis chos thams cad gtan la phebs te
NK071(du)001:3753: gnas lugs ji lta ba bzhin rang rig pa'i mngon
NK071(du)001:3754: sum du gsal bar rdzogs pas spong len med par
NK071(du)001:3755: cham gcig sku dang ye shes kyi rol bar dbang
NK071(du)001:3756: bsgyur ba'i phyir rgyal po ste 'di las che ba'i
NK071(du)001:3758: bsgrub bya'i skabs rang snang gi yan lag lnga dang dbang po lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:3759: de dag gi rnam shes dang bcas pa kun gyi
NK071(du)001:3760: rnam pa ye shes lnga'i ngo bor smin pa mtshon
NK071(du)001:3761: byed yi ge du shes par bya zhing /
NK071(du)001:3762: des mtshon bya rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rigs lnga yab kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3763: yang na gdul bya'i dbang gi khro bo rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom pa'i bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3764: de bzhin du gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya la
NK071(du)001:3765: sogs pa yul gyi rnam pa kun yum lnga'i ngo
NK071(du)001:3766: bor smin pa mtshon byed yi ge m+aum du shes
NK071(du)001:3767: par bya zhing / des mtshon bya rigs lnga yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom pa'am /
NK071(du)001:3768: yang na khro mo lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3769: sgrubs pa'i yo byad la spyad thabs ni /
NK071(du)001:3770: dar dang zhing lpags sogs bgo ba'i gos dang thod
NK071(du)001:3771: phreng sogs 'dogs pa'i rgyan dang dri ro zhim pa'i
NK071(du)001:3772: bza' btung dang snyan pa'i glu dang sbyar ba'i sgra
NK071(du)001:3773: tshig dang / rigs so so'i rkang bro dang lag gar gyi 'du 'phro ste /
NK071(du)001:3774: yo byad bzhi'i tshogs gang spyod thams cad kyi sprin phung la /
NK071(du)001:3775: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi rang bzhin h+aum gis
NK071(du)001:3776: mtshon nas rang snang gi longs spyod du shes pas
NK071(du)001:3777: chags zhen med par rab spyad na 'bras bu ngo
NK071(du)001:3778: mtshar 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad mnyes pas phan
NK071(du)001:3779: yon rlabs po che thob bo //
NK071(du)001:3780: sbyor ba la brten nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK071(du)001:3784: rnam par rnal 'byor pa'i blo khyad kyis bzang ngan so sor dbye ste bzang po bsten pa'am /
NK071(du)001:3785: yang na mi dbye bar gang rung bsten pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3786: de yang phyag rgya btsal nas chas su 'jug pa
NK071(du)001:3787: ni bsnyen pa dang yum rlob cing sbyor ba'i brdas
NK071(du)001:3788: bskul ba sogs bskul ba sogs ni nye ba bsnyen
NK071(du)001:3789: dang / rol nas dbab bzung gi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa dang /
NK071(du)001:3790: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces blangs te ldog dgram gyi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK071(du)001:3791: de yang yum gyi pad+mara tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor bskyed
NK071(du)001:3792: nas de nyid du bde ba chen po'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:3793: thugs kyi dkyiil 'khor byang chub kyi sems spro zhing
NK071(du)001:3794: bde ba'i sgras sangs rgyas kyi sprin tshogs ma lus
NK071(du)001:3795: pa mchod cing spyan drangs de rnams rjes chags kyi
NK071(du)001:3796: mes zhu ba bdag gi sbyi bo nas zhugs pad+ma'i
NK071(du)001:3797: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams chos pas thams cad rang
NK071(du)001:3798: rig gi ngo bor dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas
NK071(du)001:3799: bdag dang 'khor 'das dbyer med bde ba chen po'i
NK071(du)001:3801: de ltar sgrub par byas pa'i mkha' gsang gi nyi zla gnyis 'dres pa'i snying po de /
NK071(du)001:3802: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor nas yab kyi gsang ba rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:3803: lce yis blangs te ldog dgram gyi sbyor bas rang
NK071(du)001:3804: bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su la bazla'o
NK071(du)001:3805: // rdzu 'phrul gyis mkha' la bya ltar 'gro ba dang /
NK071(du)001:3806: lus kyi kha dog gsal zhing gzi byin 'bar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:3807: sems kyi mngon shes gsal zhing ting 'dzin dang ye
NK071(du)001:3808: shes kyi 'od 'bar bas lam gong mar bgrod pa
NK071(du)001:3809: dang / tshe nyi zla dang mnyam pa la sogs pa thun mong gi dngos grub rnams dang /
NK071(du)001:3810: yid bzhin rin po che'i sprin ltar 'dod pa'i char
NK071(du)001:3811: 'beb pa zag med slob pa'i lam rig 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)001:3812: sa dang mthar thug gi 'bras bu rigs bdag kun
NK071(du)001:3813: tu bzang por 'gyur te mchog gi dngos grub bo
NK071(du)001:3814: // bsgral ba'i zhing du gyur pa ni mchog zhing
NK071(du)001:3815: bcu las sku dgra sogs bdun dang mchog phran thugs
NK071(du)001:3816: rjes bzung bya ngan song gsum rnams so //
NK071(du)001:3817: e nang nyi zla'i steng du sgrol ba'i las la
NK071(du)001:3818: mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor pas bsgral bya bkug pa bzhag
NK071(du)001:3819: / de nas bsgral bya ru tra ste bdag 'dzin gsum sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3820: sgrol byed slob dpon dpal chen dang /
NK071(du)001:3821: sgrol ging t+aak+ki r+aa dza'i nga rgyal nga gnas pa'i
NK071(du)001:3822: gri 'jam dpal rnon por bskyed de lag gi 'du
NK071(du)001:3823: byed kyis khog pa phye bas ma rig pa'i rgya
NK071(du)001:3824: dral bar bsgom / dwangs ma h+aum yig tu gyur
NK071(du)001:3825: pa slob dpon gyi sku la bcug pas sgrib pa
NK071(du)001:3826: rnam par dag pa de nyid rdo rje'i lam nas
NK071(du)001:3827: yum gyi mkha' dbyings su thim nas gnas pa'i h+aum
NK071(du)001:3828: yig de thugs kyi phyag rgya rdo rje 'od 'bar
NK071(du)001:3829: bar gyur pa las rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur
NK071(du)001:3830: cing ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'phro bas brjid pa'i
NK071(du)001:3831: gtsug tu 'khor ba las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtags
NK071(du)001:3832: rigs bdag bsgom ste spar ba sogs byas pas sgrol
NK071(du)001:3833: ba'i thabs 'di ni ngo mtshar che ste /
NK071(du)001:3834: bsgral bya sdig can ngan 'gro las thar nas rnam
NK071(du)001:3835: grol thob pa'i thabs khyad par can yin pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:3836: ro // chos thams cad ye nas skye med de
NK071(du)001:3837: bzhin nyid kyi gnas lugs rtogs pas ji ltar sgyu
NK071(du)001:3838: mar snang ba'i skyes bus mig yor du snang ba'i
NK071(du)001:3839: gang zag la sbyor sgrol byas pa'i tshul bzhin du
NK071(du)001:3840: sbyor sgrol gyi bya ba kun byas kyang 'dzin zhen
NK071(du)001:3841: med pas rdul phra rab kyi cha tsam yang byas
NK071(du)001:3842: pa med phyi snod dang nang bcud kyi sems can
NK071(du)001:3843: rgyud rnams shes kyi bsdus pa rnams ye nas sku
NK071(du)001:3844: dang ye shes su dag par rtogs shing goms na
NK071(du)001:3845: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du gnas shing de'ang
NK071(du)001:3846: don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis spros med stong par
NK071(du)001:3847: ro // ro mnyam shing / khyad par sngags bla med las ni /
NK071(du)001:3848: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis kyis 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)001:3849: thams cad ro mnyam pa rang bzhin gyi dkyiil 'khor
NK071(du)001:3850: du rtogs pas dag ma dag gi zhing thams cad
NK071(du)001:3851: kyang kun tu bzang po'i zhing dang /
NK071(du)001:3852: sgo gsum gyi byed spyod kyang tshogs chen po gnyis
NK071(du)001:3853: lhun rdzogs su gyur nas cir snang ye shes su
NK071(du)001:3854: 'char ro // sngags kyi yan lag lnga tshang zhing
NK071(du)001:3855: dam tshig ma nyams shing sgrub pa'i rdzas kyi yo
NK071(du)001:3856: byad lnga dang ldan cing de steng sogs cho ga
NK071(du)001:3857: lnga po rdzogs par shes pa yi /
NK071(du)001:3858: rnal 'byor pa tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gang
NK071(du)001:3859: yin gyi lha grangs dang mthun pa tshogs pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:3860: 'khor gyis tshogs sgrub na nges par legs pa'i dgos
NK071(du)001:3862: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3863: tshogs sgrub skabs tshom bu lnga ni gtso bo rigs
NK071(du)001:3864: kyi yab lnga dang yum lnga'i lha zhal sbyor du
NK071(du)001:3865: bzhugs pa yis lha so so'i rig chung gi sems
NK071(du)001:3866: dpa' yab yum zung bzhi bskor bas tshom bu lnga
NK071(du)001:3867: yi lha lnga bcu bkod pa la /
NK071(du)001:3868: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcus bskor bas lha
NK071(du)001:3869: bdun cu'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam
NK071(du)001:3871: de bzhin du shar phyogs su de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK071(du)001:3872: dbus su rdo rje'i rigs dang /
NK071(du)001:3873: nub tu pad+ma'i rigs rnams la so so'i rigs chung
NK071(du)001:3874: gi sems de'i zung bzhis bskor ba ste de ltar
NK071(du)001:3875: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor cha gsum gyi mthar
NK071(du)001:3876: khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bas lha zhe
NK071(du)001:3877: drug gi tshogs dang ldan pa yi /
NK071(du)001:3878: tshom bu gsum gyi lha rnams bsgom mo //
NK071(du)001:3879: rigs thams cad kyi rigs kyi bdag po ste rigs kyi gtso bo ni thugs rdo rjer 'du zhing /
NK071(du)001:3880: de'i rgyu mtshan rgyal ba thams cad kyi thugs ye
NK071(du)001:3881: shes lnga gcig tu 'dus pa ni rang byung gi
NK071(du)001:3882: ye shes te / de nyid mtshon byed thugs kyi
NK071(du)001:3883: mchog rdo rje mi bskyod pa yab yum rigs chung
NK071(du)001:3884: gi sems dpa' zung bzhi dang khro bo yab yum
NK071(du)001:3885: bzhis bskor bas lha bco brgyad kyi tshogs dang ldan
NK071(du)001:3886: ye shes te / pa yi // tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams bsgom mo //
NK071(du)001:3887: de nas khro bo khro mo yab yum lnga'i tshogs
NK071(du)001:3888: chen po la 'khor pho nya gnas ma brgyad dang
NK071(du)001:3889: phyag brnyan yul ma brgyad bka' gnyan sgo ma bzhi'i
NK071(du)001:3890: tshogs dang / ci bgyi'i mngags gzhug dbang mo nyer
NK071(du)001:3891: brgyad la sogs pa'i khong nas khro bcu yab yum
NK071(du)001:3892: ste bdun cu don brgyad kyi tshogs rnams kyi rnal
NK071(du)001:3893: 'byor dang ldan pas sgrubs na mchog thun gyi dngos
NK071(du)001:3894: grub dang las bzhi sogs 'dod pa'i 'bras bu rnams
NK071(du)001:3896: lam bskyed rdzogs kyi rnal 'byor pa'i yid skyobs sngags
NK071(du)001:3897: kyi rang bzhin rang rig la 'chang bar bsgrub bya'i
NK071(du)001:3898: dngos grub ni / lta ba mnyam rdzogs lhun gyis
NK071(du)001:3899: grub par rtogs pa de'i ngang la sgom pa gnas
NK071(du)001:3900: dngos grub ni / shing / spyod pa ci la'ang
NK071(du)001:3901: chags thogs dang zhen pa med par spyod pa'i thabs
NK071(du)001:3902: des chos thams cad ye nas dbyer med du rtogs
NK071(du)001:3903: pa dngos grub thob pa'i rgyu'o //
NK071(du)001:3904: rdo rje'i rigs su rigs gzhan thams cad 'du bas
NK071(du)001:3905: tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor 'od 'phro gzi byin
NK071(du)001:3906: 'bar bar rab tu bsgom zhing yo byad la chags
NK071(du)001:3907: med tshul gyi spyod pas 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i
NK071(du)001:3909: de'i 'bras bu ni lta spyod gnyis med du gyur
NK071(du)001:3910: nas thob pa'i mthong lam de lam gong ma phyag
NK071(du)001:3911: rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la sbyor bar byed do
NK071(du)001:3912: // tshom bu gcig pa las gzhan yang na sku
NK071(du)001:3913: gsung thugs kyi tshom bu gsum du sgrub par bya
NK071(du)001:3914: // ba nyid de / sangs rgyas thams cad ma
NK071(du)001:3915: lus pa sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du 'dus
NK071(du)001:3916: pa'i phyir tshom bu gsum gyi lha'i ting 'dzin gsal
NK071(du)001:3917: zhing gzi byin 'bar ba'i 'od zer 'phro bar bsgom
NK071(du)001:3918: nas yo byad rnams gnyis med kyi blos mnyam pa'i
NK071(du)001:3919: dbyings kyi ngang du thim par spyad pas brnyes pa'i
NK071(du)001:3921: tshe dbang de rig 'dzin bzhi'i nang nas dngos grub
NK071(du)001:3922: mchog brnyes pa lhun grub rig 'dzin thob pa la
NK071(du)001:3923: sbyor bar 'gyur pas yon tan bdag don du rgyal
NK071(du)001:3924: ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus 'bar ba ste gsal bar
NK071(du)001:3926: gzhan don du 'gro ba'i nyon mongs sdug bsngal sel
NK071(du)001:3927: bar byed pa'i phrin las kyis thams cad kyang rdo
NK071(du)001:3928: rje gsum gyi mi phyed pa'i rigs su skye ba'i
NK071(du)001:3930: sngags 'chang gang zhig dngos grub yang dag thob par
NK071(du)001:3931: 'dod pas ni rnal 'byor pa thabs dang shes rab
NK071(du)001:3932: grangs tshad tshogs pa thams cad kyis /
NK071(du)001:3933: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor cha lnga dang khro 'phreng rnams te lha bdun cu so sor bsgom nas /
NK071(du)001:3934: yo byad la chags pa med pa'i tshul gyis ni
NK071(du)001:3935: 'dod yon ma 'gags pa'i 'od zer rnam pa mang
NK071(du)001:3936: po 'phro zhing gnyis su med pa'i dbyings su bstim
NK071(du)001:3937: par bya bas brnyes pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub mchog
NK071(du)001:3938: gi snying po sku lnga sbyor 'grub bo //
NK071(du)001:3939: rnal 'byor pa thabs yab dang shes rab yum rnams
NK071(du)001:3940: kyis rim pa ltar de bzhin gshegs pa rigs kyi
NK071(du)001:3941: yab lnga dang / rigs kyi yum lnga ru so
NK071(du)001:3942: sor bsgom zhing de bzhin du 'khor gyi rnal 'byor
NK071(du)001:3943: pa pho rnams kyi sems dpa' dang mo rnams kyi
NK071(du)001:3944: sems ma nyid du bsgom nas lha so so'i sngags
NK071(du)001:3946: ting nge 'dzin de dang de yang dag par so so ma 'dres par gsal ba bslab pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3947: sgrub pa'i gzhi rang dbang zhing bar chad mi 'byung ba'i gnas 'khor khang rim pa gsum ldan dang /
NK071(du)001:3948: 'tsho ba zas sogs nyer kho'i longs spyod thams cad
NK071(du)001:3949: bsags pas ci bde bar spyad du yod pa dang
NK071(du)001:3950: / des mtshon mthun rkyen rnams ma nyams par tshang
NK071(du)001:3951: zhing 'gal rkyen med la sgrub blo ni gzhan rkyen
NK071(du)001:3952: gyis ma 'phrog cing lha sgom sogs blo rab dang
NK071(du)001:3953: / ldan pas / dang por sgrub pa la 'jug
NK071(du)001:3954: dus don ma grub kyi bar du sgrub bo snyams
NK071(du)001:3955: pa'i dam nos pa bzhin du mthar skyel bya zhing
NK071(du)001:3956: de'i tshe le lo dang sgyid lug gi snyoms las
NK071(du)001:3957: rnams med pa'i sgo nas blo la the tshom med
NK071(du)001:3958: par sgrub par byas na tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gang
NK071(du)001:3959: sgrubs kyang thun mchog gi dngos grub thams cad 'grub
NK071(du)001:3960: / ldan pas / par 'gyur te / gang zhe
NK071(du)001:3961: na 'bras chos lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje
NK071(du)001:3962: gsang mchog rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dam pa thob par
NK071(du)001:3964: // ji tsam sgrub pa'i zhag grangs ni sum cu
NK071(du)001:3965: phrag drug sogs le'u dgu par bshad pa bzhin dang
NK071(du)001:3966: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i tshes grangs sogs ni /
NK071(du)001:3967: bshad rgyud rgyas pa sogs rgyud gzhan las smos pa bzhin du bshad par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:3968: tshogs sgrub kyi don 'di rnams rdo rje 'dzin pa gsang ba'i bdag pos tshig tu brjod pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3969: zhes 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la /
NK071(du)001:3970: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid ched du gleng ngo //
NK071(du)001:3971: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:3972: las de lta'i tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK071(du)001:3973: le'u'i skabs te bcu gcig pa'o //
NK071(du)001:3975: // gong du tshogs sgrub bstan pa de nas 'dir yang ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:3976: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos snang spyod
NK071(du)001:3977: kyi yul thams cad ye shes kyi rol mo'i sprin
NK071(du)001:3978: rnam par spros te longs spyod mi zad pa rgyan
NK071(du)001:3979: gyi 'khor lo bkod pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge
NK071(du)001:3980: 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas ched du brjod pa'i
NK071(du)001:3981: 'di brjod do // tshom bu'i lha zung 'jug sgyu
NK071(du)001:3982: 'phrul dra ba'i phyag rgyas thebs pa sa thams cad
NK071(du)001:3983: mngon par rdzogs pa'i lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:3984: du gsal zhing brtan pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang
NK071(du)001:3985: las rkang lag gi sgul spyod bro gar las mi
NK071(du)001:3986: 'da' ba'i phyag rgya 'od zer sprul pa'i 'du 'phro
NK071(du)001:3987: sna tshogs dang bcas te spyad pa yis sa 'og
NK071(du)001:3988: dang ri brag la 'dzul lam steng gi nam mkhar
NK071(du)001:3990: snyan pa'i glu dang brjod pa'i tshig thams cad rang
NK071(du)001:3991: rig ye shes kyi sgra yi don las mi 'da'
NK071(du)001:3992: ba'i phyag rgyas ni gdul byar chos kyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)001:3993: bskor ba'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:3994: rin chen rus pa sogs kyi rgyan dang /
NK071(du)001:3995: dar dang ko rlon sogs bgo ba'i chas gos rnams
NK071(du)001:3996: ye shes las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgyar spyad pa
NK071(du)001:3997: yis gzi byin 'bar rgyal po rgol ba gang gis
NK071(du)001:3998: kyang thub pa med pa'i stobs dang ldan pa 'grub
NK071(du)001:3999: par 'gyur ro // sha chang sogs bza' btung ba'i
NK071(du)001:4000: tshogs rnams ye shes las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgyas
NK071(du)001:4001: par 'gyur ro // ni / 'dod dgur sgyur ba'i
NK071(du)001:4002: yid bzhin gyi sku bzang po dang ro brgya ldan
NK071(du)001:4003: pa'i bdud rtsis 'gro ba tshim par byed pa 'grub
NK071(du)001:4004: par 'gyur ro // ni / bo // +aa li sbyor ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4005: k+aa li sgrol ba'i brda tshig ste rang rig pa'i
NK071(du)001:4006: ye shes las mi 'da' ba'i phyag rgyar spyad pa
NK071(du)001:4007: yis / las thams cad dang mchog thun gyi dngos grub thams cad 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:4008: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba rtogs shing rkyen
NK071(du)001:4009: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin goms pas lta
NK071(du)001:4010: spyod zung 'brel du 'byor ba ni sgrub byed thabs
NK071(du)001:4011: kyi nges pa mi gtong ba'i gzungs kyang yin la
NK071(du)001:4012: sa bon dang chu lud ltar 'bras bu smin byed
NK071(du)001:4013: kyi rgyu dang rkyen yang yin no //
NK071(du)001:4014: de ltar rtogs goms gnyis 'bras bu 'byin nus kyi mthu can du gang gi tshe gyur pa na /
NK071(du)001:4015: zag med slob pa'i lam rig 'dzin bzhi dang mi
NK071(du)001:4016: slob pa'i lam rgyal ba sku lnga'i go 'phang thob
NK071(du)001:4017: nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing kun tu grags par 'gyur
NK071(du)001:4020: gzugs kyi lha tshangs pa yi skye ba rnam dag
NK071(du)001:4021: 'dzin kyang gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa ste
NK071(du)001:4022: / skye ba la rang dbang 'byor bas gang la gang 'dul du skye bar snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:4023: de na nus thob mthong lam gyi sa la gnas
NK071(du)001:4024: pas rgyu'i theg pa'i rab dga' dang mthong lam tsam
NK071(du)001:4025: du skal ba mnyam kyang dgongs pa rgyu'i mi g.yo
NK071(du)001:4026: ba'i sa la bzhugs pa'i byang sems dang mnyam par
NK071(du)001:4028: de yang slob lam bcu'i ngo bo pha rol tu
NK071(du)001:4029: phyin pa bcu po kun tu rdzogs pa na rab
NK071(du)001:4030: dga' la sogs pa'i sa bcu'i bgrod pa'ang rdzogs par
NK071(du)001:4031: 'gyur zhing / thabs ma 'gags pa kun tu 'od
NK071(du)001:4032: dang mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis gos pa med
NK071(du)001:4033: pa'i ye shes ni thabs kyi mchog ste pad+ma can
NK071(du)001:4034: 'gyur zhing / gyi sa'o // shes rab spros 'bral
NK071(du)001:4035: mchog gi byin rlabs sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:4036: du ston nus pa mchog tu gyur pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:4037: ni 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa ste de yang
NK071(du)001:4038: sa yi khyad par spong gnyen skye ba'i sa mtshan
NK071(du)001:4040: sa gcig gi ngo bo la sku gsum gyi chas phye nas btags pa gong ma gsum yin la /
NK071(du)001:4041: des na mthong sgom mthar gsum gyi bsdus pa bcu
NK071(du)001:4042: ni rgyu'i sa dang kun tu 'od sogs gsum ni
NK071(du)001:4043: mthar thug 'bras bu'i sa ste de ltar na sa
NK071(du)001:4044: lam gyi khyad par de thams cad dus yun ring
NK071(du)001:4045: por sbyang mi dgos par myur du lhun gyis rdzogs
NK071(du)001:4046: par 'gyur ro // bskyed rim ltar na ting 'dzin gsum sngon du 'gro bas /
NK071(du)001:4047: mkha' dkyil ltar dngas pa'i dbyings kyi snang brnyan gzhal yas khang du pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la /
NK071(du)001:4048: rang byung ye shes kyis kun la dbang sgyur ba'i
NK071(du)001:4049: rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' stangs dpyal te yum
NK071(du)001:4050: dang / rdzogs rim ltar na dbyings dang sems te /
NK071(du)001:4051: de ltar zung 'brel du bsgom par byas pas rgyal
NK071(du)001:4052: ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun kyang lhag ma ma
NK071(du)001:4053: lus pa ni bsgom par 'gyur te /
NK071(du)001:4054: de las gzhan dus bzhi dang phyogs bcu ste yul
NK071(du)001:4055: dus gnas skabs gang nas btsal kyang rang gi sems
NK071(du)001:4056: nyid las logs su gyur pa'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:4057: rang mtshan pa zhig rnyed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:4059: sems nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa de
NK071(du)001:4060: ka rtogs na rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas te 'di ltar
NK071(du)001:4061: nang du sangs rgyas ma rtogs na gzhan phyi rol
NK071(du)001:4062: du btsal kyang mi rnyed pas ma 'tshol zhig ces
NK071(du)001:4063: gdams so // de yang bsgrub bya'i dkyil 'khor kun dang /
NK071(du)001:4064: lam du gyur pa'i 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'bras bu
NK071(du)001:4065: bzhi'i char gtogs pa'i ye shes chig chod du rang
NK071(du)001:4066: rig la gsal ba'i blos rab tu sbyor bas na
NK071(du)001:4067: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi che ba'i
NK071(du)001:4068: yon tan thams cad kyang stsol med du 'grub par
NK071(du)001:4069: 'gyur pas na cho ga ste lam gyi rim pa
NK071(du)001:4070: rnams gcig car ba'i gang zag gis rim gyis pa
NK071(du)001:4071: lhar sgoms pas / lhag gam ma sgoms pas ma
NK071(du)001:4072: tshang na'ang chad lhag gi skyon nyid dag ste de'i
NK071(du)001:4073: nyes pa med pas dngos grub thob pa la mi
NK071(du)001:4074: lhar sgoms pas / sgrib ste / nam mkha' la rdul gyis mi gos pa bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:4075: de skad ces ched du brjod pas snang spyod thams
NK071(du)001:4076: cad ye shes kyi rol mor 'char ba'i sprin gyis
NK071(du)001:4078: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:4079: las 'dir yang tshom bu tshogs sgrub pa'i le'u ste
NK071(du)001:4081: zhes de lta'i le'u 'di gnyis kyis spyir /
NK071(du)001:4082: zhi khro thun mong tshogs sgrub kyi le'u dang khyad par bcu gcig pas /
NK071(du)001:4083: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las /
NK071(du)001:4084: lta ba tshad ma bka' gzhung gtan tshigs kyi lta ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4085: spyod pa las tshogs sgrub kyi spyod pa dngos rnams bstan /
NK071(du)001:4087: dbang mchog rdzogs nas tshogs la 'jug /
NK071(du)001:4089: le'u bcu par dbang mchog sbyin par bstan nas /
NK071(du)001:4090: 'dir dbang mchog rnams rdzogs par thob nas tshogs sgrub la 'jug par bstan to /
NK071(du)001:4091: le'u bcu gnyis pas lta ba las lta ba dang 'brel ba'i mtshan nyid gsum mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4092: la dor ba spyod pa'i skabs tshogs sgrub kyi spyod pa /
NK071(du)001:4093: bkod pa dkyil 'khor las tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor rnams bstan slob dpon bi ma las /
NK071(du)001:4094: tshogs sgrub yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK071(du)001:4096: le'u bcu gcig par tshogs sgrub la 'jug par bstan cing /
NK071(du)001:4097: le'u 'dir de ltar zhugs pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab par bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:4098: le'u bcu gsum pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:4102: de nas sogs brjod do bar /
NK071(du)001:4107: man ngag gi ngo bo bshad pa de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa /
NK071(du)001:4108: yul gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa /
NK071(du)001:4110: rgyas par bshad pa dang don bsdu ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4112: mtshon par byed pa'i sgo myong bar byed pa'i thabs /
NK071(du)001:4115: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lta ba mtshon pa'i sgo /
NK071(du)001:4116: de gnyis ka'i tha snyad mtshon byed kyi sgo //
NK071(du)001:4117: mtshon bya don gyi khyad par 'byin tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:4119: ma rtogs pa dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4121: yi ge'i sgra btags sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:4123: khong nas sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4124: gnyis pa sbyor bar byed pa'i thabs /
NK071(du)001:4125: gzhung gcig gi steng du bshad tshul gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:4126: shes rab grol lam gyi dbang du bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4127: thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4129: grol lam rim gyis pa ltar du bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4130: gcig char ba ltar du bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4131: dang po la'ang mtshan nyid gsum las /
NK071(du)001:4132: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ni /
NK071(du)001:4133: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:4134: gnyis pa rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)001:4135: dkyil 'khor la ni sogs tshigs bcad phyed dang bzhi /
NK071(du)001:4136: de nas 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK071(du)001:4137: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu /
NK071(du)001:4138: gnyis pa gcig char ba ltar bshad pa la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:4140: dkyil 'khor ldan ni sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:4141: rgyas par bshad pa la gsum las /
NK071(du)001:4142: dang po dkyil 'khor ji ltar ldan par bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4144: gnyis par rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor ji ltar bsgom tshul ni /
NK071(du)001:4145: kun tu bzang po'i sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:4146: gsum pa de ltar ldan pa las cir 'gyur pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4147: snying po'i sogs tshigs bcad gsum //
NK071(du)001:4148: gnyis pa thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4149: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag ltar bshad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4150: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa 'o //
NK071(du)001:4155: khyab bdal chen po'i man ngag go /
NK071(du)001:4157: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4159: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4161: snying po'i thig le sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:4163: zag pa sogs rkang pa dgu /
NK071(du)001:4164: gnyis pa 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ltar bshad pa la /
NK071(du)001:4165: thabs nyid shes rab tu dang /
NK071(du)001:4166: shes rab nyid thabs su dang /
NK071(du)001:4167: thabs shes dbyer med du sbyor ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4169: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4171: gsang ba'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4173: snying po'i thig le sogs tshigs bcad gsum /
NK071(du)001:4174: gsum pa mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK071(du)001:4175: dkyil 'khor la gnas sogs tshigs bcad gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4176: gnyis pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK071(du)001:4177: ye shes rdzogs pa'i sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:4178: gnyis pa de gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4179: sgrub pa po gang zag gi che ba /
NK071(du)001:4180: sgrub thabs lam gyi che ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4182: gang zhig sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:4184: lam kun gyi 'bras bu yin pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:4185: rgyal ba'i gshegs shul yin pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:4186: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi lam yin pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:4187: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pa'i che ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4188: dang po ni bskal pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4195: gsum pa yul gang la gdams pa'i snod bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4196: snod ldan la sbyin pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4197: snod min la mi sbyin par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4199: kun gyi sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:4201: gzhan du sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4205: gsang ba'i snying po sogs so //
NK071(du)001:4206: sa bcad de ldan gyi gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:4208: de nas thabs grol gyi man ngag snying po ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:4209: de bzhin gshegs pa phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa
NK071(du)001:4210: thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs mi phyed
NK071(du)001:4211: pa'i rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams cad rig pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:4212: shes gcig tu bsdus nas gnas pa'i ston pa bcom
NK071(du)001:4213: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)001:4214: thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen por rang byung
NK071(du)001:4215: gi ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa las mi
NK071(du)001:4216: 'da' ba'i dam tshig snod ma yin pa la shin
NK071(du)001:4217: tu gsang ba rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de
NK071(du)001:4218: kho na nyid mtshon byed thabs kyi sprin rnam par
NK071(du)001:4219: bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas
NK071(du)001:4220: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK071(du)001:4221: grub mtha' rnams las mu stegs phyal pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4224: chad lta mur sdug pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4226: rnam par thar pa'i sgo phyogs re tsam rtogs pa nyan rang gnyis dang /
NK071(du)001:4227: yang dag nyid ma rtogs pa ni dbu sems gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:4228: chos thams cad ye nas dag mnyam chen por gnas pa'i don ma mthong ba'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:4229: 'dul ba gtso bor byed pa bya spyod gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4230: sems kyi dgongs pa ting nge 'dzin gtso bor byed pa yo ga'o //
NK071(du)001:4231: phyi rgyud man chad thun mong gi yul du ma gyur pas /
NK071(du)001:4235: chos thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK071(du)001:4236: dag pa rang byung ye shes su gnas pa'i don
NK071(du)001:4237: / a nu man chad kyi yul du ma gyur pas gsang ba ni a ti yo ga ste /
NK071(du)001:4239: mtshon bya sgo'i khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4240: mtshon bya de rnams tha snyad gang gis mtshon na /
NK071(du)001:4241: yi ge du ma las sgra'i tha snyad kyis btags pa /
NK071(du)001:4243: don gyi ngo bo tsam ston pa ming 'byung zhing /
NK071(du)001:4244: de du ma tshogs pa la brten nas don gyi khyad par gsal bar ston pa'i tshig dang /
NK071(du)001:4245: tshig gi tshogs 'dus pa las gzhung so so'i lus grub cing /
NK071(du)001:4246: des rang rang gi brjod bya'i don rab tu mtshon te gnas so //
NK071(du)001:4247: khyad par mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud sems can
NK071(du)001:4248: kun gyi rgyud sems can kun gyi khong na gnas
NK071(du)001:4249: kyang rtogs dka' bas gab cing /
NK071(du)001:4250: mtshon byed gsang ba zab mo'i lam rnams skal med kyi mi go ba'i phyir sbas /
NK071(du)001:4251: de ltar gab sbas kyi don gnyis po de 'byin
NK071(du)001:4252: pa po ni rgyud nges par ston pa rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:4253: slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas pa'i phyir des 'byin
NK071(du)001:4254: par byed do // 'di nas dam pa yin zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:4256: dang po grol lam ltar bshad pa yin te /
NK071(du)001:4257: de yang rang rig rang bzhin rnam dag gi dkyil
NK071(du)001:4258: 'khor lhag pa bden pa dbyer med 'khor 'das ris
NK071(du)001:4259: med du ldan par khyab pa ni lta ba'i ngo
NK071(du)001:4260: bo ste / gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor gtan tshig rnams kyis gtan la phabs /
NK071(du)001:4261: ye dag chos nyid don gyi dkyil 'khor de la
NK071(du)001:4262: ni rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK071(du)001:4263: dkyil 'khor stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor bsgom zhing
NK071(du)001:4264: / don dam chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor de'i rang
NK071(du)001:4265: rtsal ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor snyi nga rje'i
NK071(du)001:4266: / rnal 'byor dang / de gnyis zung 'jug ma
NK071(du)001:4267: 'gags pa las rang byung ba'i yi ge'i 'phro 'du
NK071(du)001:4269: de dag kyang thugs kyi ngo bo h+aum gi dkyil 'khor du bsgoms pa phra ba yig 'bru dang /
NK071(du)001:4270: de nyid rdo rje de yongs su gyur pa las /
NK071(du)001:4271: lha sku'i dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pas /
NK071(du)001:4272: des dkyil 'khor thams cad bsgom par 'gyur bas na
NK071(du)001:4273: mchog ste zung 'jug gi lha sku de tha dad
NK071(du)001:4274: du zhen pa'i blos rtogs dka' bas /
NK071(du)001:4276: mtha'i spros pa dang bral bas thig le ste /
NK071(du)001:4277: de ltar spros bcas kyi dkyil 'khor 'char gzhir gyur pas na dbyings so //
NK071(du)001:4278: de'ang 'byung ba lnga ni shes rab kyi rang bzhin rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:4279: chen po'i sgras phung lnga rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa lnga nyid de /
NK071(du)001:4280: de ltar rtog tshogs thams cad byang chub kyi sems
NK071(du)001:4281: su dag pas lha rtogs dbyer med ni rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:4282: tshogs te / 'di ltar mig sogs dbang po dang /
NK071(du)001:4285: mig gi rnam shes sogs rig pa ste /
NK071(du)001:4286: de ltar rtog pa rnams sems dpa' sogs lhar dag pas na kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor ste /
NK071(du)001:4287: rgyal ba gnyis la yan lag gi lha de snyed bsgom pa thabs kyi lha dang /
NK071(du)001:4288: de rnams kyang rang gi rnams 'phrul bdag nyid chen po yan lag lhag pa yi /
NK071(du)001:4289: lha thugs ye shes sems dpa' re sgom pa shes rab dang /
NK071(du)001:4290: thabs lha bzhi bcu po la sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re ste /
NK071(du)001:4291: bzhi bcu tshan bzhi la ye shes lngas dbu brgyan pa'i lha lnga blta zhing /
NK071(du)001:4292: bsgom pa ni spros bcas so //
NK071(du)001:4293: dwangs ma'i snying po'i theg le dbab ldog gi sbyor bas lhan skyes ye shes kyis /
NK071(du)001:4294: yul yul can gnyis med mnyam par sbyor bas spyod bzhin ma chags pa /
NK071(du)001:4295: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis /
NK071(du)001:4296: rtog tshogs ye shes su gsal bas dgyes pa dang
NK071(du)001:4297: ldan pa'i lha nyid la nyid rol pa'i tshul du
NK071(du)001:4298: mchod pa dbul ba ni tshogs sgrub bo //
NK071(du)001:4299: de ltar zag pa med pa'i ye shes dang bsod
NK071(du)001:4300: nams kyi gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu mthong lam 'od
NK071(du)001:4302: zung 'jug ye shes sgyu ma'i skur rang snang ba'i /
NK071(du)001:4303: rol mo dag pa rab 'byams lha'i dkyil 'khor mtha'
NK071(du)001:4304: yas par 'char zhing snang stong mi phyed pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:4305: shes mchog thugs su chud la de nyid rtogs dka'
NK071(du)001:4306: zhing spros bral gsang ba'i thig le ste mnyam pa
NK071(du)001:4307: nyid kyi dbyings so zung 'jug de ni sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:4308: kun gyi ngo bo'am dngos gzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:4309: de'i tshe na phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dbyings su mngon
NK071(du)001:4310: par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i rgyal ba thams cad
NK071(du)001:4311: kyi sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs te 'bras
NK071(du)001:4312: chos rnams ma lus pa bdag nyid la yod pa
NK071(du)001:4313: de'i zhal bdag gi mthong bas 'khor 'das gnyis med
NK071(du)001:4314: du dbang sgyur ba'i mchog nyid de slob lam gyi
NK071(du)001:4315: rtse mor phyin pas lam gyi nang nas dam pa
NK071(du)001:4316: yin no // gnyis pa thabs lam gdams ngag gi dbang du bshad pa la /
NK071(du)001:4317: dang po steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag dang sbyar ba las /
NK071(du)001:4318: snying dbus na rtsa'i dwangs ma rtsa 'dab brgyad yod pa bzhir 'dus pas /
NK071(du)001:4319: rtsa de dag gi sbub na dkar zlum sogs 'od bzhi dang /
NK071(du)001:4320: de'i khrod na sbyang bya su sogs drug dang /
NK071(du)001:4321: sbyong byed sa bon sogs gsum /
NK071(du)001:4322: kun gzhi sogs rnam shes rnams gnas pa'i snying gi
NK071(du)001:4323: dkyil 'khor rtsa chen bzhi dang ldan pa de'i nang
NK071(du)001:4324: nas / dwangs ma lnga'i dkyil 'khor rang bzhin gyis
NK071(du)001:4325: gnas pa'i dbus na ye shes snying po'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:4326: ni ye nas bzhugs pa ltar lam pas thig le'i
NK071(du)001:4327: dkyil 'khor phra la gsal ba bsgom pas /
NK071(du)001:4328: dwangs ma lnga ye shes snying po dang drug ye
NK071(du)001:4329: shes drug gi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba de
NK071(du)001:4330: la sems gtad de bsgom pas ye shes snying po'i
NK071(du)001:4331: dkyil 'khor ste thig le 'od 'bar ba las byung
NK071(du)001:4332: ba'i 'od kyi sku gsung thugs kyi yi ges sbyang
NK071(du)001:4333: bya'i yi ge drug sogs sbyangs te /
NK071(du)001:4334: 'khor ba chos nyid du grol zhing /
NK071(du)001:4335: dwangs ma lnga'ang ye shes snying po la bsdus pas bde ba'i ye shes 'byung ste /
NK071(du)001:4336: ye shes de'i ngo bo ni dmigs med mtha' bral thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ste /
NK071(du)001:4337: 'di ni dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi nang nas mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4338: lte ba'i rgya 'dab kyi dbus na yum lnga'i thig
NK071(du)001:4339: le a thung gi rnam par gnas pa ni chos
NK071(du)001:4340: dbyings zab mo // gsang ba shes rab kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin nyi ma'i thig le ste /
NK071(du)001:4341: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas dbyings so //
NK071(du)001:4342: thig le de las byung ba 'byung ba lnga'i dwangs
NK071(du)001:4343: ma cha phra ba rang bzhin med pa'i dbyings ni
NK071(du)001:4344: shes rab ste rigs kyi yum lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:4345: chen po'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i thabs /
NK071(du)001:4346: rigs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa ste yab lnga'o //
NK071(du)001:4347: de ltar thig le byang chub kyi sems thabs shes dbyer mi phyed pa ni rdo rje ste /
NK071(du)001:4348: de las byung ba'i rtogs tshogs /
NK071(du)001:4352: yul so so rig par byed pa'i rnam shes rnams
NK071(du)001:4353: sems dpa' sogs thams cad bde ba chen po'i ye
NK071(du)001:4354: shes kyi spyod yul du rnam par dag pas kun
NK071(du)001:4355: tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK071(du)001:4356: de dag kyang dbyings rang byung gi ye shes su rdzogs pas /
NK071(du)001:4358: de dang kha sbyor snying ga'i 'khor lo la rgyal
NK071(du)001:4359: kun gyi lhag pa'i dgongs pa zab mo thugs stong
NK071(du)001:4360: pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi snang cha me long
NK071(du)001:4361: lta bu la sogs pa lnga ye nas gnas pa
NK071(du)001:4362: ste / des lta ba'i snyigs ma nas mar lte
NK071(du)001:4363: ba'i thig le sems gtad de sgom pa sogs thabs
NK071(du)001:4364: kyis bde ba chen po rang rig pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:4365: rang shar ba la blta bya blta byed med pa'i
NK071(du)001:4366: tshul gyis lta zhing nyams su len pa ni lte
NK071(du)001:4367: ba'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i man ngag go /
NK071(du)001:4368: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus na mkha'
NK071(du)001:4369: 'gro rngam ma'i yi ge am gi rnam par gnas
NK071(du)001:4370: pa la bzang btung gi bcud 'dud pa nas /
NK071(du)001:4372: de snying ga'i dwangs ma'i drod kyis zhu ba'i dwangs ma snying gar mchod /
NK071(du)001:4373: dbug thig ler thim pas rlung dang rtogs pa 'gags
NK071(du)001:4374: ste 'khor lo gnyis bde ba dus gcig tu mnyam
NK071(du)001:4375: par sbyor zhing / de ltar sbyar bas bde ba'i
NK071(du)001:4376: ngang gdangs ye shes lngar ma 'gags pa'i rol mo
NK071(du)001:4377: yis drod rlung rtsa gsum gcig tu 'dres te bde
NK071(du)001:4378: gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mi g.yo
NK071(du)001:4379: bar rang gsal ba'i dgyes pa chen po la yul
NK071(du)001:4380: yul can gnyis med kyi ngang du mchod par 'bul
NK071(du)001:4381: zhes bya ste mgrin pa'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i man
NK071(du)001:4382: par sbyor zhing / ngag go / spyi bo'i rtsa
NK071(du)001:4383: 'khor dbus na kun bzang zla ba'i thig le ham
NK071(du)001:4385: de'ang sngar mgrin pa'i thig le'i bde ba ni yul yul can gyi rtog pa zad pas /
NK071(du)001:4386: zag pa med pa'i bde ba yin pa /
NK071(du)001:4387: de nyid ma 'gags pa'i bsod nams kyi mthus thig
NK071(du)001:4388: le nyid rang bzhin med de bde ba chen po'i
NK071(du)001:4389: ye shes sgyu ma lta bur snang ba /
NK071(du)001:4390: de las bde ba'i rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas par spro ba'i mchog ces bya ste /
NK071(du)001:4391: mgrin pa'i thig le'i 'od kyis shin tu rtogs dka' bas /
NK071(du)001:4392: gsang ba ste spyi bo'i thig le la phog pas
NK071(du)001:4393: 'od du zhu ba de nyid chos kyi dbyings dang
NK071(du)001:4394: ro gcig pas khams gsum thams cad /
NK071(du)001:4395: bde gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chos kyi skur gyur pa /
NK071(du)001:4396: de ni dus gsum sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos te /
NK071(du)001:4397: de ltar rnal 'byor pa bde ba chen po chos kyi skur gyur pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4399: gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma lus
NK071(du)001:4400: pa thams cad bdag nyid las gzhan du ma gyur
NK071(du)001:4401: pas sku'i zhal dus gcig la mthong ste de gsung
NK071(du)001:4402: la dbang sgyur ba dang yon tan phrin las mchog
NK071(du)001:4404: thugs don dam pa'i ye shes su ro gcig tu
NK071(du)001:4405: gyur pa yin te spyi bo'i 'khor lo sgom pa'i
NK071(du)001:4406: man ngag go / 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag ni /
