NK071(du)001:4407: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor bde ba'i
NK071(du)001:4408: ye shes kyi ro dang bcas pa yab yum gnyis
NK071(du)001:4409: la rang chas su ldan pa de nyid rtogs par
NK071(du)001:4410: byed pa'i dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i lung rigs man ngag
NK071(du)001:4411: gsum gyis gtan la phab nas /
NK071(du)001:4412: yab yum lha'i dkyil 'khor du bskyed pa la skye
NK071(du)001:4413: mched rlob pa ni yan lag gi lha yab la
NK071(du)001:4414: yab dang / yum la yum gyi dkyil 'khor sgom zhing /
NK071(du)001:4415: mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mora rlobs te snyoms 'jug
NK071(du)001:4416: gi brda' bzhis bskul nas yab thabs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:4417: dang yum shes rab kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis phyag rgya
NK071(du)001:4418: bzhis gnyis med du rol pa'i rjes chags kyis rkyen
NK071(du)001:4419: gyis rlung bskyod pas dmar cha 'bar ba des dkar
NK071(du)001:4420: cha zhu ba yas 'bab kyi dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis
NK071(du)001:4421: phyin pa'i rim gyi zla ba rdo rje'i bum par
NK071(du)001:4422: 'dzag med du bzung ste gang la gang ba las
NK071(du)001:4423: bde ba'i ye shes byung ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4424: de nyid gnyis med kyi ye shes su gsal la mi rtog pas thugs kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK071(du)001:4425: de ltar myong ba'i tshe khams lnga'i bcud kun rdzob
NK071(du)001:4426: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas na
NK071(du)001:4427: mchog gi / de'i tshe yum gyi gsang ba pad+ma'i
NK071(du)001:4428: ze'u 'brur thig le nyi ma byang chub sems kyi
NK071(du)001:4429: dkyil 'khor snang ba gnas pa'i tshe /
NK071(du)001:4430: de nyid thabs kyis zin na rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su 'byung ba'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:4432: ji ltar na yum gyi 'byung ba'i dwangs ma cha
NK071(du)001:4433: phra ba ni shes rab rigs kyi yum lnga dang
NK071(du)001:4434: / chen po ste rags pa rigs kyi yab de
NK071(du)001:4435: bzhin gshegs pa lngar gsal ba nyid lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)001:4436: / cing / byang chub sems kyi bde bas rtog
NK071(du)001:4437: tshogs thams cad ni sku dang ye shes kyi rdo
NK071(du)001:4438: rje dbyer mi phyed pa'i tshogs so //
NK071(du)001:4439: de'ang dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams lhar yongs
NK071(du)001:4440: su dag pa spyod yul kun tu bzang po'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:4441: 'khor la / sems lnga mthar phyin pa'i lhan skyes
NK071(du)001:4442: bde ba'i ye shes zag pa med pa'i bdag nyid
NK071(du)001:4443: chen po skyes pa de nyams su myong bas /
NK071(du)001:4444: lhag pa'i thugs kyi dgongs pa'i ngo bo bde ba
NK071(du)001:4445: chen po'i ro ye shes lngar 'char bas lta bya
NK071(du)001:4446: lta byed med pa'i tshul gyis lta zhing rang gsal
NK071(du)001:4447: ba'o // yab yum gyi rtsa thams cad kyi bcud
NK071(du)001:4448: 'dus pa'i snying po nyi zla'i dwangs ma theg le
NK071(du)001:4449: dus gcig tu mnyam par sbyor bas dngos po lhan
NK071(du)001:4450: cig skyes pa bde ba'i ye shes nyams su myong
NK071(du)001:4451: nas dga' bzhi'i rol mo yis rtogs tshogs lhan cig
NK071(du)001:4452: skyes pa'i ye shes su rnam par grol nas rab
NK071(du)001:4453: tu dgyes par gyur pa'i dkyil 'khor la bde stong
NK071(du)001:4454: gnyis su med pa'i mchod par dbul zhes bya'o //
NK071(du)001:4455: de ltar tshogs drug gi rten gyi dwangs ma thams
NK071(du)001:4456: cad dbab gzung ldog pa'i thabs kyis tshogs brgyad rtog
NK071(du)001:4457: pa'i dngos po thams cad lhan skyes kyi ye shes
NK071(du)001:4458: su rang gsal bas zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:4459: kyi ro ma 'gags par myong ba bsod nams kyi
NK071(du)001:4460: tshogs kyis bde ba'i ye shes sgyu ma lta bur
NK071(du)001:4461: snang la 'dzin med du spyod pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs
NK071(du)001:4462: pa dang / 'dod chags bde stong gi ye shes
NK071(du)001:4463: su rang snang ba'i rol mo rtog tshogs sku dang
NK071(du)001:4464: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab pas mtha'
NK071(du)001:4465: yas pa'i mchog tu rang gsal zhing /
NK071(du)001:4466: nyi zla gnyis med kyi ye shes nyams su myong dka' bas gsang ba'i thig le ste /
NK071(du)001:4467: de nyid 'bras chos thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su gyur pas dbyings so //
NK071(du)001:4468: de ltar bsgoms pa'i yon tan kyang /
NK071(du)001:4469: bde ba chen po'i ye shes de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:4470: de thob pa'i tshe phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi /
NK071(du)001:4472: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs te 'bras chos
NK071(du)001:4473: nyi shu rtsa lnga ma lus pa mngon du byas
NK071(du)001:4474: shing bdag nyid kyi zhal mthong ba med pa'i tshul
NK071(du)001:4476: 'dzag med kyi bde bas dbang po'i sdug bsngal bcom
NK071(du)001:4477: ste 'dod chags bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:4478: shes su dbang ba sgyur bas na lam gyi nang
NK071(du)001:4480: thabs kyi nang nas dam pa ste bde myur gyi lam rmad du byung ba yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:4481: thabs grol lam gyi dkyil 'khor la goms pa'i mthus /
NK071(du)001:4482: gnas lugs kyi dkyil 'khor de nyid mngon du rtogs
NK071(du)001:4483: pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor rang
NK071(du)001:4484: rig la lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyan du sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:4485: kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa yongs rdzogs su thogs
NK071(du)001:4486: te / 'bras bu'i yon tan gyis mdzes pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4487: de ltar spangs rtogs rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor rang snang
NK071(du)001:4488: sku gsum dbyer med mnyam par sbyor ba las gdul
NK071(du)001:4489: bya 'dul byed thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor btsal ba med
NK071(du)001:4490: par yongs te / rang byung gis 'byung ste /
NK071(du)001:4491: phyogs dus kyi bsdus pa'i gdul bya'i zhing du gzugs
NK071(du)001:4492: sku'i dkyil 'khor gang la gang 'dul ba'i mgon po
NK071(du)001:4493: sgyu ma lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK071(du)001:4494: sgyu ma lta bu'i 'khor ba la /
NK071(du)001:4495: sgyu ma lta bu'i sems can rnams sgrol ba yis /
NK071(du)001:4496: don mdzad pa ltar snang yang /
NK071(du)001:4497: snang dus nyid nas bsgral bya dang sgrol byed gnyis
NK071(du)001:4498: ka rang mtshan pa med par 'dul byed sprul pa'i
NK071(du)001:4499: dkyil 'khor gyis 'dul ba'i spyod pa ston par mdzad
NK071(du)001:4500: do // chos thams cad ye dag rang byung gi
NK071(du)001:4501: ye shes chen por rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor tu gnas
NK071(du)001:4502: do // pa la / thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK071(du)001:4503: gnas lugs kyi don la blo mnyam par sbyor ba'i
NK071(du)001:4504: thabs kyis yin lugs ji lta ba mngon du gyur
NK071(du)001:4505: pa ni 'bras bu rang byung ba sku dang ye
NK071(du)001:4506: shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang bas gdul bya'i
NK071(du)001:4507: don la thugs rje chen po kun nas dam pa'i
NK071(du)001:4508: phrin las lhun gyis grub par snang ngo //
NK071(du)001:4509: tshul 'di ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad
NK071(du)001:4510: kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam mchog don du gnyer
NK071(du)001:4511: ba rnams kyis 'da' bar mi mdzad pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)001:4514: gang zhig rgyud 'di la mos par gyur pa tsam yang /
NK071(du)001:4515: sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK071(du)001:4516: phyogs dang dus kun nas gzigs te /
NK071(du)001:4517: rnam pa thams cad du gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ma
NK071(du)001:4518: lus rgyud la bsnyen te thob par byed pa yis
NK071(du)001:4519: // nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:4520: dus bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du /
NK071(du)001:4521: rgyu'i theg par shin tu blo sbyangs pa la rab tu gnas shing brtson pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4522: gsang sngags phyi nang gi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa bsnyen cing sgrub pa yis //
NK071(du)001:4523: don du gnyer bya'i 'bras bu 'tshar rgya ba la lam /
NK071(du)001:4524: gsang chen bla med theg pa 'di la rag las pa yin te gzhan med do //
NK071(du)001:4525: de yang 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i zhing na /
NK071(du)001:4528: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa /
NK071(du)001:4529: thams cad kyang lam 'di la bsnyen pa ste brten
NK071(du)001:4530: nas 'bras bu sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa yin
NK071(du)001:4531: no // da ltar 'byung bzhin pa dang ma 'ongs
NK071(du)001:4532: ba 'byung 'gyur gyi rnal 'byor pa thams cad kun
NK071(du)001:4533: kyang lam 'di yis 'bras bu lhun gyis grub par
NK071(du)001:4534: no // 'gyur ro // rgyud 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi /
NK071(du)001:4535: don rmad du byung ba ste /
NK071(du)001:4536: 'bras bu'i ngo bo ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don
NK071(du)001:4537: lam du byas pa la bsgrub bya gzhan nas sgrub
NK071(du)001:4538: mi dgos par 'grub pa'i nye lam du gyur pa
NK071(du)001:4540: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa
NK071(du)001:4541: la dgongs pa'i zhe phugs 'di las bzang ba'i lam
NK071(du)001:4542: gsang ba'i nges don gzhan zhig med nges yin pas
NK071(du)001:4543: btsal kyang gzhan gyis lta zhog rgyal bas kyang mi
NK071(du)001:4544: brnyes so te mi rnyed do //
NK071(du)001:4545: sangs rgyas kun gyi bka' rtags kyi phyag rgya chen
NK071(du)001:4546: po'i mchog tu gyur pa'i man ngag 'di ni thos
NK071(du)001:4547: bsam bsgom gsum la blo rab tu sbyangs pa'i shes
NK071(du)001:4548: rab gsum gyi mig dang ldan pa rnams kyis ma
NK071(du)001:4550: skal ldan gyi slob ma snod dang ldan la ngang tshul dge zhing /
NK071(du)001:4551: bzang la dad pa brtan pas chos phyir /
NK071(du)001:4552: lus dang longs spyod thams cad gtong nus pa de la yongs su rdzogs par sbyin cing /
NK071(du)001:4553: de las gzhan du snod min la /
NK071(du)001:4554: nam yang sbyin par mi bya ste /
NK071(du)001:4556: rmong pa la 'phyar bas gsang ma thub par gal
NK071(du)001:4557: te sbyin na bka' yi chad pas 'chi ba'i dus
NK071(du)001:4558: min par blo bur du ni srog zad nas tshe'i
NK071(du)001:4559: dus byed cing / shi ma thag tsha dmyal gyi
NK071(du)001:4560: mes bsreg pa dang grang dmyal gyi chus sbrebs par
NK071(du)001:4561: byed pa'i sdug bsngal la yun ring gnas te nyams
NK071(du)001:4563: de skad ces ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa nyid
NK071(du)001:4564: kyi 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched
NK071(du)001:4566: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK071(du)001:4567: 'dir theg pa 'og ma rnams la shin tu gsang
NK071(du)001:4568: ba'i don tshe 'di nyid la grol ba'i thabs nye
NK071(du)001:4569: bar bstan pa'i man ngag zab cing snying por dril
NK071(du)001:4570: ba'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4573: zhi khro thun mong rdzogs rim kyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:4574: don du gnyer ba sgrubs pa las /
NK071(du)001:4575: rdzogs pa'i rim pa rnams bstan /
NK071(du)001:4577: tshogs mchog rgya cher spel ba yang //
NK071(du)001:4578: man ngag snying po can gyis bya //
NK071(du)001:4580: gong du tshogs sgrub bstan tshogs mchog rgya cher spel ba'i thabs /
NK071(du)001:4581: thabs grol gyi man ngag snying po dang ldan pas bya ba'i bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:4582: le'u bcu bzhi pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:4587: de nas sogs gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:4588: 'bras chos nyer lnga so sor bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4591: dang po sku lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4592: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:4593: gnyis pa gsung lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4595: gsum pa thugs lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4597: bzhi pa yon tan lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4599: lnga pa phrin las lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4601: gnyis pa spyir bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4602: thams cad sogs gsum pa mtshan ni /
NK071(du)001:4603: gsang ba'i snying po sogs nas bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4605: sa bcad de dang 'brel ba'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:4606: lam thabs grol gyi man ngag snying po bstan pa
NK071(du)001:4607: de nas rang snang gi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i
NK071(du)001:4608: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po
NK071(du)001:4609: rigs drug pa nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan bzhi
NK071(du)001:4610: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang la
NK071(du)001:4611: dgyes pa chen po'i glu drug po 'di blangs so
NK071(du)001:4612: // rnams ni ye shes lnga'i glu'i mgo 'dren rim pa bzhin sku lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:4613: de bzhin du gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga rnams mtshan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4614: phyogs bcu'i dus bzhi'i rgyal rnams rang rig ye shes
NK071(du)001:4615: gcig la lhun gyis rdzogs pas sku gsum snang ba
NK071(du)001:4616: yi go 'byed pa ni mngon byang sku dang /
NK071(du)001:4617: rig pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dbyings thig le
NK071(du)001:4618: chen po'i klong du grol ba ni chos kyi sku
NK071(du)001:4619: dang / bsod nams las grub pa'i sku mtshan dpe
NK071(du)001:4620: dkyil 'khor dag pa'i gdul bya la snang ba ni
NK071(du)001:4621: dang / longs sku dang / gang la gang 'dul
NK071(du)001:4622: gyi sku yi bkod pa sna tshogs par ston pa
NK071(du)001:4624: snang stong dbyer med pa'i thig ler sku gsum po
NK071(du)001:4625: kun ro gcig tu rdzogs pa ni rdo rje'i sku'o
NK071(du)001:4626: // hohzhesa pa mnyes pa'i don te 'og ma rnams la'ang 'agre'o /
NK071(du)001:4627: 'gro ba sgrol ba la thogs pa med pa rdo
NK071(du)001:4628: rje'i tshig gis gdul bya'i bsod nams dang mthun par
NK071(du)001:4629: ston pa brjod pa'i tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK071(du)001:4630: brjod med thig le chen po'i rang bzhin brjod pa
NK071(du)001:4631: thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa ni skye med don
NK071(du)001:4632: gyi gsung ngo // sgra rnams rang rig pa'i rdo
NK071(du)001:4633: rjer lhun gyi grub pas rig pa ye shes gsung
NK071(du)001:4634: gi dkyil 'khor cir yang ma 'gags par ldan pas
NK071(du)001:4635: brda sprod pa ni rig pa byin rlabs kyi gsung
NK071(du)001:4636: gyi gsung ngo // ngo // don tha dad pa
NK071(du)001:4637: tshig gcig tu mi phyed par 'bab pas rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:4638: sgra chen po ste tshul mtha' yas pa go bar
NK071(du)001:4639: byed pa ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyi gsung ngo //
NK071(du)001:4640: sku'i brdas thogs pa med par gdul bya'i blo la don 'jal bas dbang sgyur ba ni /
NK071(du)001:4641: rdo rje rgyal po dgongs pa brda'i gsung ngo //
NK071(du)001:4642: sgra thams cad grags stong dbyer mi phyed pa thig
NK071(du)001:4643: le chen por grol ba ni rdo rje gsung ngo
NK071(du)001:4644: // hoh me long ye shes ni ye shes kun 'char ba'i rten byed pas sku dang /
NK071(du)001:4645: sor rtog ye shes ni shes bya kun ma 'dres par gzigs nas chos ston pas gsung dang /
NK071(du)001:4646: chos dbyings ye shes ni snying por gyur pas thugs kyi thugs te /
NK071(du)001:4647: de gsum rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid chen po de la
NK071(du)001:4648: yon tan ma lus pa'i 'byung gnas mnyam nyid dang
NK071(du)001:4649: / gdul bya 'dul ba'i phrin las bya grub ye shes kyang kun tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4650: de ltar ye shes ye nas lngar lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin te /
NK071(du)001:4651: ye shes re re la'ang lnga lnga 'dus pa'i tshogs
NK071(du)001:4652: rang byung gi ye shes chen po gcig gi ngo
NK071(du)001:4653: bor 'dus pa'i thig le che hohzhesa so //
NK071(du)001:4654: mtha' dbus gang du'ang mi dmigs shing cir yang ma
NK071(du)001:4655: 'gags pa'i sgyu 'phrul ris med kun khyab mnyam pa'i
NK071(du)001:4656: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa ni zhing khams
NK071(du)001:4658: rgya tshad kyis gzhal ba'i yul rang snang gi bkod
NK071(du)001:4659: pa dang bcas pa mtha' yas par kun nas snang
NK071(du)001:4660: ba ni gzhal yas khang gi yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:4661: ba spu'i bu ga re re nas kyang gsal zhing
NK071(du)001:4662: dag pa'i 'od zer sna tshogs pa spro ba ni
NK071(du)001:4664: 'dod yon gyi lha mo re re yang mtha' yas
NK071(du)001:4665: pa phyogs bcu kun nas ma btsal bar lhun gyis
NK071(du)001:4666: grub cing / dbang po so so la thim pas
NK071(du)001:4667: dgyes dgur spyod pa ni longs spyod kyi yon tan
NK071(du)001:4668: grub cing / no // mi 'jigs bzhi sogs yon
NK071(du)001:4669: tan sna tshogs pa thugs la mnga' bas seng ge
NK071(du)001:4670: la sogs pa lngas bteg pa'i khri'i steng du khu
NK071(du)001:4672: sku gsung thugs zla nyid pad+ma'i gdan dang /
NK071(du)001:4673: gdul bya'i re ba skong ba'i chen po ste rin
NK071(du)001:4674: chen sna tshogs pa'i khri rkang ste khyad par 'phags
NK071(du)001:4675: pa gdan khri'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:4676: hoh don bya ba'i yul phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul
NK071(du)001:4677: phra mo snyed kyi zhing khams dag ma dag kun
NK071(du)001:4678: tu / byed pa'i thabs rgyal ba rnams kyi gdul
NK071(du)001:4679: bya'i don rnams thogs med mdzad phrin las rdul phran
NK071(du)001:4680: gyi grangs de snyed du ston pa kun kyang /
NK071(du)001:4682: don byed po ni zhi ba dang khro bo sogs
NK071(du)001:4683: gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul pa yang rdul phran
NK071(du)001:4684: gyi grangs dang mnyam pa bsam yas kyis don mdzad
NK071(du)001:4686: sprul pa de dag gis zhing de dag tu /
NK071(du)001:4687: skad cig yud tsam la 'bad rtsol med par phrin las bzhis don mdzad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4688: lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las sogs /
NK071(du)001:4689: hoh phyogs dus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK071(du)001:4690: thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin ni sku gsung
NK071(du)001:4691: thugs yon tan phrin las thams cad sangs rgyas kun
NK071(du)001:4692: gyi spyi gzugs rgyal ba drug pa'i bdag nyid chen
NK071(du)001:4693: por 'du zhing / khyab byed drug pa'i sku gsung
NK071(du)001:4694: thugs yon tan phrin las lnga char gyis kyang khyab
NK071(du)001:4695: bya rgyal ba thams cad la kun tu khyab bo
NK071(du)001:4696: por 'du zhing / // de yang sku gsung thugs
NK071(du)001:4697: yon tan phrin las kyi snang tshul kun gcig gi
NK071(du)001:4699: gcig kun tu 'char bas na gcig dang du ma'i
NK071(du)001:4700: mtha' las grol ba thig le chen po'i rang bzhin
NK071(du)001:4701: no // hohzhesa mnyes pa ste de skad ces rang
NK071(du)001:4702: snang gi dkyil 'khor la dgyes pa chen pos ched
NK071(du)001:4703: no // du bsgrags so // gsang ba'i snying po
NK071(du)001:4704: de kho na nyid nges pa las 'dis mnyes pa'i
NK071(du)001:4705: glus nyid kyi dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u ste
NK071(du)001:4706: no // du bsgrags so // bcu bzhi pa'o // //
NK071(du)001:4708: zhi ba rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:4709: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las gnas su stob pa mchod pa las /
NK071(du)001:4710: glu ye shes rgyan gyi mchod pa bstan /
NK071(du)001:4711: bi ma las tshogs 'dus mchod pa glu yi bya //
NK071(du)001:4712: zhes gsung gong du bstan pa'i tshogs sgrub kyi 'dus /
NK071(du)001:4713: dkyil 'khor lha bstod pa rdo rje'i glu yis bya ba bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:4714: le'u bco lnga pa khro bo'i gleng gzhi bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4717: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor mngon par du mdzad tshul mdor bstan /
NK071(du)001:4718: de'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4720: de nas sogs gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:4722: gang gis ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs /
NK071(du)001:4725: rgyu gang gis gol ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4726: gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa'o //
NK071(du)001:4728: de ci'i phyir nas rmongs pas zhes pa'i bar /
NK071(du)001:4729: gnyis pa gol ba'i 'bras bu ji ltar smin pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:4730: rnam smin gyi 'bras bu sdug bsngal myong ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4731: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu gzhan la 'tshe ba'o //
NK071(du)001:4734: yi dwags su skye tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:4736: srid par sogs myong ngo bar /
NK071(du)001:4739: gnyis pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu ni /
NK071(du)001:4741: gnyis pa gang gi ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:4742: gdul byar gzigs nas 'dul ba mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4746: gnyis pa la bcu gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:4748: che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:4750: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK071(du)001:4751: byin gyis rlobs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK071(du)001:4753: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:4754: phrin las rmad du byung ba'i ngo bo dang /
NK071(du)001:4756: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:4758: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK071(du)001:4773: de nas sogs brgyad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:4781: bcu gnyis pa la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:4784: sgo ma rnams spro ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4792: gsum de ltar btul ba'i 'bras bu la bzhi ste /
NK071(du)001:4794: gnas spar nas snang 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin thob pa /
NK071(du)001:4795: 'bangs su dam bcas nas lus gnad du phul ba /
NK071(du)001:4796: 'khor phul te gus pas mchod par dam bca' ba /
NK071(du)001:4797: dbang mo rnams las nod pa la dbang bskur nas mu ran la bkod tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:4807: gsang ba'i snying po sogs so //
NK071(du)001:4808: sa bcad de ldan gyi gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:4809: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas khro bo'i
NK071(du)001:4810: dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK071(du)001:4811: thams cad kyi bdag po drug pa kun tu bzang
NK071(du)001:4812: po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK071(du)001:4813: ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa nyid kyis rang snang
NK071(du)001:4814: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor las ma g.yos par
NK071(du)001:4815: / 'dul byed sprul pa sku'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:4816: ji ltar mtshams pa mngon par 'du bar mdzad de
NK071(du)001:4817: / / de ltar mdzad pa de dgos ched ci phyir zhe na zhes dris pa'i lan ni /
NK071(du)001:4818: gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i ched du'o //
NK071(du)001:4819: de su zhig snyams pa la /
NK071(du)001:4820: spyir srid pa'i rtsa ba bdag tu rmongs pa ma
NK071(du)001:4821: rig pa'i rnam par rtog pa bdag tu zhen pa
NK071(du)001:4822: dang / chos thams cad blos sgro btags tsam las
NK071(du)001:4823: bden par grub pa ma yin kyang phyin ci log
NK071(du)001:4824: gi bzung yul la bdag gir mngon par zhen pas
NK071(du)001:4825: 'khor bas nges par 'byin byed yang dag pa'i lam
NK071(du)001:4826: dang bral ba dag ni srid par du byed pa
NK071(du)001:4827: dang / yin la / de'i steng du byed pa yin la /
NK071(du)001:4828: de'i steng du khyad par ru tra ni /
NK071(du)001:4829: gab pa'i gsang ba gnas lugs de bzhin nyid ma
NK071(du)001:4830: rtogs par sbas pa'i gsang ba sbyor sgrol sogs spyod
NK071(du)001:4831: pa rlang po la mngon par 'chel nas byol nyog
NK071(du)001:4832: tu spyod cing / de yang rgyu las dge sdig dang /
NK071(du)001:4833: 'bras bu bde sdug gi 'grel pa la rmongs pa'i dbang gis /
NK071(du)001:4834: de ltar spyod pa rnams ru drar gol ba'i rgyu'o //
NK071(du)001:4835: de yang srid par skye ba'i sa bon mi dge
NK071(du)001:4836: ba las rtsub mos 'phangs nas bar ma do med
NK071(du)001:4837: pa'i rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal bar skad gcig gis
NK071(du)001:4838: skyes so // de nyid du rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal drag pos yun ring gdungs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4839: 'di bas shin tu grang yang ci ma rung snyam
NK071(du)001:4840: pa'i mod la khab sogs kyis rab tu sbrebs pas
NK071(du)001:4841: grang ba dang / lus pad+ma ltar cher gas pa'i
NK071(du)001:4842: sdug bsngal drag po bdag gis rab tu gdungs par
NK071(du)001:4843: grang ba dang / byas so // de lta bu'i
NK071(du)001:4844: sdug bsngal rab tu tsha ba la sogs pa ste
NK071(du)001:4845: grang ba dang / byas so // / tsha ba nas yang sos kyi bar brgyad dang /
NK071(du)001:4846: shin tu grang ba pad+ma ltar cher gas pa la
NK071(du)001:4847: sogs pa ste chu bur can gyi bar brgyad po
NK071(du)001:4848: dag tu tsha grang gi dmyal ba phan tshun zung
NK071(du)001:4849: re re zhing skye ris kyis 'jig rten gyi khams
NK071(du)001:4850: de 'jig pa'i dus su khams gzhan dang gzhan du
NK071(du)001:4852: tshe tshad ni bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis su tsha grang gi sdug bsngal myong ngo //
NK071(du)001:4853: de nas dmyal bar skye ba'i las kyi rnam par smin pa de myong stobs kyis zad pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4854: yi dwags su skyes te ltog pa dang skoms pa'i
NK071(du)001:4855: sdug bsngal rab tu nyen pa spyi mthun gyi sgrib
NK071(du)001:4856: pa can dang / phyi rol gyi 'dod pa'i dngos
NK071(du)001:4857: po rnams yid du mi 'ong ba chu nag tu
NK071(du)001:4858: mthong ba lta bu phyi sgrib can dang /
NK071(du)001:4859: bza' btung cung zad rnyed pa bzos pa na /
NK071(du)001:4860: gdug cing rtsub pa'i dngos po me sogs /
NK071(du)001:4861: sna tshogs su gyur pas nang khrol sreg pa sogs me lce'i 'khor lo can dang /
NK071(du)001:4862: zas skom sogs mthong ba spyod 'dod pas drung du
NK071(du)001:4863: snyegs pa'i tshe rdzas tsam yang yongs su med par
NK071(du)001:4864: 'gyur zhing / lus shin tu rid cing skam pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4865: lto ba ri bo tsam la kha khab mig lta
NK071(du)001:4866: bu sogs lus dang yan lag dang dbang po rnams
NK071(du)001:4867: mi 'tshams par nyams thag pa de ltar bskal pa
NK071(du)001:4868: chen po drug tu 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing
NK071(du)001:4869: skyes so // de nas yi dwags su skye ba'i
NK071(du)001:4870: las kyi sgrib pa rtsub mo'i rnam par smin pa
NK071(du)001:4871: de yang khad kyi srabs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4872: sngon gyi dus su sngags spyod log pa'i srid pas ru tra'i rgyud du 'tshams sbyar nas /
NK071(du)001:4873: yi dwags su 'gro bas bsdus pa'i srin po chen
NK071(du)001:4874: po bya'i gshog pa can lus rab tu 'jigs shing
NK071(du)001:4875: sems gdug pa khro zhing gtum po ste /
NK071(du)001:4876: las kyi rdzu 'phrul lus gcig la mgo bo brgya yod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4877: de yang mgo brnyan mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4878: lus mi gcig pa brgya la mgo bo gcig las med pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4879: stag seng sogs kyi lus sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4880: lus gcig la yan lag mang po dang /
NK071(du)001:4881: yan lag rigs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4882: de dag gis mda' mdung sogs gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thog pa /
NK071(du)001:4883: gsod byed kyi 'khor bya gcan sogs rab tu mang po dang /
NK071(du)001:4884: 'jigs pa'i sprul gzugs sdom sdig sogs sna tshogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4885: 'jigs pa'i sgra ra la ra la sogs sna tshogs sgrogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4886: 'jigs pa'i gzugs dang mi snyan par nga ro dang /
NK071(du)001:4887: mi zhim pa'i dri dang kha rlangs kyis nad gtong zhing /
NK071(du)001:4888: lus can thams cad skyi bung zhes dngangs par byed pa /
NK071(du)001:4889: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag gis phyogs kun khebs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:4890: grang ba dang tsha ba'i dbugs phyogs bcu kun tu
NK071(du)001:4891: stong khams thams cad 'khrugs par byed pa rlung mkhris
NK071(du)001:4892: bad kan 'dus pa las gyur pa'i nad bzhi brgya
NK071(du)001:4894: sems myos shing dran pa nyams par byed pa'i byed
NK071(du)001:4895: las kyi klu'i ris dang lha ma yin gyi ris
NK071(du)001:4897: gzugs khams las tshangs pa'i ris sogs bsam tan dang po dang /
NK071(du)001:4900: 'bras bu che ba bzhi pa'i bar ste /
NK071(du)001:4901: gnas ris bcu gnyis pa man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK071(du)001:4902: ru tra des sngon dge ba'i bshes gnyen bsten cing
NK071(du)001:4903: sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa'i stobs kyi 'brel bas
NK071(du)001:4904: thams cad mkhyen pas 'dul ba'i dus la bab par
NK071(du)001:4905: gzigs nas thugs rje dang phrin las kyi 'dul bar
NK071(du)001:4906: gyur to // gdul bya bstan pa de nas 'dul
NK071(du)001:4907: byed ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i
NK071(du)001:4908: rdo rje gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bkod pa'i zung 'jug
NK071(du)001:4909: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las don bya ba'i yul 'jig
NK071(du)001:4910: rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyi bdag
NK071(du)001:4911: po dreg pa can ru tra 'dul ba'i nga rgyal
NK071(du)001:4912: chen pos zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi brjid ston pa'i
NK071(du)001:4913: phyir de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK071(du)001:4914: thugs dbyer mi phyed pa rdo rje'i bdag po rigs
NK071(du)001:4915: drug bcom ldan 'das dregs pa 'dul ba'i thabs la
NK071(du)001:4916: dgyes pa chen po khro bo'i rgyal po che mchog
NK071(du)001:4917: he ru ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam
NK071(du)001:4918: par 'phro ba'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i ting nge 'dzin
NK071(du)001:4919: la dgongs pa snyoms par zhugs te chos nyid de
NK071(du)001:4920: bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas yum khro mo dbang phyug
NK071(du)001:4921: chen mo mngon du phyungs te hi hi zhes yab
NK071(du)001:4922: la dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyi bskul pas /
NK071(du)001:4923: thabs shes kyi mkha' gsang rin chen dang pad+ma bde
NK071(du)001:4924: bas rgyas par mdzad nas yab yum gnyis su med
NK071(du)001:4925: par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas pad+ma nor bu thim nas
NK071(du)001:4927: rgyu gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi sprin
NK071(du)001:4928: spros pa las rkyen de'i tshe h+aum h+aum h+aum rdo
NK071(du)001:4929: rje gsum gyi bdag nyid bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha
NK071(du)001:4930: dz+wa la man+dala rdo rje khro bo sna tshogs 'bar
NK071(du)001:4931: ba'i dkyil 'khor phata phata phata ha la ha la
NK071(du)001:4932: ha la h+aum sgo gsum bkas shing gtor cig ces
NK071(du)001:4933: bskul tshig go / de skad ces brjod pas yab
NK071(du)001:4934: yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol ba'i sprin
NK071(du)001:4936: gang du spro na 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu
NK071(du)001:4937: mtha' yas pa khyab par gang spro na khro bo
NK071(du)001:4938: 'chol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs che chung stong gsum
NK071(du)001:4939: gyi 'jig rten tsam la grangs phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten
NK071(du)001:4940: gyi rdul phra mo snyed tsam 'thon pas stong khams
NK071(du)001:4941: gang bar gyur nas gdug pa can rnams bag 'khum
NK071(du)001:4942: par byed pa'o // de ltar khro bo'i sprin spros
NK071(du)001:4943: pa des 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad
NK071(du)001:4944: kyi sa rnam pa drug tu g.yos rab tu g.yos
NK071(du)001:4946: zin pa'i sgra thams cad drag por 'ur 'ur rab tu 'ura'ura kun tu rab tu 'ur 'ur ro //
NK071(du)001:4947: ma zin pa'i sgra rnams kyang rang 'khrol du chem
NK071(du)001:4948: chem rab tu chem chem kun tu chem chem mo
NK071(du)001:4949: // ri gling sogs dum bur shig shig rab tu shig shig kun tu shig shig go /
NK071(du)001:4950: de dag kyang gtor gtor rab tu gtor gtor kun tu gtor gtor ro //
NK071(du)001:4951: de ltar ltas chen po bco lnga dang khro bo'i
NK071(du)001:4952: sprin tshogs mi zad pa'i chos kun tu snang ba
NK071(du)001:4953: de'i tshe 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong gsum
NK071(du)001:4954: gyi khams thams cad na gnas pa'i gtso bo so
NK071(du)001:4955: so'i gnas su dbang che ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4956: 'phrul dang gzi brjid che ba dang /
NK071(du)001:4957: nus mthu che ba'i ris dbang phyug chen po dang
NK071(du)001:4958: tshangs pa la sogs te dregs pa can thams cad
NK071(du)001:4960: rab tu brgyal kun tu rab tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK071(du)001:4961: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul bstan pa de nas bcom
NK071(du)001:4962: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po che mchog nyid 'jig
NK071(du)001:4963: byed chen po shin tu rngam pa'i sku gdug pa
NK071(du)001:4964: can rnams skyi bung zhes byed pa'i gzi byin 'bar
NK071(du)001:4965: ba chen po'i me 'od 'phro ba khrag 'thung sku
NK071(du)001:4966: smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba'i rnam pa can dbu
NK071(du)001:4967: dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed ltar mtha'
NK071(du)001:4968: yas pas mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa de nyid
NK071(du)001:4969: la gong du spros pa'i khro bo'i sprin las rdo
NK071(du)001:4970: rje'i rigs kyi khro tshogs thams cad 'dus te stong
NK071(du)001:4971: nyid ye shes kyi bdag nyid badz+ra he ru ka
NK071(du)001:4972: rnam thar gyi dbu gsum ye shes kyi phyag drug
NK071(du)001:4973: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i rtags zhabs bzhi par gyur te
NK071(du)001:4974: / dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang chen por
NK071(du)001:4975: bzhugs par dgyes nas mkha' rlung gi dkyil 'khor la
NK071(du)001:4976: brten pa'i khrag gi rgya mtshor chags pa zhing chen
NK071(du)001:4977: gyi sa gzhi'i dkyil na keng rus chen po'i ri
NK071(du)001:4978: / rab kyi steng / ye shes kyi me dpungs
NK071(du)001:4979: 'bar ba chen po'i klong gzhal yas khang gi dbus
NK071(du)001:4980: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i dkyil na dbang phyug lha
NK071(du)001:4981: / rab kyi steng / chen po dang / dur
NK071(du)001:4982: khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa chen po khyo shug
NK071(du)001:4983: gi gdan la zhabs g.yas brkyang g.yon bskum du bzhugs
NK071(du)001:4984: / rab kyi steng / chen po dang / so
NK071(du)001:4985: // gzhan yang rigs bzhi'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK071(du)001:4986: sprin phung de dag kyang so sor 'dus pa las
NK071(du)001:4987: me long lta bu la sogs pa ye shes bzhi'i
NK071(du)001:4988: bdag nyid rigs bzhi'i he ru kar gyur pa'ang la
NK071(du)001:4989: la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po bud+d+ha he ru
NK071(du)001:4990: / rab kyi steng / chen po dang / so
NK071(du)001:4991: // kar gyur te / 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i shar
NK071(du)001:4993: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po cher gyur te lho phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:4994: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+mara gyur te nub phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:4995: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las su gyur te byang phyogs su bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:4996: khrag 'thung de dag kun kyang 'jigs byed chen po'i
NK071(du)001:4997: cha lugs dur khrod kyi chas dang h+aum phata sogs
NK071(du)001:4999: me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis shar du dri za dang /
NK071(du)001:5000: byang du gnod sbyin dang nub tu srin po dang /
NK071(du)001:5001: lhor gshin rje la sogs te gdug pa can thams
NK071(du)001:5002: cad bsdus pa khyo shug gi gdan la g.yas rkyang
NK071(du)001:5003: gis bzhugs so // btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo
NK071(du)001:5004: rigs lnga'i tshogs rnams kyang rigs so so'i he ru
NK071(du)001:5005: ka'i sku la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK071(du)001:5006: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang bas dregs pa gdan
NK071(du)001:5007: du byas pa de nas dregs pa chen po ru
NK071(du)001:5008: tra la sogs pa pho rgyud rnams kyis khro zhing
NK071(du)001:5009: gtum pa'i sems kyis dgra zlar mthong ste /
NK071(du)001:5010: lus gdan du gnas kyang gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen
NK071(du)001:5011: po sna tshogs bstan nas 'khor bcas mgrin gcig tu
NK071(du)001:5012: gdug pa'i nga ro sa mi snyan barlanga po'i gtum
NK071(du)001:5013: tshig gis 'di skad du smras pa /
NK071(du)001:5014: nged rnams gdan du bcings pa las thong thong khyed
NK071(du)001:5015: cag snying rje'i bdag po ma yin nam ci bdag
NK071(du)001:5016: cag la de ltar tho 'tshams par byed dam zhes
NK071(du)001:5017: zer zhing / shin tu gdug pa'i sems kyis khros nas da dung rngam mo //
NK071(du)001:5018: de nas gdug pa can de dag gi gnyen par
NK071(du)001:5019: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po rigs lnga'i he
NK071(du)001:5020: ru ka nyid sgrol byed rdo rje srin po dbu
NK071(du)001:5021: dgu phyag bco brgyad zhabs brgyad du gnas par sprul
NK071(du)001:5022: nas gsung rngam pa'i skad kyis /
NK071(du)001:5023: thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pa nyid kyis
NK071(du)001:5024: ru tra'i ngor shin tu khros pa ltar snang nas
NK071(du)001:5025: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes de dag gi sgo gsum bsdus
NK071(du)001:5026: shig pa'o // ha ha ha zhes dug gsum zhal du gsol bar dgyes pa'i bzhad sgra'o //
NK071(du)001:5027: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi kh+aa hi zhes sha khrag rus gsum zo zhig pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5028: sngags de skad ces brjod pas dbang phyug chen po
NK071(du)001:5029: la sogs pa gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag
NK071(du)001:5030: gi bdag 'dzin gcod phyir don snying dang /
NK071(du)001:5031: yul 'dzin gyi sgo 'gags phyir dbang po kun phyung mngon zhen dgag phyir nang khrol kun drangs /
NK071(du)001:5032: las ngan gyi bag chags gcod phyir yan lag kun
NK071(du)001:5033: dum bur bcad cing gtubs nas dug gsum dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:5034: phyir gti mug sha kun zos 'dod chags khrag kun
NK071(du)001:5035: 'thung / zhe sdang rus pa kun 'chos so //
NK071(du)001:5036: pho rgyud bsgral te btul ba de nas mo rgyud
NK071(du)001:5037: sbyor bas 'dul ba'i phyir h+aum h+aum h+aum ni sgo
NK071(du)001:5038: gsum bsdus shig pa'i bskul tshig b+h+yo ni ma mo
NK071(du)001:5039: rnams kyi snying po dang bod pa e 'dir +aa
NK071(du)001:5040: ra li rol pa dzahdzahdaguga pa'i sa bon no //
NK071(du)001:5041: de skad ces brjod pas phyogs bcu'i snod kyi 'jig
NK071(du)001:5042: rten khams nam mkha'i gtug pa dang bcas pa kun
NK071(du)001:5043: ma lus par yungs 'bru gcig tsam du chud par
NK071(du)001:5044: dbang 'byor ba'i rdzu 'phrul chen pos bsdus so //
NK071(du)001:5045: de nas bcud kyi sems can 'byung po phal pa'i
NK071(du)001:5046: rigs ma lus pa'i rgyal po ni lha dang lha
NK071(du)001:5047: min gyi blon po chen po rnams yin la /
NK071(du)001:5048: de'i yang rgyal po dregs pa chen po /
NK071(du)001:5049: srin po la sogs pa dbang phyug chen po pho rgyud nyi shu rtsa brgyad po yin pas /
NK071(du)001:5050: de rnams so so'i chung ma ni 'byung po mo
NK071(du)001:5051: rgyud phal pa'i rigs thams cad kyi rje mo ste
NK071(du)001:5052: blon po chen po'i chung ma de tsho'i yang rje
NK071(du)001:5053: mor gyur pa dbang mo nyer brgyad de /
NK071(du)001:5054: khyo'i ming chung mar grags pas /
NK071(du)001:5055: srin por da sha gri wa'i chung ma chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5057: lha chen drag po'i 'khrug mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5058: brgya byin gyi dbang mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5060: gdong drug gi gzhon nu mo dang drug ni shar gyi ma mo'o //
NK071(du)001:5062: nyi ma'i bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5063: zla ba'i zhi ba mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5064: be con gyi be con mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5065: srin po khrag mig srin mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5066: lha za byed kyi za ba mo dang drug ni lho yi ma mo'o //
NK071(du)001:5067: dga' byed dbang phyug gi dga' ba mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5068: stobs bzang gi ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5069: b+h+rim gi ri ti'i gcig pur spyod ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5071: nor srung gi grub mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5072: rlung lha'i rlung mo dang drug ni nub kyi ma mo'o //
NK071(du)001:5073: lha gsod byed kyi gsod byed mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5075: sa bdag phag chen gyi phag mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5076: gshin rje'i rgan byed mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5077: tshangs bdag gi sna chen mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5078: klu'i chu lha mo dang drug ni byang gi ma mo'o //
NK071(du)001:5079: lha nag po chen po'i nag mo chen mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5080: ra gdong chen mo'i ra mgo dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5081: srin po bum sna'i bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5082: gsus po che'i bsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo dang bzhi ni sgo ma'o //
NK071(du)001:5083: de la sogs pa ma mo'i tshogs te phyi'i las byed bran dang /
NK071(du)001:5085: nang gi las byed g.yog dang /
NK071(du)001:5086: de'i yang g.yog dang bcas pa 'khor zhing gi rdul
NK071(du)001:5087: snyed ltar mtha' yas pas thams cad kyang bsdus so
NK071(du)001:5089: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK071(du)001:5090: khrag 'thung chen pos ma mo rnams 'dul ba'i thabs
NK071(du)001:5091: kyis slar yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen mo lnga
NK071(du)001:5092: ka yongs su rdzogs par ma mo rnams la snang
NK071(du)001:5093: bar byas nas / de dag kun kyang dgyes pas
NK071(du)001:5094: rol pa las khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin 'byung
NK071(du)001:5095: ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK071(du)001:5096: bar byas nas / zhugs te / sku dang gsung
NK071(du)001:5097: dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo rje las sngags
NK071(du)001:5098: bar byas nas / zhugs te / 'di phyung ngo
NK071(du)001:5099: // +aahmh'u rdo rje gsum badz+ra ni rdo rje ste
NK071(du)001:5100: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje /
NK071(du)001:5101: pra be sha rab tu zhugs pa ste gsang ba'i pad+mara ro //
NK071(du)001:5102: a la la hohdagyesa pa'i ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5103: de skad ces brjod pas 'byung mo'i rgyal mo rnams
NK071(du)001:5104: rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang la shin tu chags
NK071(du)001:5105: pa'i yid g.yos nas rang rang gi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:5106: sdud pa ste 'dzum zhing rgyas par 'gyur nas /
NK071(du)001:5107: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul
NK071(du)001:5108: du dbang mo rnams bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen
NK071(du)001:5109: po he ru ka'i rigs lnga'i sku la 'khril te
NK071(du)001:5110: / 'di ltar dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje he ru ka'i sku brgyud du snang ba las /
NK071(du)001:5111: phyogs kyi gtso mo srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5115: srin mo bzhi sgo skyong nag mo chen po dang /
NK071(du)001:5118: ser nag chen mo dang bzhi brgyad po rnams so sor 'khril te /
NK071(du)001:5119: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rigs bzhi po lnga lngar snang ste /
NK071(du)001:5120: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la tshangs ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5124: gzhon nu mo dang shar phyogs kyi lnga rnams 'khril lo //
NK071(du)001:5125: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po che'i sku la /
NK071(du)001:5131: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+ma'i sku la khrag gi myos ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5136: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las kyi sku la me mo dang /
NK071(du)001:5142: dgyes pa chen po rigs lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de dag gis /
NK071(du)001:5143: h+aum zhes brjod pas dbang mo rnams kyi pad+ma'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:5144: 'khor gyi tshogs rigs lnga'i rdo rje la bsdus nas
NK071(du)001:5145: sku'i stod smad shin tu bcum pas rol par gyur
NK071(du)001:5146: to // gnyis med du rol pa de nas dgyes
NK071(du)001:5147: te ha zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgras sbyor mtshams nas
NK071(du)001:5148: yab yum gyi byang chub sems kyi sprin las zhi
NK071(du)001:5149: ba'i las dag par byed pa dkar mo'i tshogs dang
NK071(du)001:5150: to // / dbang gi sdus pa rkun mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5151: zhi bas spang blang 'byed pa med pa'i dbyings su sbyar ba rmongs mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5152: drag pos mi mthun pa 'joms pa thal byed mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5153: rgyas pa'i yon tan gyis gang ba spos mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5154: drag pos zhe gcod pa gtum mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5155: las thams cad pas gang yang 'grub pa sme sha can gyi tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5156: rgyas pa sa 'phel ba'i las grub pa ma tshogs
NK071(du)001:5157: ma'i tshogs rnams zhing dbyug dang thod khrag sogs rang
NK071(du)001:5159: ngo mtshar ba'i gzugs rgyan dang bcas pas dbang mo'i mkha' nas phyir 'thon to //
NK071(du)001:5160: gnas ma brgyad po re re yang nyi shu rtsa
NK071(du)001:5161: brgyad du 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba
NK071(du)001:5162: chen po 'khor lo'i rtsibs mchan dang gru chad bzhir
NK071(du)001:5163: shar lho'i phyogs nas g.yas skor gyis 'khor bar 'jigs
NK071(du)001:5164: pa'i gzugs rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas nas
NK071(du)001:5165: 'khod do // gnas ma 'thon pa de nas shin
NK071(du)001:5166: tu dgyes nas he zhes brjod pa'i bzhad sgra dang
NK071(du)001:5167: sems sprin las rtogs pa zil gyis gnon pa seng
NK071(du)001:5169: de bzhin du dpa' zhing brtul phod pa stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5170: thabs la mkhas pas phung po'i bdud 'joms pa wa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5171: mel tshe mkhas shing lha bu'i bdud 'joms pa khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5172: mig rno zhing shes bya la ma thogs pa bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5173: dbug bral la spyod cing 'chi bdag gi bdud 'joms pa kang+ka'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5174: nyon mongs pa zad par byed pa kh+aa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5175: gdul bya phra ba'ang mi 'dor ba 'ug gdong ste /
NK071(du)001:5176: de ltar phra man chen mo re re'ang nyer brgyad
NK071(du)001:5177: kyi tshogs dang bcas pa rnams lag gnyis bsnol bas
NK071(du)001:5179: rang rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du bcas nas 'thon par gyur to //
NK071(du)001:5180: 'thon nas kyang rigs bsdus te 'bar ba chen po'i
NK071(du)001:5181: 'khor lo'i phyi rol gser khyams la shar phyogs nas
NK071(du)001:5182: 'khor bar phyogs bzhir mche ba can dang /
NK071(du)001:5183: mtshams bzhir gshog pa can bzhi rngams pa'i mdangs kyi 'khod do //
NK071(du)001:5184: yul ma 'thon pa de nas shin tu dgyes pas
NK071(du)001:5185: phrin las bzhi'i snang bas phyogs bcu'i zhing khams ma
NK071(du)001:5186: lus par khyab nas phata ces brjod pa'i bzhad sgra
NK071(du)001:5187: dang sems sprin las byams pas 'dzin pa rdo rje
NK071(du)001:5188: sring 'gro rta gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5189: snying rjes 'ching ba rdo rje phag gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5190: dga' bas sdom pa rdo rje 'jig rten 'ug gdong ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5191: btang snyoms kyi myos par byed pa rdo rje ro
NK071(du)001:5192: langs spyang gdong ma'i tshogs rnams lcags kyu sogs rang
NK071(du)001:5193: rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar du ma bcas
NK071(du)001:5195: 'thon nas kyang nyer brgyad sogs rigs bsdus te /
NK071(du)001:5196: 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhir shin tu rngams pa'i gzugs kyi gnas so //
NK071(du)001:5197: dkyil 'khor 'khod pa'i mdzad pa rdzogs pa de nas
NK071(du)001:5198: yab yum dgyes par rol pa'i sbrin las phyogs bcu
NK071(du)001:5199: nas phata ces bsgrags pas thams cad rngams shing khros
NK071(du)001:5200: nas ma mo thams cad kyang sngon gang nas 'ongs
NK071(du)001:5201: pa'i rang rang gi gnas ga la ba der yud
NK071(du)001:5202: tsam la rdzu 'phrul gyi phyin par bakye'o //
NK071(du)001:5203: sbyor sgrol gyi phrin las rmad du byung ba bstan
NK071(du)001:5204: pa de nas bcom ldan dgyes pa chen po dpal
NK071(du)001:5205: khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga po de dag kun
NK071(du)001:5206: badz+ra he ru ka bsdus pa nyid rang byung gi
NK071(du)001:5207: thugs rje chen po gso bar byed pas bdud rtsi
NK071(du)001:5208: byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin snyoms par
NK071(du)001:5209: zhugs nas sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed
NK071(du)001:5210: pa'i rdo rje las dbang bskur ba'i dam rdzas sngags
NK071(du)001:5211: dang bcas pa 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK071(du)001:5212: badz+ra ma h+aa a mri ta mchog ster rdo rje
NK071(du)001:5213: bdud rtsi chen po ma h+aa kro d+ha khro bo
NK071(du)001:5214: chen po am am am zhes brjod pas lan gsum
NK071(du)001:5215: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lcer bzhag cing dbang bskur /
NK071(du)001:5216: sngar zhal du stab pa'i dbang phyug chen po la
NK071(du)001:5217: sogs pa thams cad bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen
NK071(du)001:5218: po de dag gi lto ba na gnas pa dpal
NK071(du)001:5219: chen po'i bsnams te gshang lam nas bton te mi
NK071(du)001:5220: gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor chud pa las slar
NK071(du)001:5221: yang bsnams nas u tsush+ma kro d+ha zhes pa khro
NK071(du)001:5222: bo rme ba brtsegs pa dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi
NK071(du)001:5223: phyung nas gong gi badz+ra ma h+aa sogs kyis dbang
NK071(du)001:5224: bskur / rme ba brtsegs pas 'dam kun 'thungs te
NK071(du)001:5225: gsol pas dregs pa can de dag dran pa slar
NK071(du)001:5226: rnyes nas snang ba rnam pa ra 'byed pa'i ting
NK071(du)001:5227: nge 'dzin thob pas 'bar ba khro bo'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:5228: gyi tshogs bsam yas lhun grub kyi zhal mngon gsum
NK071(du)001:5229: bskur / du mthong ste / khro bo de dag thams cad kyang dbu dgu brgya pa /
NK071(du)001:5232: sku gzi byin mtha' yas pas 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par mthong ngo //
NK071(du)001:5233: ye shes kyi cho 'phrul gyi gdug pa'i ru tra
NK071(du)001:5234: btul ba de'i dus su gdul bar bya ba'i yul
NK071(du)001:5235: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum po
NK071(du)001:5236: kun tu gnas shing dbang sgyur ba'i dregs pa'i dbang
NK071(du)001:5237: phyug chen po thams cad gang la gang 'dul gyis
NK071(du)001:5238: ji ltar 'dul ba'i thabs kyi sgo sna tshogs su
NK071(du)001:5239: snang ba'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab par rang
NK071(du)001:5240: rang gi zhing so sor snang bas snga phyi med
NK071(du)001:5241: par dus gcig tu btul lo //
NK071(du)001:5242: gnas spar ba de nas dregs pa can de dag skrag pas lus shin tu 'dar zhing /
NK071(du)001:5243: sems bred pas rab tu dpa' zhum pa'i nga ros bdag cag khyed kyi 'bangs su mchi /
NK071(du)001:5245: gal te 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na bdag
NK071(du)001:5246: cag rnams kyi mgo dang lus ni dum bu brgyar
NK071(du)001:5247: 'gas shing / snying yang tshal par 'gas shing dum bur gtub par gyur cig /
NK071(du)001:5248: lus kyang rul zhing myags la dmod tshig gis mes 'tshig nas thal bar brlag pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5249: tshe phyi mar yang rdo rje'i dmyal bar ltungs nas 'o 'dod 'bod par shog /
NK071(du)001:5250: de skad ces 'bangs su mchi bar mna' bor nas
NK071(du)001:5251: rang rang gi lus khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:5252: gyi gdan du phul nas bzhag go /
NK071(du)001:5253: de nas dregs pa can thams cad mgrin gcig tu yang smras pa /
NK071(du)001:5254: bdag cag rnams kyis mchis brang ste chung ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5255: ma dang bu mo dang sring mo rnams kyang khro
NK071(du)001:5256: bo'i dkyil 'khor chen por 'bul bas bzhes su gsol
NK071(du)001:5257: / gang gis na dregs can 'joms pa'i dpa' bo
NK071(du)001:5258: lha chen po de rnams kyis yang rje por gyur
NK071(du)001:5259: pa dpal he ru kas bzhes su gsol //
NK071(du)001:5260: zhes 'khor phul nas mchod par dam bca' ba ni /
NK071(du)001:5261: bdag cag so so 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK071(du)001:5262: 'di ltar zhal mthong ba'i khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:5263: 'khor chen po 'di'i ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa'i
NK071(du)001:5265: rang gi gtsug gis nor bu 'od 'bar ba bskur ba ltar /
NK071(du)001:5266: sems la g.yo sgyu med cing mchog tu gus pa
NK071(du)001:5267: dang ldan pa'i sems kyi blangs nas rnam pa thams
NK071(du)001:5268: cad du sbyi bo'i gtsug tu bzhag ste bskur bsti
NK071(du)001:5269: dang rim gro phun sum tshogs par bgyi bas dkyil
NK071(du)001:5270: 'khor gyi mtshan 'chang ba de yi dgos pa'i las
NK071(du)001:5272: 'dod pa'i re ba ma lus pa rdzogs par bdag cag rnams kyis sgrub bo //
NK071(du)001:5273: gal te dpa' bo he ru ka'i spyan snga 'dir
NK071(du)001:5274: bdag cag gis yal gam bcas pa'i tha tshig smras
NK071(du)001:5275: pa 'di bzhin du ma bsgrubs na /
NK071(du)001:5276: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo lus snying rnams rim par
NK071(du)001:5277: tshal par bkas shing dmod pa'i mtshon gyis gtubs dum
NK071(du)001:5278: bur 'thor nas rul bar mchi'o zhes smras so //
NK071(du)001:5279: bro bor ba de nas dregs pa can de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5282: bu mo'i tshogs thams cad sngar bkye ba'i las slar
NK071(du)001:5283: yang dkyil 'khor gyi drung du yud tsam gyis 'ongs
NK071(du)001:5284: nas de dag thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu smras
NK071(du)001:5285: pa bdag cag dbang mo 'khor gyi tshogs dang bcas
NK071(du)001:5286: pa thams cad kun g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba'i
NK071(du)001:5287: dpa' bo chen po 'bangs su mchi bar bgyi na
NK071(du)001:5288: dpa' bo chen po bdag cag rnams la phrin las
NK071(du)001:5289: rnam pa bzhi las 'di dang 'di gyis shig ces
NK071(du)001:5290: las gang byed kyi bka'i bsgo ba skal pa dang
NK071(du)001:5291: mthun pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK071(du)001:5293: ci bgyi zhus pa de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes
NK071(du)001:5294: pa chen pos de rnams kyi lag tu rdo rje
NK071(du)001:5295: byin nas rdo rje'i mi'i srin mo sogs rang rang
NK071(du)001:5296: dang mthun pa'i ming gi dbang bskur te /
NK071(du)001:5297: dkyil 'khor chen po'i gser khyams kyi phyi rol tu
NK071(du)001:5298: khrag khyams la so so'i las bskos pa'i phyogs kyi
NK071(du)001:5299: rim pa ji lta bar bkod do //
NK071(du)001:5300: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:5301: las 'dis khro bo rang bzhin 'bras bu mthar phyin
NK071(du)001:5302: gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sprin rnam par bkod pa'i le'u
NK071(du)001:5306: khro bo sngon byung 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK071(du)001:5308: bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor de yang khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan /
NK071(du)001:5310: gal te zhi bas mi thul na //
NK071(du)001:5311: rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor spro //
NK071(du)001:5313: le'u bcu bzhi yan chad kyi zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gtso bor bstan cing /
NK071(du)001:5314: gal te zhi bas mi thul ba'i gdug pa can rnams kyi ngor /
NK071(du)001:5315: le'u bco lnga par rdo rje khro bo'i bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:5316: le'u bcu drug pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5317: lo rgyus dang gzhung dang mtshan no //
NK071(du)001:5319: de nas sogs nas phyung ngo bar gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5323: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i sngags dang /
NK071(du)001:5324: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor sbyan drangs pa sogs las kyi rim pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:5326: rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK071(du)001:5327: khro mo nyi shu'i rtsa bskyed las sngags dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)001:5328: dbang mo rnams kyi rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:5329: dang po ni badz+ra ma h+aa sogs /
NK071(du)001:5334: dang po badz+ra g+aoo ri sogs gnyis pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5338: gsum pa dbang mo'i rtsa sngags b+h+yo drug tshan bzhi
NK071(du)001:5339: bzhi mtshan gcig gnyis pa las kyi rim pa'i sngags
NK071(du)001:5340: la gsum ste / dbang cing drang ba'i sngags me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba'i tshigs sngags /
NK071(du)001:5341: drin lan du mchod cing brtan pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:5348: gnyis pa yon tan ni ces brjod pas sogs /
NK071(du)001:5352: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas gsung
NK071(du)001:5353: sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom ldan 'das
NK071(du)001:5354: dgyes pa chen pos khro ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs chen
NK071(du)001:5355: po sngar bstan pa 'di dag gsung sngags kyi dam
NK071(du)001:5356: tshig gis grub par bya ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)001:5357: pa khro bo khrag 'thung chen po rigs lnga rang
NK071(du)001:5358: rang gi btsun mo dang bcas pa'i tshogs de dag
NK071(du)001:5359: sku dang gsung dang thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i rdo
NK071(du)001:5360: rje'i bdag nyid rang byung gi ye shes rang shar
NK071(du)001:5361: ba'i sngags kyi nga ro rngam pa las lhag ting
NK071(du)001:5362: gsung gi dkyil 'khor gsang sngags 'di dag phyung ngo
NK071(du)001:5363: // skabs 'dir khro bo'i phrin las sgom rim gyi
NK071(du)001:5364: sdebs sogs bshad du yod kyang 'grel pa las shes
NK071(du)001:5365: // par bya'o // de la sngags kyi mgo 'dren
NK071(du)001:5366: rnams ni ye shes lnga'am rdo rje gsum gyi bdag
NK071(du)001:5367: nyid rab sngags kyi sa bon no //
NK071(du)001:5368: badz+ra rdo rje rigs kyi mtshan ma h+aa chen po
NK071(du)001:5369: sh+r+ai dpal he ni he la ste spyod cing brtson
NK071(du)001:5370: pa ru ni ru d+hi ra ste khrag ka ni
NK071(du)001:5371: bdag po'i sgra ste khrag la rol pa'i don gyis
NK071(du)001:5372: khrag 'thung ngo 'bru drug po 'di spyi'i mtshan sngags
NK071(du)001:5373: so // ma h+aa tsan+da gtum po chen po sarba
NK071(du)001:5374: dush+tam ni gdug pa can thams cad an+ta ka ni
NK071(du)001:5375: mthar byed pa ha na bsnun pa da ha sreg
NK071(du)001:5376: pa pa tsa chod pa h+aum h+aum h+aum ni dang
NK071(du)001:5377: po rtsa ba'i sa bon gnyis pa thugs bskul ba'i
NK071(du)001:5380: phata ces bkas par gyis zhes te /
NK071(du)001:5381: 'di rnams las las bskul ba'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:5382: 'og ma rnams la'ang de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5383: sarba ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK071(du)001:5384: cad ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK071(du)001:5385: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK071(du)001:5386: h+aum h+aum phata / rat+na rin po che ma h+aa
NK071(du)001:5387: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka
NK071(du)001:5388: ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata
NK071(du)001:5389: h+aum h+aum phata / / pad+ma skad sor bzhag ma
NK071(du)001:5390: h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka karma las ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK071(du)001:5391: he ru ka yum lnga'i sngags ni /
NK071(du)001:5392: badz+ra sngar bzhin d+ha ra 'chang ba ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai /
NK071(du)001:5393: khro mo dbang phyug ma chen mo /
NK071(du)001:5394: dz+wa li n+ai 'bar ba ma h+aum rtsa ba'i sa bon phata sngar bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:5395: de bzhin du sarba ta th+aa ga dang ma h+aa
NK071(du)001:5396: kro d+hi shwa ri sngar bzhin sarba dush+ta na gdug
NK071(du)001:5397: pa can thams cad h+aum phata /
NK071(du)001:5398: ma h+aa s+aur+ya nyi ma chen mo /
NK071(du)001:5399: rat+na ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai sngar bzhin bi
NK071(du)001:5400: da ma rig ma h+aum phata h+r+ai sh+aut+ta sa man
NK071(du)001:5401: ta kun tu rgod pa pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hii
NK071(du)001:5402: shwa ri sngar bzhin kh+aa hi zo zhig h+aum phata
NK071(du)001:5403: sarba a mo g+ha thams cad don yod pa ma
NK071(du)001:5404: h+aa kro d+he shwa ri'i bi shwa sna tshogs h+aum
NK071(du)001:5405: phata / de nas ni rab basngagasa badz+ra ni rdo rje ste dbang rtags mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5406: goo r+ai dkar mo 'am mdzod ldan ma ha ni
NK071(du)001:5407: rtsa ba'i sa bon badz+ra tso r+ai chom rkun ma'am
NK071(du)001:5408: rkun mo ha / badz+ra pra mo he ha /
NK071(du)001:5409: rang rmongs ma'am rmong mo ha /
NK071(du)001:5411: ro langs ma'am thal byed ma h+aa /
NK071(du)001:5412: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai gtum mo ha /
NK071(du)001:5413: badz+ra puk+ka s+ai spos mo ha /
NK071(du)001:5414: badz+ra g+ha sma r+ai sme sha can nam drod mo ha /
NK071(du)001:5415: badz+ra sme sha n+ai dur khrod ma'am ma tshogs ma ha rnams gong bzhin no //
NK071(du)001:5416: dang badz+ra 'dra sid+ha mu kh+ai seng gdong ma he
NK071(du)001:5417: rnams rtsa ba'i sa bon badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai
NK071(du)001:5419: badz+ra sring g+aa la mu kh+ai /
NK071(du)001:5421: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai khyi gdong ma'am spyang gdong ma he /
NK071(du)001:5422: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK071(du)001:5423: bya rgod gdong ma'am bzhad gdong ma he /
NK071(du)001:5424: badz+ra kang+ka mu kh+ai kang+ka'i gdong ma'am dur bya'i gdong ma he /
NK071(du)001:5425: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he gdong ma'am bya rog gdong ma he /
NK071(du)001:5426: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai 'ug gdong ma he
NK071(du)001:5427: rnams 'dra de nas dang badz+ra 'dra +aar+ya te dza
NK071(du)001:5428: te nga dzah 'phags ma sring 'gro ma'i rigs 'gro
NK071(du)001:5430: badz+ra a mu kh+ai gdong mo 'am don yod ma h+aum badz+ra lo ka 'jig rten la bam /
NK071(du)001:5431: badz+ra b+hi sma pa la ya ba tu thal bar
NK071(du)001:5432: byed pa hoh de nas b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo
NK071(du)001:5433: b+h+yo / b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)001:5434: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)001:5435: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK071(du)001:5437: zhes pa'i b+h+yo yig nyer brgyad ni ma mo'i tshogs kyi don dang /
NK071(du)001:5439: 'jig byed ma zhes bod pa dang bskul ba'ang yin no //
NK071(du)001:5440: rab sngags ru ru dzo'i sgra las 'jigs par gyis
NK071(du)001:5441: lu ni lu nya'i sgras gcod pa ru lu gong
NK071(du)001:5442: bzhin h+aum ni bsdig pa ste de rnams snyan gsan
NK071(du)001:5444: e h+ye hi tshur spyon tshur spyon +aa na ya dgug pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5445: dzahh+aum bam hoh tshad med bzhi 'gro don la bskul ba ste de rnams spyan drangs pa'i sngags so //
NK071(du)001:5446: ram ni dam ye gnyis med me'i 'dab 'byor tsam du bzhugs pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5447: yang ni glu'i 'go 'dren gdul bya khro la gdul
NK071(du)001:5448: byed khro bar snang bas rgyud zhi bar mdzad pa
NK071(du)001:5449: / thugs rje ngang gis khro bar bstan pas 'gro
NK071(du)001:5450: ba'i dpal mgon 'jig byed chen po rngams pa'i tshogs
NK071(du)001:5451: khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sku gsung thugs yon
NK071(du)001:5452: tan 'phrin las lnga'i byin rlabs gzhan las ches che
NK071(du)001:5454: de nyid dus da lta nyid du 'dir ni bdag la rtsol /
NK071(du)001:5455: bar mdzod cig pa ste dngos grub bskul ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5456: rab sngags badz+ra kro d+ha rdo rje khro bo sa
NK071(du)001:5457: ma ya dam tshig h+aum bsdus shig pa ste me
NK071(du)001:5458: tog dor ba'o // badz+ra krod+ha sngar ltar sa ma
NK071(du)001:5459: ya dam tshig 'dus la s+t+wam khyed ces bod pa'am
NK071(du)001:5460: tog dor ba'o // bab sngags so // badz+ra sa
NK071(du)001:5461: ma ya sngar 'dra phata spros shig badz+ra sa ma
NK071(du)001:5462: ya hoh mnyes par mdzod ces pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5463: a li sogs 'di rnams a ba b+h+ram sha'i skad yin ces gsungs so //
NK071(du)001:5464: de la a li ni chang ste btung ba u
NK071(du)001:5465: li sha ste bza' ba t+aa li ta p+aa li
NK071(du)001:5466: / 'bru 'bras sogs dam tshig gi rdzas sna tshogs damsh+t+aa zhal che ba bsgrad pa /
NK071(du)001:5467: go n+aa rdo rje roo dri khro ba'am drag po kha ram stob pa ste /
NK071(du)001:5468: rdo rje khro bo mche ba bgrad pa'i zhal du stob bo //
NK071(du)001:5470: yo gi n+ai rnal 'byor ma kh+aa hi gsol cig hoh mchod pa stobs pa ste /
NK071(du)001:5472: h+aum ha he phata ni dam ye gnyis med du gyur nas gsal zhing brtan par byas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5473: de skad ces gsung sngags brjod pa'i mthun byin gyis
NK071(du)001:5474: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba thams cad
NK071(du)001:5475: lus snang ba'i rtog tshogs thams cad rab tu 'tshig
NK071(du)001:5476: / ngag grags pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad rab tu 'tshig /
NK071(du)001:5477: sems sgrib pa'i rtog tshogs thams cad kun tu 'tshig go /
NK071(du)001:5478: des snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'bar grags pa
NK071(du)001:5479: sngags kyi dkyil 'khor du rab tu 'bar dran rig
NK071(du)001:5480: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du kun tu 'bar ro //
NK071(du)001:5481: de'i tshe nam mkhas gar khyab thams cad du 'bar
NK071(du)001:5482: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs kyi skus gang gsung gis
NK071(du)001:5483: khyab par rab tu gang thugs ye shes kyis kun
NK071(du)001:5484: tu khyab cing gang bar gyur to //
NK071(du)001:5485: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:5486: las 'dis khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i lhag ting gsung
NK071(du)001:5487: gi dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o
NK071(du)001:5489: // // zhes gsungs pas 'di khro bo rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:5491: don du gnyer ba sgrub pa'i skabs khro bo'i skyed sngags dang /
NK071(du)001:5492: 'ching zlos gnyis las khro bo'i sngags bstan to //
NK071(du)001:5494: khros pa'i dus kyi skur bton nas //
NK071(du)001:5496: le'u bco lnga par sngon byung ston pa'i rnam 'phrul
NK071(du)001:5497: khro bo rang snang gi dkyil 'khor gleng gzhi'i tshul
NK071(du)001:5498: du bshad nas / khros pa'i tshul de nyid rjes
NK071(du)001:5499: 'jug nyams len gyi dus kyi tshe skur bton pa
NK071(du)001:5500: ste bskyed bzlas kyi sngags gsal bar bstan to //
NK071(du)001:5501: le'u bcu bdun pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5506: de nas sogs gnyis pa gzhung la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5513: ngo bo rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK071(du)001:5516: 'bar ba'i 'khor lo sogs rkang pa drug /
NK071(du)001:5517: gnyis pa ni khyu mchog sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:5518: gnyis pa brten pa lha la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:5519: gtso bo rigs lnga'i tshul bzhugs dang /
NK071(du)001:5528: smug nag sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5530: dbu gsum sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:5532: ko rlon sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:5536: btsun mo sogs rkang pa gcig /
NK071(du)001:5537: gnyis pa 'khor gyi bkod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5538: gnas dang sogs rkang pa drug /
NK071(du)001:5544: gsung gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa de nas lhag pa
NK071(du)001:5545: sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ston pa'i phyir bcom
NK071(du)001:5546: ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos khro bo'i sprin gsang
NK071(du)001:5547: sngags dang bcas pa de dag gis bskyed pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:5548: 'khor gyi rnam pa gsal bar bstan pa'i phyir ched
NK071(du)001:5550: 'og gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i lte ba la
NK071(du)001:5551: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rin po che'i rang bzhin b+hany+dza
NK071(du)001:5552: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus su ye shes
NK071(du)001:5553: lnga'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa
NK071(du)001:5554: / de'i phyir bden bzhi'i gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan cing /
NK071(du)001:5555: che bas yon tan rgyas pas dbyibs gru bzhi rnam
NK071(du)001:5556: thar bzhi'i sgo bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan pa
NK071(du)001:5557: bden gnyis mtshon pa'i 'bar bar khyams nang ma gser
NK071(du)001:5558: khyams dang / phyi ma khrag khyams gnyis kyis mdzes shing /
NK071(du)001:5559: thod pa'i rtsig pa la sbrul sbram dang thod phreng
NK071(du)001:5560: gi dra ba sogs rgyan sna tshogs kyis bkra ba
NK071(du)001:5561: / steng zhing lpags kyi thog phub nyi ma dang
NK071(du)001:5562: zla ba'i mthong dkar dang bcas pa'i dbus lha chen
NK071(du)001:5563: gyi mgo dang tsit+ta'i tog gis brjid pa phyi rol
NK071(du)001:5564: du dur khrod brgyad kyis bskor zhing 'bar ba'i me
NK071(du)001:5565: phung me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba'i klong nas khro chung
NK071(du)001:5566: mang po 'phro zhing 'khrug pas mdzes pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5567: gdan dbus kyi lte ba dang rtsib bzhir pad+ma dang
NK071(du)001:5568: zla nyi'i steng gti mug sogs dug lnga dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:5569: rtags su shar rtsibs la khyu mchog lhor ma he
NK071(du)001:5570: nub tu gzig dang byang du stag dbus su gtum
NK071(du)001:5571: po dom rnams zung gi spar bas ni dreg pa
NK071(du)001:5572: zil gnon gyi gdan dbus su dbang phyug dang lha
NK071(du)001:5573: chen po drag po la sogs pas shar du dri
NK071(du)001:5574: za sogs pho mo la sbub dang gan rkyal du
NK071(du)001:5575: bzung ba'o // 'khor gnas yul sgo skyong rnams nyi
NK071(du)001:5576: ma dang zhing dbang mo rnams la zhing skam gyi
NK071(du)001:5577: bzung ba'o // gdan no / sku mdog /
NK071(du)001:5581: rat+na ser nag pad+ma dmar nag /
NK071(du)001:5582: karma he ru ljang nag ste /
NK071(du)001:5583: gdug pa can gyi ngor shin tu 'jigs pa'i sku /
NK071(du)001:5584: che zhing yan lag rags pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5585: thams cad kyang rnam thar gsum mtshon pa'i dbu gsum
NK071(du)001:5586: ye shes drug gi phyag rgya drug rdzu 'phrul gyi
NK071(du)001:5587: zhabs bzhi / g.yas rkyang ba'i 'dor stabs su bsgrad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5588: glang chen gyi ko rlon gyi gos ni sna tshogs
NK071(du)001:5589: gyon pa sogs bgo ba'i gos gsum rgyal rigs dkar
NK071(du)001:5590: pos skra 'chings sogs sbrul gyi rgyan dang /
NK071(du)001:5591: thod phreng ni skam po lnga yi dbu rgyan sogs gdogs pa'i rgyan gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5592: dpral bar thal chen tshom bu sogs byug pa'i rtse
NK071(du)001:5593: gsum ste dur khrod chas brgyad snyan gong g.yas g.yon
NK071(du)001:5594: nyi zla'i 'od zer spro ba gsal ba'i chas gnyis
NK071(du)001:5595: po gsung rngams pa'i sgra chen drag po shin tu
NK071(du)001:5597: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten 'khor yug dang bcas pa
NK071(du)001:5598: ni badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag g.yon tha mas bsnams
NK071(du)001:5599: pa yin la rdo rje rtse dgu de'i g.yas dang
NK071(du)001:5600: po dang / rtse lnga dang dung chen gang ba
NK071(du)001:5601: ni thams cad kyi phyag bar pa gnyis dang ral
NK071(du)001:5602: gri ni karma he ru'i g.yas dang pos dgra s+t+wa
NK071(du)001:5604: thong gshol ni karma'i g.yon tha ma'o //
NK071(du)001:5605: de la sogs pa rang rang gi lag cha sna tshogs 'dzin pa ste /
NK071(du)001:5606: rang rang gi rigs kyi btsun mo 'jigs pa'i tshogs lnga ka sku mdog yab dang mthun pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5609: de'i yul brgyan bcas dag pas goo r+ai brgyad dang /
NK071(du)001:5610: seng ha brgyad de dag gi phyag rgya ni goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5611: seng+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5612: sgo ma bzhi'i phyag rgya ni rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu'i 'dzin sogs /
NK071(du)001:5613: de ltar khro mo nyi shu'i 'khor gyi bkod pas rab tu mdzes shing /
NK071(du)001:5614: gzhan yang slas dang byi mo bran mo'i zlas phye
NK071(du)001:5615: ba'i dbang phyug ma'i tshogs grangs bcu tshan gnyis dang
NK071(du)001:5616: ni brgyad de nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis mdzes par
NK071(du)001:5617: bskor ba de dag kyang rang rang gi stan zhing
NK071(du)001:5618: skam re dang sku mdog dang /
NK071(du)001:5619: lag cha ni srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang sogs dang /
NK071(du)001:5620: las skal ci bgyi zhes zhu zhing rdzu 'phrul ni
NK071(du)001:5621: thogs med du chas te so so'i las dang mthun
NK071(du)001:5623: de skad ces brjod pa'i mthus 'jig rten drug gi
NK071(du)001:5624: phyogs bcu thams cad du 'bar ba chen po khro
NK071(du)001:5625: bo'i dkyil 'khor gyis kun tu khyab cing gsal bar
NK071(du)001:5626: gyur to // gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK071(du)001:5627: 'di khro bo'i lhag ting sku dang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5629: // zhes pa 'dis khro bo rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:5630: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las /
NK071(du)001:5632: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor sgrub pa
NK071(du)001:5633: las bskyed bya khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan bi ma
NK071(du)001:5634: las / dkyil 'khor nyid du dgod par bya //
NK071(du)001:5635: zhes pas le'u gong mar khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sku
NK071(du)001:5636: las bton pa de nyid le'u 'dir dkyil 'khor so
NK071(du)001:5637: so'i go sar dgod par bya ba bstan no //
NK071(du)001:5638: le'u bco brgyad pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5644: gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5647: de gsung ba'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:5654: de la sogs rkang pa lnga /
NK071(du)001:5658: mnyam pa sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5660: bza' dang sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:5661: gnyis pa mchod pa'i 'bras bu la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5665: phyogs bcu sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5674: de nas khyad par gyi mchod pa ston pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:5675: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos dkyil 'khor gyi
NK071(du)001:5676: lha tshogs mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen po 'di ched
NK071(du)001:5677: du brjod do // lhag ting gi dkyil 'khor brten
NK071(du)001:5678: nas tshogs bsags pa de la bde gshegs rnams mchod
NK071(du)001:5679: pa dang mkha' 'gro rnams la sbyin pa gnyis las
NK071(du)001:5680: mchog dam pa ni 'di yin te /
NK071(du)001:5681: thog mar rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid lta ba rtogs
NK071(du)001:5682: shing ting nge 'dzin goms pas zhen rtogs chos dbyings
NK071(du)001:5683: su bsgral te rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5684: de nas thugs rjes gzhan sgrol ba ni bsgral bya
NK071(du)001:5685: sgrol byed gnyis med du rtogs pa'i blo yis zin
NK071(du)001:5687: de'i ngang las rgyu 'bras kyi don la rmongs pa'i
NK071(du)001:5688: blo ngan zhing bcu'i sa bon srid pa'i 'jig rten
NK071(du)001:5689: 'og mar brgyud pa 'di dag snying re rje zhes
NK071(du)001:5690: thabs snying rje chen po'i sgo nas bsgral bya'i rnam
NK071(du)001:5691: shes gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems nyid
NK071(du)001:5692: kyi dbyings su der bsgral bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5693: yab yum gnyis su med par 'khril bas bde ba'i
NK071(du)001:5694: mchod rdzas chen po nyi zla byang chub kyi sems
NK071(du)001:5695: mnyam par sbyor bas rnal 'byor bdag nyid bde ba'i
NK071(du)001:5696: rol mos mnyes par byas nas sems sprin spros pas
NK071(du)001:5698: 'khor 'das chos rnams mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i dngos
NK071(du)001:5699: grub sgrub pa'i rdzas chen po bdud rtsi lnga po
NK071(du)001:5700: 'di dag / bdag dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang /
NK071(du)001:5701: ye shes lha'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med du mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul lo //
NK071(du)001:5702: sha zan sogs bza' ba dang /
NK071(du)001:5703: shing thog sogs bca' ba dang /
NK071(du)001:5704: ja chang sogs btung ba dang srab 'jam sogs bgo ba dang /
NK071(du)001:5705: gzhan yang lha mi'i longs spyod 'dod yon lnga ldan
NK071(du)001:5706: thams cad lha dang lha mor rnam par dag pas
NK071(du)001:5707: 'bul tshul ni / mchod yul ye shes kyi dkyil
NK071(du)001:5708: 'khor lha ni mchod rdzas 'dod yon lha mo'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:5709: 'khor gnyis med bde ba chen po ro gcig tu
NK071(du)001:5711: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhir 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pa yi /
NK071(du)001:5712: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi che ba'i yon tan
NK071(du)001:5713: rmad po che rnams kyang rang rig rtogs pa las
NK071(du)001:5714: gzhan nas btsal du yod pa'am tshur 'ongs ba ma
NK071(du)001:5715: yin na / gzhan 'jig rten pa'i dngos grub lha
NK071(du)001:5716: srin la sogs pa'i mthu las byung ba'i yon tan
NK071(du)001:5717: 'grub pa ni lta smos kyang ci dgos so //
NK071(du)001:5718: rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin las rung ba rnams
NK071(du)001:5719: kyis lha sku phyag rgya chen po rang rig la
NK071(du)001:5721: de nyid yul gyis mi 'phrog par gsal ba la
NK071(du)001:5722: brtan pa thob nas 'bras bu 'grub bam mi 'grub
NK071(du)001:5723: snyam pa'i yid gnyis dang the tshom med pas na
NK071(du)001:5724: / rang bzhin 'bras bu'i dkyil 'khor dngos grub chen po 'bar bar 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:5725: de skad ces brjod pa'i mthus mnyes pa'i mchod pa
NK071(du)001:5726: chen pos 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad
NK071(du)001:5727: du mchod pa'i sprin gyi rol mos khyab par gyur
NK071(du)001:5728: to // gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK071(du)001:5729: 'dis rgyal ba rnams mchod cing ma mo dang mkha'
NK071(du)001:5730: 'gror sbyin pa'i thabs thun mong du ma grags pas
NK071(du)001:5731: mchog dam pa'i bstan pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o
NK071(du)001:5734: khro bo rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:5735: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu las /
NK071(du)001:5736: gnas su stobs pa mchod pa'i skabs /
NK071(du)001:5738: dam rdzas kyi mchod pa bstan /
NK071(du)001:5740: de nyid la ni mchod pa 'bul //
NK071(du)001:5742: le'u bcu bdun par so so'i gnas su bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha de dag la /
NK071(du)001:5743: le'u 'dir mchod pa sprin rab 'byams dbul bar bstan to //
NK071(du)001:5744: le'u bcu dgu pa la gsum te /
NK071(du)001:5751: dam tshig dngos kyang de'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:5753: dam tshig gi rtsa ba dang /
NK071(du)001:5754: rnam grangs mdor bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5755: mnyam pa'i dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5756: dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon dang /
NK071(du)001:5757: dam tshig gi rang bzhin dang /
NK071(du)001:5758: dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad dang /
NK071(du)001:5759: de ma nyams pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:5762: 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus pa'i che ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5764: bla med theg par sogs tshigs bcad /
NK071(du)001:5767: ji ltar 'dus shing dag tshul rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5769: bla med sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5774: mi tshangs par spyod pa spong ba ji ltar 'dus shing dag pa'o /
NK071(du)001:5776: yod med sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5777: gnyis pa ni bden pa sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5779: chos rnams sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5781: ma chags sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5782: gnyis pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5783: rtsa ba'i dam tshig de gnyis nges tshigs bshad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:5785: bla med sogs rkang pa drug /
NK071(du)001:5786: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:5788: mi dor ba lnga bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5791: gti mug sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5793: dkar rtsis sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5795: yan lag sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5797: bsrung zhing sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5798: gsum pa dam tshig skyon yon dang bcas pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5799: mnyam la sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5800: bzhi pa nyams pa'i skyon la gsum ste nyams dang 'grogs pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:5802: yan lag nyams pa'i skyon no //
NK071(du)001:5804: rtsa ba nyams pa'i tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5806: rtsa ba'i dam tshig tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5807: gsum pa yan lag sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5808: lnga pa dam tshig gi rang bzhin ni /
NK071(du)001:5809: dam tshig rnams ni sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5810: drug pa dam tshig gi rnam grangs rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5811: sum brgya drug cu dang mtha' yas par spro ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5813: rtsa ba'i dam tshig sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5815: dam tshig 'di ni sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5816: bdun pa ma nyams pa'i yon tan la drug /
NK071(du)001:5817: 'bras bu thob cing tshad med pa'i yon tan dang /
NK071(du)001:5820: rgyal ba'i spyod yul thob pa'i /
NK071(du)001:5822: nyams kyang bskang ba'i thabs yod pa'i yon tan no //
NK071(du)001:5824: gzhan yang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:5826: rgyal ba'i sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5828: dam pa sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5830: bde gshegs sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5832: ji bzhin sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:5834: nyams na sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:5839: sa bcad de ldan gyi gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:5840: khyad par can gyi mchod sbyin bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:5841: de nas dam tshig gi rim pa ston pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:5842: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po sngags 'chang rnal
NK071(du)001:5843: 'byor pa rnams log par mi ltung zhing 'bras bu
NK071(du)001:5844: myur du grub pas lam la 'bad pa don yod
NK071(du)001:5845: par bya ba'i phyir bla na med pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)001:5846: chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK071(du)001:5847: gang zag rtogs sgoms gdengs ldan mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig la gnas pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5848: bla med theg par rab tu nges pa ste nyams su lon na nyon mongs pa dug lnga dang /
NK071(du)001:5849: des bskyed pa'i las rnams kun la spyad kyang sgyu
NK071(du)001:5850: ma mkhan gyis sgyu ma'i longs spyod la spyad par
NK071(du)001:5851: ltar byas par snang kyang de la 'dzin zhen med
NK071(du)001:5852: pas de'i sgrib pa dang bag chags mi gsog pa'i
NK071(du)001:5853: steng du tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur te /
NK071(du)001:5854: spyod pa de'i ngo bo la so byang phyid rgyud
NK071(du)001:5855: rnams kyi tshul khrims dang sdom pa thams cad kyang
NK071(du)001:5856: phun sum tshogs par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK071(du)001:5857: gsang sngags bla med rdo rje'i theg pa mchog gi
NK071(du)001:5858: dam tshig 'di'i nang du 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang
NK071(du)001:5859: gis rnam par bzhag pa'i nyan thos kyi tshul khrims
NK071(du)001:5860: dang / byang sems dang gsang sngags phyi nang bsrung
NK071(du)001:5861: bya ji snyed pa'i sdom pa bsam yas yod pa
NK071(du)001:5862: dang / / ma lus pa'i yon tan kun yar
NK071(du)001:5863: ldan gyi tshul du 'dir 'dus shing nyes pa phra
NK071(du)001:5864: mos kyang gos pa med pas rnam par dag pa'i
NK071(du)001:5865: dang / / phyir ro // don dam par chos
NK071(du)001:5866: thams cad yod pa rtag pa dang med pa'i chad
NK071(du)001:5867: dang / / phyir ro // pa'i mtha' dang /
NK071(du)001:5868: de gnyis ka dang bral ba'i dbu ma tsam du'ang
NK071(du)001:5869: dang / / phyir ro // pa'i mtha' dang /
NK071(du)001:5870: mi dmigs shing / kun rdzob tu sgyu ma'i skyes
NK071(du)001:5871: bus mig yor gyi sems can bsad pa lta bu'i
NK071(du)001:5872: tshul du snang yang snang dus nyid nas bcad bya'i
NK071(du)001:5873: srog bden par grub pa med pas srog gcod mkhan
NK071(du)001:5874: dang bcad pa'i 'du shes kyang ma grub pas don
NK071(du)001:5876: srog dang de ldan gyi skyes bur 'dzin pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5877: log rtog 'khrul ngo tsam yin pa'i phyir de ltar
NK071(du)001:5878: rtogs nas zhing bcu'i srog bcad kyang nyes pas mi
NK071(du)001:5879: gos shing / tshogs rdzogs pas na srog bcod spong
NK071(du)001:5880: ba'i sdom pa'i ngo bo dang yon tan yar ldan
NK071(du)001:5881: gos shing / du 'dus so // de ltar 'og ma rnams la'ang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5882: chos thams cad bden pa gnyis ka'i tshul la bdag
NK071(du)001:5883: dang gzhan zhes dbyer med pas don dam par mi
NK071(du)001:5884: gnas shing tha snyad kun rdzob du'ang 'phrul dag'i lha
NK071(du)001:5885: rnams rang gi sprul pa'i longs spyod la rang gi
NK071(du)001:5886: len pa'i tshul gyi blangs te /
NK071(du)001:5887: spyad kyang don la tha dad min pa de bzhin
NK071(du)001:5888: du blang bya'i yul gzhan dang des bdag gir bzung
NK071(du)001:5889: ba'ii rdzas ma byin par len rgyu zhig gud na
NK071(du)001:5890: med pa'i phyir / blangs pa'ang med ces blangs kyang
NK071(du)001:5891: thams cad bdag nyid las mi 'da' bar gnyis med
NK071(du)001:5892: kyi dbyings su ro gcig tu rtogs pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)001:5893: med pa'i phyir / // chos rnams bden med sgyu ma lta bu ste rdzun tsam du zad la /
NK071(du)001:5894: de bzhin du brjod byed kyi ming dang tshig tu
NK071(du)001:5895: sgro btags nas de la der 'dzin pa'ang rdzun no
NK071(du)001:5896: de lta bu'i rdzun pa nyid la ni shes byed
NK071(du)001:5897: dang rjod byed rdzun pa nyid spyod pa ste chos
NK071(du)001:5898: gang la'ang bden pa nyid ma grub na des ltos
NK071(du)001:5899: kyi rdzun pa'ang ma grub pas rdzun zhes bya ba'i
NK071(du)001:5900: chos ni ming tsam btags pa tsam du'ang yod ma
NK071(du)001:5901: yin no // chos thams cad la yul so sos
NK071(du)001:5902: gnyis med du gsal ba ni ma chags pa'i ye
NK071(du)001:5903: shes te de la gnyis su zhen cing chags pa'i
NK071(du)001:5904: dus na gnyis med du shes pa'i lta ba dang
NK071(du)001:5905: yin no // / 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK071(du)001:5906: thabs kyis zin pa'i spyod pa dang ldan pas 'khrig
NK071(du)001:5907: pa'i 'dod chags la spyod pa ltar snang ba'i dus
NK071(du)001:5908: nyid na yang tha mal gyi chags pa'i dri ma
NK071(du)001:5909: rdul tsam yang med pa de ni 'dzag med kyi
NK071(du)001:5910: tshul khrims tshangs par spyod pa thams cad kyi mchog
NK071(du)001:5912: chos thams cad shin tu rnam dag bde stong zung
NK071(du)001:5913: 'jug gi ngo bor grol ba ni chags pa chen
NK071(du)001:5914: po bde chen gyi ye shes yin no //
NK071(du)001:5915: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga las /
NK071(du)001:5916: bla med mi spang ba ni /
NK071(du)001:5917: yul bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi sems gnyis
NK071(du)001:5918: mi spang ba'i dam tshig gi tshul ni lhag pa
NK071(du)001:5919: bden gnyis dbyer med du rtogs nas sgo gsum lha'i
NK071(du)001:5920: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' bar
NK071(du)001:5921: byed pa'o // bla ma la bskur ba ni /
