NK071(du)001:5922: spyi yi bla ma sogs drug dang /
NK071(du)001:5923: khyad par du'ang dbang bskur rgyud bshad /
NK071(du)001:5924: man ngag ston pa'i bla ma gsum ni /
NK071(du)001:5925: lhag par yang sgo gsum mnyes pa sgrub pa'i sgo nas bkur ba'o //
NK071(du)001:5926: sngags rgya rgyun mi bcad pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5927: yul sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi dus rgyun mi bcad par 'bad par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5929: spyi ring nye 'dres kyi spun rnams las khyad par phyi ma gsum ni /
NK071(du)001:5930: yang dag pa'i lam du zhugs pa'i mched la byams brtse'i lhag bsam rgyun mi chad par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5932: spyir gsang ba'i sngags kyi tshig don rnams phyir gyur pa ste snod min la gsang ba dang /
NK071(du)001:5933: khyad par gsang bcu rnams gzhan du smra bar mi bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5934: de ltar lnga po 'di ni yon tan gyi gzhi
NK071(du)001:5935: rten yin pas rtsa ba lnga zhes gsungs pa rnams
NK071(du)001:5936: te / de'ang byang sems dang sngags rgya gnyis sgrub
NK071(du)001:5937: pa'i dam tshig dang gzhan gsum bsrungs pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)001:5939: yang log gi dug lnga gnyis las /
NK071(du)001:5940: chos thams cad mnyam nyid du rtogs pa'i tshe /
NK071(du)001:5941: lta ba la phyogs ris dang /
NK071(du)001:5942: spyod pa la blang dor gyi 'byed pa med pa ni /
NK071(du)001:5943: gti mug dang de ma rtog pa la dmigs med
NK071(du)001:5944: kyi snying rje rjes su chags pa'i 'dod chags dang
NK071(du)001:5945: / rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'i zhe sdang dang /
NK071(du)001:5946: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba gshongs su mi 'bebs
NK071(du)001:5947: pa'i nga rgyal gnyis 'dzin mnyam nyid kyi klong du
NK071(du)001:5948: mi shong ba'i phrag dog ste /
NK071(du)001:5949: rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas mi spang ngo //
NK071(du)001:5950: log pa'i dug lnga rang mtshan pa rnams kyang thabs
NK071(du)001:5951: kyi zin na sbyad kyang mi 'ching bar rnam par
NK071(du)001:5952: grol ba'i lam yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK071(du)001:5953: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir mi spang ngo //
NK071(du)001:5954: dkar rtsi byang sems dkar po dang /
NK071(du)001:5955: dmar rtsi byang sems dmar po dang /
NK071(du)001:5956: sha chen dag pa'i snod de dwangs ma dang /
NK071(du)001:5957: dri chu rnams ni rigs lnga ye shes lnga sgrub
NK071(du)001:5958: pa'i dam rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i mi dor
NK071(du)001:5959: ro // de dag la ni yan lag bcu yi dam tshig zhes bya ste /
NK071(du)001:5960: ye nas dag pa gsum dang mnyam pa bzhi'i don rtogs pas spyad par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:5961: sngar bshad bsrung zhing sgrub pa'i dam tshig rnam pa
NK071(du)001:5962: lnga ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig yin te de dag
NK071(du)001:5964: nyams na byang chub kyi rigs kyang med par 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)001:5965: mi spang mi dor ba'i dam tshig lnga tshan gnyis
NK071(du)001:5966: ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi grogs su dgos pas
NK071(du)001:5967: yan lag gi dam tshig ces bya ste de dag
NK071(du)001:5969: chos thams cad bden gsum ris med du mnyam pa
NK071(du)001:5970: la shes 'jug gi lam zab mos mnyam par sbyor
NK071(du)001:5971: ba yi / don de las mi 'da' bas mnyam pa'i dam tshig ste /
NK071(du)001:5972: de'i ngang la gnas na 'bras bu mnyam rdzogs chen
NK071(du)001:5973: po kun tu bzang po bye ba med pa'i sa
NK071(du)001:5974: thob pa 'gyur bas bsrung bar bya zhing /
NK071(du)001:5975: gal te de'i 'gal zla mnyam pa las 'das te
NK071(du)001:5976: tha dad du rtogs na 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob
NK071(du)001:5978: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i bslab sdom 'chal ba
NK071(du)001:5979: dag dam tshig gso ba'i thabs la dus nye bar
NK071(du)001:5981: skad cig tsam yang mi 'grogs shing yud tsam du'ang gtam smra bar ma byed cig /
NK071(du)001:5982: ci'i phyir na nyams pa dang 'grogs par gyur pa'i
NK071(du)001:5983: nyes pa brjod kyis mi lang ste zlas nyams zhes
NK071(du)001:5984: bya'o // rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams par gyur na /
NK071(du)001:5985: char phab pas than pa 'byung ba lta bu tshe
NK071(du)001:5986: 'dir yang las gang sgrub pa thams cad kyang 'bras
NK071(du)001:5987: bu phyin ci log par 'gyur ba sogs mi 'dod
NK071(du)001:5989: phyi mar yang yid du mi 'ong ba sna tshogs
NK071(du)001:5990: pa'i 'bras bu ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal mi
NK071(du)001:5991: 'dod bzhin du khab len gyi lcags ltar rang dbang
NK071(du)001:5993: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na /
NK071(du)001:5994: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub med cing phyi mar
NK071(du)001:5995: ngan song gsum gyi gnas su ltung bar 'gyur ro
NK071(du)001:5996: // rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams
NK071(du)001:5997: kyi rang bzhin ni sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed
NK071(du)001:5998: rdo rje chen po'i rang bzhin gsum gyi gnas su
NK071(du)001:5999: ltung bar 'gyur 'di ni dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK071(du)001:6000: kun gyi bdag nyid chos kun gyi srog dang bslab
NK071(du)001:6001: pa thams cad kyi dam pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:6002: rtsa ba'i dam tshig la brgya drug cu dang yan
NK071(du)001:6003: lag gi dam tshig la nyis brgyar phye bas sum
NK071(du)001:6005: de yang rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po la ni /
NK071(du)001:6006: gcig ste re re la'ang thabs shes gnyis gnyis su phye bas bcu dang /
NK071(du)001:6007: yang rtsa ba lnga po re re la'ang bcu phrag gsum rer phye bas chig brgya lnga bcu ste /
NK071(du)001:6008: de sngar gyi bcu dang sdom pas brgya drug cu'o //
NK071(du)001:6009: yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag ni gzhan las
NK071(du)001:6010: khyad par du gyur pas rmad po che yin te
NK071(du)001:6011: des don bya ba'i yul 'jig rten lnga tshan gnyis
NK071(du)001:6012: te bcu po re re la dbye tshul gti mug
NK071(du)001:6013: lta bu gcig la'ang nang tshan pa bcu phrag gnyis
NK071(du)001:6014: su ste nyi shu nyi shur dbye bas nyis brgya
NK071(du)001:6015: ste / de dag sdom pas sum brgya drug cu'o //
NK071(du)001:6016: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag
NK071(du)001:6017: ni gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas rmad po
NK071(du)001:6018: che yin te / des don bya ba'i yul 'jig
NK071(du)001:6019: rten drug gi phyogs bcu na srid pa gsum gyis
NK071(du)001:6020: bsdus pa'i 'gro ba ji snyed cig yod pa de
NK071(du)001:6021: rnams so so'i rnam par rtog pa 'dul ba'i gnyen
NK071(du)001:6022: por dam tshig gi rnam grangs kyang de snyed cig
NK071(du)001:6024: mnyam pa'i dam tshig las gzhan yang rtsa lag gi
NK071(du)001:6025: dam tshig rnams bsrung ba'i 'bras bu rgyal mchog rigs
NK071(du)001:6026: kyi bdag po kun bzang gi go 'phang thob par
NK071(du)001:6027: 'gyur te / de'i ngo bo 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK071(du)001:6028: thams cad lhag ma ma lus pa rgyal ba'i sku
NK071(du)001:6029: gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya yis ngo bor lhun gyis
NK071(du)001:6030: grub pas ched du sgrub pa med par 'bras bu'i
NK071(du)001:6031: mchog dam pa kun bzang gi yon tan ma lus
NK071(du)001:6033: de la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa'i mchog go /
NK071(du)001:6034: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog gsang sngags 'dzin cing dam tshig
NK071(du)001:6035: la gnas pa de lha chen po la sogs pa
NK071(du)001:6036: 'jig rten gyi gtso bo rnams dang /
NK071(du)001:6037: de'i 'khor ma mo dang mkha' 'gro thams cad kyis
NK071(du)001:6038: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ltar bkur ba'i gnas dam pa
NK071(du)001:6040: dam pa'i mchog sangs rgyas dang dam pa sar gnas
NK071(du)001:6041: kyi byang chub sems dpa' yis rim par rang gi
NK071(du)001:6042: sras dang spun du dgongs pas thugs rje'i byin gyis
NK071(du)001:6044: dam ldan 'di ni bde gshegs nyid kyi spyod yul
NK071(du)001:6045: rigs pa 'dzin pa'i sa la rim par zhugs nas
NK071(du)001:6046: ltung gnas kyi 'jigs pa dang bag tsha ba med
NK071(du)001:6047: pa spyod yul yongs dag kun tu bzang pos sar
NK071(du)001:6049: gnas lugs ji bzhin pa'i chos nyid mngon du byed pa bla med kyi dam tshig dang /
NK071(du)001:6050: de'i nang du gdul bya blo dang 'tshams par 'dul
NK071(du)001:6051: ba'i thabs nyan rang sogs theg pa ji snyed pa
NK071(du)001:6052: de dag gi sdom pa bsam yas pa thams cad
NK071(du)001:6053: kyang 'dir yar ldan gyi tshul du 'dus shing dgag
NK071(du)001:6054: bya ma lus pa rnam par dag pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6055: yon tan thams cad ma btsal bar rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:6056: gal te gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams par gyur
NK071(du)001:6057: na nyan thos kyi pham pa ltar gsor mi rung
NK071(du)001:6058: ma yin te / skong ba'i khyad par can gyi tshogs bskang bas sngar bzhin sor chud cing /
NK071(du)001:6059: dam tshig gi yon tan thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6060: de la sogs pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa'i mchog
NK071(du)001:6061: rdo rje'i theg pa 'di la mnga' ba yin no
NK071(du)001:6062: // de skad ces brjod pas dam tshig gi rang
NK071(du)001:6063: bzhin gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid yin pas na
NK071(du)001:6064: // / de'i rang bzhin las rgyal ba de bzhin
NK071(du)001:6065: gshegs pa nyid kyang 'da' bar mi mdzad na gzhan
NK071(du)001:6067: de'i phyir gdul bya rnams la bla na med pa'i dam tshig bstan nas 'dul bar gyur to //
NK071(du)001:6068: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:6069: las 'dis rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig
NK071(du)001:6070: gi rnam bzhag bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o
NK071(du)001:6075: mi 'da' ba dam tshig bstan pa yin la /
NK071(du)001:6076: slob dpon bi ma las zhi khro rab 'byams mchod pa'i tshe //
NK071(du)001:6077: sdom la gnas pa shin tu gces /
NK071(du)001:6078: zhes pas le'u gong mar dkyil 'khor gyi lha zhi khro rab 'byams mchod pa sogs kyi tshe /
NK071(du)001:6079: le'u 'dir rnal 'byor pa rnams dam tshig la gnas pa shin tu gces par bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6080: le'u nyi shu pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:6090: rdzas rnams sogs las bya ba dang /
NK071(du)001:6092: bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan dang /
NK071(du)001:6093: las bzhi'i gnas gzung thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6094: don stongs kyi sems bstan pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6095: dang po la'ang las rnam pa bzhi las thog mar /
NK071(du)001:6100: mchod sbyin bya ba yon tan dang bcas pa lug rgyud kyi bro'i yon tan dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6102: bdud rtsi lnga sogs rkang pa /
NK071(du)001:6103: gnyis pa la e sogs rkang pa /
NK071(du)001:6104: gsum pa bkug nas sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6105: bzhi pa 'bar ba sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:6106: lnga pa e yi sogs tshig bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6107: dbang sogs sa bcad gzhan des khog phub la /
NK071(du)001:6108: khyad par sgos chos rnams gzhung du smos la /
NK071(du)001:6109: gnyis pa lhag ma'i las la gnyis te /
NK071(du)001:6113: slas dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6115: dam ba sgrag cing las la bskul ba las de ma sgrub pa'i skyon /
NK071(du)001:6116: las sgrub pa'i yo tan no //
NK071(du)001:6118: sngon tshe sogs rkang pa dgu /
NK071(du)001:6120: dam bca' sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6123: gsum pa bro gar glu tshig gi yon tan la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6129: khrag 'thung yab yum gyi las bzhi ka 'grub pa /
NK071(du)001:6130: phyogs kyi khro mos dbang rgyas /
NK071(du)001:6131: mtshams kyi khro mos zhi drag /
NK071(du)001:6132: phyogs mtshams kyi phra men mas drag po /
NK071(du)001:6133: dbang phyug mas mngag gzhug gi las 'grub pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6137: mdzod ldan sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6139: spos mo sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6143: slas dang sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6145: gzung thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:6146: ljon pa sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6147: lnga pa don stong sems bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:6148: dang bas sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6153: sa bcad de ldan gyi gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:6155: de nas phrin las ston pa'i phyir de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)001:6156: pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos ye nas
NK071(du)001:6157: sems nyid phrin las bzhi'i rang bzhin du lhun gyis
NK071(du)001:6158: grub pa'i dam tshig gi de nyid cho ga bzhis
NK071(du)001:6159: bskul bas mngon du sbyang bar byin gyis rlobs pa
NK071(du)001:6160: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK071(du)001:6161: nas phrin las kyi don ched du brjod par 'di
NK071(du)001:6162: brjod do // phyi snod gru gsum yi ge e yi rnam pa can gyi dbus su /
NK071(du)001:6163: nang bcud khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor drag po'i las la mchog tu shis shing /
NK071(du)001:6164: drag po'i sreg blug skabs badz+ra he ru kas gtsos
NK071(du)001:6165: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i lha tshogs gtum chen
NK071(du)001:6166: gtum pa'i cha byad can la stangs kyi sems rab
NK071(du)001:6167: tu khros pa'i yid kyis sreg blugs kyi mchod sbyin
NK071(du)001:6168: byas na tshogs gnyis las grub sangs rgyas bsod nams
NK071(du)001:6169: brgya'i mtshan gyis brgyan pa'i sku yang 'jig na bsgral
NK071(du)001:6170: bya'i sems can rnams lta ci smos /
NK071(du)001:6171: ling+ga bsgrub bya'i bdud rtsi lnga ste zag rdzas 'am
NK071(du)001:6172: zas sha bu ram sbrang rtsi til dang lnga sogs
NK071(du)001:6173: la rgyu byas pa'i ling+ga pho mo gang yin gyis
NK071(du)001:6174: mtshan ma can rus dang ming du bcas pa bris
NK071(du)001:6176: 'brub khung gru gsum du gzhug par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:6177: bsgrub bya bkug nas bstiim la lcags sogs la byas
NK071(du)001:6178: pa'i rdo rje phur bu sras mchog tu bskyed pas
NK071(du)001:6179: gdab cing gris gtub mtshon char phab pas lus ngag
NK071(du)001:6180: rdul du brlag par byas nas khrag 'thung gi tshogs
NK071(du)001:6181: la dbul te sdeb par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:6182: phyi snod e yi rnam pa'i dbus su bcud khrag
NK071(du)001:6183: 'thung 'bar ba'i lha tshogs rnams kyi dkyil 'khor gtso
NK071(du)001:6184: mchog badz+ra he ru kar byas par bsam la /
NK071(du)001:6185: ling ro spung pa'i phyir bro ra gru gsum du
NK071(du)001:6186: byas la mathe'u'i chung rnams lu gu rgyud du sbrel
NK071(du)001:6187: zhing bsdams nas h+aum bzhi'i sngags kyis bskul zhing /
NK071(du)001:6188: phyag rgya de ltar bcings par gyur pa la mig
NK071(du)001:6189: dang lus bskyod nas bro brdungs pas rdo rje'i khro
NK071(du)001:6190: tshogs phyogs bcur g.yos pas bsgrub bya brlag par bsam
NK071(du)001:6191: la / slar yang sngags drag dang phyag rgyas gzam
NK071(du)001:6192: pa'i dran pa myos nas snying gas te lus 'tshig
NK071(du)001:6193: la / par 'gyur ro // de bzhin du dbang
NK071(du)001:6194: la bam gyi rnam pa'i dkyil 'khor zla gam dmar
NK071(du)001:6195: po'i nang khrag 'thung tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor las la
NK071(du)001:6196: shis pa'i mchog dbang la pad+ma he ru ka'i lha
NK071(du)001:6197: tshogs 'od 'bar ba gzi brjid che zhing sku lhun
NK071(du)001:6198: po chen po lta bu pad rigs gtso bor byas
NK071(du)001:6199: pa la stangs kyi sems chags pa'i yid kyis mchod
NK071(du)001:6200: sbyin byas pas rdo rje gsung pad+ma gar dbang yang
NK071(du)001:6201: dbang du 'gyur na gzhan lta ci smos /
NK071(du)001:6202: dbang gi ling+ga rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la
NK071(du)001:6203: bsgrub bya'i mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya ste
NK071(du)001:6204: / zangs sam shing dmar po las dbal zla gam can /
NK071(du)001:6205: rdo rje chags pa'i steng pad+ma k+ai la yar bskyed pa'i phur bus dbang po lnga gdab ste /
NK071(du)001:6206: mtshon char phab ste bsgral ba chags pa'i tshogs la
NK071(du)001:6207: thim par 'bul la sngar bzhin bam gyi tshogs kyi
NK071(du)001:6208: dkyil 'khor du bskyed la srin lag lu gu rgyud
NK071(du)001:6209: du sbrel zhing bsdams nas bro brdungs bas 'gro ba
NK071(du)001:6210: gzhan du 'gugs par 'gyur ba lta ci smos /
NK071(du)001:6211: phyag na rdo rje'ang rang gi phyi bzhin du 'brang
NK071(du)001:6212: ba sogs yid la ci 'dod pa de bzhin du
NK071(du)001:6214: rgyas pa la ma yi rnam pa'i gru bzhi ser
NK071(du)001:6215: po lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gtso mchog rat+na he
NK071(du)001:6216: ru kar gtso bor byas pa'i lha 'od 'bar ba
NK071(du)001:6217: sprul pa'i 'du 'phro can gzi brjid chen po la
NK071(du)001:6218: / sems dga' ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas pas tshe bsod 'phel ba sogs /
NK071(du)001:6219: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:6220: rgyas pa'i ling+ga rgyu bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la
NK071(du)001:6221: 'dod pa'i yon tan 'byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi gter
NK071(du)001:6222: du btags par byas la gser sogs las dbal gru
NK071(du)001:6223: bzhi par byas pa nga rgyal dga' 'phro ste rat+na
NK071(du)001:6224: he ru kar bskyed pa'i phur bus gdab pa sogs
NK071(du)001:6225: byas te rdo rje gzi brjid ste rat+na he ru
NK071(du)001:6226: ka'i tshogs la 'bul bas tshe bsod sogs 'phel bar
NK071(du)001:6227: 'gyur ro sngar bzhin ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:6228: du bskyed pa gung mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel
NK071(du)001:6229: zhing bsdams nas bro brdung bas gzi brjid 'bar ba'i
NK071(du)001:6230: rnam 'phrul chen po rigs kyi khro bo spro ba'i
NK071(du)001:6231: ting nge 'dzin gyi yon tan tshe dang ye shes
NK071(du)001:6232: bsod nams sogs 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i yid bzhin gyi
NK071(du)001:6233: nor bus nam mkha'i khams thams cad gang bar 'gyur
NK071(du)001:6234: ro // zhi ba la ya yi rnam pa'i zlum
NK071(du)001:6235: po dkar po lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gtso mchog
NK071(du)001:6236: bud+d+ha he ru kas gtso byas pa'i lha tshogs dwangs
NK071(du)001:6237: shing gsal ba'i gzi brjid mchog tu 'bar zhing 'od
NK071(du)001:6238: zer 'tsher ba la stangs kyi sems zhi zhing dang
NK071(du)001:6239: ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin byas na ma rung pa
NK071(du)001:6240: gtum chen rngam pa'ang zhi ba'i sems su lhan ner
NK071(du)001:6241: ro // 'gyur ro // zhi ba'i ling+ga rgyu bdud
NK071(du)001:6242: rtsi lnga'i zas lnga la ma rung pa gtum rngam
NK071(du)001:6244: dngul lam dkar po las dbal zlum por byas pa
NK071(du)001:6245: lhan ner gsal ba ste bud+d+ha k+ai la yar bskyed
NK071(du)001:6246: pa'i phur bu drug gis yan lag lnga dang snying
NK071(du)001:6247: la gdab pa sogs byas te /
NK071(du)001:6248: 'bar ba lhan ne'i ste bud+d+ha he ru ka'i tshogs la 'bul ba dang /
NK071(du)001:6249: sngar bzhin ya yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du bskyed
NK071(du)001:6250: la mdzub mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel zhing bsdams
NK071(du)001:6251: nas bro brdung bas pha rol ma rung pa'i sems
NK071(du)001:6252: me ltar 'bar ba'ang lhan ner zhi ba'i byin rlabs
NK071(du)001:6253: kyis khyab pas sdig pa dang gdug sems thams cad
NK071(du)001:6254: cung zad kyang yid la mi rgyu bas g.yo ba
NK071(du)001:6256: de nas lhag ma'i las ni /
NK071(du)001:6257: dpal chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi mu ran du gnas
NK071(du)001:6258: pa slas te lha chen po'i chung ma dang byi
NK071(du)001:6260: g.yog byed pas bran mo'i tshogs te dbang phyug nyer
NK071(du)001:6261: brgyad po lhag ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa'i mgron yin
NK071(du)001:6262: pas cho ga bzhin du sbyin te sngon rang rang
NK071(du)001:6263: gi khas blangs pa'i dam tshig rnams rab tu bsgrags
NK071(du)001:6265: gang 'dod pa'i las de dang de byed par bka' bsgo bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:6266: de yang sngon ru tra 'dul ba'i tshe dpal chen
NK071(du)001:6267: po he ru ka gdul bya dang mthun par shin
NK071(du)001:6268: tu gdug cing gtum bag can du bzhengs te /
NK071(du)001:6269: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad kyi dregs pa can /
NK071(du)001:6270: ma lus pa rnams 'dul bar mdzad pa'i /
NK071(du)001:6271: dbang phyug dang byin rlab khyad par du gyur phyir
NK071(du)001:6272: rmad po che mnga' bas lha chen po sogs dbang
NK071(du)001:6273: du bsdus nas de dag gi 'khor rnams longs spyod
NK071(du)001:6274: pa'i phyir dbang dang slas su dbang bskur ba byas
NK071(du)001:6275: te zhi sogs so so'i las rnams skal ba bzhin
NK071(du)001:6276: bskos pa de nyid sngon ji ltar dam bcas shing
NK071(du)001:6277: khas blangs pa rnams skad cig kyang ma thogs par
NK071(du)001:6278: myur du las 'bras mngon par phyung bar mdzod cig
NK071(du)001:6279: pa'o // rang gi dam bcas pa bzhin du las
NK071(du)001:6280: ma byas na sngon ji ltar rang gis dam bcas
NK071(du)001:6282: sdoms bcas kyi mtshams de las 'da' bar 'gyur la
NK071(du)001:6283: gal te dam tshig de las 'das par gyur na
NK071(du)001:6284: ni khyed cag rnams kyi mgo lus dang snying yang
NK071(du)001:6285: tshal pa bdun du yak+sha khro bos dum bur gtub
NK071(du)001:6286: par 'gyur ro // de bas na rnal 'byor sngags
NK071(du)001:6287: 'chang bdag gis las ji ltar bcol ba bzhin du
NK071(du)001:6289: gal te las de mngon du ma byas na rang rang gis mna' bor zhing khas blangs pa'i /
NK071(du)001:6290: dmod pa bzhin rul myags 'tshig nas thur du bltas te rdo rje'i dmyal bar 'gro bar gyur ro //
NK071(du)001:6292: rnal 'byor pa dam la gnas par gyur pa'i las
NK071(du)001:6293: gang 'dod rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba dang
NK071(du)001:6294: rnal 'byor pa de'i 'khor rnams kyang rang gi bu
NK071(du)001:6295: gcig pu la mas dungs pa bzhin du skyongs shig
NK071(du)001:6296: dang de'i mthus khyed cag phra men ma rnams kyang
NK071(du)001:6297: dngos grub rnam pa gnyis thob par gyur pas rnal
NK071(du)001:6298: 'byor pas ji ltar bcol ba'i las rnams mngon sum
NK071(du)001:6299: du grub par byos shig ces bka' basgo'o //
NK071(du)001:6300: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang tshogs kyi sgrub pa'i dus
NK071(du)001:6301: su 'phrin las bzhi'i bya thabs kyi gtso bo ni
NK071(du)001:6302: bro gar glu tshigs 'di yin no //
NK071(du)001:6303: de yang khrag 'thung chen po badz+ra he ru ka
NK071(du)001:6304: la sogs pa'i rigs lnga he ru ka yab yum
NK071(du)001:6305: gyi rkang pa'i bro lag pa'i gar zhal gyi glu
NK071(du)001:6306: tshig gi nga ro chen pos ni zhi sogs las
NK071(du)001:6307: thams cad dang mchog mthun gyi dngos grub thams cad
NK071(du)001:6308: ci dang ci thob par 'dod pa ltar las thams
NK071(du)001:6309: cad dang dngos grub thams cad 'grub par byed pa
NK071(du)001:6310: yin no // goo r+ai'i sgra las mdzod ldan chen
NK071(du)001:6311: mo la sogs pa'i khong nas tsoo r+ai ma pra
NK071(du)001:6312: mo ha pe ta li rnams kyi bro gar glu
NK071(du)001:6314: 'gro ba dbang du 'du bar 'dod na dbang 'du
NK071(du)001:6315: bar byed cing tshe bsod sogs 'phel bar 'dod na
NK071(du)001:6317: puk+ka s+ai'i sgra las spos mo chen mo la sogs
NK071(du)001:6318: pa'i khong nas g+has sma r+ai sha ni tsan+da li
NK071(du)001:6319: rnams kyi bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni mi
NK071(du)001:6320: mthun pa'i phyogs rnams lhan ner zhi bar 'dod na
NK071(du)001:6321: zhi zhing lhan ner byed la drag pos dran pa
NK071(du)001:6322: nyams te sems rmug cing mi gsal bar 'dod na
NK071(du)001:6324: seng gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i mche ba can bzhi'i bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni /
NK071(du)001:6325: gdug pa thams cad kun gyi srog lus la za
NK071(du)001:6326: bar byed cing rdul phran gyi cha tsam yang med
NK071(du)001:6328: g+h+ri d+h+ra'i sgra las bzhad gdong chen mo la sogs
NK071(du)001:6329: pa'i gshog pa can bzhi'i bro gar glu tshig chen
NK071(du)001:6330: mos ni / gdug pa can thams cad kyi mthu
NK071(du)001:6331: rtsal ma lus pa'am rang gnas las 'byin pa ste
NK071(du)001:6333: de dag kun la yod pa'i phun sum tshogs pa rnams rab tu nyams par byed do //
NK071(du)001:6334: gzhan yang slas dang byi mo bran mo ste dbang
NK071(du)001:6335: phyug ma'i tshogs kyi bro gar glu tshig chen mos
NK071(du)001:6336: ni / dgra la rbad cing mngags gzhug gi las la gtang bar bya ba ste /
NK071(du)001:6337: 'gal byed thams cad rlag par byed pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6338: mthun pa'i phyogs rnams grub pa pho nya'i las thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:6339: zhi ba'i gnas shing ljon pa can dang ni lcug phran gyi tshal ni rgyas pa'i dang /
NK071(du)001:6340: dbang gi gnas sdong gcig dang ni mes reg drung
NK071(du)001:6341: ste nag tshal 'tshig pa'i gnas su drag po'i las
NK071(du)001:6342: shis pa'o // zhi ba'i gzungs ma shing ljon pa
NK071(du)001:6343: lta bu dang chos mtshungs pa dung can ma sogs
NK071(du)001:6344: rigs bzhi gzung ma rnams la'ang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK071(du)001:6345: stangs kyi sems zhes bya ba ni /
NK071(du)001:6346: mthun pa'i grogs byed pas rkyen gyi sems las so sor kun nas slong ba'i sems pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6347: de'ang zhi ba la zhi zhing dang bas rgyas pa
NK071(du)001:6348: la dga' zhing spro bas dbang la chags shing zhen
NK071(du)001:6349: pas dang drag po la zhe sdang khros pas sems
NK071(du)001:6350: dang ldan pas k+aa li thabs te phrin las rnam
NK071(du)001:6351: pa bzhi'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa rab tu bsgrub
NK071(du)001:6352: par bya'o // de skad ces brjod pas gdul bya
NK071(du)001:6353: rang bzhin gyi de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de sems
NK071(du)001:6354: can rnams la 'dul byed rtogs pa mngon du gyur
NK071(du)001:6355: pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis 'phrin las rnams
NK071(du)001:6356: bzhis rgyud dag par sbyod par pas 'dul bar gyur
NK071(du)001:6357: par bya'o // to // gsang ba'i snying po de
NK071(du)001:6358: kho na nyid nges pa las 'di ye nas lhun
NK071(du)001:6359: gyis grub pa'i 'a phrin las bzhi mngon du snang
NK071(du)001:6360: bar byed pas byin gyis rlobs pa zhes bya ba'i
NK071(du)001:6363: // zhes le'u 'di zhi khro thun mong phrin las kyi
NK071(du)001:6364: le'u ste dngos po bcu las rol pa phrin las
NK071(du)001:6365: kyi skabs rdzas hmo lug rgyud sogs sgo nas las
NK071(du)001:6366: bya bar bstan bi ma las dam tshig ldan pa'i
NK071(du)001:6367: skyes bu des // rnam bzhi'i las kyi gzhan don bya //
NK071(du)001:6369: le'u bcu dgu par sdom la gnas pa'i dam tshig
NK071(du)001:6370: dang ldan pa'i skyes bu des le'u 'dir zhi sogs
NK071(du)001:6371: rnam pa bzhi'i las kyi gzhan gyi don bya bar
NK071(du)001:6372: bstan no // le'u nyer gcig pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:6376: de nas sogs gnyis pa la gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6377: 'bras chos lnga so sor bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6378: rten dang brten pa'i spyir bstod pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6380: h+aum gtum chen sogs tshigs bcad lnga /
NK071(du)001:6381: gnyis pa rten dang brten pa spyir bstod pa ni /
NK071(du)001:6382: rdo rje brag chen sogs tshigs su bcad pa /
NK071(du)001:6385: sa bcad de dang 'brel ba'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:6386: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:6387: de nas rang snang gi 'khor la bstod pa'i phyir /
NK071(du)001:6388: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po khrag 'thung nga
NK071(du)001:6389: rgyal 'dul ba'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis zhal shin
NK071(du)001:6390: tu rngams mdangs kyis rang snang gi 'khor lo dgyes
NK071(du)001:6391: pa'i glu drug po 'di blangs so //
NK071(du)001:6392: h'u ni mgo 'dren khro ba'i snang glu ste /
NK071(du)001:6393: sku lnga ye shes lngar mtshon pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6394: de la dpal chen po'i sku ni /
NK071(du)001:6395: dreg pa can rnams 'dul bas gtum chen te dus
NK071(du)001:6396: kyi mtha'i me chen ltar 'bar ba'i sku la ye
NK071(du)001:6397: shes kyi 'od zer nyi ma 'bum dus gcig la
NK071(du)001:6398: shar bar ltar gyi gzi brjid chen pos thams cad
NK071(du)001:6400: mi sdug pa'i khro gnyer rnam par 'gyur ba ni /
NK071(du)001:6401: glog stong dus gcig la 'gyu ba bzhin 'khyug pas bsdig par mdzad pa /
NK071(du)001:6402: gdug pa can tshar gcod pa'i mche ba ni tik+sh+na'i
NK071(du)001:6403: sgra las zangs yag ste rnon pos ma rung pa
NK071(du)001:6404: za bar byed pa'i 'jig byed chen po'o //
NK071(du)001:6405: hohzhesa dgyes pa'i gad rgyang ngo //
NK071(du)001:6406: 'jigs rung khros shing rngam pa'i gsung gi nga ro
NK071(du)001:6407: ni 'brug stong dus gcig la ldir ba ltar sgra'i
NK071(du)001:6408: gtum chen gyi drag shul ri rab 'bum dus gcig
NK071(du)001:6409: la bsnyil ba'i skad dang mnyam pa a la la
NK071(du)001:6410: dang ha ha dang a la la zhes rdo rje'i
NK071(du)001:6411: gad rgyangs chen po rgod pas sa gsum g.yo ba
NK071(du)001:6412: dbugs kyi shugs las spyug pa'i 'thor byed kyi rlung
NK071(du)001:6413: chen pos gdug pa can rnams g.yeng ba ste /
NK071(du)001:6414: dus mtha'i rlung chen pos gtor ba ltar byed pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6415: hoh ye shes chen pos ma rig pa'i tshogs la
NK071(du)001:6416: ngang ngam shugs kyis khros pa'i khro bo yang dag
NK071(du)001:6417: pa'i shes rab kyis gdul bya'i mun pa sel bar
NK071(du)001:6419: thugs ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyis shes bya'i yul
NK071(du)001:6420: kun dus gcig tu rang gsal ma 'gags par mkhyen
NK071(du)001:6421: cing 'bar ba'i ye shes des gdul bya'i log rtogs
NK071(du)001:6422: kun tu 'joms par mdzad pa de yang ye shes
NK071(du)001:6423: mkhyen gnyis sogs sna tshogs pa'i ye shes rnam pa
NK071(du)001:6424: tha dad du gsal ba kun kyang rang 'byung gi
NK071(du)001:6425: ye shes thig le chen po gcig gi ngo bor
NK071(du)001:6426: dbyer med pa'o // hohh+aum gdug pa can 'dul ba
NK071(du)001:6427: khro bo'i mdzad pas gdul bya la dbang sgyur ba'i
NK071(du)001:6428: dbyer med pa'o // rgyal po ste / yon tan
NK071(du)001:6429: 'byung ba'i sprin chen po las 'phros pa'i 'dul byed
NK071(du)001:6430: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi thugs rjes char chen po
NK071(du)001:6431: 'bebs pas gang la gang 'dul gyi sprul pa'i dkyil
NK071(du)001:6432: 'khor zad pa med pa 'god yid bzhin du 'byung
NK071(du)001:6433: ba rin po che'i gter dang 'dra bas don mdzad
NK071(du)001:6434: pa sna tshogs su snang ba phyag rgya chen po'i
NK071(du)001:6435: skur khros pa thams cad kyang ye shes chen po'i
NK071(du)001:6436: khro bor ro gcig pa'i thig le chen por gnas
NK071(du)001:6437: dbyer med pa'o // rgyal po ste / pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6438: hohh+aum bdud bzhi po kun gyi rang bzhin ma spang
NK071(du)001:6439: bar dbang du byed pa ni bdud chen po ste
NK071(du)001:6440: dbyer med pa'o // rgyal po ste / pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6441: he ru ka'o // de'ang bdud bzhi'i dpung mthar byed
NK071(du)001:6442: kyi bdud de sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa'i
NK071(du)001:6444: bdud dang gshin rje sogs 'jigs pa'i tshogs rnams kyang 'jigs par byed pas /
NK071(du)001:6445: 'jigs byed chen po khrag 'thung gi tshogs rnams kyang
NK071(du)001:6446: ngo bo chos sku spros bral thig le chen por
NK071(du)001:6447: ro gcig pa'o // hohh+aum khrag 'thung lha tshogs kyi
NK071(du)001:6448: sku ni rdo rje brag chen po ltar skye shi
NK071(du)001:6449: dang 'pho 'gyur med pas sra ba po ste che
NK071(du)001:6450: ba'i yon tan kun gyi rten du gyur pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6451: gsung dang yon tan ni rdo rje'i chu bo lta bu ste /
NK071(du)001:6452: gdul bya'i tshogs ma lus pa sdud pas bde ba chen pos rgyud brlan cing tshim par mdzad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6453: thugs ni rdo rje me ste thugs rje'i ye shes
NK071(du)001:6454: kun tu 'bar ba chen pos mtshan ma'i rtogs pa
NK071(du)001:6455: thams cad sreg cing shes bya'i yul thams cad mngon
NK071(du)001:6457: 'phrin las ni rdo rje'i rlung ste gdul bya khyab
NK071(du)001:6458: cing g.yo bas 'dul bar mdzad cing khyad par gdug
NK071(du)001:6459: can rnams chos dbyings su 'thor bar byed pa'i rlung
NK071(du)001:6460: chen po'o // hohgazhana rten gzhal yas khang la sbyar tshul ni 'grel pa sogs las shes par bya'o //
NK071(du)001:6461: de skad ces rang snang gi dkyil 'khor dgyes pa chen pos ched du glu blangs so //
NK071(du)001:6462: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK071(du)001:6463: 'dir rang snang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6465: // zhes le'u 'di khro bo rjes 'jug nyams len gyi le'u dang /
NK071(du)001:6467: gnas su stob pa mchod pa'i skabs khro bo gtum chen gyi mchod pa bstan /
NK071(du)001:6468: bi ma las khros pa'i glu yis bstod par bya /
NK071(du)001:6470: gong du bstan pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de rnams la le'u 'dir /
NK071(du)001:6471: rdo rje khros pa'i glu yis bstod par bya ba bstan par bzhed do //
NK071(du)001:6472: le'u nyer gnyis pa la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:6477: gnyis pa gzhung la gsum ste /
NK071(du)001:6480: rgyud rdzogs nas mdzad pa chos nyid du bzhugs tshul lo //
NK071(du)001:6482: gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba rtogs byar gdams pa /
NK071(du)001:6483: log rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba dag byar gdams pa /
NK071(du)001:6484: gdul bya lam gyi snang ba bgrod byar gdams pa /
NK071(du)001:6485: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba thob byar gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6487: kyee phyogs bcu sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6488: gnyis pa ni gzung 'jin sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6490: sa rnams sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6491: bzhi pa ni ye shes sogs rkang pa gnyis /
NK071(du)001:6492: gnyis pa gtad pa la gsum /
NK071(du)001:6493: lhan gcig pa'i 'khor sdud pa po dang /
NK071(du)001:6494: go cha phye ba'i 'khor phyi rabs kyi gang zag dang /
NK071(du)001:6495: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams la gtad pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6499: gang zag chos mig can dang /
NK071(du)001:6500: nges par lung bstan pa'i sgo nas gtad pa'i 'thad pa dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6502: de bzhin sogs tshigs bcad gcig /
NK071(du)001:6504: de ni sogs rkang pa gsum /
NK071(du)001:6505: gsum pa mdzad pa chos nyid du bzhugs tshul ni /
NK071(du)001:6509: sa bcad de dang ldan pa'i gzhung dngos ni /
NK071(du)001:6510: rgyud don rdzogs par bstan pa /
NK071(du)001:6511: de nas rgyud gdams shing gtad pa ston te /
NK071(du)001:6512: gang gis na ston pa bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal kun tu bzang pos so /
NK071(du)001:6513: gang la na lhan cig pa'i 'khor rgyud yongs su
NK071(du)001:6514: dag pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa nyid dang go phye
NK071(du)001:6515: ba'i 'khor / ye ji bzhin pa'i de bzhin gshegs
NK071(du)001:6516: pa nyid de phyi rabs kyi gang zag chos kyi
NK071(du)001:6518: gang gtad na bstan pa gsang sngags rmad du byung ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po 'adi'o //
NK071(du)001:6519: ji ltar na rgyud 'di nyid 'gro ba'i phan bde'i
NK071(du)001:6520: gzhir mi nub par brtan par bzung ba 'di ched
NK071(du)001:6521: du brjod do // kye kye zhes 'khor gnyis la bos nas /
NK071(du)001:6522: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das kyi
NK071(du)001:6523: chos rnams rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa 'di
NK071(du)001:6524: ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po ste /
NK071(du)001:6525: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du rtogs byar gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6526: phyi bzung 'dzin gyi sems kyi spros pa la zhen
NK071(du)001:6527: pas blo mngon par 'chel zhing goms pa yis rang
NK071(du)001:6528: gi rnam rtog zhags pa dang 'dra bas khams gsum
NK071(du)001:6529: rigs drug gi gnas so sor 'dzin cing sdug bsngal
NK071(du)001:6530: gyis nyams thag par gyur pas na de las grol
NK071(du)001:6531: bar gdams pa'o // de las grol byed dbang po'i
NK071(du)001:6532: rim pas theg pa so so'i sa rnams dang lam
NK071(du)001:6533: gyi khyad par ma 'dres par bkod pa nyan rang
NK071(du)001:6534: byang sems phyi rgyud gsum gyi theg pa yang /
NK071(du)001:6535: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'dir 'gro ba'i lam
NK071(du)001:6536: stegs yin pas na bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam 'di
NK071(du)001:6537: nyid nyams su blangs byar gdams pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6538: de ltar lam mthar phyin pas spangs rtogs kyi ye
NK071(du)001:6539: shes ngo mtshar ba'i yon tan rab 'byams mnga' ba
NK071(du)001:6540: nyid kyis phrin las gsung chos kyi rnam grangs bsam
NK071(du)001:6541: gyis mi khyab par snang ba'ang gdul bya'i don du
NK071(du)001:6542: mi 'gyur ba ni gang cung zad gcig kyang rnam
NK071(du)001:6543: pa thams cad du yongs su ma gsungs te gsung
NK071(du)001:6544: bar mi mdzad pas na de nyid thob byar gdams
NK071(du)001:6545: pa'o // phyogs 'dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK071(du)001:6546: cad kyi gsung gi phyag rgya gsang chen snying po
NK071(du)001:6547: yi ge'i rgyud 'di ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pas
NK071(du)001:6548: gang zhig rang gi tshul bzhin du rtogs nas gzhan
NK071(du)001:6549: la ma nor bar smra bar gang byed pa /
NK071(du)001:6550: de nyid ni kun tu bzang po nga dang tha
NK071(du)001:6551: mi dad pa yin cing phan nus zab mo'i dbang
NK071(du)001:6552: yang rang bzhin gyis rdzogs pa'i phyir rgyud 'di zung
NK071(du)001:6553: la mi nub par zungs shig ces pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6554: phyogs dus kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la
NK071(du)001:6555: dgongs pa gsang ba'i snying po 'di las lhag pa'i
NK071(du)001:6556: don gzhan cung zad kyang mi mnga' bas 'di'i brjod
NK071(du)001:6557: bya ni zab pa'i phyir yod la sgro 'dogs dang
NK071(du)001:6558: med par skur pa 'debs pa sogs mtha'i spros pa
NK071(du)001:6559: thams cad nyer bar zhi ba yi rang bzhin te
NK071(du)001:6560: de brjod byed lam rkyen sdud yi ge'i rgyud gsang
NK071(du)001:6561: ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa zhes
NK071(du)001:6562: bya ba 'di nyid sgro skur thams cad dang bral
NK071(du)001:6563: ba'o // de ltar ston pa'i bdag nyid kyi rang
NK071(du)001:6564: bzhin chos nyid de bzhin nyid nges pa'i dbyings rum
NK071(du)001:6565: nas phyung ba'i rgyud 'di zungs shig ces sdud pa
NK071(du)001:6567: rgyud 'di 'dzin cing ston pa'i gang zag de ni
NK071(du)001:6568: nges par gzhan la ston pa'i rig pa'i skyes bu
NK071(du)001:6569: dang / de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs zhes
NK071(du)001:6570: sangs rgyas su lung bstan te de ltar de bzhin
NK071(du)001:6571: gshegs pa thams cad kyi sras kyi dwangs ma yin
NK071(du)001:6572: te de ni kun tu bzang po'i thugs kyi gsang
NK071(du)001:6573: ba zab mo 'di las skyes pa yin pa'i phyir
NK071(du)001:6574: sa rab ste sa thams cad mchog rig 'dzin pa'o
NK071(du)001:6575: dang / // rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa la gnas
NK071(du)001:6576: pa yin te snod ldan rnams la gtad cig ces
NK071(du)001:6577: dang / // gtad pa'o // rgyud don de skad
NK071(du)001:6578: ces brjod pas ston 'khor gyi de bzhin gshegs pa
NK071(du)001:6579: thams cad dgongs pa dbyer med par gyur cig /
NK071(du)001:6580: rgyud kyi mdzad pa rdzogs pas dgyes nas dus tha
NK071(du)001:6581: dad du mi dmigs pa chos nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK071(du)001:6582: kyi dbyings su rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams snang
NK071(du)001:6583: zhing bkod pa thams cad ston pa nyid kyi sku
NK071(du)001:6584: gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor lhun
NK071(du)001:6585: gyis grub pa stug po bkod pa'i rgyan nyid du
NK071(du)001:6587: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i
NK071(du)001:6588: rgyud 'di la le'u nyer gnyis su yod pa las
NK071(du)001:6589: 'di tha ma rgyud rdzogs shing ston 'khor dgongs pa
NK071(du)001:6590: dbyer med du gyur pa la mnyes pa dang gdams
NK071(du)001:6591: shing gtad pa'i sgo nas rgyud yongs su bzung ba'i
NK071(du)001:6592: le'u ste nyi shu gnyis pa'o //
NK071(du)001:6593: zhes le'u 'dis gdams shing gtad pa ston te bstan
NK071(du)001:6594: pa'i snying po rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po mtshon
NK071(du)001:6595: byed lam rkyen yi ge'i rgyud dang bcas pa 'di
NK071(du)001:6596: nyid mi nyams pa'i ched du 'khor rnams la gdams
NK071(du)001:6597: shing gtad pa ston pa yin no //
NK071(du)001:6599: // gsum pa 'jug gi don rgyud rdzogs pa'i bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK071(du)001:6601: de yang brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras gsum dbyer med
NK071(du)001:6602: pa'i rang bzhin lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK071(du)001:6603: don ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)001:6604: du sangs rgyas par ston pas na gzhan las khyad
NK071(du)001:6606: de brjod byed yi ge'i rgyud 'di la'ang 'phags pa zhes btags so //
NK071(du)001:6607: rtog pa ni dngos grub rnams gnyis sgrub pa'i thabs kyi rgyud thams cad la grags shing /
NK071(du)001:6608: de dag thams cad la rgyud 'di mchog tu gyur
NK071(du)001:6609: pas na rgyal po 'o de lta bu'i rgyud kyi
NK071(du)001:6610: rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul dra ba
NK071(du)001:6611: zhes bya ba de'i le'u'i grangs ni stong phrag brgya
NK071(du)001:6612: pa ste 'bum phrag gcig bzhugs pa las phyungs pa
NK071(du)001:6613: rtsa ba'i rgyud le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi bdag
NK071(du)001:6614: nyid du bstan pa 'di ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK071(du)001:6615: theg pa dang / 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi rgyud
NK071(du)001:6616: thams cad kyi 'byung khungs sam 'phro gzhir gyur pas
NK071(du)001:6617: lung gi spyi 'grel phyogs bcu dang /
NK071(du)001:6618: dus gzhir bsdus pa'i de bzhin gshegs thams cad kyi
NK071(du)001:6619: thugs kyi gsang ba las kyang che gsang ba dpal
NK071(du)001:6620: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa
NK071(du)001:6621: zhes bya ba'i rgyud 'di las bstan pa dang theg
NK071(du)001:6622: pa thams cad ma lus par 'phros te chos kyi
NK071(du)001:6623: 'khor lo bsam gyi mi khyab pa bskor ba de
NK071(du)001:6624: dag gang nas zhugs kyang mthar thug bgrod pa gcig
NK071(du)001:6625: pas kun gyi 'bras bu bla na med pa'i mchog
NK071(du)001:6626: rtsa ba'i rgyud chen po rdzogs so //
NK071(du)001:6627: zhes pa ni gtan la phab zin pa'i dang i
NK071(du)001:6628: ti zhes pa ni shin tu zab pa'i don no
NK071(du)001:6629: // mthar rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma la
NK071(du)001:6630: mi tra'i ste dri med bshes gnyen gyi zhal snga
NK071(du)001:6631: // nas dang / bod kyi lo tsa ba gnyags
NK071(du)001:6632: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra ste ye shes gzhon nu
NK071(du)001:6633: // nas dang / dang / rma +aa tsar+ya ste
NK071(du)001:6634: slob dpon rin chen mchog gis bsgyur cing gtan la
NK071(du)001:6635: // nas dang / dang / phab pa'o // zhes
NK071(du)001:6636: lo pan de rnams kyi legs par bsgyur zhing 'chad
NK071(du)001:6637: nyan gyis gtan la phab nas dar rgyas su mdzad
NK071(du)001:6638: // nas dang / dang / phab pa'o // do
NK071(du)001:6639: // zab dang rgya cher ston pa'i chos tshul rnam
NK071(du)001:6640: grangs mtha' klas las brtsam ste //
NK071(du)001:6641: gdul bya'i blo dang mtshams par rtog pa'i 'dul byed theg pa ji snyed pa //
NK071(du)001:6642: kun gyi dpal gyur bgrod pa gcig pu zab lam rdo rje theg pa'i chos //
NK071(du)001:6643: rgyud sde rgya mtsho spyi dang khyad par nang rgyud sde gsum mchis so 'tshal //
NK071(du)001:6644: lus pa med pa'i gsang ba chen po rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i bcud //
NK071(du)001:6645: snying po'i snying po dpal ldan rdor sems sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal //
NK071(du)001:6646: kun rtog las 'das gdod ma'i gnas lugs de kho na nyid nges pa'i don //
NK071(du)001:6647: lam mchog yongs rdzogs legs bshad nyung ngu rnam dag tshig gis gsal bar byas //
NK071(du)001:6648: de lta'i rnam dpyod 'dab ma cung zad grol 'di yang //
NK071(du)001:6649: gter chen chos rje'i smin grol bdud rtsis gsos btab cing //
NK071(du)001:6650: kun mkhyen bla mas nyin byed shar bas mngon dgar byas /
NK071(du)001:6651: d+harma sh+r+ai'i legs bshad 'od 'bum brdal bas kyang //
NK071(du)001:6652: 'di ltar bgyis la 'gal khrul dri mas nongs pa gang //
NK071(du)001:6653: ye shes spyan ldan lha dang srung ma'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK071(du)001:6654: chos kyi spyan ldan mkhas dang grub pa'i spyan sngar bshags //
NK071(du)001:6655: sgrib med rgyal ba'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes par shog /
NK071(du)001:6656: legs byas pad+ma'i dga' tshal la brten nas //
NK071(du)001:6657: theg chen bung ba'i sgra dbyangs snyan sgrogs shing //
NK071(du)001:6658: zab gsang sbrang rtsi'i ro yi lus can rnams //
NK071(du)001:6659: zag med bde bas rtag par 'tsho gyur cig /
NK071(du)001:6660: ces rgyud kyi rgyal po dpal gsang ba snying po'i
NK071(du)001:6661: 'bru re gnyer gyi sgo nas mchan 'grel cung zad
NK071(du)001:6662: bgyis pa 'di / gter chen chos kyi rgyal po mchog gyur bde chen gling pa dang /
NK071(du)001:6663: kun gzigs bla ma 'jam pa'i rdo rje mkhyen brtse'i
NK071(du)001:6664: dbang po rnams gnyis kyi zhal snga nas smin grol
NK071(du)001:6665: gyi gdams pa'i bka' drin tshad med pa thob cing
NK071(du)001:6666: gsung gi gsang bas rjes su gnang ba dang gzhan
NK071(du)001:6667: yang bshes gnyen dam pa mang po'i thugs rjes nye
NK071(du)001:6668: bar bskyang ba'i mthu las theg pa mchog la mos
NK071(du)001:6669: pa'i blo can btsun gzugs karma rin chen rnam rgyal
NK071(du)001:6670: gyis rdzong sar bkra shis lha rtse'i chos grwa nas
NK071(du)001:6671: dbu brtsams / shar phyogs kahthoga rdo rje gdan gyi
NK071(du)001:6672: gnas su grub par bris pa don dang ldan par
NK071(du)001:6674: snga 'gyur rnying ma'i bshad sgrub gnyis kyi rtsa ba sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po'i dbang /
NK071(du)001:6675: rgyud bshad rdzogs rim nyams len bcas kun bzang rdo
NK071(du)001:6676: rje sems dpa' nas da lta'i bar ring brgyud ma
NK071(du)001:6677: chad pa bzhugs pa 'jam mgon mkhyen kong gnyis kyis
NK071(du)001:6678: zhe chen dpon sprul 'gyur med mthu stobs rnam rgyal
NK071(du)001:6679: las gsan te bsnyen sgrub nyams bzhes gnang bas kun
NK071(du)001:6680: gzigs mkhyen brtse'i dbang po la zur chen yab sras
NK071(du)001:6681: kyi ye shes sku'i rjes su bzung ba'i nye brgyud
NK071(du)001:6682: bcas chu bo gcig 'dres gter chen mchog gling dang
NK071(du)001:6683: dpal yul rgya sprul mdo sngags bstan 'dzin sogs kyis
NK071(du)001:6684: gsan pa'i rgyun bzhugs pa rnams thugs sras tsha ba
NK071(du)001:6685: lo ts+aa ba rin chen rnam rgyal zhes pas 'jam
NK071(du)001:6686: mgon rnam pa gsum ka las dbang lung gi rgyun
NK071(du)001:6687: gsan nas mchan 'grel 'di mdzad pas brgyud pa'i chu
NK071(du)001:6688: bo gcig 'dres su song ba'i gnad kyis rnying sngags
NK071(du)001:6689: rgan po dil mgo mkhyen sprul pas dpe lung gi
NK071(du)001:6690: rgyun 'phel phyir spar 'grem zhus pa'i rnying bstan gces
NK071(du)001:6691: spras su 'dzin pa rnams la 'chad nyan nyams bzhes
NK071(du)001:6692: ma chad tsam gnang bar gsol 'debs dang dge bas
NK071(du)001:6693: 'gro kun rdo rje sems dpa'i go 'phang thob par
